Known for his infallible eye, refined simplicity, and elegance, Piguet''s influence on women''s fashions lives on through the designers he helped train and through the iconic perfumes launched under the Robert Piguet brand.', 'France', 'https://img.fragrancex.com/images/l/29/us/0/homeimage_mobile.jpg?v=VVMM9DGZ0GH7QG2', NULL),
('MiN NEW YORK', 'MiN NEW YORK is a luxury fragrance house founded in 1999 by Chad Murawczyk. It is a New York City founded fragrance label designed to represent a lifestyle wrapped in scent. The fragrances are produced in Grasse, France, and skillfully designed with the purpose of passing down authenticity, illuminating the path to a well-lived life. MiN NEW YORK''s Scent Stories are both timeless and refined, allowing you to heighten your best self without compromising authenticity.', 'United States', 'https://img.fragrancex.com/images/l/29/us/0/homeimage_mobile.jpg?v=VVMM9DGZ0GH7QG2', 'https://www.min.com/'),
('Dusita', 'Parfums Dusita is a niche Parisian perfume house that creates unique fragrances using the finest, rare natural materials for their own fragrant accords. They are an eclectic mix of French traditional perfumery and oriental philosophy. Dusita is named for a heavenly realm in Oriental belief where the spirit finds pure delight and contentment. The perfumes are inspired by the poetry of Montri Umavijani.', 'France', 'https://img.fragrancex.com/images/l/29/us/0/homeimage_mobile.jpg?v=VVMM9DGZ0GH7QG2', NULL),
('The Merchant of Venice', 'The Merchant of Venice is a luxury niche perfume house launched in 2013 by the Vidal family, whose fragrance legacy stretches back over a century. Rooted in Venice''s rich history as a perfumery and trade crossroads, the brand weaves the spirit of the “Mude”—the city’s ancient maritime routes spanning Europe, Asia, and Africa, into its identity. The line is inspired by the ancient Art of Perfumery originated in Venice and from its centuries old trade with the Orient.', 'Italy', 'https://img.fragrancex.com/images/l/29/us/0/homeimage_mobile.jpg?v=VVMM9DGZ0GH7QG2', NULL),
('Olibere', 'Olibere Parfums is a French perfume brand which gets its inspiration from the aesthetics of films. Each perfume has its own short film. Marjorie Olibere, the inspired creator, feeds on moments lived or observed, moments of life to tell olfactory and visual stories that touch it while being universal. These perfumed tales revisit the themes that have punctuated his life: love, travel and chance.', 'France', 'https://img.fragrancex.com/images/l/29/us/0/homeimage_mobile.jpg?v=VVMM9DGZ0GH7QG2', NULL),
('Laboratorio Olfattivo', 'Laboratorio Olfattivo is an Italian niche perfumery based in Rome. It is a project born in 2009 from Daniela Caon and Roberto Drago''s love for niche perfumes. Laboratorio Olfattivo is a magical space where the inspirations, ideas, visions, and projects of the most eclectic perfumers on the scene come together. The reason why a new perfume is created is never a market necessity, but the need to tell a story.', 'Italy', 'https://img.fragrancex.com/images/l/29/us/0/homeimage_mobile.jpg?v=VVMM9DGZ0GH7QG2', 'https://www.laboratorioolfattivo.com/'),
('Paradis Des Sens', 'Paradis des Sens is a French brand founded in 2020 by Arcadie de Niche. It was created with a profound appreciation of your individuality & personal style, cased in simple clear bottles, to be your reflection glass & encourage you to see yourself subtly interpreted in our bespoke scents. Paradis Des Sens is a modern and distinctive brand in the world of perfumes has originated in France.', 'France', 'https://img.fragrancex.com/images/l/29/us/0/homeimage_mobile.jpg?v=VVMM9DGZ0GH7QG2', 'https://paradisdessens.com/'),
('The Woods Collection By Natural', 'The Woods Collection is a fragrance brand inspired by forests, sunlight, and moonlight, managed by UAE Company Extravaganza and produced in France. Their fragrances are designed for both men and women, evoking the aromas of foliage and grass, with elegant and solemn scents.', 'France', 'https://img.fragrancex.com/images/l/29/us/0/homeimage_mobile.jpg?v=VVMM9DGZ0GH7QG2', NULL),
('D.S. & Durga', 'D.S. & Durga, founded in 2009 by husband-and-wife team David Seth Moltz (D.S.) and Kavi Ahuja Moltz (Durga), is a Brooklyn-based perfume house. D.S. is a self-taught perfumer and musician, while Durga is an architect and visual designer. They create original scents based on feelings and places, with a focus on artistry and unique narratives. Their motto is ''Perfume is Armchair Travel''.', 'Usa', 'https://img.fragrancex.com/images/l/29/us/0/homeimage_mobile.jpg?v=VVMM9DGZ0GH7QG2', 'https://www.dsanddurga.com/'),
('PH', 'pH fragrances, founded in 2014 by Camille Le Feuvre, is a niche fragrance brand from France that offers customized fragrances in personal care, home care, and fine fragrances. The brand emphasizes sustainability and uses natural ingredients, with a commitment to health and the planet. Their perfumes are created by master perfumers from Givaudan.', 'France', 'https://img.fragrancex.com/images/l/29/us/0/homeimage_mobile.jpg?v=VVMM9DGZ0GH7QG2', 'https://www.phfragrances.com'),
('Lengling', 'Lengling is a Munich-based perfume house founded in 2014 by Ursula and Christian Lengling. They specialize in unisex fragrances inspired by personal memories and emotions. Each fragrance is based on two contrasting accords, LENG and LING, and created with high-quality, vegan ingredients. The brand emphasizes sustainability and craftsmanship.', 'Germany', 'https://img.fragrancex.com/images/l/29/us/0/homeimage_mobile.jpg?v=VVMM9DGZ0GH7QG2', 'https://lengling.com/'),
('Ermanno Scervino', 'Ermanno Scervino launched his own brand in 1999 after working with Italian fashion industry leaders. His brand, synonymous with Italian quality and international style, features innovative luxury and unexpected pairings of materials. Based in Florence, the brand manages its collections independently, blending tailoring techniques with sportswear influences.', 'Italy', 'https://img.fragrancex.com/images/l/29/us/0/homeimage_mobile.jpg?v=VVMM9DGZ0GH7QG2', 'https://www.ermannoscervino.com/'),
('Ella K', 'Ella K is an artistic perfumery brand created by master perfumer Sonia Constant. Inspired by pioneering female explorers, the brand''s fragrances invite exploration and aim to capture unique and precious moments from around the world. Ella K emphasizes a personal and unexpected vision of luxury.', 'France', 'https://img.fragrancex.com/images/l/29/us/0/homeimage_mobile.jpg?v=VVMM9DGZ0GH7QG2', 'https://www.ella-k.com/en/'),
('Maison TahitÃ©', 'Maison Tahité – Officine Creative Profumi, founded in 2020, is an Italian fragrance workshop dedicated to exploring iconic perfumery ingredients in fresh, contemporary ways. The brand focuses on gourmand favorites like vanilla and cacao, reinterpreting them with a primal yet modern perspective. Maison Tahité emphasizes sustainable luxury, using recycled materials for its packaging.', 'Italy', 'https://img.fragrancex.com/images/l/29/us/0/homeimage_mobile.jpg?v=VVMM9DGZ0GH7QG2', 'https://www.maisontahite.com/'),
('Lucien Ferrero Maitre Parfumeur', 'Lucien Ferrero Maître Parfumeur is a brand launched by master perfumer Lucien Ferrero, drawing from his experience in Belle Parfumerie.  The brand is inspired by Provence and natural scents, with fragrances conceived as hymns to love and renewal.', 'France', 'https://img.fragrancex.com/images/l/29/us/0/homeimage_mobile.jpg?v=VVMM9DGZ0GH7QG2', 'https://www.lucienferreroparfums.com'),
('RPL', 'RPL Parfums, founded in 2012 by Rupert Peter Landendinger, is a Berlin-based perfume house creating bespoke fragrances. The brand combines Landendinger''s passion for fashion, design, and world travel, aiming to create luxurious, modern, and accessible scents. RPL fragrances are produced in France in collaboration with talented olfactory experts.', 'Germany', 'https://img.fragrancex.com/images/l/29/us/0/homeimage_mobile.jpg?v=VVMM9DGZ0GH7QG2', 'https://www.rplmaison.com/'),
('Zenology', 'Zenology, founded in 2009 by Jeroen Oude Sogtoen, is a lifestyle company committed to creating sensible, luxurious, quality beauty and lifestyle products with care for the environment. Originating in the hotel industry, Zenology aims to elevate the staying experience through quality and scent. The brand balances nature and science, using renewable resources and recyclable packaging.', 'Netherlands', 'https://img.fragrancex.com/images/l/29/us/0/homeimage_mobile.jpg?v=VVMM9DGZ0GH7QG2', 'https://www.zenology.com'),
('Ghawali', 'Ghawali is an UAE fragrance and body care products brand. Rooted in heritage and originating from the early development of perfumes in the region, Ghalia was a word used to describe the precious and expensive scents that the traveling merchants brought to the region, offering the Royal families their own exclusive scents, or Ghawalis as they came to be known. We have developed our luxurious collections specifically for the layering ritual, allowing the heady scents to envelope your skin at every touch point. From our Purifying Shower Gel to the final spray of our long lasting Parfum, your skin and senses will be treated to layer upon layer of beautiful fragrances and formulas. - a note from the brand.', 'United Arab Emirates', 'https://img.fragrancex.com/images/l/29/us/0/homeimage_mobile.jpg?v=VVMM9DGZ0GH7QG2', 'https://ghawali.com');


