(120, 'Paco Rabanne Ultraviolet For Men', 'Paco Rabanne Ultraviolet For Men an oriental fragrance. The scent is soft, unique and elegance with a unique bottle. You will enjoy wearing it today and every day.', 100, 1904400.0, 1904400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_paco_rabanne_perfumes_ultraviolet_for_men_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(87, 'Lanvin Eclat D''arpege Pour Homme', 'Ãƒâ€°clat dÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ArpÃƒÂ¨ge Pour Homme by Lanvin has a masculine essence. The top notes are Bergamot, Lime, and Mandarin. The heart notes are Jasmine, Rosemary, and Violet leaves. The base notes are Sandalwood, Cedar, and Musk. The composition clearly represents a blend of sophistication, tradition, and style.', 100, 2028600.0, 2028600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_lanvin_perfumes_eclat_d_arpege_pour_homme_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(13, 'Juicy Couture Glistening Amber', 'Glistening Amber is an oriental floral feminine parfume was released in 2018. This fragrance adds a sensation of alluringness to your attitude. The fragrance opens at the top with intense floral notes from Raspberry and Frangipani. The composition then moves to the core with a sensational mix of Vanilla, Orris, and Incense. At the base, the scent crowns with sweet and balmy fragrance from Cashmeran, Amber and Musk to bring you a permanent base.', 100, 2035500.0, 2035500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/1/719346645447_juicy_couture_glistening_amber_100_ml_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(80, 'Jennifer Lopez Still', 'STILL Eau de Parfum by Jennifer Lopez is a feminine and sensual aroma whose opening is luminous and gentle, and the reason is top notes of the perfume. The top notes of the perfume contain White Pepper, Mandarin, Earl Grey Tea, and Sake note. The heart notes contain Freesia, Rose, Jasmine, Orange Blossom, and Lily of the Valley. The base notes contain Sandalwood, Musk, Amber, Orris, and Pepper, which give it a sensual, woody, and Musky touch.', 100, 834900.0, 834900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_jennifer_lopez_perfumes_still_for_women_eau_de_patfum-c.jpg'),
(147, 'Braccialini Pour Femme', 'Braccialini Pour Femme an oriental fragrance for women. The scent is strong, unique, nice and long-lasting and is developed for an ambitious chic woman who relishes fashion and style. The fragrance opens with fresh green notes of bergamot blended with bright tangerine and lush red berries. The middle notes include honey aromas mixed with white flowers and juicy peach. The dry-down is powdery thanks to Florentine iris. Praline and patchouli give a warm woody trail. The yellow bottle is modern corresponding to the woman it is designed for; trendsetting and striving.', 50, 1938900.0, 1938900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_braccialini_perfumes_poue_femme_for_women_eau_de_perfum_8007033040029.jpg'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Vert Boheme', 'It is a free-spirited interpretation of a green scent, sparkling like a jewel in the sun. Sicilian mandarin and magnolia reflect the bohemian femininity, enhanced by gustavia wood, known as "The Tree of Heaven," with flowers that last only one day. Additional notes such as galbanum, violet leaf, and honeysuckle are also placed.', 50, 7617600.0, 7617600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066060493-tom-ford-tom-ford-vert-boheme-_u_-edp-50-ml-1.jpg'),
(71, 'Hermes L''Ombre Des Merveilles', 'This oriental woody fragrance for women represents the key that opens the door to wonders. Its amazing composition of black tea and incense, mixed with tonka bean provides you a scent with the magical power to see the world from a new angle.', 100, 1035000.0, 1035000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346131797080-hermes-her-r-ombre-des-merveilles-edp-100ml-1.jpg'),
(49, 'Lalique L''Insoumis', 'Lalique L''Insoumis is a woody aromatic fragrance for men. A rich and masculine scent, this fragrance spells energy. Made for a charming, sophisticated, original modern man. Lalique L''Insoumis celebrates the adventurous, audacious, cosmopolitan man whose limit is nonexistent. The composition of the fragrance is exquisite as the top notch ingredients blend together marvelously. The opening notes are fresh and fruity. The combination of Bergamot and Basil give a picnic-like feel. Along with Rum, the mood is uplifted and shiny. At the heart, Lavender gives a distinct personality to the scent as it blends with Clary Sage and Black Peppercorn. The sandalwood base sends you to the core of a waterfall rejuvenating you with the scents of Haiti Vetiver, Patchouli, Clearwood and dewy moss.', 100, 1669800.0, 1669800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_lalique_perfumes_l_insoumis_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(29, 'Lorenzo Villoresi Firenze Teint De Neige Hair Mist', 'This shiny romantic floral hair mist gives your days a luxurious glowing fragrance.
The main ingredient in this distinctive fragrance is Jasmine which is considered to be the symbol of softness and sensual aromatic delicacy.
The scents of flowers powder and tonka beans spread around your hair, enveloping it in an aura of unique charm
If you want to attend one of the special occasions in your life then this hair mist is the perfect choice to make you look fantastic.', 50, 2049300.0, 2049300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8028544103515-lorenzo-villoresi-lorenzo-villoresi-firenze-teint-de-neige-_u_-hair-mist-50-ml.jpg'),
(45, 'Coach Set For Women ', 'Coach Set for Women is a three-piece gift set that contains a 100ml Eau De Perfum, a 7.5ml Eau De Perfum, and a 100ml body lotion. This gift set is designed to convey the spontaneous energy and cool vibe of New York City. The two Coach perfumes are fruity-floral fragrances for women. They open with top notes of pink pepper, pear, and raspberry leaf, and then reveals a luxurious heart of Turkish rose. The base notes are a blend of suede musk and rich sandalwood, to give the perfume an undeniable allure. This gift set is a perfect companion for keeping you fresh all day and night.', 100, 2311500.0, 2311500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3386460099820_coach_coach_edp_100_ml_coach_edp_7.5_ml_body_lotion_100_ml_1.jpg'),
(31, 'Dkhoun Red Tea EDP', 'A fragrance with warm scents of tea and musk that will fill your heart with joy.
The delicate notes of iris and dried fruits express your elegance and provide you with a distinctive look.
Discover your beauty with this attractive and lively perfume that will stay with you throughout the day.
The fragrance is designed with precision to suit both men and women on their different occasions.', 70, 2208000.0, 2208000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/1/310079-dkhoun-_-_.png'),
(337, 'Clive Christian Clive Original C 1872', 'This citrus fragrance leaves a mysterious and attractive Masculine scent with a refreshing smell of Jasmine and Neroli that adds vitality and strength feeling.', 50, 11667900.0, 11667900.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(50, 'Laurent Mazzone Ambre Boheme EDP', 'The bustling twentieth mentality has added luxury and feeling of freedom and hope to the innovation of The Majestic Oud fragrance.
It expresses the sensual nights.
It is enriched with a splendid blend of unique scents of natural ingredients.
Bergamot reveals a splendid and fresh scent, blended in Lemon at the top. While the floral and fruity scent of Apple and Watermelon at the top melts in the other notes in an enticing way to give the fragrance a wonderful start.
The fragrance reveals the main ingredients of Amber, Musk and Oud hat make the fragrance scent strong, long-lasting and precious.', 100, 3981300.0, 3981300.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(348, 'Goutal Paris Ambre FÃ©tiche EDP', 'A round trip to the east to enjoy a beautiful tour of the markets of the east
A new story told by the sparkling and shining crystal fragrance
The highly acclaimed scent of classic leather would make the day a beautiful memory in your heart
The fragrance blends labdanum and vanilla aromas to create a wonderful scent that highlights your presence & softness', 50, 3926100.0, 3926100.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(18, 'Penhaligon''s Terrible Teddy', 'A great perfume understands the emotive power of scent. It can unlock memories and open doors. It can stop us in our tracks, lost somewhere for a moment in time. Recollections triggered by a dusting or iris, a whisper of clove, a burst of juicy nectarine, a trail of smoky incense, a creamy lick of vanilla. This fragrance provides you with a perfect attractive scent that lasts for a long time.', 75, 8597400.0, 8597400.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(36, 'Narciso Rodriguez Eau de Rouge', 'Eau de Rouge is a seductive perfume with a heart of musk heart and warm bouquet of Bulgarian rose and iris mixed in with an amber-woody base that includes vetiver as well as cedar wood.', 50, 2352900.0, 2352900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_narciso_rodriguez_perfumes_narciso_eau_rouge_for_women_eau_de_parfum.jpg'),
(20, 'Givenchy Dahlia Noir L''Eau', 'When the fragrance arm of French fashion designer Givenchy unveiled Dahlia Noir L''eau in 2011, it gave the world a unique elixir that embodies the irresistible allure of the natural woman. Top notes bestow the blessedness of sacred dawn as cleansing neroli and the fresh dew of green notes bask in the soft daylight of grapefruit and lemon. The thirst-quenching power of rose dripped with divine peony hint at the power of the inner spirit. The foundation holds strong as patchouli grasps the depth of amber wood and unleashes the arousing power of musk.', 90, 3615600.0, 3615600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/i/givenchy_dahlia_noir_leau.jpg'),
(7, 'The Woods Collection Dark Forest EDP', 'Distinctive and exciting aromatic freshness with notes of green meadows and glowing and spicy saffron notes.
The fragrance immerses you in a luxurious oriental scent and increases the splendor of your look on all different occasions.
The warm endnotes of musk and tobacco give you a high feeling of comfort, pleasure, and relaxation after a busy day.
The scent is always the best choice for loud evenings and nights and remains strong and intense for long hours.', 50, 3705300.0, 3705300.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(168, 'Jimmy Choo Rose Gold Edition', 'A chypre fruity fragrance that reflects the woman''s sophisticated and sparkling aspect. With top notes of orchid, heart notes of toffee and base of patchouli, the scent will envelope you with sensuality and refined elegance so you stay chic and attractive.', 60, 2118300.0, 2118300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3386460087599-jimmy-choo-jimmy-choo-rose-gold-edition-_w_-edp-60-ml.jpg'),
(62, 'Memo Paris Lalibela Oud', 'This amazing fragrance will take you on a journey of renewed pleasure. It has a blend of wonderful notes including Orchid, jasmine, coconut and patchouli, mixed with notes of vanilla, tobacco, olibanum, labdanum and agarwood. It has a long-lasting effect that you will not resist.', 75, 14283000.0, 14283000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(45, 'Coach Coach', 'Launched in 2007, Coach from Coach is a perfume for the classy woman. The fragrance starts with fresh and energetic notes of mandarin and guava decorated with tender floral nuances of lily and violet leaves. The flower of Genet is in the center, arranged with jasmine and mimosa with just a hint of honey. The precious base includes woody notes, vanilla, amber, and iris. With this unique, beautiful, and elegant falcon design, you will feel the same. A fresh, energetic, and long-lasting scent that suits any occasion.', 100, 2297700.0, 2297700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3386460079136_coach_coach_coach_edt_90_ml.jpg'),
(8, 'Chopard Aigle Imperial', 'Eau de Parfum with precious natural oud, Arabian jasmine and Mandarin orange that blended with water notes of bergamot and ginger. It is a luxurious perfume for men leaves refreshed and vibrant fragrance.', 100, 10791600.0, 10791600.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(244, 'Creed Asian Green Tea', 'A morning spritz of Asian Green Tea, by Creed, is an invigorating start to the day. This exquisite fragrance boasts a playful bit of citrus grounded in earth tones and calming florals. Citrus characterizes the top notes, which consist of mandarin orange, lemon, bergamot, and neroli. A field of wildflowers grows in the middle notes, with violet, heliotrope, rose and black currant in the forefront. Here, too, is where the perfume gets its name, as green tea ties it all together. Earth tones like sandalwood, musk, and amber make up the base notes.', 100, 9032100.0, 9032100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/5/3508441001442_creed_creed_asian_green_tea_edp_100_ml_1.jpg'),
(237, 'Roja Amber Aoud EDP', 'A rich base with rare and luxurious notes.
The soft notes of sandalwood are blended with musk, oud and cinnamon, delivering an attractive oriental feature to the fragrance.
The heart is infused with delicious notes of fig and roses, which touch your heart with happiness and joy.
Be ready for real happiness on all your romantic nights, which remain immortal.', 100, 22494000.0, 22494000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/5/0/5060270291015-roja-parfums-roja-parfums-amber-aoud-_u_-edp-100-ml-2.png'),
(24, 'Candy Addict Blue Light EDP ', 'Its fragrance radiates everywhere and anytime without stopping, captivating you with its beauty, so you follow its long-lasting fragrance among fruit trees, which flow in with great softness.', 50, 959100.0, 959100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/l/blue_light_bottle.jpg'),
(77, 'Valentino Uomo Noir Absolu', 'Valentino Uomo Noir Absolu is an oriental woody fragrance for men. This scent is a rich, mysterious and sexy journey to the heart of the orient. The opening of the fragrance is spicy with black pepper, delicate and lively with cinnamon. A touch of incense at the heart with a hint of resinoid give a spicy and bold vibe. The base is woody, spicy and creamy with sandalwood. This well-blended scent is pleasant, smooth and seductive. Cause a sensation and get showered with compliments as you wear Valentino Uomo Noir Absolu.', 100, 3650100.0, 3650100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/v/a/valentino_uomo_noir_absolu_edp.jpg'),
(22, 'Nicolai Oud Sublime Elixir De Parfum', 'A unique oriental fragrance for men and women full of precious and rare natural raw materials, the fragrance combines the fragrance of the past and present French parfumes, the fragrance begins with attractive herbal ingredients Artemisia then softens towards the ambrette and strong Atlas Cedar wood with earthy patchouli and ends with the oud and musk to take you on a journey to a world of excellence, luxury and self-confidence.', 35, 13351500.0, 13351500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_nicolai_perfumes_oud_sublime_elixir_de_parfum_for_unisex_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(67, 'Alwaleef Alwaleed Mabthoth', 'Home Fragrance Oil gives your home a sophisticated oriental aroma with a touch of distinctive oud wood. Add a smart scent to your home, and a relaxed feeling.', 100, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/n/e/new_2_6287006901225_1.jpg'),
(90, 'Elizabeth Arden Green Tea Yuzu', 'Elizabeth Arden Green Tea Yuzu is a nice summer fragrance for women. Soft, serene and bright, it encompasses a balanced mixture of light citrus notes and green tea. This luscious fragrance opens with the citrusy notes; lemon and bergamot combined. Green tea tones swim in the sweet scents of Yuzu. The heart is rich with green tea leaves, Yuzu pulp accord, wild thyme, black currant buds and Tunisian Neroli. The dry-down has a hint of musk, a shade of white birch and ambrette seed. Elizabeth Arden Green Tea Yuzu is a delicious scent that is perfect for spring.', 100, 634800.0, 634800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/e/l/elizabeth_arden_green_tea_yuzu_edt_100_ml.jpg'),
(47, 'Van Cleef & Arpels So First', 'It is a soft floral scent that develops with gourmand sweetness. It begins with fresh bergamot and cheerful magnolia. The heart of the perfume features an elegant and intoxicating bouquet of white flowers that include jasmine, freesia, and frangipani. The base consists of sensual sandalwood and sweet vanilla.', 100, 1607700.0, 1607700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3386460078641-vc_a-vc_a-so-first-_l_-edp-100-ml.jpg'),
(223, 'Ojar Ciel D''orage EDP', 'The notes of saffron and warm leather draw your oriental identity, making it clear for everyone.
The fragrance is enriched with a soft creamy touch of patchouli and guaiac wood, adding to the sweetness of the scent.
Feel unique and special in all different occasions to remain as a memory in your mind.
It''s an intense perfume oil for both men and women with a glowing aromatic scent.', 15, 1656000.0, 1656000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(7, 'Xerjoff Oud Stars Alexandria Travel Perfume EDP', 'The Perfume embodies the glamor of fashion and luxury, inspired by the words of distinctive poems and literary books.
Enjoy a tour inside the Horse Club with a spicy and incandescent spray of spices, patchouli, and basil.
The scents of vetiver and green lands leave you feeling refreshed and revitalized and rejuvenate your soul.
Always start your day with different moments of happiness and activity with a breeze of sage and algae filling your heart with happiness and joy.', 50, 5996100.0, 5996100.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Emporio Armani In Love With You ', 'A gift set for women containing a basic perfume of 100 ml and a small bottle of the same perfume of 15 ml with an aromatic hand cream.
The set belongs to the soft attractive floral family that gives you a lively refreshing scent of delicious black currant and cherry.
The fragrance heart exudes jasmine and rose, that express passion, love and excitement.
The set comes to you in an elegant unique package, so that you can present it as a gift to anyone you love in various occasions and happy celebrations.', 50, 4250400.0, 4250400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614272855762-emporio-armani-in-love-with-you-eau-de-parfum-50ml-fragrance-gift-set-01.png'),
(20, 'Givenchy Accord Particulier EDP', 'Enjoy special nights that will remain engraved in your memory for many years to come with this special fragrance.
The fragrance mix is rich in rose notes with sensual patchouli that ignites your passion and gives you a sense of pleasure and sophistication.
The fragrance is strong and intense, spreading over the horizon for the first moments and staying with you for long hours without fading.
The fragrance is designed with precision and professionalism to suit both men and women.', 100, 6893100.0, 6893100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/2/3274872395442-givenchy-givenchy-accord-particulier-de-givenchy-_u_-edp-100-ml.png'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Vert D''encens', 'This new fragrance represents the scented interpretation of the coast of Corsica, sophisticated, aromatic, and wild. The composition includes notes of incense, pine resins, balsam fir, heliotrope, and woods. It was launched in 2016. This edition is available in a 250ml splash.', 250, 7617600.0, 7617600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066060592-tom-ford-tom-ford-vert-d_encens-_u_-edp-50-ml-1.jpg'),
(8, 'Chopard Or De Calambac', 'This woody oriental fragrance comes with precious natural oud that refreshes your memories to restore old memories taking you to discover new aspects of your personality with new tastes of pink pepper and star anise.', 100, 10791600.0, 10791600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/6/7640177367501_chopard_collection_de_calambac_eau_de_parfum_100ml_1.jpg'),
(216, 'Jo Malone Tuberose Angelica Intense EDC', 'A unique elegant fragrance designed specifically for women.
A sensual refreshing floral fragrance.
The fragrance is rich in an unparalleled aromatic blend extracted from the finest natural ingredients.
Get a glamorous look with this amazing scent that will capture everyone''s attention from the first moment.
You will be addicted to this amazing composition at the first touch.
About the Brand:
Jo Malone joined the EstÃ©e Lauder Companies, which is available in 69 countries and territories, in 1999. Jo Malone London is a British brand known for its unique fragrances and luxurious products for bath, body, and home. It has written the rules of perfumery by blending unexpected components of ingredients and introducing elegant and playful concepts, the Jo Malone world continues to develop beautifully.', 100, 4857600.0, 4857600.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(17, 'Calvin Klein Women Gift Set ', 'This set includes an Eau de Parfum 100ml + a Body Lotion 75ml
This fragrance celebrates the feminine spirit in all its shades. It is a pink chroma composed of fresh eucalyptus acorns followed by delicate orange flower petals. The base is warm with cedarwood notes. The set also includes a gentle body lotion to indulge your senses.', 75, 3477600.0, 3477600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614226921734-calvin-klein-calvin-klein-women-_w_-set-edp-100-ml-_-body-lotion-75-ml-1.jpg'),
(85, 'Tiziana Terenzi Kirke', 'This sweet, fruity perfume is inspired by the enchanted potions of Goddess Circe. Its scent guides you through mythic paths to explore stunning marvels. It is distinguished by a lush bouquet of sensual fruits, including raspberries and pears. The juicy scent is warmed by the indulgent, sweet heliotrope flower and a seductive base of musk.', 100, 5837400.0, 5837400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8016741072482-tiziana-terenzi-tiziana-terenzi-kirke-_u_-extrait-de-parfm-100.jpg'),
(164, 'Mercedes Benz The Move Express Yourself EDT', 'Enjoy an unparalleled aroma with this amazing fragrance.
The fragrance gives you a perfect final touch, and enhances your sense of comfort all the time.
The fragrance starts with a mixture of mint, ozone leaves and sage.
And at the heart are refreshing touches of pineapple and green apple.
The fragrance ends with amber and patchouli.', 100, 1718100.0, 1718100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/5/3595471091031-mercedes-benz-mercedes-benz-the-move-express-yourself-for-men-_m_-edt-100-ml.png'),
(20, 'Givenchy Live Irresistible Blossom Crush', 'Givenchy Live Irresistible Blossom Crush is floral fragrance for women. It is formed to satisfy the needs of the spontaneous woman. It is charming as it celebrates freedom and spontaneity. The irresistible and charming scent reflects new beginnings, sweet memories and blissful moments. Wearing it makes you feel like you are on cloud number 9. The fragrant befits spring, breezy summer days and warm moments. Givenchy Live Irresistible Blossom Crush combines bouquet of peony and rose, cocoa beans and musk. The bottle is an elegant addition to the charming perfume.', 100, 2007900.0, 2007900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_givenchy_perfumes_live_irresistible_blossom_crush_for_women_eau_de_perfum_3274872367807_1st.jpg'),
(55, 'Hugo Boss Hugo Just Different', 'It is the perfect fragrance and the first choice for every man who strives to excel and create his own personality, the man who attracts the attention of everyone and captures his attention within moments, Here is this perfume that you will not regret for a moment after its acquisition, do not miss the opportunity to enjoy the mixture of basil, mint and patchouli found in this special fragrance', 125, 1173000.0, 1173000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/u/hugo_boss_hugo_jsut_different_eau_de_toilette_1.jpg'),
(51, 'Al Dakheel Oud Goldum Cream ', 'The perfect solution for dryness and the best choice for silky smooth skin. It envelops your skin with a fresh vibrant scent that lasts for hours long. It''s a body cream with a soft and delicate floral composition that helps you get rid of all dryness and roughness in your skin to enjoy a velvety complexion with an attractive glowing luster.
Benefits:
Envelopes your skin with a strong and fresh scent that remains present for a long time.
How to use:
