(19, 'Very Important Notes No 4 EDP ', 'For the rebel soul in you. This fragrance is the most evoking scent from this collection. It started with a quest to find a true adventurous fragrance. This scent emerged to fulfill this pursuit, by blending the earthly scent of oud wood, the strength of tobacco, the refreshing coffee accord & the complexity of vetiver. A timeless combination, only a true braveheart can own it.', 100, 2035500.0, 2035500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/v/i/vin_4-ver2-3.jpg'),
