(244, 'Creed Aberdeen Lavender', 'Creed introduced Aberdeen Lavander in 2014 to add to its Oriental Fougere collection. Rosemary, artemisia, bergamot and lemon top notes start the scent off with herbal touches and a citrus edge. This dissipates into a floral bouquet of middle notes dominated by its namesake scent, lavender. Rounding out the heart are subtle glimpses of rose and lily. Finally, the base notes are earthy and woody, with patchouli and leather giving the overall aroma and exotic green feel. This fragrance is appropriate for all seasons at any time of day, making it a versatile scent for almost every occasion.', 100, 9025200.0, 9025200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/5/3508441001473_creed_creed_aberdeen_lavender_edp_100_ml_1.jpg'),
(21, 'Ajwa Home Must Have Room Sprays Set', 'Ajwa Home Scent Sprays are home fragrances which replace the bad odour and make the atmosphere gaiety. These home fragrances are long-lasting, refreshing and aromatic. They are suitable for a daily cleaning routine.
