(55, 'Hugo Boss Hugo XY', 'A fragrance with a fresh and sensual aroma for a man who believes in his own potential, searches for challenges and knows how to achieve his goals .. For a strong and self-confident man, an oriental perfume composed of a mixture of sweet and spicy oils with a refreshing masculine herbal fragrance, fragrant musk and sharp woody notes.', 100, 1669800.0, 1669800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/3/737052130934_hugo_boss_hugo_boss_huugo_xy_edt_100_ml_1.jpg'),
