(64, 'Parfums Gres Cabotine Rose', 'Cabotine Rose by Perfumes Gres is a wonderful floral fruity perfume for women. This soft, light and refreshing scent is suitable for summertime. The composition starts with fruity top notes. A mix of tender black currant, sweet mandarin and cherry pear dances in a background of cherry blossom. The heart is floral with a mÃ©lange of clean peony, fresh mimosa, sweet tuberose, orange blossom, exotic lily, jasmine, subtle rose and a shade of pepper. The dry-down is an elegant combination of sandalwood, musk, vetiver and frangipani. Cabotine Rose by Perfumes Gres is for a bubbly woman who likes, just like all girls, to have fun.', 100, 690000.0, 690000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_parfums_gres_perfumes_capotine_rose_for_women_eau_de_toilette_7640111492955.jpg'),
(6, 'Versace Eros Pour Homme ', 'Aromatic fragrance for men is inspired by Greek mythology, the name of the perfume came from Eros, the Greek god of love and the son of the goddess Aphrodite, and its scent reveals the unrestricted passion, with a mixture of mint, ambroxan, and vetiver.', 30, 1511100.0, 1511100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/v/e/versace-eros_eau_de_toilette_1.jpg'),
