(309, 'Oud Lover Dkhon Nawadr Aloud ', 'A new experience in the world of oriental fragrances. It''s enriched with oud and oriental oils, filling the place around and deivering a feeling of luxury.', 30, 241500.0, 241500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/9/6954567547819-oud-lover-dkhon-nawadr-al_oud-30g-1.png'),
(32, 'Guerlain Eau de Fleurs de Cedrat EDC', 'This fragrance was designed in the early twentieth century with freshness and absolute vitality in mind.
