(20, 'Givenchy Ange Ou Etrange Le Secret Poetry Of A Winter', 'New verses from poems of love and passion are written for you by the sweetness of sugar orange and delicate drops of honey in the mixture of the luxurious and fantastic perfume that immerses your soul with a powerful aromatic aura. It spreads around you once you show up and remains in the hearts of those present until the end of the day, which makes you always superior to all women.', 50, 2442600.0, 2442600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/2/3274871371492-givenchy-givenchy-ange-ou-etrange-le-secret-poetry-of-a-winter-_l_-edp-50-ml-1.jpg'),
(203, 'Vertus Fresh Orient EDP', 'This dynamic surprising oriental fragrance is formulated with an ancient and luxurious Latin touch.
