(60, 'S.T. Dupont Essence Pure Pour Femme', 'Essence Pure Pour Femme by S.T. Dupont is an Oriental Floral fragrance for women. This heavenly scent was developed just for you. The opening of the fragrance is sparkling and citrusy with mandarin orange and bergamot with a floral hint of freesia. The heart bursts with jasmine and rose. Rich and warm, the dry-down includes sweet amber, smooth patchouli, pleasant vanilla and spicy cedar. Essence Pure Pour Femme by S.T. Dupont is a fantastic, sophisticated and feminine fragrance presented in a classic bottle. Wear this long-lasting scent to your special occasions. Perfect for winter.', 100, 2145900.0, 2145900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/t/st_dupont_essence_pure.jpg'),
(244, 'Creed Original Santal', 'Original Santal is a distinctive menÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s scent steeped in the heritage of centuries of perfumery. This scent pays homage to the spiritual richness and royal splendor of India. As the name hints, precious sandalwood is the center of this scent, around which all other elements slowly dance. Top notes of Indian sandalwood, coriander, cinnamon, and juniper berry provide immediate satisfaction. The olfactory journey continues with middle notes of ginger, lavender, rosemary, and leaves of the absolute orange tree. The warm base of vanilla and tonka bean provides a lingering, satisfying finish.', 100, 10432800.0, 10432800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_creed_perfumes_original_santal_for_men_eau_de_perfum_3508441001107_1st.jpg'),
(32, 'Guerlain Mon Guerlain', 'Guerlain Mon Guerlain is an ideal perfume for an inspirational woman. This fragrance was inspired by womenÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s dreams, ambitions and choices. It delivers an elixir for elegance and femininity. The opening is audacious and fresh with lavender and bergamot. Sambac jasmine and vanilla occupy the heart giving the fragrance subtlety. Sandalwood at the dry-down gives the scent a mysterious feel. Guerlain Mon Guerlain is a soft and calming fragrance that is unique in its breathtaking composition and beautiful bottle. The classical bottle is charming in its own simple design, taut lines and sensual curves.', 100, 3332700.0, 3332700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_guerlain_perfumes_mon_guerlain_for_woman_eau_de_parfum.jpg'),
