Reapply throughout the day whenever you need a dose of awesomeness!', 30, 1028100.0, 1028100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/-/c-candyaddict-minis-hairmist-set2-1.png'),
