The heart of the fragrance carries a hot and glowing flood of coffee and saffron that boosts the strength and brilliance of the scent.', 100, 828000.0, 828000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/1/719346233408-britney-spears-britney-spears-prerogative-_w_-edp-100-ml.png'),
(244, 'Creed Tabarome', 'This fragrance is designed for men who aspire to be leaders. Its top notes feature Bergamot, lemon, mandarin, and ginger, complemented by a heart of jasmine, sandalwood, and vetiver. The base has notes of Musk, tobacco, and tea.', 100, 10432800.0, 10432800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/5/3508441001077_creed_tabarome_eau_de_parfum_100ml_1_1_.jpg'),
(253, 'Amouroud Miel Sauvage', 'Amouroud''s Miel Sauvage evokes a precious harmony between seduction and mystery. This parfume heightens the sense of sensuality when embodying the sense of nostalgia for the ancient east. This parfume is a rich olfactive treasure that anchors the composition of the hypnotic Incense, addictive Wild Honey and Night Blooming Jasmine, which have been magically intertwined. The inclusion of the spellbinding heart of Oud in this fragrance offers unparalleled intensity and longevity. Miel Sauvage is the smell of the beauty of the night rain and the gloomy evening.', 100, 5499300.0, 5499300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_amouroud_perfumes_miel_sauvage_for_unisex_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(44, 'Bvlgari Omnia Paraiba', 'This fragrance inspired by Brazilian jungle, beaches and ocean that gives natural and relaxing touch. This fruity fragrance of bitter orange and Maracuja that combines with vetiver and cocoa. This scent takes you to the heart of Brazilian gardenia to enjoy a fresh and beautiful view.', 65, 1911300.0, 1911300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/v/bvlgari_omnia_paraiba_edt_65_ml.jpg'),
(3, 'Yves Saint Laurent Black Opium', 'Black Opium, the new fragrance announced as a rock''n''roll interpretation of the classic that should highlight the dark, mysterious side of the YSL brand. Master perfumers Nathalie Lorson and Marie Salamagne, in collaboration with Olivier Cresp and Honorine Blanc, developed the composition. Notes of coffee, present in large quantities, dominate the scent. Additional accords are pink pepper, orange blossom, jasmine, vanilla, patchouli and cedar. The perfume comes in the bottle designed as the last editions of the Opium collection. The bottle is dark and decorated with sequins that give a glam rock look.', 50, 2925600.0, 2925600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/y/v/yves_saint_laurant_black_opium.jpg'),
(328, 'CnR Create Star Sign Sagittarius', 'Feel energized and dynamic with this floral fruity fragrance. The amazing composition has upper notes of magnolia, followed by peach in the heart and amber in the base, delivering a sophisticated scent for the sagittarius woman whose positivity influences everyone around.', 50, 3574200.0, 3574200.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(16, 'Al Majed For Oud Retaj EDP', 'A wonderful composition in the spring with its refreshing breeze and blooming flowers. The composition has notes of French roses, along with citrus, which makes it the best option for daily refreshment. Classic touches of musk and vanilla adds to your elegance.', 50, 952200.0, 952200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6285091000489-almajed-for-oud-retag-unisex-perfume---50-ml-50-ml-1.png'),
(76, 'Thierry Mugler Angel', 'An elegant, delicate, sensual, and soft perfume was designed with a refillable bottle resembling a dazzling star in the night sky. It has a perfect blend that''s enriched with bergamot and helional, to give you a refreshing, charming scent, keeping your attraction on for a long time.', 100, 2187300.0, 2187300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/4/3439600191011-thierry-mugler-thierry-mugler-angel-_w_-edt-40-ml.jpg'),
(7, 'Xerjoff Luxor EDP', 'A charming oriental fragrance with sharp notes of leather wrapped with spicy cinnamon.
Fill your day with tobacco and warm incense, which deliver a mysterious touch on days of winter and autumn.
The fragrance is spicy oriental to explode the feelings of vitality. It''s the perfect choice for special nights.
The base is powerful, thanks to the notes of oud and patchouli, which remain until the end of your day to boost your self confidence.', 50, 10557000.0, 10557000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(147, 'Braccialini Casual Pour Femme', 'Braccialini Casual Pour Femme a floral woody musk fragrance for stylish and aspiring women. The fragrance opens fresh, rich and crispy with a mixture of bergamot, black currant and green leaves. The heart bursts with a bouquet of lily-of-the-valley, rose, ylang-ylang and jasmine. The dry-down is woodsy and musky with notes of vanilla, sandalwood, white cedar extract and musk. Braccialini Casual Pour Femme with its soft and feminine blue bottle is designed for a funky cool woman with high aspirations. Indulge in your favorite pursuits with the blue magic from Braccialini.', 100, 2035500.0, 2035500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_braccialini_perfumes_casual_pour_femme_for_women_eau_de_perfum_8007033040333.jpg'),
(111, 'Carolina Herrera CH Men', 'The life of the CH man is like a long journey, full of emotions. A journey with a destination but no fixed duration, a journey to encounter new sensations, to meet people and discover places: a journey as the most important personal experience. And during this journey, an unmistakable styleÃ¢â‚¬Â¦ that touch of spontaneous and contemporary elegance that he takes with him everywhere he goes.', 100, 2449500.0, 2449500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_carolina_herrera_perfumes_ch_eau_de_toilette_for_men_2018.jpg'),
(380, 'Xerjoff Casamorati Lira', 'Enjoy the freshness and vitality that spreads in the air, carrying notes of black tea and guaiac wood, enhanced with the soft scents of clary sage. The fragrance will provide you with an amazing sensation of comfort that lasts for a long time.', 300, 9680700.0, 9680700.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(16, 'Al Majed for Oud Rima Elegance EDP', 'A soft fragrance that restores to your soul the psychological stability with its soft and pure scent
The musk with the softness of Jasmine and Vanilla forms an amazing blend of fragrance to suit you on all special days
It is the perfect aromatic composition to keep you comfortable all the time until the last moments
