About the Brand:
Thomas Carlyle Ford is a famous American fashion designer and filmmaker. He has been one of the most important people in pop culture from the 1990s till this day. He is the owner of the luxury brand which was founded in 2005, in New York City. Tom Ford has produced amazing menswear, beautiful fragrances, high quality sunglasses and cool watches that are very popular with high fashion enthusiasts. His line can be found all over the world. In Europe alone, you can shop his products in many countries such as UK, Spain, France, Belgium, Germany, Greece, Finland, Sweden, Portugal, Ireland, etc.', 100, 6506700.0, 6506700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066117692-tom-ford-tom-ford-ombre-leather-_u_-parfum-100-ml.png'),
(71, 'Hermes Un Jardin Sur Le Toit', 'This aromatic fruity fragrance is inspired by the luxurious garden on the Hermes headquarters in Paris. The amazing composition has notes of rose, basil and magnolia, delivering a delicate scent that fills the atmosphere with sweet and fresh aromas to captivate the hearts.', 100, 3098100.0, 3098100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346132400019-hermes-hermes-un-jardin-sur-le-toit-_u_-edt-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(50, 'Alexandre.J The Collector Rose Oud', 'Rose Oud Perfume by Alexandre.J is a feminine perfume that appeals with its sweet and spicy notes that remind you of warm summers. The fruity opening notes of apple, lemon, toffee, and raspberry invite attention. The middle notes of rose, white woods, patchouli, and saffron beautifully blend with amber and vanilla to lend a sweet and spicy character.', 100, 4278000.0, 4278000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(1, 'Dolce & Gabbana Velvet Black Patchouli EDP', 'A luxurious woody fragrance that is perfect for both men and women.
It is featured with a sophisticated blend of refreshing orange, patchouli, and coriander with a special touch of vanilla.
