This fragrance is the perfect choice for you at all special times.', 150, 10501800.0, 10501800.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(165, 'Laura Biagiotti Roma', 'It''s a distinctive oriental fragrance that combines, energy, delicacy with elegance. The aromatic composition of jasmine, vanilla along with bergamot and bitter orange expresses your femininity with a heightened sense of emotion.', 100, 1476600.0, 1476600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_laura_biagiotti_perfumes_roma_for_women_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(33, 'Lacoste Pour Femme Intense', 'It is a floral fragrance with a natural sense of French elegance. It is charismatic, radiant, and full of inexhaustible energy. In the original composition, a delicate rose gives way to an armful of Bulgarian rose of heightened sensuality. It has aromatic caramel top notes mixed with musk and woody base.', 90, 1373100.0, 1373100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614226702074-lacoste-lacoste-pour-femme-intense-_l_-edp-90-ml_1_.jpg'),
(211, 'Palquis Love''n Blue Rose EDP', 'A stunning floral fruity fragrance specially designed for elegant women.
