(309, 'Oud Lover Dokhon Crystal ', 'A warm and glowing crystal fragrance with an elegant and luxurious oriental feature. The fragrance of the incense spreads in the place quickly, remaining for a long time.', 30, 255300.0, 255300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/1/2/1245111174588-oud-lover-dokhon-cristal-30g-1.png'),
(348, 'Goutal Paris Eau d''Hadrien Set ', 'This set features a 100 ml EDP and a 75 ml cream.
