(17, 'Calvin Klein Eternity Flame For Men', 'It is a balsamic leathery fragrance for men. It starts with aromatic-fruity top notes of pineapple that surrounds the rosemary heart. The addictive base incorporates leather labdanum and amber hints. It is an unforgettable fragrance.', 100, 1925100.0, 1925100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614225670435-calvin-klein-calvin-klein-eternity-flame-for-men-_m_-edt-100_ml-1.jpg'),
(71, 'Hermes Kelly Caleche', 'It''s a luxurious fragrance designed for the charming and gentle woman who gets what she wants through her special charisma. Its sensual composition has notes of iris and mimosa, mixed with leather, delivering an irresistable scent that adds attractiveness to your character.', 100, 5237100.0, 5237100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346131500031-hermes-hermes-kelly-caleche-_w_-edt-100-ml-1.png'),
(111, 'Carolina Herrera Very Good Girl EDP', 'This fragrance is inspired by the modern fashion and wonderful designs that get attention.
