Al Majed For Oud Company was established in 1956 AD to establish a promising market in the field of oud trade through the wholesale sector by culminating in more than 60 years of experience in the manufacture of oud and perfumes. Their preparations across the Gulf market, by creating and innovating new aromatic lines have contributed in expanding their customer base and heading to the retail trade to reach more than 160 sales platforms in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia and the Gulf countries.', 75, 1117800.0, 1117800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6285091001387-2187-_-_-_-_-_-_.png'),
(44, 'Bvlgari Man Glacial Essence', 'An amazing scent dedicated to the power of natural elements. The captivating composition has notes of juniper berries in the top, artemisia in the heart, and cedar in the base. In addition to a blend of woody notes & musk, offering a scent that accentuates the unstoppable masculinity with long-lasting effect.', 100, 4209000.0, 4209000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/8/783320411946-bvlgari-bvl-man-glacial-essence-edp-100ml.jpg'),
