(63, 'Dior Miss Dior Hair Mist', 'This lightweight perfumed hair mist will give your hair a seductive fragrance. It has a warm blend of Italian mandarin essence, mixed with Damascena rose absolute, Indonesian amber and patchouli essence. It''s also enriched with active ingredients that will nourish and protect hair, leaving it soft and fresh.', 30, 1738800.0, 1738800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3348901255820_dior_christian_dior_miss_dior_hair_mist_30_ml_30_ml_1.jpg'),
(317, 'Estee Lauder Sensuous Nude', 'This fragrance for women was launched by the brand in 2000 and, as the names suggest, was defined by the company as a tribute to the Ã¢â‚¬Ëœwoman who listens to her inner voiceÃ¢â‚¬â„¢. This rich fragrance lives up to its description with a top of mandarin, bergamot, and garden notes. Then at the heart of the fragrance, you can sense notes of gardenia, rose, and freesia, and the base notes are precious woods, amber, and warm-skin accord.', 100, 2829000.0, 2829000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/7/27131845614-estee-lauder-estee-lauder-sensuous-nude-_w_-edp-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(48, 'Lancome La Vie Est Belle Flowers of Happiness EDP', 'The aromatic notes spread positivity all the time.
