Reapply throughout the day whenever you need a dose of fabulousness!', 100, 1235100.0, 1235100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/w/award-candy_addict_musky_musk_hair_mist_100_ml_2.jpg'),
