(17, 'Calvin Klein Eternity Now for Men', 'A refreshing and attractive men''s perfume released in 2015 with an unexpected mixture and notes of bitter ginger dissolved in coconut water, in addition to the star anise liquid. They also sensed the pleasure of Moroccan rice and the sweetness of patchouli in addition to tonka beans and Madagascar beans to get a rich and distinctive aroma without any perfume else.', 100, 1311000.0, 1311000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_calvin_klein_perfumes_eternity_now_for_men_eau_de_toillete.jpg'),
