(317, 'Estee Lauder Pleasures Eau Fraiche', 'It''s a magnificent blend of sweet and smoky notes that highlights its Middle Eastern roots with warm amber, Taif rose, oud, and exotic incense leading the way for a divine blend of seductive scents. Hints of blackcurrant, raspberry, ylang-ylang, Bulgarian rose, and rich white jasmine all incorporate their own fruity and floral accords, while the addition of pink pepper, sandalwood, patchouli, musk, and leather encompass the senses with a spicy and earthy final touch.', 100, 2035500.0, 2035500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/7/27131474852-estee-lauder-estee-lauder-pleasures-eau-fraiche-_w_-edp-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(79, 'Atelier Cologne Silver Iris', 'Silver Iris by Atelier Cologne is a unisex oriental floral fragrance that was launched in the year 2013. The top notes of the fragrance are tangerine, pink pepper, and black currant, heart notes are mimosa, iris and violet leaves, base notes are white amber, musk, and patchouli.', 100, 7928100.0, 7928100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/t/atelier_cologne_silver_iris_pure_perfume_100_ml.jpg'),
(37, 'Chanel Coromandel', 'It is a rich woody oriental fragrance, mystical and filled with contrasts. It combines dry notes of incense, rose, jasmine and benzoin. Wooden accords give away the elegance and depth of its magical trail.', 75, 16332300.0, 16332300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/1/3145891016154-chanel-chanel-les-exclusifs-coromandel-_u_-edt-200-ml-1.jpg'),
(244, 'Creed Viking ', 'Creed Viking is an aromatic woody fragrance for men. The incredibly beautiful, heavy and warm perfume. Very attractive scent with very unique notes. Suitable for daily use.', 100, 14400300.0, 14400300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/5/3508441001169_creed_viking_100_ml_eau_de_perfum_men.png'),
(72, 'Franck Olivier Franck Olivier', 'Franck Olivier by Franck Olivier is a floral fruity fragrance for women. This fragrance is a journey to beautiful wonders and nostalgic times. The opening is fruity. Grapefruit and peach give the scent its freshness. Black currant accords unite with ripe plum developing into a soft and soothing scent. The heart envelops the floral notes. Warm jasmine, velvety heliotrope and smooth jasmine bring about a sweet rush before ylang-ylang joins in to make the scent lovelier. The dry-down is exquisite with the warm balance of sandalwood and musk and soft and creamy touch of vanilla. Melancholic and sweet, Franck Olivier is ideal for casual occasions and enjoyable times.', 75, 717600.0, 717600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_franck_olivier_perfumes_franck_olivier_for_women_eau_de_perfum_3516649401322_1st.jpg'),
(28, 'Burberry My Burberry Black Gift Set ', 'An aromatic set for women that contains a 90 ml Eau de Parfum with a 5 ml bottle of the same perfume and lotion in a size of 75 ml
