(27, 'Gucci Bloom Nettare Di Fiori Intense', 'A sensual and darker interpretation fragrance, with aromatic notes of rose, ginger, osmanthus and patchouli mixed with Jasmine and Musk. It celebrates the intimate and authentic character of a woman. It was launched in 2018.', 30, 2035500.0, 2035500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614227570085_gucci_gucci_bloom_nettare_di_fiori_bayan_w_edp_intense_30_ml_1.jpg'),
(11, 'Mont Blanc Starwalker', 'Mont Blanc Starwalker is a Woody Spicy fragrance for men. The product is formulated with the top notes of mandarin orange, bamboo, and bergamot; middle notes are sandalwood, cedar, and white musk; base notes of nutmeg, ginger, amber and fir resin.', 75, 1104000.0, 1104000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/o/mont_blanc_starwalker.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Modern', 'Modern 100 ml is an Eau de Parfum For Men and Women from Tous Les Jours that will reflect the charm of your personality and how open it is to the world with top notes of Pink Pepper, Red Berry that will grab your attention immediately, then the heart notes of Raspberry, Violet, Peach, Red Currant, Lilac Flower that will take control representing the essence of the perfume to leave you in the end with the base notes of Amber, Patchouli, Caramel that will linger with you far beyond that.', 100, 1373100.0, 1373100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006905575_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_modern_100_ml_tayamun_1.jpg'),
(187, 'Widian Aj Arabia New York EDP', 'An elegant woody fragrance characterized by its distinctive and unique scent.
