(44, 'Bvlgari Le Gemme Orientali Lazulia', 'This fragrance by Daniela Andrier that takes you to a night journey through the Arabian desert that tells fabulous and sensual tales of the Arabian Nights. This woody oriental fragrance combines with jasmine Natural Incense and Royal Oud Wood Essence that comes in a bottle of brilliant azure blue', 100, 10833000.0, 10833000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_bvlgari_perfumes_le_gemme_orientali_lazulia_edp_100_ml_for_unisex_783320461620.jpg'),
(381, 'Xerjoff Casamorati La Tosca', 'Al Athal is an aromatic resin perfume bridging and celebrating the bonds between the generations of the region. Love, respect and innovative traditions are carried in the scent of Al Athal. Spices, flowers and Frankincence at the top lay on an olfactive bed of Amber and Musk. Al Athal Oud takes the beautiful initial scent, and adds pure precious Indian Oud Oil, to make the scent deeper and warmer. Ghawali Concentrated Perfumes are a 100% oil-based fragrance, ideal for your pulse points and for layering with our perfumes.', 6, 9680700.0, 9680700.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(59, 'Dunhill Signature Collection British Leather', 'It is a leathery fragrance, with a unique heart blooming with mate, lavender, orange blossom and violet. Vetiver, sandalwood and leather form a skinny and warm trail while the top incorporates citrus and spicy hints of bergamot and juniper and hazelnut.', 100, 3470700.0, 3470700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/5/85715806635-dunhill-dunhill-signature-collection-british-leather-_m_-edp-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(83, 'Montale Pure Gold', 'Pure Gold by Montale belongs to the Golden Selection collection of the same brand. It is crafted by Pierre Montale and launched in the year 2009. The fragrance has notes of neroli, Egyptian jasmine, Italian tangerine, white musk, apricot, patchouli, and vanilla. The main accords of the perfume are white floral, musky, citrus, fruity, and patchouli.', 100, 2035500.0, 2035500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_montale_perfumes_pure_gold_for_women_eau_de_perfum_m0060119b.jpg'),
(245, 'Kajal Perfumes Paris Alujain', 'This adorable fragrance represents celebritations, festive sense and joy which collects traditional and modern fragrances into one. It brings a joyful mood to its wearer by its wooden oriental scent, that could be layered with others or worn alone. With notes of roses and amber and woods.', 100, 7072500.0, 7072500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden-scent_-perfume_-kajal-perfumes-paris-perfumes_-alujain-for-unisex_-eau-de-perfum_-627843352914-1.jpg'),
(208, 'Lootah Musk Al Rose Fragrant Oil', 'Enjoy Musk Al Rose fragrant oil from the Lootah collection, it instantly envelops the wearer in a cloud of elegance.
