The rose musk blend also adds an extra touch of purity and sparkle to your special occasions.', 3, 1662900.0, 1662900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6297000943213-lootah-lootah-musk-al-rose-fragrant-oil-3-ml.png'),
(20, 'Givenchy Gentleman EDT Gift Set', 'This set includes two pieces of Gentlemen Eau de Toilette 100 ml and shower gel 75 ml. A unique fragrance that balances strength with delicacy, with masculine interpretation for the notes of Honey, Cinnamon, citrus notes, along with Jasmine and Cedar. The rich base has a blend of Leather, Amber, Patchouli, and Musk. For a sensual, vibrant aromatic experience.', 100, 3663900.0, 3663900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/2/3274872401792_givenchy_gentleman_set_eau_de_toilette_for_man_sh_gel75ml_men_1.jpg'),
