(28, 'Burberry Brit Rhythm', 'Brit Rhythm is a youthful and instinctive fragrance for men. Experience top notes of basil verveina, cardamom and a shot of juniper berries Discover adrenalized heart notes of black leather, patchouli, and styrax resin and sensual base notes of cedarwood, incense, and tonka bean.', 90, 1580100.0, 1580100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/burbery_birt_rhythm.jpg'),
