(32, 'Guerlain Insolence ', 'Guerlain Insolence Eau de Toilette is a scent that takes you to the spirit of the fragrance. It is a beautiful, powdery, floral scent that is both feminine and dreamy. This fragrance witnesses the first ever use of berries in a scent. The enticing combination of berry notes, violet, orange blossom and iris makes this sensual fragrance irresistible. This fragrance is chic, bold and stunning; created for the ambitious cool woman, who welcomes new opportunities, fearlessly. Make Guerlain Insolence Eau de Toilette your signature scent and it will sweep you off your feet to new, more exciting world.', 100, 3995100.0, 3995100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_guerlain_perfumes_insolence_for_women_eau_de_toilette_1.jpg'),
