(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 343', 'It''s a woody fragrance that adds to your special collection. The composition has upper notes of grapefruit, followed by peach in the heart and cedar in the base, delivering a sophisticated scent that makes your presence noticed wherever you go.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000343-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-343-1.png'),
