(8, 'Chopard Happy Spirit Elixir D''Amour', 'Happy Spirit Elixir d''Amour is inspired by love and by the gemstone that symbolizes passion - ruby. Irresistible sensuality, fullness and femininity are what give the character to this perfume. Lush floral compositions with the core of precious Sambac jasmine and delicate touch of yellow freesia in the top, dries down to the warm base of white musk, amber and cashmere. The fragrance expresses the happiness of that moment in which the romance blossom.', 75, 2780700.0, 2780700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/a/happy_spirit_elixir_d_armour_edp.jpg'),
(156, 'Victoria''s Secret Pink Golden Honey Body Mist ', 'It empowers your soul to have a special place.
