(86, 'Cartier Declaration Essence Cartier', 'Declaration Essence by Cartier is a Citrus Aromatic fragrance for men. Declaration Essence was launched in 2001. The fragrance opens up with notes of lemon and lime in an energetic and zesty atmosphere, while giving way for orange blossom and tea leaf to wind down their intensity with something more smooth and floral. Red geranium and lavender continue the botanical trend, while warm amber and sensual musk institute a seductive element thatÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s robust and charming. Finally, vetiver and sandalwood lend their earthy sweetness for an overall light and airy cologne that brings to mind long walks through rural settings.', 100, 3491400.0, 3491400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/cartier_declaration_essence.jpg'),
(295, 'Chaugan Fleur De Pavot EDP', 'For men looking for a bold look with soft and attractive touches.
