(369, 'Gucci Moonlight Serenade Acqua Profumata Perfumed Water', 'An elegant bottle reveals sticks, made of black fibers and exudes a charming scent to scent the place with a refreshing and luxurious scent that enhances the elegance and attractiveness of the place. The scent spreads quickly in the place to freshen your breath and gives you a high sense of joy and pleasure. < p>', 500, 7728000.0, 7728000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
