(244, 'Creed Aqua Fiorentina', 'A fruity-fresh perfume for women and was released in 2009. The fragrance contains a wonderful blend of fruits such as valuable plum, and apple mixed with Rose, white carnation bergamot and lemon then enhanced with Virginia cedar, sandalwood, and delicious grapefruit. The production of this perfume was actually discontinued for a while and re-launched after an adjustment to the formula.', 75, 10356900.0, 10356900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/5/3508441104631_creed_aqua_fiorentina_eau_de_parfum_75ml_1_1_.jpg'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Tobacco Vanille All Over Body Spray', 'It is an spicy oriental body spray for women and men that was launched in 2007. The nose behind this fragrance is Olivier Gillotin. Tobacco leaf and spicy notes are on the top with middle notes of tonka bean, tobacco blossom, vanilla, and cacao. Dried fruits and woody notes form the base.', 150, 2656500.0, 2656500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066056069-tom-ford-tom-ford-tobacco-vanille-_u_-all-over-body-spray-150-ml-1.jpg'),
(47, 'Van Cleef & Arpels Collection Extraordinaire Rose Velours', 'This floral fragrance is based on the feminine and complex aromas of rose and is described as velvety, opulent, voluptuous, warm, and captivating. It has a luminous top note featuring Italian bergamot oil and soft violet leaves. The velvety heart combines intense shades of rose absolute with the sweetness of honey and powdery iris absolute. Ambroxan and benzoin lend an unforgettable trail to the composition.', 75, 3201600.0, 3201600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3386460056939-vc_a-vc_a-col.-extraordinaire-rose-velours-_u_-edp-75ml.jpg'),
(158, 'Amouage Beloved', 'Amouage Beloved is a distinctive oriental fragrance for men that breathes confidence and warmth into every action and interlude. Its top notes combine spicy black pepper, orange, and grapefruit, followed by fresh cardamom to open floral heart of geranium, jasmine, orris, and saffron. The cologneÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s rich, comforting base is intricately woven of cedarwood, guaiac, leather, and patchouli, finished with lingering musk and earthy vetiver to create a deep, sensual and enduring chypre. A classy and imposing scent that is long-lasting while not too overpowering. Amouage Beloved is a perfect choice to give yourself or someone you love. An ideal choice for the spring season.', 100, 8976900.0, 8976900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_amouage_perfumes_beloved_for_men_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(51, 'Al Dakheel Oud Musk Vanilla EDP', 'A wonderful perfume belonging to the luxurious oriental fragrance family.
