The fragrance is based on a luxurious base of musk and tonka bean.', 50, 717600.0, 717600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6281150554030-al-dakheel-for-oud-musk-vanilla.png'),
(330, 'Boadicea Joyous EDP', 'Taste the sweetness of the glowing woody scent on your special days
