(55, 'Hugo Boss Boss Bottled Collector''s Edition', 'The woody spicy fragrance is simple and elegant, however, it highlights the sophistication of the brand. The composition features notes of plum, cinnamon and vetiver, delivering a timeless classic scent designed specially for the man of today.', 100, 1283400.0, 1283400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8005610424262-hugo-boss-hugo-boss-bottled-man-of-today-edition-_m_-edt-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(301, 'Wadi Halfa Wooden Incense Burner With A special Modern Design ', 'A circular incense burner in dark wood with a luxurious classic design and a fixed base with golden Arabic inscriptions, in addition to a golden charcoal base.', 100, 614100.0, 614100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3375-wadi-halfa-_-_-_-_-_---_.png'),
(20, 'Givenchy Dahlia Divin Le Nectar De Parfum', 'An ecstatic perfume to match the alluring presence of a charismatic woman. GivenchyÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s Dahlia Divin Le Nectar De Parfum is luxurious scent that accentuates femininity and glamor. The fragrance stands out in its unique addition of the golden flowers of mimosa. The sensual rose adds a sexy vibe to the scent. The sparks of vanilla, the spiciness of sandalwood and the glorious mimosa makes this fragrance exceptional. The sweet scent lingers on, gently, smoothly and softly. The bottle is gorgeous, just like the fragrance it contains. Winter would be simply warmer with Dahlia Divin Le Nectar De Parfum.', 50, 2580600.0, 2580600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/2/3274872328860_givenchy_dahlia_divin_le_nectar_de_parfum_1.jpg'),
(20, 'Givenchy L''Ange Noir', 'Givenchy LÃ¢â‚¬â„¢Ange Noir is a sensational perfume that is Ã¢â‚¬Å“Radiant as an angel, elusive as the darkness.Ã¢â‚¬Â The fragrance that means the Ã¢â‚¬Å“black angelÃ¢â‚¬Â emits alluring mystery and the irresistible charm of a femme fatale. It accentuates the enigmatic side of a woman. The lasting trail of the fragrance leaves everybody wanting more. The paradox of shadow and light is evident in the presence of both light and dark notes. The opening notes are pink pepper, bergamot and fresh almond. The heart notes ooze nobility with the symbol of purity, the white lily mixed with salty black sesame. The final notes are warm. They consist of ambrette seeds, tonka beans and amber.', 100, 3249900.0, 3249900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfumes_givenchy_perfumes_lange_noir_for_women_eau_de_parfum.jpg'),
(6, 'Versace Pour Femme Dylan Turquoise EDT', 'An innovative fragrance that embodies your youthful soul in the refreshing atmosphere of spring and summer.
The notes of lemon along with pink pepper take you on a journey to an island located far away to escape the noise.
The refreshing green heart has notes of cassis and freesia along with delicious notes of guava, which accompany you all the daylong.
It delivers freshness and enthusiasm, boosting your desire in freedom without restrictions.', 100, 2780700.0, 2780700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8011003858552_versace_versace_pour_femme_dylan_turquoise_w_edt_100_ml.png'),
(276, 'Eutopie No 8 EDP', 'He is brave and strong with free spirits.
Your fresh fragrance reveals the vitality of your heart on all occasions.
Enjoy the notes of lemon and spicy mint on the bright days of summer.
Don''t hesitate to be unique with this nice gentle composition.', 100, 4498800.0, 4498800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/7/3760224770154-eutopie-eutopie-eutopie-no.-8-_u_-edp-100-ml.png'),
(93, 'Ad Astra Noble Spices EDP ', 'Stars were always the fascination of the wanderers. Ever since mythical stories were wrapped around the stars, "Ad AstraÃ¢â‚¬Â is your journey towards the stars. A spicy powerful scent with notes like bergamot, pepper & vetiver. Ã™ÂA mixture rich in oriental notes that will captivate your heart.', 30, 310500.0, 310500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/d/ad-astra-noble-spices1.png'),
(49, 'Lalique Lalique', 'Lalique is a floral woody fragrance for women. A soft, sweet, powdery and feminine scent, Lalique is a heavenly scent, like a momÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s embrace, warm family dinners or a walk on a fresh snow. The opening is lovely with warm oriental notes. A strong presence of Chinese gardenia is well-blended with Sicilian mandarin orange. Black currant accords unite with blackberry into a soft and soothing scent. The heart envelops the fruity notes. Peony, Tunisian orange blossom and Bulgarian rose bring about a sweet rush before magnolia and ylang-ylang join in to make the scent lovelier. The dry-down is exquisite with the warm balance of Indian sandalwood and Tibetan musk, soft amber, mystical Yugoslavian oakmoss and feminine cedar; all of which are smoothed by creamy vanilla.', 100, 1524900.0, 1524900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_lalique_perfumes_lalique_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(16, 'Al Majed for Oud Waed EDP', 'A classic and luxurious blend that is designed with an unparalleled aromatic mix of carefully selected natural ingredients.
It will boost your sense of confidence and highlight your beautiful look.
The fragrance is designed with precision and professionalism to stay with you for long hours.
This perfume is suitable for all seasons and times and you will love it from the first spray.
About the Brand:
Al Majed For Oud Company was established in 1956 AD to establish a promising market in the field of oud trade through the wholesale sector by culminating in more than 60 years of experience in the manufacture of oud and perfumes. Their preparations across the Gulf market, by creating and innovating new aromatic lines have contributed in expanding their customer base and heading to the retail trade to reach more than 160 sales platforms in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia and the Gulf countries.', 50, 1200600.0, 1200600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6285091000205-2028-_-_-_-_.png'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Black Orchid', 'It''s a Natural Eau de Parfum that with a composition that begins with notes of Jasmine, Black Truffle, Ylang-ylang, Black Currant, Effervescent Citrus, the heart notes of Black Orchid that represents the essence of the parfume, and the base notes of Patchouli, Sandalwood, Dark Chocolate, Incense, Amber, Vetiver, Vanilla, Balsam which stays with you through out the day.', 100, 2221800.0, 2221800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_tom_ford_perfumes_black_orchid_for_women_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(117, 'Laboratorio Olfattivo Biancotalco Fragrance Diffuser ', 'p>
This fragrance was designed in the honor of the biggest diamond in the world.
The fragrance is rich with a group of breath-taking and perfect scents to suit the tastes of men and women.
The fragrance opens with a condensed scent of black pepper that perfectly blends with vanilla, iris, and rose.
In addition to a long-lasting base of cashmere musk, cedarwood and amber.
Enjoy an attractive and distinguished look with this fabulous fragrance that will grab attention from the first spritz.', 50, 2145900.0, 2145900.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(319, 'Jovan Musk', 'This amazing perfume was launched in 1973. Enjoy a woody fragrance for men that presents basic notes of wood and musk, giving you a strong masculine scent. The fragrance contains a heart of spices and mint preceded by top notes of clove and lemon. The perfume''s perfect blend lasts with you for a long time to keep your attraction and charm on.
About the Brand:
Established in Chicago in 1968 by Bernard Mitchell, Jovan Musk is a sophisticated production line for the production of perfumes. In 1972, Bernard Mitchell began designing different perfumes for both genders and he also offers different types of aftershave and deodorant products. Their scents are commonly sold in pharmacies and supermarket chains and are described as a mixture of uncommon spices and woods that meet the authentic strength of musk. The products are known for their high quality and strong scent that lasts long.', 88, 345000.0, 345000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/5/35017009029-jovan-jovan-musk-_m_-edc-88-ml-1.jpg'),
(298, 'Jul Et Mad Garuda Extrait de Parfum', 'A gorgeous floral blend enhanced by refined oriental influences.
This fragrance is perfectly designed to suit both men and women.
Stay attractive and stand out while feeling confident and comfortable all the time.
This perfume will be the perfect companion for you on all your special occasions, as the fragrance stays with you until the last minute.', 50, 6748200.0, 6748200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/7/3700748605440-jul-et-mad-j-_-m-white-nea-50ml-50ml-1.png'),
(141, 'Moschino Cheap And Chic I Love Love', 'I Love Love was launched in 2004. A refreshing fragrance for women, it is the perfect balance of flowers and fruits. The top notes introduce this with red fruits and citrus and the heart notes consist of tea rose, bulrush, lily of the valley and cinnamon leaves. The base notes bring this all together with musk and woods. This fragrance is what you keep in your perfume wardrobe when you need a burst of warm and bright citrus. The woods stop it from being too fruity and the hint of spice gives it a little depth. A fun fragrance!', 50, 1117800.0, 1117800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_moschino_perfumes_cheap_and_chic_i_love_love_for_women_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Stronger With You Freeze', 'This charming fragrance will take you on a journey to the world of beauty and joy, with the blend of cardamom, pink pepper and violet leaves at the top, for a sensual, warm scent, enhanced by the heart notes of sage, and the base notes of chestnut, vanilla Jungle Essence and Amberwood. A fragrance that conveys your elegance along with youth, for an unforgettable experience.', 50, 2242500.0, 2242500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614272889590_giorgio_armani_emporio_armani_stronger_with_you_freeze_eau_de_parfum_100ml_men_1.jpg'),
(314, 'Two Mark Leather EDP', 'Luxury and classic elegance in your life will highlight your position in society
