Be ready for timeless romantic moments with your feminine charm.', 100, 3850200.0, 3850200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614273459051-valentino-valentino-voce-viva-intensa-_w_-edp-intense-100-ml.png'),
(33, 'Lacoste Pour Femme ', 'Style on Skin - The Eau de Parfum Lacoste Pour Femme expresses elegance. The fragrance opens with delicate Freesia marks. Fragrance notes of white heliotrope and hibiscus dominate the heart note. Noble cedar wood and Mysore-sandalwood give the fragrance magic and depth. The special feature in the rear is the ''Velvet Skin'' chord. This conveys a sense of smell that is reminiscent of the delicate skin contact. The bottle appears with charm in a sleek and minimalistic style.', 30, 1000500.0, 1000500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/3/737052949161_lacoste_lacoste_pour_femme_l_edp_30_ml_1.jpg'),
(141, 'Moschino Fresh Gold Couture', 'Fresh Gold Couture is a floral woody fragrance that conveys the delicious sensations. It is an ode to femininity that Exemplifys sparkling elegance and intoxicating sensuality. It combines mandarin, pear, white peach, rhubarb leaf, jasmine, lily of the valley, orchid, akigala wood, sandalwood, vanilla and musk.', 100, 1221300.0, 1221300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8011003838011_moschino_moschino_fresh_gold_edp_100_ml_1.jpg'),
(166, 'Korloff In White Intense', 'Korloff In White Intense is a perfume for Men with an Aromatic Fougere fragrance, it was launched in 2010. The top notes are cardamom, bergamot and violet leaf; middle notes are lavender, African orange flower, and clary sage; base notes are cashmere, Virginia cedar, musk, and tonka bean.', 88, 1738800.0, 1738800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_korloff_perfumes_in_white_intense_for_men_eau_de_perfum_3760251870261.jpg'),
(71, 'Hermes Le Jardin de Monsieur Li', 'This citrus aromatic fragrance mixes between reality and imagination. The amazing composition contains notes of jasmine mixed with bergamot, taking you to a wide garden full of beautiful flowers with special aromas that you cannot miss.', 30, 2180400.0, 2180400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346132600051-hermes-hermes-le-jardin-de-monsier-li-_u_-edt-30-ml-1.jpg'),
