(20, 'Givenchy Ange Ou Demon Santal D''Hiver Perfume', 'Various stories will be written about the charm of your glowing femininity and the secrets of your own beauty in the mysterious winter days and cold nights. The feminine scent mixes the texture of warm, feminine scents of gingerbread and praline, known for their ability to delight you in the love of winter and enjoy its quiet times as well. Jasmine is added to immerse you with a delicate scent and provide you with a feeling of femininity and elegance.', 50, 2014800.0, 2014800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/2/3274871373052-givenchy-givenchy-ange-ou-etrange-le-secret-poetry-of-a-winter-_l_-edp-50-ml-1.jpg'),
(28, 'Burberry London', 'A magical fragrance that reflects an elegant and exciting nature, thanks to the fresh notes of fresh Clementine oil mixed with rose extract enriched with the sweetness of honey blossom, to give you a feeling of vitality and elegance. Burberry London was created in 2006 by Dominique Ropion. His advertising campaign was used by actress Rachel Weiss and actor Ian Grover.', 100, 1173000.0, 1173000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/burberry-burberry_london_for_woman_edp.jpg'),
(33, 'Lacoste Pour Femme', 'This floral musky fragrance is full of sensuality, thanks to its combination of jasmine, rose and musk. It embodies the free spirit of the modern woman, providing the feeling of freshness and sweetness.', 90, 1062600.0, 1062600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/a/lacoste_pour_femme_eau_de_parfum_1.jpg'),
(86, 'Cartier Pasha Noire Sport', 'Simple and clean, Pasha De Cartier Noire Sport blends the smooth sweetness of fruit with the masculine scent of wood. This cologne, released in 2015, opens with fresh top notes of citrus and watery accords. Sea notes in the fragranceÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s heart add a wild saltiness to the mix. Rich and milky sandalwood creates the foundation of the scentÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s base notes, mingling with the natural scent of cedar and warm hints of amber. A modern addition to a classic collection, this cologneÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s sophisticated balance of lightness and depth is sure to intrigue.', 100, 3491400.0, 3491400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_cartier_perfumes_pasha_noire_sport_for_men_eua_de_toilette.jpg'),
(59, 'Dunhill Icon Racing Red', 'Embodying the spirit of racing, this fragrance is designed for the thrill seeker, who gets excited by driving fast. The composition combines upper notes of grapefruit, a heart of geranium and base of vetiver, bringing to you a fascinating scent with a long-lasting effect to make you spend a great time.', 100, 3560400.0, 3560400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/5/85715806345-dunhill-du-icon-racing-red-edp-100ml-01.jpg'),
