The delicate heart has notes of iris and cypress, adding softness to the scent to keep you as elegant as usual.
The luxurious base has notes of comarin and creamy cedarwood, which provide tranquility and comfort after a long busy day.', 100, 2615100.0, 2615100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/2/3274872422995-givenchy-gentleman-21-edt-int-60ml-60-ml-1.png'),
