(44, 'Bvlgari Man Wood Neroli', 'Description
It is a new woody floral musk fragrance for men that was launched in 2019. The nose behind this fragrance is Alberto Morillas. It is enriched with bergamot and neroli mixed with orange blossom, Virginia cedar and nagarmotha; based on leather, white musk, amber, ambergris and woody notes.', 100, 2732400.0, 2732400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/8/783320403897-bvlgari-bvlgari-man-wood-neroli-_m_-edp-100-ml.jpg'),
