The fragrance is enhanced by Bulgarian rose, Turkish rose and mimosa that add to the sweetness of the scent.
The fragrance ends with white musk to increase your sense of confidence all the time.', 50, 3098100.0, 3098100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/5/2/5285006700597-ideo-parfumeurs-ideo-parfumeurs-roses-de-grasse-_w_-parfum-de-lingerie-50-ml.png'),
(158, 'Amouage Sunshine', 'Amouage Sunshine cologne is a fragrance for men who love the outdoors. This elegant scent weaves together the warmth and brightness of afternoon sunshine to produce an aromatic cologne for any time of the year. It effortlessly blends into daytime adventures and shifts gears seamlessly when the sun goes down and the night heats up. Long-lasting with a moderate sillage, this is one cologne that wonÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t have any trouble keeping up with your fun-loving, adventurous lifestyle. Top notes for this cologne are immortelle, lavender, yellow flowers and brandy. Heart notes feature clary sage, juniper berries, and bergamot. Base notes include vanilla, Tonka beans, and cedar.', 100, 8976900.0, 8976900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_amouage_perfumes_sunshine_for_men_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(17, 'Calvin Klein Mini Set For Men ', 'This mini set contains Eau de toilette of One, All and Gold (10 ml), all are suitable for both men and women. One is a citrus aromatic fragrance that spreads its freshness everywhere, thankst to its green notes, blended with papaya, freesia and rose. Be brave with Gold Eau de toilette, which makes you stand out from the crowd, with its notes of bergamot, jasmine and patchouli. Continue your freshness with All Eau de Toilette that makes your signature touched everywhere, with its notes of mandarin, jasmine and amber.', 10, 1290300.0, 1290300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614225551925_calvin_klein_calvin_klein_ck_one_m_edt_10_ml_ck_gold_edt_10_ml_ck_all_edt_10_ml_mini_set_gs-dmm_cross_dock_1.jpg'),
