(97, 'WAW Vanilla EDP ', 'If you are a fragrance expert & know your way around perfume notes, you will definitely fall in love with Vanilla! This warm, elegant & deep scent is an exact replicant of how fresh Vanilla smells like. This note represents one of the most popular ingredients added to perfumes, and you can spray with any of the other "WAW" perfumes to create your own blend and fragrance that reflects your personality.', 50, 655500.0, 655500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/a/waw-vanilla1.png'),
(60, 'S.T.Dupont Noble Wood', 'Noble Wood by S.T. Dupont is a new oriental unisex fragrance. This scent is, like its name, noble, magnificent and alluring. The elegant composition starts with sparkling pink pepper and invigorating bergamot before it develops into smooth woody notes mixed with aromatic sandalwood, powdery patchouli and spicy Frankincense in the heart. The base emits balsamic sweetness from benzoin. The rich and intense amber dancing in the woody aromas leaves a sweet scent that would soon mingle in your skin. Noble Wood with its tall and exquisite bottle is ideal for fall and winter occasions.', 100, 3291300.0, 3291300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_s.t.dupont_perfumes_noble_wood_for_women_eau_de_perfum_3386460083249.jpg'),
(318, 'Miu Miu L''eau Bleue Gift Set ', 'It''s a two-piece gift set features EDP (100ml) and body lotion (100ml). A floral fragrance with fresh scent of the spring awakening. The composition has lily of the valley notes in the top, followed by a heart of white flowers and musk in the base, providing a scent devoted to the woman who revels in her contradictions.', 100, 3339600.0, 3339600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614225547898-miu-miu-miu-miu-l_eau-bleue-_w_-edp-100-ml-_-body-lotion-100-ml-gift-set-2-piece.jpg'),
