(6, 'Versace Eros Flame', 'A spicy aromatic fragrance for men, based upon the concept of interpretation of emotional love and is made for men who enjoy strength, passion, and self-confidence together and have a deep connection with their feelings, with a wonderful blend of mandarin, vanilla, and patchouli.', 100, 1780200.0, 1780200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8011003845347_versace_eros_flame_edp_50_ml_1.jpg'),
(91, 'Tommy Hilfiger Tommy Girl Eau De Prep', 'It is a new floral, fruity fragrance for women. The fragrance opens with pink peppercorn and violet leaves. The heart carries the scent of white roses, and the composition closes with sandalwood, hawthorn, and musk. It is the ultimate accessory that completes your look and delivers a long-lasting, memorable image.', 100, 1152300.0, 1152300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/2/22548252383-tommy-hilfiger-tommy-hilfiger-tommy-girl-eau-de-prep-_w_-edt-100-ml.jpg'),
(165, 'Laura Biagiott Roma Uomo', 'This oriental woody fragrance reflects the mood of a classic man whose elegance conveys his strength. Whenever you use it, you will get a luxurious touch that you cannot resist, thanks to its strong and fresh notes of basil, geranium and vanilla.', 125, 1580100.0, 1580100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/_/c_users_hp_appdata_local_packages_microsoft.skypeapp_kzf8qxf38zg5c_localstate_541a5743-9cbd-438d-9448-a2199359d6db.jpg'),
(1, 'Dolce & Gabbana The Only One Hair Mist ', 'Designed to complement The Only One Eau De Parfum, this hair ritual has a luxurious scent infused with Violet, Iris & Patchouli. Spray it into your hair & enjoy captivating wafts that envelopes your hair for hours.', 30, 1511100.0, 1511100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/4/3423478851955_dolce_gabbana_the_only_one_hair_mist_30_ml.jpg'),
