(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 11', 'A luxurious fragrance with an amazing touch that gets you all the attention you want. The seductive composition has notes of blackberry in the top, rose in the heart and sandalwood in the base, releasing a scent that captivates the stares and hearts.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000011-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours---perfume-day-11-1.png'),
(20, 'Givenchy Dahlia Divin', 'GivenchyÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s new fragrance, Dahlia Divin, preserves the spirit of the Dahila Noir line while standing out with its floral woody combination. The opening is fruity with the distinct aromas of jasmine and plum. The Jasmin sambac fills the air minutes after. Wearing Givenchy will give you a fragrant aura. The scent is lush and feminine. It is a must-have for the summer. This fragrance is perfect for every occasion due to its smooth and sweet lingering effect. It is casual but elegant, soft but impactful. Luxurious in its simplicity and divine in its balance.', 50, 3719100.0, 3719100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_givenchy_perfumes_dahlia_divin_for_women_eua_de_toilette.jpg'),
