(4, 'Mancera Roses Jasmine', 'The perfumer Pierre Mancera presents Roses Jasmine which hits you first with notes of Mandarin, Pear, Citrus from Calabria and then sneaks on you with Jasmine, French Rose, Orange Blossom & Leaves of Patchouli with the base notes of Cedarwood, Oakmoss, White Musk, which lingers on with you the whole day long with chypre floral fragrance.', 120, 3084300.0, 3084300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_mancera_perfumes_roses_jasmine_for_unsex_eau_de_perfum_mrj01ab.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Chic', 'Chic 100 ml is an Eau de Parfum For Men and Women from Tous Les Jours that represents harmony and freshness with top notes of Black Pepper, Pink Pepper, Saffron that will grab your attention immediately, then the heart notes of Lavender, Roses, Robert Herb that will take control representing the essence of the perfume to leave you in the end with the base notes of Tonka Beans, Oud, Sandalwood, Amber Oil that will linger with you far beyond that.', 100, 1373100.0, 1373100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006907050_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_chic_100_ml_tayamun_1_1_.jpg'),
(380, 'Xerjoff Casamorati Mefisto', 'It''s a charming oriental fragrance with notes of spices, amber and the added mystery of the dark woods. The composition adds a dramatic touch to the place, that remain intense for long hours, which reinforces the relation between the people and the place.', 300, 9680700.0, 9680700.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(372, 'Xerjoff Casamorati 1888 Mefisto Gentiluomo EDP', 'A special fragrance possesses a unique scent.
The fragrance is rich with a wonderful perfume blend, made especially for men.
