It reveals a fresh scent of the Italian Coastal Citrus peels of Red Orange, Lemon, Green Tangerine, with Ambrette Seed and the luxurious Musk.
The fragrance is utterly gentle on the skin and lasts as long as possible.
p> About the Brand:
D.S. & Durga Perfume brand was founded in 2007, in New York City. It is distinguished by its special high-quality fragrances and unique scents. It collects herbs and flower extracts from all over the world to create the perfumes manually. It has recorded 76 fragrances. The earliest edition was released in 2000 and the latest one in 2021. D.S. & Durga fragrances were created in collaboration with perfumers David Seth Moltz, Kavi Moltz and Rayda Vega.', 100, 9680700.0, 9680700.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(27, 'Gucci Rush', 'This mysterious fragrance comes in a bottle inspired by the video casette. It features bergamot, peony and freesia at the top, which give a way to violet, jasmine and carnation at the heart, while the base contains orris sandalwood and vetiver, which provide you with a rich sense of fantasy.', 75, 3036000.0, 3036000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gucci_rush_edt_75_ml.jpg'),
(120, 'Paco Rabanne Lady Million EDP', 'This vibrant sensual fragrance was released after the huge success of its counterpart scent for men One Million, creating both a flamboyant couple. The bottle is designed like a gold luxurious diamond, to create a vision of true luxury.
It is a dazzling, ultra-feminine, voluptuous fragrance, fresh, floral and woody, like a nectar of voluptuous flowers, trailing delicately but still very present.', 50, 2622000.0, 2622000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/a/paco_rabanne_one_million_eau_de_parfum_1.jpg'),
(168, 'Jimmy Choo Jimmy Choo Man', 'Jimmy Choo MAN is the first parfume for men from Jimmy Choo. A extreme fresh and modern parfume made for an independent and refined man with a mutinous spirit seizes the confident attitude of the dynamic and urban Jimmy Choo man. The parfume opens with the crisp vigor of mandarin and citrus notes tempered with quieting lavender and the fluffy sweetness of the honeydew melon. Extravagant notes of geranium and pineapple leaf mixes harmoniously on the skin with the sweet decent of rare patchouli. At the base, notes of sung, amber-based wood are mixed to form an imprint parfume that is attractive and alluring.', 50, 807300.0, 807300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/i/jimmy_choo_exotic_man_1.jpg'),
(8, 'Chopard Rose Seljuke', 'A luxurious perfume with Damascene rose, Madagascar vanilla, tonka bean and Peruvian balm that blends to make an exceptional fragrance. It comes together with the warmth of aromatic woods that give you a high sense of calm and comfort.', 100, 10474200.0, 10474200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/6/7640177367471_chopard_collection_chopard_collection_rose_seljuke_eau_de_parfum_100ml_1.jpg'),
(2, 'Roberto Cavalli Florence', 'A chypre floral fragrance inspired by the city of Florence that known of its historical, artistic and cultural beauty, with a mixture of mandarin, grapefruit, patchouli, and amber.', 50, 1152300.0, 1152300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614223519576c-roberto-cavalli-florence---75-ml.jpg'),
(27, 'Gucci Bloom Ambrosia di Fiori', 'This floral fragrance is inspired by the freedom of being who you really are. It invites you to celebrate your true self and the emotions you feel. It features new ingredients like the rare velvety orris as well as Damascena rose, which gives the powerful rendition of the flower', 100, 2953200.0, 2953200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614228958691_gucci_bloom_ambrosia_di_fiori_edp_100_ml_1.jpg'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Armani Code Profumo', 'Armani Code Profumo by Giorgio Armani encompasses the masculine and sensual intensity of Armani Code. Its top notes are green mandarin, green apple and cardamom; middle notes are orange blossom, lavender and nutmeg; base notes are addictive tonka bean, glowing amber accord and leather.', 110, 752100.0, 752100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_giorgio_armani_perfumes_armani_code_profumo_for_men_parfum.jpg'),
(32, 'Guerlain L''homme Ideal Sport', 'The ideal man is a myth, but with L''Homme IdÃƒÂ©al Sport, Guerlain makes his fragrance a reality. It features stimulating fresh spices, reinvigorating the aquatic notes, and an irresistible almond trail. It''s a fresh fragrance that will trigger your athletic potential. Masculine, luxurious, and elegant, the square faceted bottle has clean lines and unique deep blue sides in a lacquered matte finish.', 100, 1621500.0, 1621500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470303652-guerlain-guerlain-l_homme-ideal-sport-_m_-edt-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(32, 'Guerlain Shallimar', 'Guerlain Shalimar, the fragrance that was inspired by one of the greatest love stories of all time, the love story that gave the world one of its seven wonders; Taj Mahal. The Oriental fragrance embodies the qualities of its inspiration; intense love, sensuality, mystery and eternity. It also introduces the new revolution in the world of perfumes, ethylvanillin, blended with the Jicky accord. Shalimar takes flight with the freshness of flowers and bergamot. Warm at the heart are the powdery notes of iris, jasmine and rose. The final notes are sensual with vanilla and Tonka beans.', 100, 2408100.0, 2408100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_guerlain_perfumes_shalimar_for_women_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(209, 'Moresque Edition Rand EDP', 'RAND honors the desert flower, a delicate flower yet strong enough to grow and survive in the most challenging environments.
The oriental floral scent is rooted in a delicate iris powder from Florence, to bring you a different allure
The fragrance blends with the whistling breeze and the delicious taste of pineapple to express your spontaneity and your passion for life
Do not hesitate to add an element of joy and pleasure to your life and your special days to remain a memory in your heart', 50, 8569800.0, 8569800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8051277311414-moresque-moresque-edp-50ml-edition-rand.png'),
(17, 'Calvin Klein Obsessed For Women', '  Here is a breathtaking fragrance with luxurious oriental accents for classic women who always draw attention with their elegance and beauty, an ideal perfume for all seasons that refreshes your senses and makes you feel all day long. ', 100, 3891600.0, 3891600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_calvin_klein_perfumes_obsessed_for_women_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(77, 'Valentino Uomo Intense', 'Valentino Uomo Intense Eau de Parfum is an intense masculine fragrance for men, presented in a magnificent bottle. This modern scent is developed for a cosmopolitan man celebrating his youthful vigor and exciting ventures. The fragrance has a bright opening with mandarin enriched by a hint of sweet clary sage oil. The heart is a perfectly blended combination of lovely iris absolute and beautiful Tonka bean. The base is charming and smooth thanks to the mixture of black leather and vanilla bean. Valentino Uomo Intense, the scent of irresistible sophistication, is the perfect fit for your romantic endeavors and special nights.', 50, 2718600.0, 2718600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_valentino_perfumes_valentino_uomo_tntense_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(353, 'Ormonde Jayne Ta''if Elixir EDP', 'A strong and bold fragrance with a distinctive composition for men and women.
Soft notes of yellow mandarin and elemi will fill you with a refreshing scent.
Heart notes of oak and black pepper are the epitome of allure.
Leather notes give off a classic, luxurious and sexy touch to the fragrance.', 50, 7728000.0, 7728000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(240, 'Jean Antoine Celebrity EDP', 'A smooth and creamy balsamic scent blended with the enchanting scents of jasmine and rose.
A lively and refreshing fragrance for men that pampers your skin with love and envelops it in a very attractive and sexy scent.
Own women''s hearts with your glowing and warm scent of smoke and calm woods.
The fragrance has a strong and high concentration that stays with you for long hours without fading.', 100, 552000.0, 552000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287015120105-jean-antoine-jean-antoine-celebrity-homme-_m_-edp-100-ml.png'),
(272, 'Reminiscence Rem Pour Homme EDT', 'The art of making special immortal memories in the hearts and minds of men and women.
A distinctive composition that evokes feelings and nostalgia to the best memories with notes of rose and Fenugreek.
The warm base has notes of musk and tonka bean, which boost your elegance.
Enjoy the bright days of summer and the rays of the sun on your skin with this cool fragrance.', 100, 3201600.0, 3201600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/5/3596935576286-reminiscence-reminiscence-rem-_m_-edt-100-ml-1.png'),
(27, 'Gucci Guilty Eau ', 'This floral fruity fragrance comes in an iconic bottle between the cold metal and soft frosted glass. It subtly opens with watery notes and litchi at the top. At the milky delicate heart, comes the lily blended with wild strawberry, giving way to musk in the base.', 75, 2035500.0, 2035500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_gucci_perfumes_gucci_guilty_eau_for_women_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 357', 'Slide your mesmerizing charismatic Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 357 perfume into your handbag so you can inhale your fragrance every time you open it! The wearer revives his self-confidence and sensuality, so quick spritz daily for a boost of both. Whether you bury your nose in the complex woody profile or the exotic spicy aromas of this perfume, the elegance and majesty will immediately be identified.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000357-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-357-1.png'),
(136, 'Salvatore Ferragamo Intense Leather EDP', 'This fragrance was inspired by the charming nature with luxurious classic notes of leather.
The luxurious scent boosts your look and adds to your charm on all your busy days and distinctive nights.
The composition starts with the freshness of pink pepper and pepper, which keep you revitalized.
The power of apple and iris from the heart reveal your strong character to boost your self confidence.', 100, 3650100.0, 3650100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8052464890699-salvatore-ferragamo-ferragamo-intense-50ml-50-ml-1.png'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 110', 'Enjoy the scent of spring with this sweet charming perfume. Its formula infused with aromatic ingredients mixed together to offer you a fresh floral oriental sensation.', 55, 683100.0, 683100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000110_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_perfume_day_110_tayamun_1.jpg'),
(55, 'Hugo Boss Boss Alive', 'This body fragrance will provide you with long lasting freshness. Its amazing composition contains notes of lemon, vetiver, patchouli and vanilla will give an aromatic scent that leaves your special touch wherever you go.', 80, 3056700.0, 3056700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614228830393-hugo-boss-boss-alive-80-ml.jpg'),
(100, 'Perfume Co. Velvet Vanilla EDP ', 'Designed for the modern woman, delicate yet intoxicating. The opening notes of fresh pink pepper & orange blossom gently give way to the softness of vanilla, to complement a youthful, vibrant character.', 100, 1028100.0, 1028100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/perfume-co-velvet-vanilla.png'),
(208, 'Lootah Signature Small Jar Incense ', 'A distinctive incense enriched with an amazing aromatic blend of unique and carefully selected natural ingredients. Enjoy the freshness of jasmine with the luxurious scent of musk, exotic spices and nutmeg to rejuvenate your energy. This scent is made to last with you for long hours without fading.', 100, 1890600.0, 1890600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6297000836522-lootah-lootah-signature-incense---small-jar-incens.png'),
(307, 'Banafa For Oud Albashawat Charcoal', 'A pack of highly flammable charcoal tablets designed to help you spread the aromatic smell of incense in the room perfectly and harmoniously and remain burning for long hours.', 100, 269100.0, 269100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/9/6944402000012-banafa-albashawat-coal-xxl.png'),
(101, 'One Word Stardust Hair & Body Mist ', 'From the dawn of time, stars were the fascination of the wonderers. This hair & body mist was created for the wanderers looking for some mystical powers, from the blend of rare saffron spice to the radiant tangy aroma coming from the blood orange scent. Magic can only be found in the most iconic combinations!', 80, 483000.0, 483000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/n/oneword-stardust-1_1_.jpg'),
(1, 'Dolce & Gabbana The One for Men EDT', 'A woody fragrance for men characterized by its sense of elegance and charm, refreshing for all time, with a wonderful mixture of tobacco extract, spices, grapefruit, coriander and basil with accents of cardamom and ginger that highlight the beauty of your look.', 100, 1649100.0, 1649100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/o/dolce_gabbana_the_one_for_men_eau_de_toilette_1.jpg'),
(51, 'Al Dakheel Oud Laha EDP', 'A sophisticated and elegant fragrance for women seeking excellence.
The fragrance reflects your glamorous beauty and gives you a special attractiveness.
Express your femininity and elegance to grab the attention of everyone around you and capture their hearts.
The fragrance is enriched with luxurious notes of carefully selected natural ingredients.
This amazing fragrance deserves to be in your perfume collection.', 50, 476100.0, 476100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6281150551244-al-dakheel-for-oud-for-her.png'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Armani Code Satin', 'The scent is a floral oriental gourmand. It opens with sparkling notes of ginger and pear sorbet. Neroli essence illuminates the heart of the entire composition, combined with about orange blossom absolute and Arabian jasmine. The base is intense and sweet: it features patchouli, cocoa, praline and vanilla.', 50, 3788100.0, 3788100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfum_giorgio_armani_perfumes_armani_code_satin_for_her_eau_de_parfum.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 252', 'A floral unisex fragrance that reveals your inner beauty. The upper notes of geranium, come on notes of jasmine in the middle and musk in the base, delivering a delicate composition that boosts your self-confidence to impress everyone there.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000252-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-252-1.png'),
(85, 'Tiziana Terenzi Sirrah Extrait De Parfum', 'Passion and excitement along with enthusiasm while climbing up the mountain to reach the top.
Reach the top and get the chance to show your power with this powerful composition.
The green notes of pepper along with tarragon boost your activity in the beginning of the day, spreading positivity.
The oriental notes of cardamom and classic leather blend together to show your love of elegance in all occasions.', 100, 7217400.0, 7217400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8016741642555-tiziana-terenzi-tiziana-terenzi-sirrah-_u_-extrait-de-parfum-100-ml-1.png'),
(8, 'Chopard Noble Vetiver', 'This fragrance is for those who share their passion for high quality and beautiful things. It is a woody spicy leathery scent that opens with elegant vetiver, accompanied by accords of bergamot, cardamom and red hot pepper. The heart captures clary sage and mahogany leaving an impression of freshness and sophistication, while the leather and tobacco form the base.', 80, 1669800.0, 1669800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3607340182044-chopard-chopard-noble-vetiver-_m_-edt-80-ml-1.jpg'),
(89, 'Azzaro Chrome Legend', 'Azzaro Chrome Legend is an aromatic fruity fragrance for men. This fresh and cool scent is perfect for the modern man. The fragrance opens fresh and pleasant with green apple and a blast of orange and tea giving an exquisite vibe. The heart notes are magical with soft musk and a hint of cedar. Tonka bean and amber give a sweet vibe to the heart while vetiver and oakmoss surround it with spiciness. The dry-down is delightful with amber. Azzaro Chrome Legend is a refreshing and uplifting fragrance that is ideal for daywear and summertime.', 125, 1124700.0, 1124700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/z/azzaro_chrome_legend_edt_125_ml_1_.jpg'),
(246, 'Yantami Citrine EDP ', 'A fragrance for the success makers! It stimulates creativity and determination with its scents of freesia & amber - transforming dreams into tangible realities. Inspired by the semi-precious stone Citrine which is believed to be a gift from the sun!', 100, 690000.0, 690000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/y/a/yantami-citrine1.png'),
(141, 'Moschino Fresh Couture Gift Set ', '#NAME?', 25, 703800.0, 703800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8011003827909-moschino-moschino-fresh-couture-_w_-edt-5-ml-_-fresh-couture-edt-.png'),
(298, 'Esteban CÃ¨dre Fragrance Refill For Bouquet ', 'This set contains a 50ml perfume and a 7ml perfume.
The set comes in an elegant package that you can give as a gift to everyone you love on different occasions.
A sophisticated fragrance characterized by its strong scent that charms lovers of floral fragrances with a touch of powder.
Enjoy the fragrance for long hours without fading.', 100, 972900.0, 972900.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(216, 'Jo Malone Pomegranate Noir EDC', 'Enjoy a delightful aromatic composition of exotic fruits.
The fragrance is enriched with an amazing aromatic blend of natural ingredients with unique aromas.
The fragrance opens with berries, watermelon, and pomegranate to give you a feeling of freshness and happiness.
The heart of the fragrance is infused with touches of carnation and pink pepper to give you a special elegance.
The fragrance ends on a base of luxurious musk and amber.
About the Brand:
Jo Malone joined the EstÃ©e Lauder Companies, which is available in 69 countries and territories, in 1999. Jo Malone London is a British brand known for its unique fragrances and luxurious products for bath, body, and home. It has written the rules of perfumery by blending unexpected components of ingredients and introducing elegant and playful concepts, the Jo Malone world continues to develop beautifully.', 100, 3601800.0, 3601800.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(279, 'Shakespeare King Henry 4 EDP', 'A luxurious aromatic scent that gives you a very bold and attractive look.
The aromatic composition is enhanced by touches of rose and coffee with vanilla that give you a classic and mystery that excites the feelings of those around you.
The scent is the perfect choice throughout your day if you are looking for a strong and intense scent for long hours.
This wonderful fragrance deserves to be in your perfume collection.', 100, 3926100.0, 3926100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/7/3755646565662-shakespeare-perfume-shakespeare-king-henry-iv-spray-100ml.png'),
(361, 'Unique Luxury King Collection EDP', 'It is a luxurious and luminous royal scent for men and women seeking luxury and sophistication.
Enjoy a unique appearance that will attract everyone around you by the spicy and glowing notes of saffron and nutmeg.
Delicious honey drops come at the base of the perfume to feel the taste of the sweetness that lasts for the day.
Roses and warm cinnamon notes make you attractive, elegant and unique among all societies.', 50, 3505200.0, 3505200.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(67, 'Alwaleef Remal Gold Incense', 'Incense inspired by the scent of Rimal Gold with a charming touch of precision in design and smart scent that attract us from far to breathe it in and enjoy its wonderful scent.', 100, 1235100.0, 1235100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_home_fragrances_alwaleef_alwaleef_-_rimal_gold_incense_6287006904028-1c.jpg'),
(305, 'Keba Perfumes Ylang EDP', 'A perfect fragrance for those looking for distinction and elegance.
A charming aromatic blend that reflects the beauty of your soul and the elegance of your appearance.
The fragrance enchantingly blends sensual floral notes with luxurious woody notes.
The fragrance will add a special touch to your time to spend it all with joy and vitality.', 50, 1214400.0, 1214400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6285560012715-keba-perfumes-yalang.png'),
(10, 'Boucheron Quatre Pour Homme', 'A strong masculine fragrance that leaves an elegant and luxury sense with a unique fresh violet and lemon scent. This fragrance combines soft jasmine and strong musk that makes it last or long hours.', 50, 1200600.0, 1200600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_boucheron_perfumes_quatre_pour_homme_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(47, 'Van Cleef & Arpels Rose Rouge', 'An aromatic fragrance with spicy notes that blends cocoa and patchouli with musk. A soft woody perfume that gives you a sweet and fresh scent that lasts for hours.', 75, 5395800.0, 5395800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3386460102278_van_cleef___arpels_van_cleef___arpels_rose_rouge_eau_de_parfum_75_ml_1.jpg'),
(234, 'Zadig & Voltaire Just Rock! Pour Elle EDP', 'An oriental floral fragrance specially designed for women.
The fragrance was launched in 2017, with an aromatic composition of luxurious and carefully selected natural ingredients.
The fragrance features refreshing jasmine, tuberose, patchouli and vanilla with luxurious woody notes.
Designed for a rebellious woman with unparalleled elegance.', 100, 3532800.0, 3532800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/4/3423474894352-zadig-_-voltaire-zadig-_-voltaire-just-rock_-pour-elle-_w_-edp-100-ml-1.png'),
(18, 'Penhaligon''s As Sawira EDP', 'A unique fragrance belonging to the luxurious woody scents.
This fragrance helps you shine on all your special occasions.
With this charming fragrance, enjoy a strong, bold, and captivating presence that draws everyone''s attention.
The fragrance is perfectly designed to suit both men and women.', 100, 6499800.0, 6499800.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(63, 'Dior Dolce Vita', 'Dolce Vita, a womenÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s fragrance released by Christian Dior in 1994, is a floral and woody perfume with just the right touch of sweet and spice. Crafted by Pierre Bourdon and Maurice Roger, this feminine scent produces the kind of luscious aroma that wonÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t be easily forgotten in your wake. Bursting with luscious fruits, the top notes of the scent contain soft lily, fleshy and juicy peach, tart grapefruit, citrusy bergamot, romantic rose, and sweet cardamom. Fuzzy apricot, lush magnolia, sensuous cinnamon, heliotrope, and woody palisander rosewood combine to form the heart of the fragrance. Milky sandalwood, tropical coconut, comforting vanilla and familiar cedar comprise the perfumeÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s base notes.', 100, 4416000.0, 4416000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/i/dior_dolce_vita_edt_100_ml.jpg'),
(55, 'Hugo Boss Deep Red', 'Designed for women who reveal in the night, this intoxicating fragrance expresses her passion and sensuality. The notes of tangerine, freesia and vanilla reveal a distinctive composition designed for active and strong women.', 50, 1531800.0, 1531800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/3/737052683522-hugo-boss-hugo-boss-hugo-deep-red-woman-_w_-edp-50-ml-1.jpg'),
(208, 'Lootah Al Sultan Oud Incense ', 'An incense with a dreamy and attractive French scent. Through its beautiful blend of natural ingredients comes a really distinctive and beautiful aroma that captivates everyone around. The smell of incense quickly spreads around lasting for long periods of time without fading.', 100, 4533300.0, 4533300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6297000836782-lootah-lootah-al-sultan-oud-incense-220-gms.png'),
(32, 'Guerlain L''homme Ideal L''intense', 'A masculine fragrance with an oriental woody scent designed for the man who seeks elegance and intensity in one fragrance. The compelling composition combines notes of chilli and Bulgarian rose, mixed with woody notes, delivering an intriguing scent that awakens the senses.', 100, 3056700.0, 3056700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/-/c-3346470134911-guerlain-guerlain-l_homme-ideal-l_intense-_m_-edp-100-ml-1.png'),
(33, 'Lacoste Eau De Lacoste L.12.12 Rouge', 'Change your mood with this dynamic passionate fragrance. Its refreshing blend of Rooibos tea extract and acacia wood will fill you with energy and enthusiasm to let you enjoy a nice day. Its memorable scent is designed for the elegant man with an audacious style.', 100, 2035500.0, 2035500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/a/lacoste-eau-de-lacoste-l-12-12-rouge.jpg'),
(24, 'Candy Addict V Vanille Hair Mist ', 'An intoxicating blend of vanilla and floral notes with a touch of Oriental spice! Take your fragrance game to a whole new level with this one of a kind hair sensation.
Moisturize, soften and strengthen your hair with Vitamin E, a powerful antioxidant, and Provitamin B5. Give your hair that extra shine and volume that it deserves, whilst leaving your hair less prone to breakage.
How to use:
From about 20 cms away, spritz the mist evenly over your hair.
Then enjoy the V Vanille vibes!
Don''t forget to shake the bottle before use to liven up the candy!
Reapply throughout the day whenever you need a dose of fabulousness!', 100, 1235100.0, 1235100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/ca-hair-mist-vanille-copy-_2_.jpg'),
(38, 'Elie Saab Girl Of Now', 'A beauty galmorous fragrance that chain all the eyes to you with its unique valuable scents that open with mandarin orange, pear, pistachio, moving to orange blossom, magnolia, almond in the heart, to end with cashmeran, tonka bean, almond milk in the base.', 90, 2028600.0, 2028600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_elie_saab_perfumes_girl_of_now_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(59, 'Dunhill Icon', 'Dunhill Icon by Alfred Dunhill is the perfect woody-aromatic cologne for the refined gentleman. A well-rounded citrus bouquet of fresh bergamot and neroli absolute set the stage for this classic aroma fougere. Spicy and aromatic black pepper crackle at the heart while lavender and cardamom smooth the experience into a rich memory. Smoky oud and leather base notes entice an aroma reminiscent of timeless luxury and grounded in the present through hints of fresh vetiver and oakmoss. The heavy metal bottle reflects the timelessness and quality of this scent created by perfumer Carlos Benaim. This cologne is sure to draw compliments in any environment.', 100, 731400.0, 731400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_dunhill_perfumes_icon_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(304, 'Dize Home Patchouli Hair Mist', 'The fragrance contains the aroma of dry woods with unique depth and elegance to boost the fragranceÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s formula.
