It will always be the perfect fragrance for your special occasions.', 50, 1304100.0, 1304100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6281074756015-dize-home-_-_-_-_-_.png'),
(86, 'Cartier L'' Heure Brillante VI EDP', 'Launched in 2009, VI L'' Heure Brillante is an Aromatic fragrance created for both men and women by Cartier''s in-house perfumer Mathilde Laurent. Cartierâ€™s Les Heures de Parfum is a collection of olfactory moments capturing pure emotion. These high perfumery fragrances focus on only the most sophisticated of senses and materials. At dawn, everything seems new, fresh and joyful. Radiant and smiling, a soft light brightens the sky. A moment of pure emotion to keep with you, in bundles of lemon, gin, aldehydes.', 75, 7458900.0, 7458900.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(121, 'IL Profvmo Silvana EDP', 'A new adventure of your life that is full of excitement.
A soft floral composition for both men and women delivers a seductive scent to boost your feelings of entertainment.
