It''s professionally-designed to suit both men and women for all your special days and occasions.', 100, 4761000.0, 4761000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(16, 'Al Majed for Oud Shtha Alward EDP', 'It shows the beauty of your pretty soul on all occasions
