(59, 'Dunhill Desire Blue Ocean', 'First released in 2018, Desire Blue Ocean is a smooth and well-textured scent. This aquatic and minty male fragrance brings to mind the sensation of open-air and water. Heart notes of sea breeze and orange refreshingly harmonize with top notes of lime and peppermint over an aromatic and woody base of vetiver and patchouli. This warm, fresh and spicy blend will rise throughout the day due to your body warmth and is an ideal complement to spring and summer outdoor activities. The base notes also include hints of ambroxan, a musk-like aroma reminiscent of tobacco and clean laundry, along with tonka bean, a cinnamon-like essence that evokes almond and vanilla.', 100, 2380500.0, 2380500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/5/85715801906_dunhill_desire_blue_ocean_edt_100_ml.jpg'),
