(3, 'Yves Saint Laurent Mon Paris', 'A new perfume came with an expression of love today, inspired by the city of lovers - Paris. The amazing scent opens with Calabria bergamot, strawberry, raspberry and pear. A flowory heart includes a bouquet of peony, Chinese and Sambac jasmine and orange blossom. Finaly base notes are white musk, ambroxan and an intense patchouli.', 50, 2822100.0, 2822100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_yves_saint_laurant_perfumes_mon_paris_for_her_eau_de_parfum.jpg'),
(37, 'Chanel Coco Noir', 'An exceptional and wonderful fragrance that contains a great deal of excitement and elegance and transports you to a fictional world with its incredible scent, and combines the experiences of luxurious aromatherapy with its sparkling oriental touch and a mix of charm and mystery, with a blend of bergamot, vanilla, and white musk.', 50, 3739800.0, 3739800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chanel-coco-noir.jpg'),
