(168, 'Jimmy Choo Flash', 'Flash is constructed as a fragrance which accentuates delicate white flower notes with a hint of spices and fruit. Top notes encompass passionate strawberry combined with tangerine and pink pepper adding exciting and cheerful note to white floral notes in the heart. The white bouquet is composed of tuberose, jasmine and white lily on a base of heliotrope and blond wood.', 60, 2373600.0, 2373600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/i/jimmy_choo_flash_edp.jpg'),
(23, 'Dukhoon Alshuyukh Set', 'This set contains:
Remal Taif Rose Bakhoor - 60 gm
