(18, 'Penhaligon''s The Revenge of Lady Blanche', 'Penhaligon''s The Revenge of Lady Blanche is a floral fragrance designed for women who love a combination of spicy, floral, and woody scent. This Eau de Parfum features powdery orris, narcissus flower, and hyacinth.', 75, 8355900.0, 8355900.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
