About the Brand:
Kilian is a famous eco-friendly fragrance brand founded in Paris, created by Kilian Hennessy. It is featured by the production of luxury goods, and its fragrances are distinguished by their unique and distinctive designs. The company is interested in the environment and sustainability through the use of refillable and reusable packaging. Her fragrances were released in collaboration with the most talented perfume designers.', 50, 8818200.0, 8818200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/7/3700550218203-kilian-kilian-good-girl-gone-bad-extreme-_w_-edp-50-ml-refillable.png'),
