(43, 'Alkhuraiji Soma White Lotus Room Spray ', 'A natural unique scent for your house, office and car. The fragrance adds a personal touch to the place, keeping the air refreshed. Made of rare components, the composition helps keep you relaxed and comfortable.', 100, 241500.0, 241500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6281074743732-alkhuraiji-soma-white-lotus-room-spray-250ml-1.png'),
(168, 'Jimmy Choo Jimmy Choo', 'Imagine womankind, elegance, and style - bottled. Expressing the glory of strength, beauty, charm, and dependability, it is inspired by newfangled women. Jimmy Choo Eau de Parfum has illuminating green top notes, a heart of wealthy and exotic tiger orchid, and permanent sensational base notes of surgery toffee and Indonesian patchouli give a sensual memory on the skin.', 60, 1414500.0, 1414500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/2/82_jimmy_choo_jimmy_choo_edp_women.jpg'),
(156, 'Victoria''s Secret Bombshell', 'Victoria''s Secret Bombshell is a parfume for women, described by the scent of fruits, orchids, vanilla and passion. The parfume is said to be an eye-catching parfume, Bombshell was developed by skilled parfumers known for crafting some of the most exciting parfumes in the world.', 100, 3270600.0, 3270600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_victoria_secret_perfumes_bomb_shell_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 358', 'Let the tous le jours Perfume Day 358 perfume reacts with your body and emits a seductive and acidulated scent! The fusion is overwhelmed by spellbinding scents of Honeysuckle, Almonds, and Vanilla, performing in harmony. The result is a tingling sensation that will capture your senses and never let go!', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000358-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-358-1.png'),
(71, 'Hermes Eau de Rhubarbe Ecarlate', 'This attractive unisex fragrance is bold and fresh. Its velvet-smooth composition has notes of rhubarb, mixed with red berries and white musk, giving you an irresistable scent that energizes you and boosts your charismatic character, wherever you go to attract the eyes towards your vitality.', 100, 4416000.0, 4416000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346132003531-hermes-hermes-eau-de-rhubarbe-ecarlate-_u_-edc-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(136, 'Salvatore Ferragamo Incense Suede EDP', 'A classic, luxurious, creamy, strong, and intense perfume.
The aromatic blend of leather and saffron immerses you in a glowing and attractive scent.
This fragrance is designed for men and women with refined taste, with its irresistible luxury and sophistication.
It is a new experience rich in details of elegance and sophistication that gives you a unique appeal.', 75, 4298700.0, 4298700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8034097957659-salvatore-ferragamo-salvatore-ferragamo-tuscan-scent-incense-suede-_u_-edp-75-ml.png'),
(154, 'L''Arc Memoire Carnet De Voyage', 'Experience an amazing fragrantic journey where you pick a fruit from every tree with this oriental-spicy scent. The fascinating blend of bergamot, saffron and rose along with musk will boost your spirits during the experience that you will never forget.', 100, 4250400.0, 4250400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_l_arc_perfumes_memoire_carnet_de_voyage_for_unisex_eau_de_perfum_3770007220059.jpg'),
(20, 'Givenchy Organza', 'Organza is a magical mix of classical sensuality, delicacy and warmth, a hymn to eternal beauty possessed by every woman. An attractive bottle designed by Serge Manseau is the embodiment of virtues of this fragrance, which is oriental-floral, warm and sweet. It is composed of intoxicating notes of opulent white flowers: gardenia, tuberose and jasmine. The combination is incredibly exciting; soft vanilla in the base tames the voluptuous luxuriance of the floral heart.', 100, 2332200.0, 2332200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/i/givenchy_organza_edp.jpg'),
(208, 'Lootah Suave EDP', 'Enjoy all of your occasions with an irresistible presence, thanks to the distinctive Suave perfume from the Lootah perfume collection
The secret of the fragrance''s brilliance lies in the mixture of refreshing citrus scents, which occupies a special place in the perfume industry
With a blend of lemon and bergamot that reveals the floral heart of the gardenia with a charming scent
This blend also includes sandalwood, which leaves behind a luxurious trail.', 80, 2415000.0, 2415000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6297000836966-lootah-lootah-suave-eau-de-parfum-80-ml.png'),
(355, 'Les Eaux Primordiales Superfluide Ambre EDP', 'A perfect fragrance for both men and women.
Like the aroma of apple pie, cinnamon, and gingerbread, notes of amber, spice and honey add warmth to this moment.
The harmony of rum and tobacco imparts a sweet flavor to the fragrance.
This attractive combination will captivate you and become your favorite companion at all times.', 100, 8707800.0, 8707800.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(33, 'Lacoste Pour Femme LÃƒÂ©gÃƒÂ¨re', 'Feel the joy of life and stay confident with this woody floral fragrance that is designed for the unusal woman. The radiant notes of bergamot, jasmine petals and musk will spread the positive energy everywhere you go, unveiling all the freshness.', 90, 1083300.0, 1083300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_lacoste_perfumes_pour_femme_l_g_re_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(255, 'Shakespeare Macbeth EDP', 'Unknown', 100, 3926100.0, 3926100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/0/3015285288583-shakespeare-perfume-shakespeare--macbeth-edp-spray-100ml.png'),
(244, 'Creed Rose Imperiale', 'This perfume was created to remember the elegance and grandeur of classical Europe and the gilded crowns, thrones, and triumphs of extraordinary monarchs. This luxurious scent is a tribute to the noble rose and its countless devotees throughout history. It has a beautiful, long-lasting blend full of natural ingredients.', 75, 7141500.0, 7141500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/5/3508441104778-creed-creed-rose-imperiale-_w_-edp-75-ml.jpg'),
(358, 'Maison Rebatchi Bois D'' Enfants EDP', 'A childhood memory of running through the mysterious dense forest.
A fragrance that represents a child spending his summer days between fun adventures and playing around freely with a desire to discover the world around him.
The strong and complex fragrance blend immerses you in a glowing and sexy scent to boost your attractive and elegant look.
A soft floral scent that contrasts with the fresh aroma of bergamot and spicy pepper.
About the Brand:
Maison Rebatchi is a distinctive brand of luxury perfumes and fragrances designed in an elegant French style with the finest aromatic natural ingredients. It was launched in 2018, by Mohamed Rebatchi, who was inspired by his Morrocan origins.', 100, 3415500.0, 3415500.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(141, 'Moschino Fresh Couture Gold Gift Set ', 'It''s a four-piece gift set that features EDP (100ml), Body lotion (100ml), shower gel (100ml) and a pouch. A floral fresh fragrance for woman that accentuates your femininity with long-lasting effect. The composition has notes of pear in the top, orchid in the middle and musk in the base, releasing an attractive scent that draws the attention toward your presence.', 100, 2477100.0, 2477100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8011003844395-moschino-moschino-fresh-couture-gold-_w_-edp-100-ml-body-lotion-100-ml-_-shower-gel-100-ml-_-pouch-gift-set-4-piece_2.jpg'),
(76, 'Thierry Mugler Alien Mirage', 'It''s radiating with light and an ode to the creative strength of each and every woman, like a new invitation to all that is new and perfect. The fresh and surprising perfume was inspired by the vastness of a scorching desert, and a mirage entertain us with its freshness after a storm, giving life to an extraordinary flower bearing a message of hope.', 60, 2953200.0, 2953200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/4/3439600048414-thierry-mugler-thierry-mugler-alien-mirage-_w_-edt-60-ml.jpg'),
(4, 'Mancera Coco Vanille', 'this soft floral fragrance for women and women is your perfect choice for everyday use. its notes are blended together very carefully to give you warm sensations when you wear it. You will fall in love with this masterpiece.', 120, 2753100.0, 2753100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_mancera_perfumes_coco_vanille_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(207, 'Junaid Perfumes Nashmah EDP', 'Your daring masculine look narrates the scene and gets you the attention.
Your days become more beautiful with the soft creamy notes of woods, which fill your moments with excitement.
Enjoy the fresh sea notes in the very first moments to keep you revitalized.
The notes of nutmeg are blended with warmth of patchouli, delivering a sensual captivating scent.', 75, 1000500.0, 1000500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/0/6084001494444-junaid-nashmah-edp-75-ml.png'),
(379, 'Lucien Ferrero Maitre Parfumeur Pour Elle EDP', 'Unknown', 100, 6348000.0, 6348000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(203, 'Vertus 1001 EDP', 'It looks like a dream journey to the Arabian lands where you listen to the tales of the Thousand and One Nights.
A soft sensual floral note of mimosa and carnation with the pure aroma of Mongolia emanates from the heart of the fragrance.
The heart of the fragrance is enveloped with spicy and bright beginnings and ends with saffron and cardamom that feature oriental scents.
Amber notes add a charm to the scent in order to increase your sense of confidence till the last moments of the day.', 100, 5313000.0, 5313000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 72', 'It''s a floral fragrance that fills your soul with vitality and freshness. The top notes of melon, come on a heart of geranium and base of musk, releasing a scent with a delicate composition that attracts everyone toward the soft touch it leaves around.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000072-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours---perfume-day-72-1.png'),
(348, 'Goutal Paris Ã‰toile d''Une Nuit EDP', 'The fragrance reveals your beauty and lets your soul embrace the mysterious moments of the night
