The fragrance is filled with notes of raspberry to satisfy the desire of women who are coming and looking for the highest levels of charm
The roses reflect the smallest details of attractiveness and help you enjoy all the moments of romance', 100, 5789100.0, 5789100.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(117, 'Thameen Fragrance Amber Room', 'This oriental fragrance is inspired by the trapped sunshine and fiery gold. It''s glowing, warm and smoky. The composition combines notes of bergamot, grapefruit and patchouli, delivering a seductive scent that fills your heart with love and joy.', 50, 5209500.0, 5209500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/2/724120095653-thameen-thameen-amber-room-_u_-edp-50-ml.jpg'),
(71, 'Hermes Jour D''Absolu', 'Hermes Jour D''Hermes Absolu is a floral statement. A combination of flowers portrays the sensuality of gardenia and Sambac jasmine, underscored by velvety notes of apricot blossom.', 85, 4802400.0, 4802400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/e/hermes_jour_dhermes_absolu.jpg'),
(86, 'Cartier III L''heure Vertueuse', 'Released in 2012, III L''Heure Vertueuse by Cartier is a perfume for both women and men, which is famous for its green-spicy scent. III L''heure Vertueuse will walk you through a magic garden, to inhale the enchanting perfumes of miraculous plants. It offers you an aromatic caress of the fresh, gentle green notes of sweet lavender, citrusy verbena, earthy thyme, and woodsy rosemary. This Eau de Parfum comes in a simple transparent falcon that unveils a green liquid of magnificent aroma. A fresh and fruity scent that uplifts your outfit to new levels.', 75, 7458900.0, 7458900.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(16, 'Al Majed for Oud Rasmi Orient EDP', 'Quiet and pure perfume, with soft oriental notes of Frankincense
French lavender notes enhance the beauty and attractiveness of the scent
The fragrance includes new European notes of woods that make you beautiful and unique
The long- lasting fragrance embodies the meaning of beauty and excitement in your soul
About the Brand:
Al Majed For Oud Company was established in 1956 AD to establish a promising market in the field of oud trade through the wholesale sector by culminating in more than 60 years of experience in the manufacture of oud and perfumes. Their preparations across the Gulf market, by creating and innovating new aromatic lines have contributed in expanding their customer base and heading to the retail trade to reach more than 160 sales platforms in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia and the Gulf countries.', 50, 1269600.0, 1269600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6285091001301-2179-_-_-_-_.png'),
(275, 'Fly Falcon Pure Touch EDP', 'This fragrance embodies your immortal masculinity and charming look with a beautiful composition.
A new experience with rare precious notes to fill you with a glowing scent.
Enjoy your moments and details of the day with the aromatic fragrance that spreads around and captivates the hearts.
It''s the best choice for those men who seek distinction in all their occasions.', 60, 1200600.0, 1200600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/4/3458575954216-fly-falcon-fly-falcon-pure-touch-homme-_m_-edp-60-ml.png'),
(12, 'Marly Darcy', 'This stunning floral fragrance increases your natural beauty with its sensual and delicate aroma that gives attractive and vitality look at all your special occasions.', 75, 7935000.0, 7935000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(38, 'Elie Saab Le Parfum Resort Collection', 'A floral fruity and solar fragrance. Inspired by the Elie Saab Ready-To-Wear RESORT Collections, the new Elie Saab edition is the promise of an escapade in the Mediterranean. This is a springtime reinterpretation of the Elie Saab Orange Flower signature enhanced with a sweet and gourmand Fig. The top note of a sweet Fig and a Mandarin zest adds a delicious and fresh sensation. In the heart note, the white and luminous Bouquet of the original fragrance signature is enriched by a solar Frangipani Flower. The base note of Cedar and Amber gives elegance and sensuality to the fragrance trail.', 50, 3174000.0, 3174000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_elie_saab_perfumes_le_parfum_resort_collection_for_women_eau_de_parfum.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 39', 'This fragrance is inspired by the charm of the orient. The composition has upper notes of tangerine, middle notes of rose, and base notes of musk, revealing a marvelous scent for those with special tastes who take challenges boldly, impressing everyone there.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000039-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours---perfume-day-39-1.png'),
(74, 'Davidoff Zino', 'A wonderful oriental woody fragrance, which takes you to another world with its charm and attractiveness, with a great mix of lavender, jasmine, and vanilla.
About the brand
Davidoff has received acclaim since it introduced its first fragrance in 1988. The brand was founded in Switzerland and has been known for luxurious accessories like watches and leather goods. It offered popular fragrances for men and women.', 125, 655500.0, 655500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/a/davidoff_zino_edt_125_ml.jpg'),
(244, 'Creed Royal Mayfair', 'Introduced in 2015, Royal Mayfair is a fruity, floral fragrance that was created for men and women. Named after the posh, London neighborhood of Mayfair, this gourmand scent is a fresh and imaginative experience. This original scent was a bespoke creation for the Duke of Windsor; however, 80 years after the original was made, it is now available to you. The top notes are composed of gin, lime and pine tree. The heart centers around the perfect floral experience of a rose. The base notes finish with orange, cedar, and eucalyptus.', 120, 9377100.0, 9377100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_creed_perfumes_royal_mayfair_for_men_eau_de_parfum.jpg'),
(244, 'Creed Spice And Wood', 'The second product from its Royal Exclusives line, Spice and Wood by Creed was released in 2010. This unisex fragrance is noble and powerful, making it ideal for evening and formal wear. Like its name, this scent is spicy and woody with a hint of velvety sweetness. It opens with a tantalizing mix of apple, bergamot, and lemon. A deep richness is exuded from its heart of angelic root, vetiver, patchouli, and cloves. The essence of alive and glorious woods soon seeps in with notes of cedarwood, oakmoss, and musk..', 75, 19602900.0, 19602900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_creed_perfumes_spice_and_wood_for_men_eau_de_perfum_3508440752024_1st.jpg'),
(317, 'Estee Lauder Pleasures', 'Start your day with absolute vitality with the attractive blend of refreshing masculine fragrance that is rich with water and green notes with touches of perfumed floral scents and glowing peppercorns that open the door to prospect and give you the energy needed to achieve all your daily tasks with success. The perfume is also your perfect companion in special evenings and nights with an ever-lasting scent.
About the Brand:
Estee Lauder is an American company founded in 1946 in New York City. Mrs. Lauder gained early experience in the skincare and cosmetics industry under the patronage of her chemist uncle and skincare specialist. Various wonderful products such as cosmetics and perfumes. The first fragrance by Estee Lauder was announced in 1953.', 100, 2139000.0, 2139000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/7/27131521433-estee-lauder-estee-lauder-pleasures-_m_-edc-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(158, 'Amouage Interlude', 'Amouage Interlude is a woody fragrance for men that was first presented in 2012. A complex, warm, and deep mixture of scents that make you feel elegant and unique. The cologne starts with notes of pimento berry oil, bergamot, and oregano. The heart introduces traditional spices, including frankincense, opoponax, and myrrh, alongside the sweet and warm notes of amber and cistus. The base notes of sandalwood, agarwood smoke, leather, and patchouli create a lasting fragrance and give the cologne a bit more depth. This combination of strong middle eastern scents makes it very long-lasting and intense, which is perfect for special occasions.', 100, 8976900.0, 8976900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_amouage_perfumes_interlude_for_men_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(24, 'Candy Addict Marshmallow Mash Set ', 'A delightful fragrance set, it will immerse your senses in sweet notes of peach juice and marshmallow and will leave you with a pleasant feminine scent all day long.
This set contains:
Candy Addict Marshmallow Mash EDP - 50 ml
Candy Addict Marshmallow Mash Body Mist - 250 ml
Candy Addict Marshmallow Mash Hair Mist - 100 ml
Moisturize, soften and strengthen your hair with Vitamin E, a powerful antioxidant, and Provitamin B5. Give your hair that extra shine and volume that it deserves, whilst leaving your hair less prone to breakage.', 100, 1925100.0, 1925100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/-/c-sb100241-marshmallow-bundle-ar.png'),
(51, 'Al Dakheel Oud D Line Collection ', 'A unique and carefully created set of 4 luxurious fragrances (10 ml each).
Each fragrance has an amazing and distinctive aromatic scent.
Enjoy an attractive and beautiful look with this amazing set of perfumes that will satisfy all your needs.
The set is easy to carry with you everywhere.', 100, 717600.0, 717600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6281150554108-al-dakheel-for-oud-d-line-collection.png'),
(14, 'Maqam Base of Melody EDP ', 'Playing its own melody & exotic oriental beauty, a true creative Arabian fragrance has emerged! Like a well-designed melody, this fragrance releases the most irresistible components gradually & elegantly. As it starts with gentle delicate notes of lavender & nutmeg, it then slowly draws you into a world of deeply earthy warm notes of patchouli & amber.', 120, 2201100.0, 2201100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/a/maqam_base_of_melody-2.png'),
(223, 'Ojar Epine Du Desert EDP', 'A duo of rose and jasmine symbolize iconic beauty.
The floral heart is surrounded with a precious top and base to awaken your feelings.
A warm touch of leather along with sandalwood deliver a touch of elegance to boost your unique look.
The intense perfume oil is for both men and women, providing a glowing aromatic scent.', 15, 1656000.0, 1656000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(244, 'Creed Virgin Island Water', 'Virgin Island Water is an exotic paradise in an aromatic form. The bright, refreshing cologne, released in 2007, brings you all of the delicious aromas of the tropics. The composition starts with a fruity blend of white bergamot, Sicilian mandarin, and Jamaican lime. Tropical copra adds the smooth, milky scent of coconut. The heart is a rich blend of seductive florals. Jasmine, ylang-ylang, and hibiscus add a velvety freshness before being cooled by a spicy jolt of crisp ginger. The sweet base is an irresistible mix of sugar cane, white rum, and musk. Wear this exciting cologne at any time you need a relaxing escape.', 100, 7810800.0, 7810800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/5/3508441001138_creed_virgin_island_water_edp_100_ml_1.jpg'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Acqua di Gioia Essenza EDP', 'Start your day with the spicy freshness of mint and glowing lemon drops.
The lively refreshing blend of the fragrance fills you with a sense of enthusiasm and increases your passion to discover life.
The delicate touches of jasmine add some softness and sophistication to the scent.
The fragrance composition is soft, feminine, and attractive, with sugar granules at the ends that make it more seductive.', 50, 2449500.0, 2449500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3605521475343-giorgio-armani-giorgio-armani-acqua-di-gioia-essenza-_w_-edp-intense-50-ml.png'),
(59, 'Dunhil Icon Elite', 'A masculine sporty fragrance to offer freshness and energy, so that you can exert more effort and feel more active. It is one of the most common scents in London. Spry it and enjoy each single momnt of your life.', 100, 1235100.0, 1235100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_dunhil_perfumes_icon_elite_for_men_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(350, 'Arquiste The Architects Club EDP', 'Dark amber drops settle on the surface of precious woods that look like the dusk descends on the grounds of London in the 1930s.
The harmony of amber and wood surrounds the gathering of the architects responsible for Mayfair''s decorations.
The freshness of the fragrance is coming from the lemon drops accompanied by the delicious notes of bitter orange.
