(81, 'Mabkharat Alemarat Frankincense Lavender ', 'This Incense is made from the finest types of Arabic frankincense mixed with pure aromatic oil of wonderful lavender flower, for a long-lasting, wonderful scent that inspires feelings of joy and happiness within everyone.', 100, 655500.0, 655500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006907531_mabkharat_alemarat_-_frankincense_lavender_1.jpg'),
