(37, 'Chanel Allure Aftershave Lotion ', 'This aftershave moisturizing lotion provides softness to the skin with a fresh scent. The quick-absorbing non-greasy lotion helps reduce roughness caused by the razor providing hydration. It has notes of mandarin and coriander to deliver real freshness that lasts for a long time.
