(71, 'Hermes Concentre de Pamplemousse Rose', 'It''s an aromatic citrus fragrance that combines a classical approach. The distinctive composition contains notes of grapefruit and rose, blended with vetiver, providing you with a refreshing and lively scent with a long-lasting effect for your long summer day.', 100, 4098600.0, 4098600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346132000608-hermes-concentre-de-pamplemousse-rose-_u_-edt-100-ml-1.jpg'),
