(42, 'Nasomatto Pardon', 'A woody fragrance for men with a deep and strong masculine scent suitable for evening use, it changes negative feelings into positive ones to make you smile and feeling free to charm those around you with your elegance and happiness.', 30, 4609200.0, 4609200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_nasomatto_perfumes_pardon_for_men_extrait_de_parfum_perfume.jpg'),
(110, 'Trussardi Black Extreme', 'Trussardi Black Extreme is a scent for modern, successful men always in pursuit of powerful experiences. The product features the spirit of belonging meld with the elegant, timeless design to convey TrussardiÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s excellence in its field and premium Italian quality.', 100, 1159200.0, 1159200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_trussardi_perfumes_black_extreme_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(32, 'Guerlain Homme Guerlain Intense', 'Guerlain Homme Guerlain Intense is an aromatic fragrance for men. It appears as an upgraded version of the classical Homme Guerlain. The dualism between man and nature is depicted in this fragrance through the blend of different notes. Green aromas of mint, narcotic rum and rhubarb leaves are accentuated in the opening notes. The heart of the fragrance is an aromatic bouquet of geranium, enveloped in a base of patchouli, cedar and vetiver. The most complex and intense fragrance of the Homme Guerlain line, it combines several notes and accords giving it the amazing aroma it has.', 80, 2387400.0, 2387400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_guerlain_perfumes_homme_guerlain_intense_for_men_eau_de_perfum_1.jpg'),
(158, 'Amouage Memoir', 'Feel at one with nature with Amouage Memoir, a powerful menÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s fragrance by Amouage. A masterful blend of woody, spicy and green accords, this attractive cologne is a gem to have in your collection. Top notes of mint, basil and wormwood bring a sharp, refreshing vibe to the mix while the middle notes of rose, incense, and lavender lower the intensity with their soothing, heady scents. Base notes of guaiac wood, oakmoss, sandalwood, tobacco, leather, vanilla, and warm amber combine some of the richest elements in nature to enhance the fragrance with their sensual and masculine touch.', 100, 8976900.0, 8976900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_amouage_perfumes_memoir_for_men_eau_de_perfum_701666313922.jpg'),
(244, 'Creed Spring Flower', 'Stop and smell the roses with Spring Flower fragrance by Creed. This perfume is a fresh bouquet of femininity. With base notes of luxurious ambergris and warm and woody musk, you enjoy a deep feeling of contentment. Rose and jasmine blend together for a romantic splash of sun. Next, the fragrance tops its signature scent with notes of melon, peach, and apple that caress you like a cool breeze. Floral, fresh fruity, and delightful; that is all you need for kick starting your day.', 75, 10356900.0, 10356900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/5/3508441104563_creed_spring_flower_edp_75_ml_1.jpg'),
(335, 'Majda Bekkali J''ai Fait Un Re''ve Obscur', 'This oriental unisex fragrance in inpired by that wonderful portrait that depicts the love of life. The nice composition of jasmine, bergamot and oud will boost your self-confidence at any time of the day.', 120, 7065600.0, 7065600.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(150, 'Hayari Goldy', 'Hayari Goldy symbolizes the French-style luxury and mesmerizes with its top notes of rosemary and mugwort herb; heart notes of narcissus, jasmine; and base notes of musk, cedarwood, and sandalwood. This perfume strikes a perfect balance between extravagance and refinement.', 100, 5520000.0, 5520000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_hayari_perfumes_goldy_for_women_eau_de_perfum_3700675100056.jpg'),
(235, 'V Canto Curaro Extrait de Parfum', 'A distinctive fragrance belonging to the family of luxurious woody notes.
