The fragrance is based on a special base of patchouli, Cambodian oud, benzoin, vanilla, orris root, and cedarwood.', 100, 9880800.0, 9880800.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(20, 'Givenchy Very Irresistible', 'Very Irresistible is an exhilarating perfume that combines a plethora of rose notes mixed with green and aromatic accords for a delightful and luminous scent thatÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s sure to draw attention your way, no matter where you go. Top notes of zesty lemon verbena, crisp cassia leaf, and exotic star anise introduce the aroma with a bright, revitalizing atmosphere. Meanwhile, heart notes of flirty pink peony, rich magnolia, and various elegant rose essences take center stage with their lavish floral bouquet. Finally, the base note of vibrant taif rose wraps the entire perfume in more luxurious, feminine sophistication for a dazzling and enticing fragrance that works perfectly as a warm-weather accessory.', 50, 3788100.0, 3788100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/i/givenchy_very_irresistible_eau_de_parfum_1.jpg'),
