(102, 'The Different Company De Bachmakov Refill ', 'This kind of comfortable perfume diffuses a vibrant and strong scent that can imbue your senses and your spirit! The Different Company De Bachmakov astonishes you with its vintage spirit and evokes strong emotions and sweet memories that allow you to wear it with confidence. Celine Ellena has crafted this composition with tart freshness, starting from bergamot, coriander, and fig at the top. Shiso, freesia, and nutmeg are fused at the heart with delicacy and sensuality to grab your attention. Stay on track till the base reveals the beauty and the best of what the fragrance can offer in the form of cedar and amber. You wonâ€™t stop sniffing!', 100, 4112400.0, 4112400.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
