The fragrance fills you with strong freshness, making your look the best wherever you go.', 15, 1656000.0, 1656000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3665032001059-ojar-eau-de-parfum---flower-beast-15ml.png'),
(44, 'Bvlgari Pour Homme Gift Set EDT 100 ml + After Shave 100 ml + Pouch ', 'Pour Homme Gift Set EDT 100 ml + After Shave 100 ml + Pouch - 3 Pieces
