(40, 'Tom Ford Soleil Blanc', 'It is an unexpected, sultry, and addictive solar floral scent. It evokes remote private islands where summer lasts all year. The top note of this unisex fragrance combines spicy notes of cardamom and pink pepper with a hint of pistachio and bergamot. The flowery sensuality of ylang-ylang, Egyptian jasmine, and tuberose is placed in the heart of the fragrance for carnal intensity. Benzoin (a herbal substance contained in the oil of bitter almonds), amber, tonka bean, and coconut milk form the luxurious base. It is available in a 100ml bottle.', 100, 7617600.0, 7617600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066048873-tom-ford-tom-ford-soleil-blanc-_u_-edp-100-ml-1.jpg'),
