(18, 'Penhaligon''s Kensington Amber', 'Enjoy a light and gentle walk in the streets of the ancient West of London with its charming buildings and embassies coated in a soft cream color with this perfume combination rich in the scents of labdanum and spicy cinnamon particles with tonka beans and bergamot, which gives you a touch of freshness and unique vitality with A strong start that fits all moments of the day and night. It was perfectly designed to suit both men and women as it was launched in 2018.', 100, 5368200.0, 5368200.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
