(59, 'Dunhill Icon Absolute', 'Dunhill Icon Absolute is a modern scent that captures the timeless cool of masculinity. Bergamot and black pepper awaken the senses with a citrusy spice that is natural and exciting. Notes of jasmine, saffron, and black rose blend into a floral bouquet that adds an air of lightness and virility. Base notes oud, tobacco leaf, and leather create a playground of sophistication for the entire aroma to socialize. Dunhill Icon Absolute is a new fragrance that was launched in 2015. The heavy metal gold container permeates an aura of sophistication and class that are matched only by the scents contained within.', 100, 1524900.0, 1524900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_dunhill_perfumes_icon_absolute_for_men_eau_de_parfum.jpg'),
(122, 'Emanuel Ungaro Ungaro Pour L''Homme', 'Ungaro Pour LÃ¢â‚¬â„¢Homme by Emanuel Ungaro is a perfume specially crafted for men. It was launched in the year 1993. The top notes have accords of orange, mahogany, lemon, sage, coriander, lavender, and vodka. The heart notes are lily-of-the-valley, jasmine, geranium, and rose. Base notes are patchouli, musk, oakmoss, vetiver, cedar, and sandalwood.', 100, 855600.0, 855600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/e/m/emanuel_ungaro_ungaro_pour_l_homme_edt_100ml.jpg'),
(186, 'Floris London Chypress EDT', 'A unique floral fragrance that is perfect for both men and women.
