(91, 'Tommy Hilfiger Tommy Girl', 'Tommy Hilfiger parfume for Women has a Fresh and lively scent with black currant, mandarin orange and apple tree blossom, as top notes. The Middle notes include honeysuckle, violet lily, mint, grapefruit, lemon and rose. Base notes are leather, sandalwood and jasmine.', 100, 1159200.0, 1159200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_tommy_hilfiger_perfumes_tommy_girl_for_women_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Beau De Jour All Over Body Spray ', 'The notes of amber, woods and musk are blended together to boost your masculinity.
