(244, 'Creed Viking', 'Celebrate your power with Viking Eau de Parfum for the fearless and fiery modern man. This bold men''s fragrance combines fresh citrus notes of Calabrian bergamot and Sicilian lemon with pink peppercorn, Bulgarian rose, and peppermint. Woody base notes of Indian sandalwood and Haitian vetiver complete this masculine masterpiece.', 50, 14400300.0, 14400300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/5/3508441001169_creed_viking_100_ml_eau_de_perfum_men.png'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Patchouli Absolu', 'Tom Ford Patchouli Absolu parfume is one of the beloved new fragrances of patchouli. The production of this parfume transforms raw materials famous for their rich and mysterious sensitivity and long history in parfumery industry into a modern parfume. The parfume is for both men and women.', 50, 7617600.0, 7617600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_tom_ford_perfumes_patchouli_absolu_for_unisex_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(223, 'Ojar Mahrajan EDP', 'The touch of Turkish rose narrate a new story of softness and freshness.
Enjoy the scents of mimosa and delicate rose, blended with spicy carnation, which deliver an aromatic scent.
