(45, 'Coach Platinum', 'Inspired by the classic All-American road trip, Coach Platinum is a dynamic new scent that was launched in the summer of 2018. Created by perfumer Bruno Jovanovic, this fragrance appeals to the modern adventurer who is unafraid of where the highway may lead him. Top notes of pineapple, juniper berries, and black pepper provide a refreshing opening. Heart notes of geranium and floral sage combine with masculine base notes of leather, sandalwood, patchouli, and cashmere to create a warmly sensual scent. The fragrance is offered in an iconic mirrored silver bottle featuring the manufacturerÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s famous horse and carriage logo and a leather hangtag charm.', 100, 2063100.0, 2063100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_coach_perfumes_platinum_edp_100_ml_for_men_3386460096867.jpg'),
