(73, 'Tous Les Jours Mardi', 'Mardi 100 ML is an Eau de Parfum For Men and Women from Tous Les Jours which encapsulates the feelings of happiness and nostalgia with top notes of Bergamot, Heliotrope, Cumin that will grab your attention immediately, then the heart notes of Jasmine, Bitter Almond, Lavender that will take control representing the essence of the perfume to leave you in the end with the base notes of Amber, Vanilla, Sandalwood that will linger with you far beyond that.', 100, 1373100.0, 1373100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006903724_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_mardi_100_ml_tayamun_1.jpg'),
(297, 'David Kasab Elora EDP', 'A new adventure of lemon and bergamot fragrances that express the events of a life full of excitement
Go through all your days with this refreshing formula that rejuvenates you.
