(30, 'The Oud Set', 'This set includes:
The Finest Oud - 100 ml
"Warm, deep and rich"
A fragrant blend with endless creativity! Rich in its luxurious oriental Oud, deep thanks to its amber and musky notes, and warm with its woody notes, cashmere, and guaiac. This distinctive aromatic fragrance will not leave your side, as it lasts for long hours, and brings out a harmonious & beautiful Oud scent.p>
Kun Safi Oud Safi - 1.7 Tola / 20g
Ã¢â‚¬Å“Discover Oud.. Discover the Oriental charismaÃ¢â‚¬Â
Pure Luxurious perfume oil extracted from the finest Agarwood, granting you an authentic scent of Arabian charm. This oil was designed for unique perfumes collectors, to enjoy both Oud intensity and modern design. The modern tola bottle features an advanced technique, with a twist & apply cap ensuring accurate and smooth oil applying. Every aspect of this oil was created to guarantee a mesmerizing Oud experience, waiting for you to unleash it!', 100, 2270100.0, 2270100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/b/sb100253_exclusive_bundles_the_oud_set_-_edp_100_ml_perfume_oil_1.7_tola___20g.png'),
(276, 'Eutopie No 7 EDP', 'In honor of the pure soul and elegant look on all occasions.
A vital composition with notes of galbanum and mimosa blended in harmony.
The base has notes of musk and amber, adding a unique touch to your look.
The pure white floral heart has notes of jasmine and freesia to evoke your feelings.', 100, 4498800.0, 4498800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/7/3760224770147-eutopie-eutopie-eutopie-no.-7-_u_-edp-100-ml.png'),
(189, 'Solinotes Fleur De Orange EDP', 'A symbol of vitality and freshness that renews your enthusiasm at the beginning of each day.
Start all your busy days with the gentle breeze of orange blossoms.
This powerful intense fragrance contains a fresh orange blossom scent that stays with you for long hours.
The strength and stability of the scent are the secret to gaining a sense of confidence and strength within you all the time.', 50, 338100.0, 338100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3379501481166-solinotes-solinotes-fl.eur-de-oranger-edp-50ml.png'),
(128, 'J. Del Pozo Mystic Leather Nights', 'Mystic Leather Nights J. Del Pozo designed by the famous Spanish fashion house, J. Del Pozo, is a parfume for unisex. This snug parfume is related to the hot oriental house. The parfume was released in 2017.', 100, 3691500.0, 3691500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/_/j.del_pozo_mystic_leather_night_edp_100_ml_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(27, 'Gucci Memoire D''une Odeur ', 'Ã™ÂA universal perfume that is unassigned with gender or time. This fragrance contains Roman chamomile and Indian coral jasmine petals for tenderness, precious musks for depth, while the noble woods spread the warmth.', 60, 2408100.0, 2408100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614225307553_gucci_memoire_d_une_odeur_edp_100_ml_1.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Nahawand', 'Nahawand 100 ML is an Eau de Parfum For Men and Women from Tous Les Jours which encapsulates the feelings of relaxation and quietness with top notes of Pear, Fruits, Pink Pepper that will grab your attention immediately, then the heart notes of Tonka, Jasmine, Roses that will take control representing the essence of the perfume to leave you in the end with the base notes of Heliotrope, Jasmine, Rose, Musk, Sugar that will linger with you far beyond that.', 100, 1511100.0, 1511100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006900570_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_nahawand_100_ml_tayamun_1.jpg'),
(33, 'Lacoste Eau De Lacoste L.12.12 Noire', 'Lacoste is a French company, established in 1933 by tennis players RenÃ© Lacoste and AndrÃ© Gillier. Its green crocodile logo refers to the nickname of RenÃ© Lacoste, who was nicknamed "the Crocodile" by his fans, because of his tenacity on the tennis court. The company is committed to designing products that combine discovery, excellence, and style. It sells parfumes, clothing, leather goods, towels, footwear, sportswear, eyewear, and watches.', 100, 1297200.0, 1297200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/a/lacoste-eau-de-lacoste-l-12-12-noire.jpg'),
(373, 'The Merchant of Venice Suave Petals Murano Collection EDP', '#NAME?', 100, 5002500.0, 5002500.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(357, 'Les Parfums de Rosine Ballerina NÂ°3', 'Les Parfums de Rosine Ballerina NÂ°3 the floral, woody and sensual perfume for women. Its one of the best releases from Les Parfums de Rosine, It an elegant, rich, luxurious, deep and it well blended scent.', 100, 4795500.0, 4795500.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(214, 'Liz Claiborne Curve Wave Pour Homme EDC', 'Aromatic-aquatic perfume for men of refined taste.
A refreshing summer fragrance enriched with a wonderful aromatic blend that accompanies you throughout the day with full vitality and energy.
The fragrance contains notes of liquid oxygen, citruses, mint, blue anise, and lime.
This charming combination gives you a very elegant and attractive look.
This distinctive fragrance reminds us of the hot sea air.
About the Brand:
Anne Elizabeth Jane Claiborne, better known as Liz Claiborne, is an American fashion designer and businesswoman whose success has been built on affordable, elegant clothing for working women.', 125, 855600.0, 855600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/9/8/98691030482-liz-claiborne-liz-claiborne-curve-wave-pour-homme-_m_-cologne-125-ml.png'),
(244, 'Creed Sublime Vanille', 'Sublime Vanille is a vanilla fragrance with hints of citrus. It begins with the highest quality bourbon vanilla and vanilla orchid. Tonka bean sits at the heart of this carefully-crafted perfume, while lemon, bergamot, and musk form the base notes. This high-end fragrance has moderate sillage and high longevity, making it a great choice for all-day wear. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s fresh and sweet without being overly sugary or offensive. Wear it to the office, for an evening out, or a casual weekend with friends and family. This uplifting, adaptable scent pairs well with any outfit and can be dressed up or down.', 75, 19602900.0, 19602900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_creed_perfumes_sublime_vanille_for_women_eau_de_perfum_3508440752017_1st.jpg'),
(155, 'Loewe Aura EDP', 'The fragrance gives you a feminine look, and highlights your confidence all day long.
The fragrance is a combination of natural ingredients.
The fragrance opens with refreshing notes of pink pepper, red currant, violet and bergamot.
The heart of the fragrance contains rose, iris, jasmine and narcissus.
The fragrance ends with a mixture of sandalwood, leather, cedarwood and berries.', 120, 2504700.0, 2504700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/4/8426017040631-loewe-loewe-aura-loewe-_w_-edp-120-ml_1.png'),
(347, 'Simone Andreoli Business Man EDP', 'Ideal for men.
An amazing fragrance extracted with great care and precision from the finest natural ingredients.
The notes of grapefruit, black currant blend perfectly with cassis leaves, grass and vetiver give the fragrance a wonderful aroma.
The fragrance gives you an exciting presence in all societies.', 100, 6492900.0, 6492900.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(24, 'Candy Addict Addictive Temptation Mini EDP Set ', 'Candy Addict EDPs are now available in Ã¢â‚¬Å“minisÃ¢â‚¬Â to take with you wherever you go! Can''t decide on your favourite scent? No problem! The Addictive Temptation set includes:
Musky Musk:
Beautiful, earthy notes of musk are layered with bergamot and rose to create a musk perfume sensation! The combination of warm and floral notes makes a sensual, unforgettable scent.
V Vanille:
An intoxicating blend of vanilla and floral notes with a touch of Oriental! Take your perfume game to a whole new level with this one of a kind fragrance sensation.
Rosy Rose:
This seductive and addictive perfume will keep you coming back for more! The gentle, sophisticated fragrance will give you a delicate scent with floral notes of rose and geranium combined with musk. Pure heaven.', 100, 1235100.0, 1235100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/o/box_with_bottles_1_.png'),
(267, 'Kiton Black EDT', 'A luxurious woody fragrance specially designed for men.
The fragrance was launched in 2007 with a distinctive aromatic blend of high quality natural materials with unique scents.
This amazing aromatic blend gives you a bold and attractive masculine look.
You will catch everyone''s eye from the first moment with this charming scent.
The accords of violet leaf, red berries, bergamot and lemon in the top notes blend perfectly with cedar and cardamom in the heart.
The fragrance ends with luxurious touches of leather, vetiver, amber and tonka bean.
About the Brand:
Kiton is an Italian luxury menswear company founded in 1968 by Cerro Pone in Italy. The first branch opened in Milan in 2001 and is famous as one of the top sewing brands in the world. Kiton has 4 distinct fragrances in its encyclopedia, and Kiton fragrances have been created in collaboration with skilled perfumers Maurice Roussell and Nijla Berber.', 125, 1759500.0, 1759500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/2/22548134412-kiton-kiton-black-men-_m_-edt-125-ml.png'),
(35, 'Jaguar Imperial For Men', 'Jaguar Imperial for Men is a limited woody-spicy perfume. The aromatic fragrance will dazzle you with its warmth. The composition is gratifying and masculine. The top notes are a blend of bergamot, lemon, mandarin orange, hawthorn, lavender, chamomile, nutmeg, and cedar notes. At the heart, violet leaf, jasmine, cloves, cedar, honey, and sandalwood mix harmoniously. The dry-down is a combination of musk tones and leather. Imperial by Jaguar is an explosion of eternal and stylish freshness meant for the modern man. The luxurious flacon is a magnificent last touch to the divine fragrance.', 100, 945300.0, 945300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_jaguar_perfumes_imperial_for_men_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(244, 'Creed Aventus Cologne', 'The perfect perfume exudes style, success, true grit, and vigour. The classic perfume maintains the utmost quality and longevity of this newest menÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s scent. It was well designed to remain with you for a long time with an attractive, refreshing scent.', 50, 12019800.0, 12019800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/5/3508441001275_creed_creed_aventus_cologne_eau_de_parfum_100ml_1.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 327', 'Enjoy the warm sunshine with Tous Les Jours 327 fragrance, that blends the winter scent with touch of amber and jasmine flower.', 55, 683100.0, 683100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000327_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_perfume_day_327_tayamun_1.jpg'),
(345, 'Liquides Imaginaires Fleuve Tendre EDP', 'A sensual and seductive combination that represents a glowing meeting of lovers in special moments.
The composition of flowers with rose water in the heart of the fragrance gives you the opportunity to experience a charming and enjoyable intimate atmosphere.
Your emotional journey begins with a spicy oriental blend that is overshadowed by the aroma of saffron and cardamom that emanates in the first moments.
The warm ends are filled with notes of tonka bean and leather giving you the last hugs, expressing the feeling of eternal love.', 100, 6037500.0, 6037500.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(122, 'Emanuel Ungaro Diva', 'Diva by Emanuel Ungaro is a classic perfume created by Jacques Polge. The perfume has accords of citrusy notes, tuberose, ylang-ylang, rose, vanilla, iris, and sandalwood. The fragrance is dedicated to women.', 100, 1386900.0, 1386900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/e/m/emanuel_ungaro_diva_edp_100_ml.jpg'),
(246, 'Yantami Amethyst EDP ', 'A fragrance that resembles courage & intimacy. Inspired by the Amethyst stone, known for strengthening bonds in relationships, attracting love and opening up the heart. Enriched with coriander spiciness, Muguet freshness & musk classiness.', 100, 690000.0, 690000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/y/a/yantami-amethyst1.png'),
(321, 'Tory Burch Jolie Fleur Rose', 'It is a new floral, musky fragrance for women.The fragrance captures a floral blend of rose and tea rose, along with musk, pink pepper, and green notes.', 100, 4367700.0, 4367700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/2/22548339725-tory-burch-tory-burch-jolie-fleur-rose-_w_-edp-100-ml.jpg'),
(55, 'Hugo Boss Hugo Extreme', 'An aromatic fragrance that takes you to a new level with a modern, intensive twist. The enlivening composition has notes of green apple, geranium and fir resin, releasing a scent that is designed for the man who lives his life with his own rules, impressing everyone with his unmistakably masculine character.', 60, 1014300.0, 1014300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_hugo_boss_perfumes_hugo_extreme_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(40, 'Tom Ford London', 'It is a woody, spicy fragrance for women and men launched in 2013. It opens the notes with black pepper, saffron, cardamom, coriander, cumin, and coffee. Geranium, jasmine, incense, and labdanum sit in the middle. The base notes include agarwood (oud), musk, birch, cedar, and Amyris.', 50, 7617600.0, 7617600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066029209-tom-ford-tom-ford-london-_u_-edp-50-ml-1.jpg'),
(50, 'Alexandre.J The Collector Black Muscs', 'The concept of this perfume explains about the oriental desert and French baroque architecture. It is designed for women. The high notes consist of lemon and bergamot; mid notes consist of patchouli, rose and violet; bottom notes consist of musk and amber.', 100, 4278000.0, 4278000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_alexandre.j_perfumes_the_collector_black_muscs_for_unisex_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(129, 'Perris Absolue D''Osmanthe', 'It''s an Eau de Parfum that sets you ready for a new adventure of beautiful scents with top notes of Osmanthus, Jasmine Sambac, the heart notes of Sandalwood, Vanilla that represents the essence of the parfume, and the base notes of Labdanum, Tolu Balsam which stays with you through out the day', 100, 3933000.0, 3933000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_perris_perfumes_absolue_d_osmanthe_for_unisex_eau_de_perfum_652685290100.jpg'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Prive Bleu Turquoise', 'Enjoy characteristic and unique moments in your day with the concentrated and inspiring fragrance mixture that is suitable for both men and women. It is the perfect choice for mornings and evenings thanks to its spicy and glowing notes of black pepper and refreshing salt particles mixed with the cold heart of ylang-ylang and jasmine carried by a powerful and intensive base of sandalwood and moss that remains with you until the last moments of your day.', 100, 10833000.0, 10833000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614271968593-giorgio-armani-ga-prive-bleu-turquoise-_u_-edp-100-ml-1.png'),
(28, 'Burberry Brit For Her', 'Burberry Brit Eau de Toilette is a light interpretation of the timeless Burberry Brit fragrance from 2003. It opens with fresh notes of green almond, icy pear, lemon grass and Italian lime. The heart is composed of sugared almonds and lush peony, laid on the base of mahogany, amber and vanilla.', 100, 1414500.0, 1414500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/5/0/5045252667941_burberry_brit_for_her_-_50_ml_1.jpg'),
(209, 'Moresque Gold Oroluna EDP', 'A Sufi fragrance inspired by the essential element of life, air.
The fragrance is lively, without limits, and spreads around you, expressing your beauty and cheerful spirit.
Discover the true secret of seduction and elegance with the notes of patchouli and oriental oud
Labdanum with incense paints the details of your free thoughts and your liberating spirit to discover life', 50, 11868000.0, 11868000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8051277311162-moresque-moresque-gold-edp-50ml-oroluna.png'),
(298, 'Jul Et Mad Stilettos on Lex EDP', 'A fragrance characterized by its strong composition that fascinates lovers of floral fragrances with a touch of powder.
The fragrance has an amazing blend that no one can resist, day or night.
Enjoy a feeling of freshness and joy like no other with lemon and pear at the top of the fragrance.
And in the middle are leaves, violets and roses that give you a feeling of comfort all the time.
Finally, a luxurious blend of musk and cedarwood.', 50, 6348000.0, 6348000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(6, 'Versace Eros Pour Homme', 'For the strong man who is the master of himself, this oriental woody fragrance is dedicated to you. The composition has notes of mint in the top, geranium in the middle, and vanilla in the base, providing you with an irresistible scent that boosts your charismatic character at your special events.', 100, 2063100.0, 2063100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8011003861224-versace-versace-eros-pour-homme-edp-100-ml.jpg'),
(20, 'Givenchy L''interdit Solid Perfume', 'Feel the elegance and charm with this feminine fragrance. A tribute fragrance to the bold femininity, with bergamot notes, followed by a heart of Orange Blossom, Jasmine and Tuberose, while the base has notes of Vetiver, Patchouli, and Vanilla, which provides you a long-lasting freshness. Enjoy the thrill of the mysterious femininity.', 3, 1186800.0, 1186800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/2/3274872407954_givenchy_l_interdit_edp_concrete_women_1.jpg'),
(131, 'Paris Hilton Can Can Burlesque EDP', 'An elegant floral fragrance for women.
The fragrance gives you an attractive look.
It highlights your femininity and makes you feel confident all the time.
The fragrance is a combination of natural ingredients.
This perfume deserves to be in your perfume collection.', 100, 1580100.0, 1580100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/0/608940557327-paris-hilton-paris-hilton-can-can-burlesque-_w_-edp-100-ml.png'),
(22, 'Nicolai Patchouli Sublime Elixir De Parfum', 'The spicy mint is blended with delicate rose in a powerful contrasting composition.
This fragrance shows your strong personality and freedom on your busy days without restrictions so you can feel enthusiastic.
The fragrance suits your special nights, thanks to the notes of musk and warm tobacco.
The composition adds a classic touch to reveal your elegant look.', 35, 10902000.0, 10902000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(223, 'Ojar Wood Whisper EDP', 'Show your love to the charming orient with this special composition.
The charming notes of amber are blended with vanilla and musk, forming a captivating scent.
Let your heart calm down and enjoy a creamy scent of woods dipped in an elegant violet scent.
The intense perfume oil is for both men and women, providing a glowing aromatic scent.', 15, 1656000.0, 1656000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(49, 'Lalique Rose Royale Noir Premier 1938', 'Lalique Rose Royale Noir Premier 1938 is a fruity floral fragrance for both men and women. A very classy and modern scent, Rose Royale will last and linger as it sweetly mingles with your skin. Peach and Apricot open the fragrance with a sweet welcome. The ephemeral opening fades away to be overcome by the exotic Osmanthus and Rose Absolute in the heart. Musk dominates the base with a faint trace of sweet Cashmere Wood. Lalique Rose Royale is an elegant fragrance that combines luscious fruit accords and exotic tones to produce a sensational scent.', 100, 6796500.0, 6796500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_lalique_perfumes_rose_royale_noir_premier_1938_for_unisex_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(17, 'Calvin Klein Obsession for Men', 'Calvin Klein Obsession for men is one of the most famous perfumes that was famous in the late eighties and nineties and still has lovers who can not do without it until today.   The aroma of the fragrance gives you warmth and a sense of reassurance on cold winter days.', 125, 897000.0, 897000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_calvin_klein_perfumes_obsession_for_men_eua_de_toilette.jpg'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Sole Di Positano', 'It is a floral, citrus fragrance that was launched in 2017. It opens its notes with citrus fruits such as Calabrian bergamot, bitter orange, mandarin, and lemon. The Mediterranean idyll and sunny atmosphere are captured in the heart of the perfume with notes of shiso leaf, orange blossom, ylang-ylang, jasmine, lily of the valley, and neroli. The base ends with a dose of green moss. It is available in a 100ml Eau de Parfum bottle.', 100, 7617600.0, 7617600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066066471-tom-ford-tom-ford-sole-di-positano-_u_-edp-250-ml-splash-1.jpg'),
(348, 'Goutal Paris Petite ChÃ©rie Set ', 'This set features a 100 ml EDP and a 75 ml cream.
The formula of the cream works to hydrate, protect and repair the skin, thanks to shea butter along with musk.
The fragrance has a fruity scent that delivers an elegant look for women.
The fragrance provides endless elegance with notes of pear and peach, which blend with rose and vanilla to deliver freshness.', 100, 5789100.0, 5789100.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(141, 'Moschino Uomo EDT', 'Refresh your soul in the morning with this luxurious fragrance that has a blend of coriander and aldehydes.
The notes of cyclamen and labdanum boost your vitality and enthusiasm so you feel free on all your days.
The scent adds a special attractive touch to your look to get the attention of everyone there and captivates the hearts.
The base has oriental notes of amber and musk that remain intense for a long time.', 125, 1538700.0, 1538700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8011003064106-moschino-moschino-uomo-_m_-edt-125-ml.jpg'),
(48, 'Lancome Maison Parfait de RÃƒÂ´ses', 'This new high perfumery experience takes a creative stance. It has a blend of roses, pink pepper, aldehydes and liquor.', 100, 6037500.0, 6037500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614271687647-lancome-lancome-maison-parfait-de-roses-unisex-edp-100-ml.jpg'),
(13, 'Juicy Couture I Love Juicy Couture', 'I Ã¢â„¢Â¥ JUICY COUTURE is a seizing scent that mixes wealthy fruity notes with floral fragrances, with a tone of amber scent and musky scent. Given his boldness notes of integrity, the parfume extremely embodies the spirit of living and love, and reflects the right passion for all the Juicy Couture invention. This oriental parfume, with fruity notes and vanilla, will encourage every girl in love with the Juicy Couture brand to radiate self-confidence.', 50, 1166100.0, 1166100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfum_juicy_couture_i_laove_juicy_couture_for_women_eau_de_parfum.jpg'),
(255, 'Ralph Lauren The Big Pony Collection 2', 'Unknown', 125, 3015300.0, 3015300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_ralph_lauren_perfumes_the_big_pony_collection_2_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Tuscan Leather', 'Tom Ford Tuscan Leather EDP is a marvelous unisex parfume that captures the ancient scent of soft leather. The parfume contains magnificent notes and gives you a classic modern design, with the addition of flowering jasmine and black leather, giving you a distinctive touch and is also distinguished by being raw and sophisticated.', 50, 7617600.0, 7617600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_tom_ford_perfumes_tuscan_leather_for_unisex_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(156, 'Victoria''s Secret Passion Flowers Body Mist', 'The body mist by Victoria''s Secret. Part of the Wild Blooms collection, one can nearly feel the wind as it flutters through the wildflowers, bringing notes of passionflower, peony, freesia, and just a hint of fruity complexity to round off the sweetness. Victoria''s Secret Passion Flowers is a light mist that is designed to be reapplied throughout the day or night, bringing a burst of freshness wherever you take it.', 250, 503700.0, 503700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/6/667551001698-victoria-secret-victoria_s-secret-passion-flowers-body-mist-_u_-250-ml.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Intense', 'This fragrance reflects the tenderness and glow of delicate feelings that fill your life with the splendor and happiness. Its top notes feature basil, coriander and grapefruit, followed by orange buds, cardamom and ginger. The base has a blend of tobacco, rice wood and amber.', 100, 1373100.0, 1373100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006907104_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_intense_100_ml_1.jpg'),
