(38, 'Elie Saab Le Parfum Gift Set ', 'The gift set from Elie Saab contains a Le Parfum Eau de Parfum (90ml) and Eau de Parfum for woman (10ml). Elie Saab Le Parfum is an enveloping perfume that creates a long-lasting cloud of feminine charm. It contains notes of orange blossom that blend with more complex, mysterious, and warm notes of grandiflorum and sambac jasmine, followed by notes of cedar, patchouli, and honey accords that give this fragrance a sophisticated touch while remaining simple and classy.', 10, 3339600.0, 3339600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/4/3423473998051-elie-saab-elie-saab-le-parfum-_w_-edp-90-ml-_-edp-10-ml-gift-set-2-piece.jpg'),
(235, 'V Canto Sigismondo Extrait De Parfum', 'A reckless attack inspired by one of the most famous Italian leaders in history
