(76, 'Thierry Mugler Angel Muse EDT', 'A new highly addictive luxury is a genius and sublime creation full of gourmand vetiver. Wildly intoxicating, this perfume was released in 2016 in a refill bottle to let you endlessly replenish your pebble. Its long-lasting blend gives you an attractive scent that captures the hearts.', 100, 2166600.0, 2166600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/4/3439600023367-thierry-mugler-thierry-mugler-angel-muse-_w_-edt-50-ml.jpg'),
(111, 'Carolina Herrera CH Women', 'For the classic, elegant and seductive CH Carolina Herrera fragrance, its vibrant red color reveals the passion which speaks of the woman who wears it. Like a fine piece of jewelry, the bottle is immediately eye catching and captivating. The seductive red bottle is accented by a gold bottle stopper. Elegant and impossible to resist. The CH Carolina Herrera woman is a vision of femininity and style. A modern woman who is used to the finer things in life. Chic and modern, she knows exactly what to wear and how to wear it. Others marvel at her innate sense of elegance, but to her it comes easily. Possessing a modern femininity, others are drawn as much to her love of life as they are to the impeccable way she handles everything in her glamorous world. She smiles easily, knowing she can conquer anything.', 100, 3691500.0, 3691500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/carolina_herrera_ch.jpg'),
