(312, 'Layl Oud Gift Box ', 'The perfect body set for you to stay refreshed and feeling vital. It features a shower gel, hand wash, body spray, deodorant and air freshening incense. Enjoy an intense and concentrated scent for a long time with the luxurious oriental fragrance of oud.
Benefits:
