(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 316', 'Enjoy the vital scent of this marvellous scent. Its delicate composition has notes of mint in the opening, geranium in the middle and cedar in the base, which releases an attractive scent designed to be your perfect option on your busy days and special nights.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000316-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-316-1.png'),
(244, 'Creed Love In White For Summer', 'Taking the inspiration from CreedÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s best-selling womenÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s fragrance Love In White, The House of Creed debuts the new seasonal Love In White For Summer. A dreamy fresh floral that bottles white-hot nights on the CÃƒÂ´te d''Azur and the quest for eternal summer. This scent transports wearers to the French Riviera where chic white accessories, crisp waves and long holiday escapes reign. Like the sparkling hues of the oceanÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s reflection, iris and cedar shine through at the heart of this serene seasonal scent. A fresh, long-lasting, that does not overpower your presence, a perfect choice for any of your occasions.', 75, 9404700.0, 9404700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/5/3508440506955_creed_creed_love_in_white_for_summer_edp_75_ml_1.jpg'),
(32, 'Guerlain Samsara', 'Samsara Eau de Toilette Guerlain for women, will provide you with harmony and balance. A woody and oriental fragrance that you shall adore! Guerlain Samsara is a classic perfume suitable for all occasions. This potion of love and seduction is a magical combination of sandalwood, ylang-ylang and jasmine. It combines both classical glamour and modern elegance. The opening of Samsara sends out the sweet scent of jasmine. Jasmine is adorned by the ylang-ylang flower and beautified by the rich sandalwood. The base is elevated with iris, Tonka beans and vanilla. As the first woody perfume for women, this balanced fragrance is bewitching and embracing. It takes you on a trip to the Oriental mountains and into exotic realms.', 50, 2408100.0, 2408100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470132733_guerlain_guerlain_samsara_edt_100_ml_1.jpg'),
