(164, 'Mercedes Benz Cologne', 'touch the pure freedom with this lovely citrus fragrance, that represents the escape from daily noise of life, to get the required harmony, with a great blend of pink pepper, musk, and ginger.', 120, 2463300.0, 2463300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_mercedes-benz_perfumes_cologne_for_men_eau_de_toilette_3595471021199.jpg'),
