(86, 'Cartier La Panthere Edition Soir', 'Cartier La Panthere Edition Soir by Cartier is a womenÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s chypre floral perfume thatÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s made for fall and winter nights. Launched in 2016, this fragrance was signed by Mathilde Laurent, CartierÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s in-house perfumer, and is best described as a blend of floral and animal notes, along with oakmoss, musk, and gardenia. It has white floral, floral, woody, earthy, and musky main accords. The fragrance is announced as a dose of femininity and glamour of a wild and independent woman. The glass bottle is thick and square, has a pantherÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s face, and is topped with a stylish black cap.', 75, 3608700.0, 3608700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_cartier_perfumes_la_panthere_edition_soir_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(133, 'Kenzo World Power EDT', 'A soft and delicate fragrance for elegant women who seek luxury.
