(59, 'Dunhill Fresh', 'Dunhill Fresh by Alfred Dunhill is an exceptionally refreshing woody fragrance for men. With green notes propagating throughout, mint, sage, basil, and lavender clamber to the top of the bouquet. Floral notes abound with the unmistakable aroma of fressia and mimosa accompanied by the elegant subtleties of violet and iris. Base notes of amber, oakmoss, and cedar add a familiar sense of sophistication, while coumarin, vetiver finish to provide an exotic and tasteful memory. After launching in 2005, Dunhill Fresh has helped to define the scent of the modern gentleman. This cologne has been praised for its ability to provide a long-lasting, but not overpowering scent for the whole day.', 100, 862500.0, 862500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/u/dunhill_desire_fresh.jpg'),
(51, 'Al Dakheel Oud Royal Mixture Perfume Oil', 'A luxurious aromatic blend designed for those looking for luxury and sophistication.
