(111, 'Carolina Herrera 212 Vip Women', 'A fun fragrance, select and stylish. You have it all!! The juice has to be a combination of party, socialite, energy and style. A fragrance of personality, both explosive and magnetic. A fragrant pulsation combining style and attitude, a partying eau de parfum. Wearing it, you become this Ã¢â‚¬Å“itÃ¢â‚¬Â girl who gets an insider access to the hottest and trendiest club in New York to party all night long. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s a fragrance about optimism, freedom and emotions.', 50, 2622000.0, 2622000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/carolina_herrera_212_vip_-women.jpg'),
