(320, 'Thierry Mugler Chyprissime', 'An elegant and sophisticated parfume for bothe men and women. Once you open the bottle, the classical notes of bergamot and orange will explode, and transform into a dreamy parfume that can be used anytime and anywhere, for a more attractive presence.', 80, 6527400.0, 6527400.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Patchouli Absolu', 'It is a woody fragrance for women and men that was launched in 2014. It has an aromatic blend of patchouli, bay leaf, rosemary, guaiac wood, cypriol oil or nagarmotha, cashmere wood, tonka bean, moss, amber, musk, and leather.', 100, 11426400.0, 11426400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066041607-tom-ford-tom-ford-patchouli-absolu-_u_-edp-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(29, 'Lorenzo Villoresi Teint De Neige EDP', 'It''s a delicate aromatic scent for both men and women that reminds of memories with its images, lights and atmosphere. Its rich extracts and precious notes of Ylang-Ylang, heliotrope and musk will envelop you with intense smell that you cannot resist.', 100, 5451000.0, 5451000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_lorenzo_villoresi_firenze_perfumes_teint_de_neige_eau_de_parfum.jpg'),
(200, 'Avon Perceive EDP', 'When it comes to highlighting the subtle details of your beauty and glamorous femininity, your fragrance takes the leading role.
Get ready for a great journey with this soft and delicate feminine fragrance of freesia mixed with the freshness of ylang-ylang.
The fragrance is knotted on a delicate woody floral top of cedar and vanilla orchid that makes you feel confident and fun until the end of the day.
