(28, 'Burberry Mr. Burberry Indigo', 'A unique men''s fragrance from violet leaf extract mixed with peppermint oil drops coated with rosemary scent with lemon refreshing that adds to your vibrant spirit and zapping throughout the day.', 100, 1304100.0, 1304100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/2/82004067568_burberry_mr._burberry_indigo_edt_100_ml.jpg'),
(44, 'Bvlgari Le Gemme Maravilla', 'This fragrance is taking you to a journey into the Iberian Peninsula with its sunny morning and a luminous stone. This elegant scent combines with citrus notes and sweet peach. A chypre fragrance mixes with Orange Flower and Patchouli that adds fortify and energy sense of the Mediterranean light.', 100, 10508700.0, 10508700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_bvlgari_perfumes_le_gemme_maravilla_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(44, 'Bvlgari Le Gemme Garanat', 'An Oriental Floral fragrance that combines with damask rose, rose and incense. This fragrance adds masculine strength and forthrightness that makes you take the right decisions in a busy day.', 100, 10515600.0, 10515600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_bvlgari_perfumes_le_gemme_garanat_edp_100_ml_for_men_783320521034.jpg'),
(352, 'The Harmonist Sacred Water EDP', 'Description
