(133, 'Kenzo World EDT', 'This floral fragrance embodies excitment as it is designed for the woman who dares to be different, filling her with joy. Her need for enthusiasm attracts everyone through an amazing blend of peony, rose along with white musk and vanilla. It comes in an eye-shaped powdery pink bottle, revealing the femininity of the fragrance.', 50, 2456400.0, 2456400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_kenzo_perfumes_kenzo_world_for_women_eau_de_toilette_3274872365049.jpg'),
(44, 'BvlgariLe Gemme Azaran EDP', 'Achieve your ambitions and head toward the world of elegance with notes of saffron and fresh bergamot.
The creamy heart has notes of green tea and cedar, which boost your elegance and charming femininity.
The classic base has notes of leather, woods and honeysuckle, adding irresistible elegance.
