(117, 'Thameen Fragrance Regent Leather', 'It''s an oriental fragrance inspired by the 300-year old 141 carat Regent Diamond. The amazing composition has notes of jasmine, cardamom and leather, delivering a scent with a touch of luxury and elegance that envelopes you all the time.', 50, 7072500.0, 7072500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/2/724120095653-thameen-thameen-amber-room-_u_-edp-50-ml.jpg'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Armani Code Absolu', 'This unique aromatic experience that deserves to be part of your perfume has such a refreshing formula that is full of orange and neroli pervade with spicy ginger seeds and the striking aromas of tuberose that will fill your heart with great feelings and increase your passion. The fragrance has an attractive oriental appearance that captures the hearts around you easily.', 50, 3022200.0, 3022200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614272544437-giorgio-armani-giorgio-armani-code-pour-femme-absolu-_w_-edp-50-ml-1.jpg'),
(256, 'Aramis Aramis 900', 'Woody accords come out in full force with Aramis 900 cologne. This fragrance launched in 1973, and it has been a signature aroma for many men since. It opens with a strong kick with notes of lemon, Brazilian rosewood, bergamot, green notes, and coriander. The core brings geranium, rose, lily of the valley, jasmine, orris root, and carnation into the scent profile. The aromas of vetiver, oakmoss, civet, patchouli, amber, and sandalwood make up the base. Aimed to give a classical and timeless aroma, Aramis 900 is perfect for the modern-day traditional man.', 100, 890100.0, 890100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/r/aramis_aramis_900_1_1.jpg'),
(105, 'Rochas Mademoiselle Rochas', 'It''s a Extravagant Eau de Parfum that represents the playful spirit of a young Parisian woman and the epitome of French Chic with Sweet and fruity aromas with a composition that begins with notes of Woodsy Notes, Olibanum, the heart notes of Patchouli, Spices, Agarwood that represents the essence of the parfume, and the base notes of Gardenia, Rose, Saffron which stays with you through out the day.', 90, 2380500.0, 2380500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_rochas_perfumes_mademoiselle_rochas_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(208, 'Lootah Mabe EDP', 'Don''t miss the authenticity and history that weaves an oriental Emirati look with the unique Mabe fragrance from Lootah
The combination of patchouli and bergamot creates a warm touch, while jasmine adds subtle elegance
You can use it alone or with an essential oil from its range for an attractive and enchanting effect', 80, 2946300.0, 2946300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6297000836997-lootah-lootah-mabe-eau-de-parfum-80-ml.png'),
(31, 'Dkhoun Fakher ', 'This incense reflects the mix of the luxurious oud and notes of patchouli and Portuguese flower, delivering a strong scent that spreads everywhere to boost the elegance of your house.', 100, 2497800.0, 2497800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/9/390010-dkhoun-_-_80gr-1.jpg'),
(18, 'Penhaligon''s Zizonia', 'Penhaligon''s Zizonia is an anthology of the famous Zizonia perfume by Penhaligon''s that was first introduced in the 1930s. This oriental perfume has a nomadic and mysterious aura to it. The odyssey to the world of scents will lead you through the top notes of bergamot, orange blossom, and coriander; heart notes of lavender, cardamom, nutmeg, geranium, ginger, cumin, and black pepper before trailing off with the base notes of amber, patchouli, cedar, sandalwood, and vetiver. This perfume is available as 100 ml EDT.', 100, 7196700.0, 7196700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_penhaligon_s_perfumes_zizonia_for_women_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(141, 'Moschino Toy 2 Set ', 'It''s a feminine collection for women featuring a (100 ml) bottle of the fragrance, (100 ml) bottle of body lotion and (100 ml) shower gel.
