The scent remains intense and concentrated on all your busy days and special nights, keeping you as elegant as usual.
The collection comes to you in an elegant packaging so you can offer as a gift to your beloved ones on happy occasions.', 25, 614100.0, 614100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8011003845552-moschino_moschino_toy_2_w_mini_set_edp_5_ml_prfm_body_lotion_25_ml_pfrm_bath_shower_gel_25_ml-1.png'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 347', 'Add to your day an energized feeling with Tous Les Jours 347 perfume. Enjoy a unique fresh coffee scent to start your day with, and a blend of orange blossoms, pear and scent of jasmine and vanilla.', 55, 683100.0, 683100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000347_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_perfume_day_347_tayamun_1_1__1.jpg'),
(32, 'Guerlain Ambre Eternel', 'Guerlain Ambre Eternel is a profound woody and oriental fragrance for men and women alike. The name is inspired by the main ingredient in the amber accord; Ambergris. The top notes are spicy. Coriandre, cinnamon and cardamom combine to give a sweet and spicy feel. At the heart, fruity notes, Orange Blossom and Ylang Ylang radiate exotically. The fruity notes melt delicately into a blend of woody notes, masculine leather note and amber notes. You will fall in love with this noble fragrance! An extremely happy fragrance will keep you shining and glowing all day, all night!', 125, 11598900.0, 11598900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_guerlain_perfumes_ambre_eternel_for_unisex_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(50, 'Jo Malone Red Roses EDP', 'It is a feminine floral fragrance with a charming scent.
The fragrance enhances your femininity and self-confidence and reflects your soul and attraction.
It is enriched with a fresh fruity scent of peaches and grapefruit to give you the sense of joy and freshness.
The heart reveals the flower scent to make you feel relieved and relaxed.
The fragrance finally ends with a luxurious scent of Ambroxan, Vanilla, Toffee and Patchouli.', 100, 4650600.0, 4650600.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(111, 'Carolina Herrera Good Girl SuprÃƒÂªme', 'It is a new oriental floral fragrance for women that was launched in 2020. The nose behind this fragrance is Louise Turner. Egyptian jasmine and forest fruits sit on the top with middle notes of tuberose and tonka bean along with vetiver base notes.', 80, 3622500.0, 3622500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/4/8411061972151-carolina-herrera-ch-good-girl-edp-supr_me-80ml.jpg'),
(54, 'Sedr Alkhaleej Oud Touch Set', 'This set contains:
Sedr Alkhaleej Al Oud Oud - 50 g
This home incense has a distinctive Arabian scent that fast spreads in your homes and covers every corner with the elegant Arabian scent of sandalwood and musk.
Sedr Alkhaleej Lammsah Oud - 50 g
This rich Arabian Incense decorates your home with an elegant and strong scent that surrounds every corner with its rich scent of musk, sandalwood and patchouli.
Sedr Alkhaleej Luxury Oud Coal - 80 Pcs
This luxury burner oud coal was designed to put in your decorated censer that spreads in every corner of your home and adds the strong and stable scent of oud, which stay in your home until the ends of your special occasions.', 100, 627900.0, 627900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/b/sb100295-oud-touch-sedr-alkhaleej_1_.png'),
(32, 'Guerlain Cuir Intense EDP', 'A classic touch of leather and luxurious musk deliver an amazing fragrance.
