(42, 'Nasomatto Absinth', 'A woody parfume for men and women, ideal for springtime, combining earthy notes, woody green and dry herbs, for an addictive smell, that adds to your confidence and allure throughout the day.', 30, 4609200.0, 4609200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_nasomatto_perfumes_absinth_for_unisex_extrait_de_parfum_perfume.jpg'),
(33, 'Lacoste Essential', 'Woody and aromatic, this masculine scent will make you capture attention all day. Its enticing scent will keep you fresh and fragrant for long time, thanks to its impressive composition which includes bergamot, rose and sandalwood.', 125, 1235100.0, 1235100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/a/lacoste_essential_edt.jpg'),
(63, 'Dior J''Adore', 'The eau de parfum is the great Dior floral for women with a generous and well-balanced bouquet, and its richness is a source of inspiration. By celebrating Ylang Ylang from the Comoro This feminine fragrance is a blend of elegant florals and fresh fruits with a touch of woody and earthy notes. Its top notes include melon, peach, pear, magnolia, bergamot, and mandarin orange. Its heart consists of powerful florals with a touch of fruit and freshness. They include tuberose, orchid, lily of the valley, rose, violet, jasmine, plum, and freesia. Earthy musk, warm vanilla, aromatic cedar, and juicy blackberry form the base notes of this stunning fragrance. Sillage is moderate and longevity is high, making this the perfect perfume for a long day or evening. Wear this powerful scent for special occasions when you want to make an impression.', 50, 2960100.0, 2960100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/i/dior_jdore_eau_de_parfum_1.jpg'),
(122, 'Emanuel Ungaro Ungaro Masculin EDT', 'This fragrance embodies the soul of an eagle that symbolizes courage and power in its shiny eyes.
Feel the vitality with the notes of bergamot and mandarin at the beginning of the day.
The fragrance is perfect for the strong man who fights strife and realizes the importance of his power.
The fragrance embodies an eagle flying high bravely to resist the strong wind.', 90, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8034097957192-emanuel-ungaro-emanuel-ungaro-masculin-_m_-edt-90-ml.png'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Si Fiori', 'Embodies a feminine Ã¢â‚¬ËœglowÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ that is perfect for spring and summer. Dressed in delicate nude pink, the fragrance bottle will look classy and elegant on your dressing table. Make it your everyday scent.', 100, 3505200.0, 3505200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614272508323_giorgio_armani_si_fiori_edp_100_ml_1.jpg'),
(7, 'Xerjoff Shooting Stars Kobe EDP', 'Exclusive and special edition from the enchanting oriental world of perfumes enriched with the scents of apple and fresh tobacco leaves.
The sharp leather notes increase the classic scent and give you a special and distinctive look.
The ambery fragrance base is enhanced with the scent of oud and sandalwood notes that give you a feeling of comfort and relaxation after a long day.
Feel free to penetrate the world of beauty and attractiveness with the perfect drops of fragrance for all the occasions of your life and special nights.', 50, 7500300.0, 7500300.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(330, 'Boadicea Alwouod EDP', 'As bright as the sun at dawn
Enjoy your sexy look with this luxurious fragrance
Cambodian oud fills the heart with cumin and precious oriental notes
The heart has charming aromatic beginnings and ends that capture your breath and dance around you all day', 100, 10908900.0, 10908900.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Eau De Nuit', 'Fashion house Armani presented its first masculine fragrance Eau Pour Homme in 1984. Sharp, strong, citrusy and aromatic, this one has become a classic among men''s fragrances. Almost 30 years later, in February the 2013, Armani launches a new version of Eau Pour Homme and a brand new nocturnal edition Eau de Nuit. Eau de Nuit, dark and opulent, combines notes of spices, citruses, cedar and iris. The composition is warmer and more sensual than the debut. It opens with accords of bergamot and pink pepper. Spicy notes of cardamom and nutmeg form the heart of the perfume together with flowers of iris and heliotrope. The base consists of cedar, tonka and amber.', 100, 3098100.0, 3098100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/i/giorgio_armani_eau_de_nuit_edt_men.jpg'),
(194, 'Kenneth Cole Black Bold', 'This daring fragrance in inspire by the boldness of life in New York City. Its notes will make you feel the strength, power, and confidence to push the boundaries. It comes in a sleek leather-like wrapped bottle.', 100, 1449000.0, 1449000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_kenneth_cole_perfumes_black_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 389', 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 389 is an intoxicating blend of glamourous and confidence that creates a contemporary, premium feeling, whenever you inhale them. This masterpiece identifies a breath-taking fusion of strength and elegance, manifested in the freshness of an orange, tangerine, orange blossom, bergamot, blended in jasmine mimosa, Turkish rose, ylang-ylang. Tonka Bean, Patchouli, Vetiver, White Musk rhyme together at the base to share in that voluptuous style and compliment in that distinct aroma.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000389-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-389-1.png'),
(203, 'Vertus Oriental Rose EDP', 'A soft delicate fragrance that has a luxurious oriental character that adds unparalleled fancy and elegance.
Roses and spicy saffron notes express the heat of seduction and sensuality and make you stand out.
Express the emotions and feelings of your heart through violet and bloodstone scents that emanate from the heart of this soft romantic fragrance.
The fragrance has a strong and intense scent to last with you for long hours.', 100, 5313000.0, 5313000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3612345679192-vertus-vertus-oriental-rose-_u_-edp-100-ml.jpg'),
(7, 'Xerjoff Black Sukar Extrait de Parfum', 'During your journey to reach luxury and elegance, enjoy this unique scent.
The notes of oud and white musk achieve the excellence and special taste you seek.
The soft floral heart touches your soul delicately to boost your elegance.
Be ready for the real beauty and unique charm in all the different occasions and special nights.', 10, 9321900.0, 9321900.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(109, 'Aigner Debut', 'Etienne Aigner is launching the new women''s fragrance Debut, which arrives on the market in June 2013. The perfume is inspired by an elegant woman in a satin dress who attracts everyone''s attention and lures you with her beauty at first glance. Top notes of Aigner Debut accentuate fresh fruity aromas of bergamot, mandarin, grapefruit, and green apple additionally cooled down with petitgrain. The heart incorporates luminous orange blossom, water lily, jasmine, and sunflower seed, on a deeply warm and cuddly base of patchouli, cedar, vanilla, white musk, and oakmoss.', 50, 1166100.0, 1166100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/i/aigner_debut.jpg'),
(84, 'Nikos Sculpture Homme', 'A refreshing and elegant oriental fragrance for men, ideal for all occasions, with a luxurious blend of citrus (mandarin, bergamot and lemon) and spices notes, lavender and wood to enjoy a long-lasting exciting scent and self-confidence.', 100, 669300.0, 669300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_nikos_perfumes_sculpture_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(12, 'Marly Percival', 'This amazing aromatic scent gives you a unique sensual imprint, as well as reflects the strength of your personality, with a great blend of balsamic fir, cinnamon, and bergamot.', 125, 8252400.0, 8252400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/7/3700578523006_marly_percival_.jpg'),
(6, 'Versace Crystal Noir EDT', 'An oriental floral fragrance for women, giving you the perfect sensuality and charm, with a wonderful mixture of cardamom, peony, musk, and amber.', 90, 1573200.0, 1573200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_versace_perfumes_crystal_noir_for_women_eau_de_toilette_8018365071469.jpg'),
(28, 'Burberry The Beat Men', 'A new world of charm and elegance for men starts from the extract of black pepper with a refreshing lemon squeeze and covered with violet leaves with a whiff of geranium, plus a sprinkle of thyme and vetiver with a final touch of woody perfume to get a super attractive and elegant fragrance.', 100, 1531800.0, 1531800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/burberry_the_beat_edt_for_men.jpg'),
(195, 'Atkinsons Oud Save The King Perfume Oil', 'An oriental fragrance with a unique charming scent.
