(17, 'Calvin Klein Ck2', 'Share this beauty together and savor the sweetness of mandarin covered with violet leaves with the distinctive sandalwood fragrance, do not forget to feel wasabi full of fragrant powders with fragrant notes of vetiver and the scents of soft roses, a new perfume for men and women that you can taste together to become a pleasure that you have never seen before', 100, 1193700.0, 1193700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_calvin_klein_perfumes_ck2_for_men_eau_de_toillete.jpg'),
