(24, 'Candy Addict Powdery Pow Hair Mist ', 'Want to be that person that smells so good you make everyone wonder what you''re wearing? The fresh, dry sweetness of Powdery Pow will make you that person! The opening notes of osmanthus, musk & amber lead to the clean, powdery sweet base notes and POW! Love at first spritz.
