(59, 'Dunhill Pure', 'Dunhill Pure is a bright and revitalizing fragrance great for any young man to enjoy all summertime long. This scent was launched by Alfred Dunhill in 2006, and its fresh quality is attractive to almost anyone and ideal for daytime wear. This cologne contains notes of a lotus leaf with spicy cardamom and white pepper. These qualities are topped off by the bright scent of a lotus flower, perfecting that summery garden aroma. This cologne possesses a soft to moderate sillage, so the scent is gentle and enjoyable but not overly potent. Its longevity is moderate but it should last long enough to make its use well worth your while.', 75, 1587000.0, 1587000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/5/85715805911_dunhill_pure_100_ml_1.jpg'),
(12, 'Marly Byerley', 'This bold and strong fragrance made for the energetic and adventurous men that takes you to see the wild horses seeking to win to fill you with love of adventure and competition.', 125, 7935000.0, 7935000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_parfums_de_marly_perfumes_byerley_for_men_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(244, 'Creed Love In White', 'Love in White by Creed is an Oriental fragrance for women that was launched in 2005. It was largely inspired by a love for sailing and features symbolism of freedom, nature, and harmony. In keeping with that theme, this fragrance features scent notes from most of the continents. The top note is composed mainly of orange peel, hailing from South Spanish orchards. The middle notes are composed of a handful of scent notes. You may notice jasmine from Italy, narcissus from France, Egyptian iris, and Tonkin rise. The final notes to hit your senses include vanilla, sandalwood, and a touch of ambergris.', 75, 10356900.0, 10356900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_creed_perfumes_love_in_white_for_women_eau_de_parfum.jpg'),
(20, 'Givenchy Gentleman', 'GIVENCHY Gentleman it''s a perfect mixture between woody and earthy fragrance, gives you a gentle and elegant feeling, it''s more likely to be used at night time.', 50, 2822100.0, 2822100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_givenchy_perfumes_gentleman_for_men_eau_de_perfum_3274872368026.jpg'),
(160, 'Perry Ellis Perry Ellis 18', 'It''s an Eau de Parfum that has a delicate and fruity scent which is made with femininity in mind with a composition that begins with notes of Pear, Raspberry, Mojito, the heart notes of Nimfea, Pink Orchids that represents the essence of the parfume, and the base notes of Sandalwood, Vanilla which stays with you through out the day', 100, 1138500.0, 1138500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_perry_ellis_perfumes_perry_ellis_18_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(45, 'Coach Coach Women', 'Originally released in 2007, Coach perfume by Coach is a 2016 updated version that has a free-spirited and authentic attitude. Its fruity-floral scent is uplifting and refreshing with just a hint of the sort of elegant leather accessories that have made the designer famous. The fragrance opens with top notes of pink pepper, pear, and raspberry leaf, and then reveals a luxurious heart of Turkish rose. The base notes finish the aromas in a blend of suede musk and rich sandalwood, to give the perfume an undeniable allure. This is a classic fragrance that is always a good choice for any of your occasions.', 50, 1593900.0, 1593900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_coach_perfumes_coach_women_edp_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(24, 'Candy Addict Sugar Shock Duo Set ', 'Hey, sugar! Live the sweet life with this delightful duo containing a Sugar Shock Hair Mist (100ml) and Sugar Shock Body Mist (250ml).
Did someone say sugar rush? This captivating body mist will leave you smelling good enough to eat. The sweet cotton candy & caramel scents are complimented with fruity notes that will delight the senses!
How to use:
Hair mist:
From about 20 cms away, spritz the mist evenly over your hair. Then smile, this is gonna be your day! Don''t forget to shake the bottle before use to liven up the candy!
Body mist:
For best results, hold the bottle at least 20 cms away to ensure even coverage. Spray your body mist all over the body after showering or throughout the day to freshen up!', 100, 1373100.0, 1373100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/i/life-is-sweet---sb100163.png'),
(32, 'Guerlain Idylle Old Version', 'Guerlain Idylle, a perfume that captures profound moments of happiness, extremely happy and joyous situations, peaceful times and moments of bliss. Idylle opens with floral scents. Lily of the valley, peony, white lilac and freesia fill the air. The heart notes are a mix of jasmine and Bulgarian roses. Patchouli and white musk are the sensual final notes. The fragrance is soft and elegant, feminine and classy. It emits a nostalgic lingering trail and warms up the heart. It is the scent of first love, a field of sunflowers, and the sound of the oceans.', 100, 2187300.0, 2187300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470111424-guerlain-idylle-old-version-edp-01.png'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Acqua di Gio Absolu', 'This perfume is a woody aromatic fragrance that reflects your courage and confidence. It is a bold expression of Classic Acqua di Gio, where the patchouli balances the aquatic fragrance and the woody scents, revealing a cozy and sensual twist.', 125, 3042900.0, 3042900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614271992932_giorgio_armani_acqua_di_gio_absolu_edp_125_ml_1.jpg'),
(117, 'Ella K Reflet Sur L''Okavango EDP', 'Description
Enjoy shiny and healthy skin with this fabulous body lotion. This lotion features the finest qualities of argan oil and the enticing shea butter, which nourishes your skin and provides it with high moisturization. The lotion offers other luxurious nourishing ingredients and a unique refreshing feeling with the fresh scent of white jasmine, Bulgarian rose and clove; so that this charming blend makes you feel comfortable and relieved.
How to use:
Apply a suitable amount of lotion on completely dry and clean skin. Rub it gently in a circular motion until it''s fully absorbed.
Benefits:
The lotion nourishes your skin and provides it with high moisturization and a refreshing scent to enjoy healthy radiant and smooth skin.', 100, 6872400.0, 6872400.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(36, 'Narciso Rodriguez Fleur Musc', 'Fleur Musc for Her is a floral perfume with notes that envelops the heart of musc with warmth and sensuality. Enriched with the scent of pink flowers, peppercorns, blend with the rare musc, woody amber, patchouli that produces a radiant sublime rose cloud that follow you where ever you go.', 50, 2622000.0, 2622000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_narciso_rodriguez_perfumes_fleur_musc_for_women_eau_de_parfum.jpg'),
(54, 'Sedr Alkhaleej Mixed & Match ', 'This set includes:
Sedr Alkhaleej Lammsah Bakhour Haramy - 50 g
This Arabian home incense specially designed with a pyramid shape that makes it easier to ignition for long hours and touches your senses with its warmth and the stable scent of Saffron, patchouli and sandalwood that leaves vibrant and pleasant feels in every corner in your home.
Sedr Alkhaleej Luxury Oud Coal - 80 Pcs
