(56, 'Armand Basi In Red', 'Armand Basi In Red comes with a spring floral character. The product is infused with the top notes of mandarin, bergamot, ginger, and cinnamon. The heart encompasses jasmine, rose, lily, and violet leaves, and the base includes musk and woody notes.', 100, 1000500.0, 1000500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_armand_basi_perfumes_in_red_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
