The fresh beginnings of the fragrance fill you with energy to go through your day.', 100, 3491400.0, 3491400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/5/9/5902734847485-exuma-exuma-parum-ambre-d_orient-100-ml.png'),
(59, 'Dunhill Custom', 'Dunhill Custom was released in 2011 to appeal to a younger audience while holding to its classic heritage. The scent is straightforward and masculine, crafted from a relatively small range of scent notes. The opening features the crisp/tart of an English Pippin apple, starting fresh and gentling into a caramelized sweetness that reminds you of aged cognac. As the fragrance unfolds, pepper adds some spice to the top note. The base notes of cedar and incense wrap the fragrance in a hint of wood smoke thatÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s ideal for cozy evenings with someone special. The scent is restrained but never loses that distinctive appeal. Wear Dunhill Custom as your go-to cool-weather fragrance.', 100, 848700.0, 848700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/u/dunhill_custom.jpg'),
(20, 'Givenchy Play For Her EDP', 'The woman who wears Givenchy Play Eau De Parfum by Givenchy is spontaneous, playful and free. She lives by her own rules and invites those around her to come along for the ride. The heartbeat of this fragrance is an exotic chord of tiare flower, Amyris wood, and orchid. Top notes include the spicy aromas of pink peppercorn and orange blossom. Patchouli, sandalwood, benzoin, and tonka bean round out and provide the foundation of this stylish and playful perfume.', 100, 2380500.0, 2380500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/i/givenchy_play_for_her_eau_de_parfum_1.jpg'),
(28, 'Burberry My Burberry Blush', 'A world of femininity full of elegance and fragrance in its scent and design, with this fragrance Sime you feel like a garden full of fragrant flowers, you will not be able to dispense with him every day throughout the spring and summer periods.', 50, 1552500.0, 1552500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_burberry_perfumes_my_burberry_blush_for_women_eau_de_perfum_50ml.jpg'),
