(326, 'Masque Milano Luci Ed Ombre', 'Masque Milano Luci ed Ombre is an intoxicating blend of glamour and confidence that creates a contemporary, premium feeling whenever you inhale them. This masterpiece identifies a breathtaking fusion of strength and elegance, manifested in the majesty of incense, blended in tuberose, ginger, and jasmine. Olibanum, cedar, and patchouli rhyme together at the base to share in that instinctive style and complement that distinct look. Youâ€™ll never stop inhaling them.', 100, 7541700.0, 7541700.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
