(59, 'Dunhill Century For Men', 'Specially formulated to embody the spirit of the future itself, Dunhill Century is a refreshing blend that strikes a beautiful balance between clean and heady, approachable and exotic. It makes an energetic first impression via crisp top notes of juicy grapefruit and mandarin enhanced by just the right touch of sweet bergamot. It then finishes strong with toasty base notes of sandalwood, neroli, and exotic olibanum. This is a fragrance thatÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s an ideal fit for the modern man Ã¢â‚¬â€œ optimistic, innovative, and completely one of a kind. The scent itself is presented in a simple but striking bottle of clear glass that artfully juxtaposes a series of curves and contours.', 135, 1000500.0, 1000500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/5/85715806529_dunhill_century_for_men_135_ml.jpg'),
(309, 'Oud Lover Aldukhoon Alnadera Home Fragrance Set', 'A group of the most luxurious oriental scents and fragrances gathered in an elegant and distinctive box that you can present as a gift to everyone you love on happy occasions. The scent was designed mixed with an exciting oriental character that adds to the place an oriental prestige to remain in the atmosphere around you for long hours.', 100, 1290300.0, 1290300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/1/7/17955053-oud_lover-_.png'),
(20, 'Givenchy Irresistible Givenchy', 'Very IrrÃƒÂ©sistible Givenchy Eau de Toilette was inspired by the relationship between Hubert de Givenchy and his first muse and Launched in 2003. French style and elegance meet classic Hollywood glamour, feminine rose blossoms are mixed with a tangy edge of star anise and verbena leaf to make this iconic fragrance a spirited alternative to the traditional floral scent.', 50, 2456400.0, 2456400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/2/3274872400733_givenchy_irr_edp_80ml_1.jpg'),
(244, 'Creed Original Vetiver', 'Modern and sophisticated, Original Vetiver is a refreshing cologne for the active man. The masculine fragrance, launched in 2004, is inspired by the clean, clear scents of the great outdoors. Crisp bergamot and mandarin orange are the top notes. Juicy and sweet, they awaken you to a new day. A spicy kick of ginger clears your mind and energizes your body. Green vetiver stands out at the middle, grassy and deep in profile. Floral iris and creamy sandalwood add body and warmth. Musk and ambergris end the fragrance with an alluring sensuality, making you irresistible to those in your path. Wear this woody cologne to get in touch with nature.', 100, 10432800.0, 10432800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_creed_perfumes_original_vetiver_for_men_eau_de_perfum_3508441001091_1st.jpg'),
