(90, 'Elizabeth Arden Red Door', 'Elizabeth Arden Red Door is an irresistible floral, fruity and woody fragrance. A luxurious and elegant perfume for an irresistible presence. The opening of the perfume is a promising medley of lily of the valley, freesia with a light trace of violet. The heart of the composition is accentuated by a bouquet of red roses, giving it a romantic feeling. The flower combination goes on to include delicate, fresh and fragrant Moroccan orange flower, warm and sensuous jasmine and intoxicating ylang-ylang. The floral heart gives way to a masculine and sexy base that starts with a dose of honey, a splash of oak moss and sandalwood.', 100, 972900.0, 972900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/5/85805558420-elizabeth-arden-red-door-01.png'),
