(158, 'Amouage Library Collection Opus V', 'Opus V Perfume by Amouage is a classy perfume that first debuted in 2011 for both men and women. This unisex fragrance is perfect for romantic occasions, and it is the ideal choice when you want to make an impression. It features a dazzling composition that opens with rum and orris root as the top notes. These merge in the heart notes, which are a blend of jasmine, rose and iris. The woodsy base notes of Civetta and agarwood give it a fresh finish for a scent that is both charming and durable.', 100, 10577700.0, 10577700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/m/amouage_library_collection_opus_v_edp_100_ml.jpg'),
(32, 'Guerlain Insolence ', 'Guerlain Insolence Eau de Parfum is an innovation that stays true to the spirit of the Insolence Eau de Toillete but provides a more intense and exhilarating scent. The enticing combination of violets and iris set at the heart of the perfume. The addition of sweet berries and orange make it more delicious and feminine. The dry-down is a blissful mix of iris and violets. This fragrance is created for the ambitious cool woman, who welcomes new opportunities, fearlessly. Guerlain Insolence Eau de Parfum will sweep you off your feet to new, more exciting world.', 50, 2546100.0, 2546100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_guerlain_perfumes_insolence_for_women_eau_de_parfum_1_.jpg'),
