(32, 'Guerlain Le Petit Robe Noir Couture', 'Guerlain Le Petit Robe Noir Couture is glamorous, eccentric and effervescent. Black notes are dominant in this fragrance; black tea, black cherry, black rose and patchouli. The opening notes are fruity including black cherry, sparkling bergamot and raspberry. Rose takes the center of the heart. Deeper raspberry, tonka beans and more evident almond appear at the base, accentuated by black tea. The fragrance is presented in an elegant heart-shaped bottle with crystalline transparency. It displays a silhouette of a classy black dress. Elegant but flirty, peculiar but interesting, Guerlain Le Petit Robe Noir Couture is the perfect choice for a special woman.', 100, 2884200.0, 2884200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/3/63_guerlain_la_petit_robe_noir_edp_women_1.jpg'),
