(67, 'Alwaleef Bakhour Al Malaki', 'Due to the distinctive aroma of authentic incense throughout the ages, Bakhour Al Malaki was invented to preserve the wonderful heritage of incense with modern and easy solutions to last longer than ever with a choice of a pure and wonderful mixture of oud. It''s a modern solution for those with good taste.', 100, 1400700.0, 1400700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_home_fragrances_alwaleef_alwaleef_-_bakhour_al_malaki_6287006904066.jpg'),
