(320, 'Thierry Mugler Oriental Express', 'A captivating oriental parfume for men and women with an irresistible scent, giving you a fragrance with an authentic touch, thanks to its classical oriental notes, without losing its luxurious richness, a fragrance suitable for all times.', 80, 6527400.0, 6527400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_mugler_perfumes_oriental_express_edp_80_ml_for_unesex_3439604000319.jpg'),
(132, 'Angel Schlesser Les Eaux D''un Instant Absolu Sublime Rose EDP', 'A luxurious eastern palace on the vast desert lands surrounded with vital cypress.
