(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 351', 'Enjoy your special moments with this amazing fragrance. It opens with notes of spices, followed by tuberose in the middle and tonka bean in the base, forming a delicate scent with a soft touch that keeps you refreshed and chic at the same time.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000351-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-351-1.png'),
(109, 'Aigner Too Feminine', 'Aigner Too Feminine perfume is a floral fruity fragrance for women. It''s a combination of refreshing, cool, and, sweet aromas that perfectly suit the exciting summer season. The fragrance opens up with a fruit fiesta of juicy watermelon, tangy grapefruit, and sweet passionfruit. The heart is a bouquet of aromas with middle notes of jasmine, orange blossom, tuberose, violet, and magnolia. Setting it all on a sweet base of oakmoss, iris, vetiver, musk, amber, and sandalwood. Aigner Too Feminine is complemented with a girly pink and silver bottle, giving it a more flamboyant character to catch the eyes.', 100, 1690500.0, 1690500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_aigner_too_feminine.jpg'),
(11, 'Mont Blanc Legend Gift Set ', 'This fragrance for men will provide you with charismatic character you seek. With top notes of Lavender, Citrus and Bergamot, for a courageous aura, blended with White cedar, Rose, Sandalwood and Tonka beans that will let you enjoy a subtle, but unforgettable masculine fragrance.', 100, 2325300.0, 2325300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3386460105293_mont_blanc_mont_blanc_legend_eau_de_toilette_spray_100ml_eau_de_toilette_spray_7.5ml_after_shave_balm_100ml_men_1.jpg'),
(315, 'Alsalman Group For Oud Amber EDP', 'The flames of longing and magic begin in your heart with the first drops of this perfume
