About the Brand:
Kilian is a famous eco-friendly fragrance brand founded in Paris, created by Kilian Hennessy, characterized by the production of luxury goods, and its fragrances are distinguished by their unique and distinctive designs. The company emphasizes the environment and sustainability through the use of refillable and reusable packaging. Her fragrances were released in collaboration with the most talented perfume designers.', 50, 8549100.0, 8549100.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(86, 'Cartier Santos De Cartier', 'Santos de Cartier is a classic, rich, and woodsy scent for men that was launched in 1981. The warmth of this cologne makes it ideal for cold winter months or eveningwear. The light top notes of lavender and bergamot may seem odd for a menÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s cologne, but they are perfectly offset by bolder heart notes of juniper, nutmeg, and cumin. The blending of the light and bold notes results in an aroma that is both elegant and intense. The base notes round out the final scent by including aromatic patchouli, sandalwood, and cedarwood.', 100, 2739300.0, 2739300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/4/3432240003638-cartier-santos-de-cartier-01.jpg'),
(20, 'Givenchy Ange Ou Demon Le Secret', 'It''s a secret and mysterious legend in your soul. The refreshing and energetic oriental perfume features an aromatic blend enriched with delicious citrus extracts and tea leaves with cherries. The aroma of flowers provides you with special and distinctive beautiful touches that not only draw attention to you but it also overwhelms the hearts of all present with your love and adoration of your glowing femininity.', 100, 2829000.0, 2829000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/2/3274870002717-givenchy-givenchy-ange-ou-demon-le-secret-_l_-edp-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Armani Code EDP', 'This perfume arouses sweet memories of childhood, like ice cream at the beach and the surprising birthday cakes, thanks to its comforting scent.
Subtly fascinated with a mesmeric appeal, youÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ll be totally irresistible in the time it takes for a quick spritz of Armani Code perfume.
A spicy fragrance conjures up the majestic royal authority with a prevailing sense of peace and comfort.
