(47, 'Van Cleef & Arpels Coll Extraordinaire Rose Rouge Scented Candle ', 'A soft, aromatic refreshment that evokes feelings of joy. A delicately designed candle that adds a soft decorative touch to the place and fills the atmosphere with its lively scent to excite your feelings and give you the opportunity to rest and relax for long hours', 140, 1883700.0, 1883700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3386460115957-van-cleef-_-arpels-van-cleef-_-arpels-collection-extraordinaire-rose-rouge-scented-candle-140-g-1.png'),
(369, 'RPL Brise Venetienne EDP', '#NAME?', 100, 5361300.0, 5361300.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(156, 'Victoria''s Secret Pink Beach Flower Shimmer Body Mist', 'Be extra and sparkle on. Shimmer all day and every night with scented party glow perfection. The body freshener is formulated with a group of flowers and palm leaves that envelops your body with a soft and attractive aromatic aura with a shiny and exciting appearance for your delicate skin.', 250, 545100.0, 545100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/6/667548999403-victoria-secret-victoria_s-secret-pink-beach-flower-shimmer-body-mist-_u_-250-ml.jpg'),
(358, 'Maison Rebatchi Feu Patchouli EDP', 'A wonderfully composed symphony of carnation notes mixed with fragrant flowers, citruses and cinnamon.
