(28, 'Burberry Brit Rhythm Intense', 'Burberry Brit Rhythm Intense is a charming and enchanting fragrance, as it contains a powerful extract of luxurious leather perfumes blended perfectly with sage, pepper, mint and caraway extract, in addition to patchouli, amber, jujube wood, tonka beans and cashmere to form a unique and unique blend of the elegant man', 90, 1193700.0, 1193700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/_/2_3.jpg'),
(131, 'Paris Hilton Gold Rush', 'Gold Rush by Paris Hilton was launched in the year 2016. The fragrance of the perfume takes inspiration from the enchanting beauty of Old Hollywood Glamour. The top notes contain Bergamot, Lemon, and Nectarine. The heart notes contain Velvet Orchid, Rose petals, and Violet. The base notes contain Praline, Vanilla, and Cashmere Wood.', 100, 1752600.0, 1752600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_paris_hilton_perfumes_gold_rush_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(348, 'Goutal Paris Heure Exquise EDP', 'The epitome of English romance, full of fresh floral scents.
Iris chants about your beauty and elegance from its first moments to announce your unique presence.
A romantic fragrance to enjoy all your special moments
The fragrance is designed to accompany you on all your special occasions and capture the attention of everyone around you till the end of the day.', 100, 5789100.0, 5789100.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Emporio Armani Diamonds', 'Shine like movie stars with this impressive charming female perfume combination that was designed from grains of berries and delicious litchi with fragrant floral scents and drops of attractive amber. They all together overwhelm your soul with a strong and unique freshness and makes you discover for perfection. The fragrance has high power and stability that lasts with you until the last moments of the day.', 100, 2442600.0, 2442600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3605520380259-giorgio-armani-giorgio-armani-emporio-armani-diamonds-_w_-edp-50-ml-1.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 324', 'This floral fragrance is your ideal option to get the attention you need. Upper notes of jasmine are followed by lily of the valley in the middle and musk in the base, forming a unique composition with a long-lasting effect to boost your charm and complement your look.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000324-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-324-1.png'),
(327, 'Laurent Mazzone Ultimate Seduction', 'Laurent Mazzone Ultimate Seduction represents an array of sensual desires and elegance. It entwines a joyous fruity burst of invigorating cassis, orange, and pink pepper, blended in an irresistible oriental blend of sweet bouquets of rose, iris, and violet and wrapped by warm, sensuous notes of praline, patchouli, and amber. This symbol of seduction between men and women had a comprehensive understanding of men''s form and sensual desires. So close your eyes and follow your instincts!', 100, 8335200.0, 8335200.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(369, 'Laboratorio Olfattivo Vetyverso EDP', '#NAME?', 100, 3098100.0, 3098100.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(365, 'MiN NEW YORK Stardust EDP', 'An elegant fragrance made with notes of violet and carnation so you freshly start your day.
The floral heart evokes feelings of romance and comfort, boosting your feelings of entertainment.
