Don''t hesitate to try the distinctive fragrance which creates immortal memories in your mind.', 100, 9936000.0, 9936000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614227767836-gucci-gucci-the-virgin-violet-_u_-edp-100-ml.png'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 270', 'A luxurious fragrance that provides you with charming scent and elegant look to attract everyone. The composition features compelling notes of peach in the opening, jasmine in the heart and musk in the base, releasing a scent that gets you all the attention you want.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000270-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-270-1.png'),
(59, 'Dunhill London Icon Elite', 'Icon Elite was launched in 2016 representing the spirit of Dunhill brand and olfactive face of the contemporary British that celebrates the elegant man and his timeless style. The fragrance was characterized as woody and very masculine. Among keynotes of the new edition, vetiver and sandalwood were harmoniously blended and skillfully spiced with sweet cardamom.
Anout the brand:
Dunhill is a British luxury goods brand, specializing in ready-to-wear, custom and bespoke menswear, leather goods, and fragrances. The company is based in London, where it also owns and operates a leather workshop. Dunhill is currently owned by Richemont Holdings Limited and managed by CEO Andrew Maag.', 30, 883200.0, 883200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/5/85715806161_dunhill_dunhill_london_icon_elite_m_edp_30_ml_1.jpg'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Orchid Soleil', 'It is a vibrant, radiant, and sensual scent that is said to capture the magic of the most brilliant sunshine. The composition opens with spicy notes of pink pepper, bitter orange, and cypress. Its vibrant heart blooms with red spider lily and tuberose, enveloped by the warm base of chestnut cream, vanilla, patchouli, and orchid.', 50, 3850200.0, 3850200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066054300-tom-ford-tom-ford-orchid-soleil-_l_-edp-50-ml-1.jpg'),
(59, 'Dunhill London Icon Gift Set ', 'The classic gift set from Dunhill contains London Icon Eau de Parfum (100ml), Eau de Parfum (30ml), and shower gel (90ml). The men''s fragrance Dunhill London Icon opens with the ultimate blend of rare and expensive ingredients with a unique twist of masculinity and originality.', 100, 2035500.0, 2035500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/5/85715808974-dunhill-dunhill-london-icon-_m_-edp-100-ml-_-edp-30-ml-_-shower-gel-90-ml-gift-set-3-piece.jpg'),
(239, 'Joyau Unique & Sensoriel Parfums Sexy Crush Gold EDP', 'From the orient in India, with its vast forests, the wood comes with a powerful scent.
Oud is dipped in the Gurjan Balsam to deliver warmth and tranquility. Other rare components are added.
The composition is what you look for to boost your elegance and show your unique beauty in all occasions.
The notes of citron along with woods and tonka bean reflect your passion for life and freedom without restrictions.', 100, 6472200.0, 6472200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3665248000617-jus-parfums-jus-parfums-sexy-crush-gold-100ml_1.png'),
(45, 'Coach Platinum Set ', 'Coach Platinum Set is a two-piece gift set that was inspired by the spirit of the open road. The set contains a 100ml Eau De Perfum and a 7.5ml Eau De Perfum. As the name suggests, the two Eau de Perfum bottles have a platinum color that gives a magnetic and captivating impression that soon unveils an inside masculine aroma that keeps you fresh all day. This set is the perfect gift to give yourself or your loved ones.', 100, 2484000.0, 2484000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3386460100786_coach_platinum_edp_100_ml_platinum_edp_7.5_ml_shower_gel_100_ml_1.jpg'),
(325, 'Santi Burgas Lojazz', 'Santi Burgas Lojazz takes you on an enticing, sensorial voyage and crosses the sweetness borders. Blanca Dalmau is the talented nose behind this breathtaking floral fragrance. This fragrance promises its wearers a sensational harmony of jasmine, orange blossom, and violet petals. The aura creates a vibrant mood of cheerful vibes the second you wear it. You can wear Lojazz separately or as a top note for the other exciting Loant collection.', 50, 3574200.0, 3574200.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(27, 'Gucci Moonlight Serenade Acqua Profumata Perfumed Water', 'A cool relaxing breeze with notes of lavender and sage adds an attractive touch to your look.
The fragrance is induced with warm notes of tonka to boost your feeling of comfort and tranquility during your busy day.
Move on with enthusiasm, feel free and express the vitality of your soul in all your special occasions.
The fragrance is perfect for Summer and Spring, as it suits your look, working perfectly for both men and women.', 150, 7728000.0, 7728000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614227575981-gucci-gucci-moonlight-serenade-acqua-profumata-_u_-perfumed-water-150-ml.png'),
(126, 'Jean', 'A green chypre, oriental, and distinctive parfume with a fresh citrus breeze, blackcurrant, and galbanum. In the heart covers Florentine iris, jasmine essence, and Bulgarian rose, which are joined in the base note by vetiver, sandalwood, and oakmoss. The icon of imperishable stylish and femininity. A parfume like an abstraction work of art.', 50, 1235100.0, 1235100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_jean-louis_scherrer_perfumes_scherrer_2_for_women_eau_de_toilette_5050456007806_1.jpg'),
(49, 'Lalique Encre Noire A L''Extreme', 'Lalique Encre Noire A L''Extreme is an awesome oriental, woody fragrance for men. This magnificent, captivating and dark fragrance includes an extraordinary mix of the finest materials. This fragrance reconstructs masculinity giving it a powerful sensual edge. The opening is intriguing and perplexing with Elemi, Bergamot and Cypress. The heart beats sensually with the dark and lush notes of Vetyver, earthy Incense and Orris. This fragrance is quintessentially masculine, distinct and luxurious. Own the world by being the man of your dreams with Lalique Encre Noire A L''Extreme. Brilliance condensed in a bottle.', 100, 1200600.0, 1200600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_lalique_perfumes_encre_noire_a_l_extreme_for_men_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
