(17, 'Calvin Klein Secret Obsession', 'An elegant fragrance, floral and oriental, you will not be able to dispense with, it is a refreshing feminine fragrance full of vitality and departure, as well as suitable for evening times such as parties and special occasions, the packaging is designed to reflect elegance and femininity in its elegant shape!', 100, 1028100.0, 1028100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_calvin_klein_perfumes_secret_obsession_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(44, 'Bvlgari Eau Parfumee Au The Noir', 'Ã™ÂA classic authentic fragrance with Arabian oud, tobacco and leather that combines with tea and patchouli. This fragrance adds a luxurious and elegant appearance to look like members of the royal families', 75, 3650100.0, 3650100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/8/783320476105-bvlgari_eau_parfumee_au_the_noir_copy.png'),
(168, 'Jimmy Choo Urban Hero', 'Urban Hero is the new masculine parfume- a lyric to the ambiguous and independent Jimmy Choo man. With an underlying tone of mischief, he mixes elegance and susceptibility with a rebellious spirit. A woody aromatic Eau de parfum, the sweetness and extravagant undertones of priceless lemon caviar blends with the warmth of black pepper. Its heart unlock onto the carnality of rosewood and the elegance of vetiver before uncovering a base note that blends the urban sophistication of grey amber with an animalistic note of leather.', 100, 1669800.0, 1669800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3386460109369_jimmy_choo_urban_hero_edp_100_ml_1.jpg'),
(44, 'Bvlgari BLV II', 'An oriental fragrance with mandarin, licorice and anise that mixes with a soft scent of violet and iris. This fragrance leads you to an exciting adventure with touches of vetiver, tonka beans and amber to enjoy your special day with nature', 75, 2097600.0, 2097600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/v/bvlgari_b_l_v_ii_edp_75ml_1.jpg'),
