(77, 'Valentino Valentina', 'The Eau de Parfum Spray from the Valentina series of Valentino is a fresh, floral, fruity and oriental fragrance for women, presented in a gorgeous bottle. The fragrance opens with a bright citrusy note and a fragrant hint of white truffles. Tuberose emerges from the heart along with orange blossoms, with the uplifting combination of jasmine and strawberries. The distinctive base notes are deep with a mixture of cedar, vanilla and amber. A classy scent, Valentina Valentino is an ideal choice for spring and summer. It is sensual, seductive and breathtaking.', 80, 2056200.0, 2056200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_valentino_perfumes_valentina_for_women_eau_de_parfum.jpg'),
(112, 'La Perla In Rosa EDP', 'An exceptional fragrance for distinguished women seeking sophistication.
