The base notes of the perfume consists of the accords of patchouli, sandalwood and amber, giving you an elegant and attractive presence.
About the Brand:
La Perla is an Italian luxury lifestyle lingerie company, owned by German businessman Lars Windhorst. Founded by Couturier Ada Masotti in Bologna in 1954, the first fragrance from La Perla was introduced in 1986, in a sinuous bottle that reflects the feminine form. By the 1990s, La Perla was expanding both nationally and internationally, with stores in international fashion capitals Milan and Paris. La Perla expanded into ready-to-wear with the release of its first women''s collection in 2002. Continuing the luxury tradition of the house, the collection features feminine outfits in silk and chiffon.', 80, 855600.0, 855600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8002135114425-la-perla-laperla-in-rosa-_w_-edp-80-ml.png'),
