(93, 'Ad Astra By Minis', 'Stars were always the fascination of the wanderers. Ever since mythical stories were wrapped around the stars, "Ad AstraÃ¢â‚¬Â is your journey towards the stars. This set was created for the wanderers looking for some mystical powers!
