(24, 'Candy Addict Addictive Temptation Mini Hair Mists Set ', 'Candy Addict hair mists are now available in Ã¢â‚¬Å“minisÃ¢â‚¬Â to take with you wherever you go! They contain Vitamin E, a powerful antioxidant that moisturises, smoothes & adds shine to the hair! Can''t decide on your favorite scent? No problem! The Addictive Temptation set includes:
