(13, 'Juicy Couture Viva La Juicy La Fleur', 'Keep in touch with your hilarity, alluring side with the sweety viva la juicy la fleur for women. Your initiation will want to eat you right up when this hilarious scent strick their noses. luminous notes of mandarin orange and red berries produce a perfect impact, while delightful base notes of vanilla and caramel make them wanting more.', 75, 2145900.0, 2145900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/u/juicy_couture_viva_la_juicy_la_fleur_edt.jpg'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Code Sport', 'Armani Code Sport for men comes out in June 2011. Armani Code Sport radiates freshness, excitement, adrenaline and seduction at the same time, owing to its aromatic - woody composition. It refreshes with invigorating notes of lemon, mandarin and three kinds of mint, and opiates with gray amber (ambrox), ginger and vetiver. The advertising camping featuring Megan Fox also tells this new "Code Sport" story about the power and attractiveness of the male body as it moves beneath the glossy surface of the swimming pool at night, and the woman who awaits him ahead. Los Angeles night air is filled with fragrant magic, lust and dangerous attraction.', 50, 2801400.0, 2801400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/5/5/55_giorgio_armani_code_homme_sport_edt_men.jpg'),
(83, 'Montale Intense Black Aoud', 'Intense Black Oud by Montale is a unisex woody fragrance which was launched in the year 2017. The creator of this fragrance is Pierre Montale. the notes of the fragrance are Cambodian oud, Indonesian patchouli leaf, rose petals, mandarin orange, and musk. The main accords of the fragrance are citrus, rose, patchouli, musky, and warm spicy.', 100, 2697900.0, 2697900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_montale_intense_black_aoud_eau_de_parfume_1_1_.png'),
(208, 'Lootah Shurooq Fragrant Oil', 'For those looking for sophistication and brilliance, Lootah presents its Shurooq fragrant oil that evolves with every drop like a sunrise.
This luxurious blend of saffron and amber gently reveals a radiance equal to sunrise.p>
