(82, 'Viktor & Rolf Flower Bomb', 'An oriental floral fragrance made from high quality essential oils, it is considered one of the best selling parfumes in the world. FlowerBomb is a perfect fit for anything you wear, whatever your mood, this feminine parfume envelopes you in a bouquet of distinctive floral sensations and creates an exceptional impression that lasts until the end of the day.', 50, 3394800.0, 3394800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/v/i/viktor_rolf_flowerbomb_eau_de_parfum_2.jpg'),
(49, 'Lalique Fruits Du Mauvement', 'Fruits Du Mauvement is a Floral and Fruity fragrance that contains majestic scents that can give you the sexy aura that you need to mesmerize and captivate The composition starts with a playful mandarin note accompanied by a tangy shade of black pepper and a sharp hint of ginger. The heart is a burst of fruity scents, exhilarating jasmine absolute and classy plums. The dry-down closes with cashmeran, sweet amber and sexy sandalwood. Fruits Du Mauvement is a bewitching, irresistible fragrance that uplifts the spirits and boosts the mood. It is a perfect scent for daytime and warm weather.', 100, 6796500.0, 6796500.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(69, 'Fendi L''Acquarossa Gift Set ', 'This set includes: L''Acquarossa 75ml + Shower Gel 75ml + Body Lotion 75ml
This incredible fragrance comes with notes of White Musk And Patchouli. Exudes an uncompromised appeal, which is sure to linger. An oriental fragrance with a strong personality, yet surprisingly fresh.', 75, 3077400.0, 3077400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/2/3274872277953-fendi-fendi-l_aquarossa-_w_-edp-75-ml-shower-gel-75-ml-_-body-lotion-75-ml-gift-set-3-piece-1.jpg'),
(137, 'Michael Kors Exotic Blossom', 'Exotic Blossom Eau de Parfum is a fruity sweet popular parfume that designed for women to transport them to a tropical oasis with its hypnotic aroma. It combines mango and rose notes for a vibrant scent, while woodsy musk delivers a warmth of carefree days.', 50, 2435700.0, 2435700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_michael_kors_perfumes_exotic_blossom_for_women_eau_de_perfum_22548392799.jpg'),
