(90, 'Elizabeth Arden Green Tea Exotic', 'Elizabeth Arden Green Tea Exotic is a floral fruity fragrance for women. A beautiful, clean and fresh scent filled with a feminine notes. The fragrance opens with a sharp citrusy mix of bergamot and lime against a background of black tea. The heart sparkles with green tea. Tropical floral scents surface with a striking touch of orchid combined with lily tones and purple vine blossom scent. The base is pleasantly woody, ambery and floral. Elizabeth Arden Green Tea Exotic is a fresh and energetic fragrance that is perfect for summer days.', 100, 1131600.0, 1131600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/e/l/elizabeth_arden_green_tea_exotic_edt_100_ml.png'),
