(63, 'Dior Addict', 'Dior launches Addict Eau de Toilette, a rebranded version of their original 2002 Dior Addict Eau de Parfum. This 2012 Addict Eau de Toilette featured two more editions, Dior Addict Eau Fraiche and Dior Addict Eau Sensuelle, and a year after that Dior Addict Eau Delice was also launched. Dior Addict Eau de Toilette is a fresh oriental, floral fragrance that offers notes of Sicilian mandarin in the top, Sambac jasmine and Tunisian neroli in the heart, and vanilla and sandalwood in the base.', 100, 3070500.0, 3070500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/i/dior_addict_edt.jpg'),
