(63, 'Dior Higher Energy', 'Youthful and invigorating, Higher Energy is an uplifting cologne for the modern guy. Released in 2003, its blend of fresh and spicy ingredients powers you through your day. Pineapple, juniper berry, melon and grapefruit sparkle at the top. The bright, juicy scents infuse the fragrance with energy while sweet mint refreshes the mind. Pepper, nutmeg, and frankincense keep up that energy with a spicy bite. Cedar, sandalwood, oakmoss, vetiver, and musk add a layer of sexy green sweetness, making for a masculine base. Fuel yourself with pure motivation when you wear this inspiring fragrance.', 100, 3795000.0, 3795000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/i/dior_higher_energy_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
