(60, 'S.T. DUPONT Passenger', 'Passenger for Women by S.T. Dupont is a women fragrance that celebrates the original S.T. Dupont scent. The fragrance opens with an opulent fruity explosion consisting of citrusy bergamot and green mandarin softened by pear notes and earthy black current. The heart consists of cyclamen, creamy gardenia, and romantic rose giving the heart a sensual feel. The dry-down is a sweet and luxurious combination of powdery iris, sexy sandalwood and velvety musk. Passenger for Women is a long-lasting, feminine and elegant perfume presented in a exquisite bottle. Spoil yourself with this breathtaking scent.', 100, 1028100.0, 1028100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/t/st_dupont_passenger.jpg'),
