(326, 'Masque Milano Montecristo', 'Imagine a scene of a comfortable leather couch and a coffee table, where a deck of playing cards and burning tobacco are placed over. Once a glass of rum appears in this scene, a feeling of warmth and reassuring comfort of Masque Milano Montecristo looms on the horizon. This modern bowl of bliss starts with the undeniable seductive scent of ambrette, rum, and Cabreuva at the top to feel fresh and comfortable. The heart identifies a unique blend of celery seeds, labdanum, and benzoin, leaving you in ecstasy. This aroma adds its final magic touch with hyrax, styrax, and guaiac wood notes, ensuring that the fragrance is the star of the show.', 100, 7541700.0, 7541700.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
