(111, 'Carolina Herrera Insignia Men Limited Edition', 'A wonderful and imaginative fragrance that gives you a sense of comfort, happiness and elegance at every moment you live, and is one of the wonderful fragrances that will amaze your partner! Suitable for parties and special occasions.A luxurious limited-edition fragrance, an unabashed show of intent, with the dark leather flacon covered with a resplendent gold Ã¢â‚¬Å“CHÃ¢â‚¬Â clasp, making the bottle as distinctive as the scent housed within. The golden bottle cap is concentric, featuring the Ã¢â‚¬Å“CHÃ¢â‚¬Â INSIGNIA proudly etched on top, reflective of the statement fragrance it represents. A majestic duet paints the tapestry of this masculine signature, with the Ã¢â‚¬Å“liquid goldÃ¢â‚¬Â of Oud adding weight to the luxurious base, while Patchouli lends the scent a more earthy edge. A floral green middle of Rose & Violet are revealed following a spicy opening of Cinnamon and bittersweet Saffron.', 100, 3553500.0, 3553500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/4/8411061962954_carolina_herrera_ch_men_limited_edition_edp_100_ml_1.jpg'),
(189, 'Solinotes Ylang EDP', 'With the fresh and lively summer sunrise, start your special day with the scents of ylang-ylang.
