Enjoy a rich scent that is elegant, fresh and spicy at the same time.
The artistic blend takes you to the rocky forest in southeast Asia, where the roses bloom releasing a strong scent.', 180, 8942400.0, 8942400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8028713810022-acqua-di-parma-81002-sig--osmanthus-edp-180ml.png'),
(348, 'Goutal Paris Eau du Sud EDT', 'A spicy fragrance that refreshes your soul every summer day
