(20, 'Givenchy Gentleman Set ', 'Givenchy Gentlemen is a collection of three sensational scents; the woody, floral and dynamic. Givenchy Gentlemen Masculine is perfume for adventurous, energetic men. The combination of citrus, rosemary and iris will fill you up with powerful energy. The top notes are pear and cardamom. The heart notes are none other than iris and lavender. The fragranceÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s base notes are patchouli Ã¢â‚¬â€œ leather accord and black vanilla. Vitality is a given once you spray Givenchy Gentlemen. Freshness, vibrancy and freedom will overflow with this powerful fragrance. This modern scent is very masculine and seductive. It is a ManÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s scent.', 100, 3146400.0, 3146400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/2/3274872356924_givenchy_gentleman_edt_100_ml_travel_spray_15_ml_1.jpg'),
(378, 'Thameen Fragrance RiviÃ¨re Body Lotion ', '-The sunrise announces the beginning of a new day, and the floral scents blended with lemon leaves announce the beginning of a refreshing aromatic journey.
