(63, 'Dior Pure Poison', 'Pure Poison is a romantic perfume for sultry evenings. Bold and powerful, this 2004 release enchants with a sensual strength. Irresistible bergamot captivates at the top. Luscious and bright, it instantly draws you in. Fresh jasmine and gardenia thrust a lush powder into the fragrance. Their hypnotizing aromas create a dreamy experience. Musk, amber, and sandalwood are the base notes, layering on a luxurious cream. Pure Poison by Dior is your go-to accessory to complement your look for any evening occasion. Wear this alluring scent to seduce the object of your desire.', 100, 3795000.0, 3795000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/i/dior_les_poison_pure_eau_de_parfum_1.jpg'),
