(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 336', 'Enjoy your special moments with this luxurious fragrance. The upper notes feature bergamot, followed by leather in the heart and chocolate in the base, bringing to you a warm scent with a sensual touch that reminds you of those unforgettable memories with a long-lasting effect.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000336-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-336-1.png'),
