(11, 'Mont Blanc Explorer', 'It is an amazing woody fragrance, designed for men. It''s a fragrance that tells the story of adventures, quests and aspirations, in addition to exploring the world. High notes consist of Clary Sage, Pink Pepper, Bergamot, while bottom notes consist of Vetiver, Leather, Cedarwood. This complete blend gives an attractive fragrance.', 100, 1414500.0, 1414500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3386460101035c-mont-blanc-explorer---100-ml.jpg'),
(32, 'Ti amo Set', 'This set contains:
- Givenchy Eau De Moiselle - 100 ml
Create a vintage vibe around your outfit by wearing Eau Demoiselle perfume from Givenchy. This fragrance is wholly on its own. It is not quite modern but not quite traditional. It exists on its own terms with a composition that consists of notes of Italian winter lemon, tangerine, ylang-ylang, rose, Japanese basil, tonka, ambrette seed, and musk. Eau Demoiselle offers the sensation of walking through a garden on a dewy morning. Its composition was developed by the expert perfumer, Francois Demachy. This perfume is available in a gorgeous, cylindrical flacon.
- Givenchy Xeryus Rouge - 100 ml
Xeryus the first oriental perfume for men by Givenchy, is a sensual and seductive fragrance created to impress. This intriguing fragrance presents an ideal balance of sweet amber, delicate carnation, attractive cypress, spicy sandalwood, aromatic juniper berries, earthy floral geranium, creamy leather and manly musk. The classy and masculine scent is befitting of your perfect summer night. Sweetness mixed with spiciness makes the perfume irresistible. The freshness and spiciness combination makes the fragrance both classy and chic. The epitome of charm; Xeryus is a masculine fragrance made for you. Make your presence known.', 100, 3864000.0, 3864000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/b/sb100420_ti_amo.png'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Lei', 'It is an oriental fragrance for women. It heps you to feel fresh all the day. Use it and enjoy a great mood. Must have!', 100, 3339600.0, 3339600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_giorgio_armani_perfumes_lei_elle_she_ella_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(24, 'Candy Addict Colourful Moments Hair Mist Set ', 'Candy Addict hair mists are now available in Ã¢â‚¬Å“minisÃ¢â‚¬Â to take with you wherever you go! They contain Vitamin E, a powerful antioxidant and Provitamin B5 that moisturises, smoothes & adds shine to the hair! Can''t decide on your favourite scent? No problem! The Colourful Moments set includes:
Purple Rain:
Falling from afar from a magical world full of flowers and purple roses, dreamy and delicate, touching your hair and returning again with its abundant aroma and musky notes that will last for a long time.
Pink Moon:
As soon as it''s there, it controls the vibes, and when it appears, it announces a new beginning in which flowers bloom to spread their oriental fragrance in your hair. A long-lasting fragrance for your hair with a wonderful and harmonious blend of raspberry, caramel and leather.
Blue Light:
Its fragrance radiates everywhere and anytime without stopping, captivating you with its beauty, so you follow its long-lasting fragrance among fruit trees, which flow in your hair with great softness.
Moisturize, soften and strengthen your hair with Vitamin E, a powerful antioxidant, and Provitamin B5. Give your hair that extra shine and volume that it deserves, whilst leaving your hair less prone to breakage.
How to use:
From about 20 cm away, spritz the mist evenly over your hair.
Then go out and be awesome!
Don''t forget to shake the bottle before use to liven up the candy!
Reapply throughout the day whenever you need a dose of fabulousness!', 100, 1028100.0, 1028100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/-/c-candyaddict-minis-hairmist-1.jpg'),
(244, 'Creed Erolfa', 'This Eau de parfum is inspired by family memories of sailing on a beautiful yacht. Its scent embodies the sparkling seas, salty air and citrus-scented breeze with its marvelous notes that feature Bergamot, Lemon, Orange, Violet, Cumin, Basil, Rosemary and Melon on the top. The heart has notes of Cyclamen, Jasmine, Ginger, Coriander and Pepper, coming in a base of Cedarwood, Sandalwood, Oakmoss, Amber and Musk.', 100, 10432800.0, 10432800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/5/3508441001015_creed_creed_erolfa_eau_de_parfum_100ml_1_1_.jpg'),
(95, 'COZY Ocean Breeze Room Spray ', 'Best for:
- Bathroom & storage room
- Lavender & musk scent lovers
- Sophisticated & elegant atmosphere
Reasons to buy:
- Long-lasting
- Anti-bacterial
- Suitable for big spaces
- Luxurious Oriental scent
Descent into a mystical reality with this beautiful anti-bacterial home fragrance, Ocean Breeze. Discover the elegance it hides within, and enjoy its magnificent Oriental scent. What makes this home fragrance unique, is the rich base made from fresh musk and ignited first by its flowery soft accords of lavender & lily of the valley. Perfect to add a sophisticated touch within seconds to all your rooms!', 500, 683100.0, 683100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/o/copy_of_cozy_ocean_breeze_room_spray_-_500ml.png'),
