(44, 'Bvlgari Rose Goldea Gift Set 50 ml + 15 ml Gift Set', 'Description
After the great success of Goldea, Bvlgari launches its successor Rose Goldea in July 2016. It focuses on the intoxicating sweetness of exotic ylang-ylang flowers mingling with elegant white flowers of jasmine and neroli, while the warmth comes from Goldea''s creamy shades of musk. It is feminine and seductive, but its beauty is reflected in the softness of rose petals. Pomegranate opens it at the top of the composition. As the fragrance develops, the emphasis is on the Damascus rose absolute and jasmine, supported by musk, creamy sandalwood, and olibanum. The smell is very expressive, with a distinctive oriental aroma.', 100, 2925600.0, 2925600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/8/783320401121-bvlgari-bvlgari-rose-goldea-_w_-edp-50-ml-edp-15-ml-gift-set-2-piece.jpg'),
(102, 'Who Am I Just Wow EDP ', 'Who Am I? In this modern world, Am I ready to break the norms & go all Wow? Beyond the walls of the ordinary, I Am sweet like the cardamom notes, calm but ready to flower like peonies, & can strike you with my fresh sandalwood aroma anytime, anywhere!  Exclusive only at Golden Scent.', 100, 1028100.0, 1028100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/h/who_am_i_just_wow_1.jpg'),
(319, 'Jovan Black Musk', 'The unique legendary perfume suits classic men. Its amazing long-lasting blend has attractive notes, where woody notes meet with musk to create a strong masculine fragrance. The perfume gives you a mysterious and captivating scent. It was launched in 2009.
About the Brand:
Established in Chicago in 1968 by Bernard Mitchell, Jovan Musk is a sophisticated production line for the production of perfumes. In 1972, Bernard Mitchell began designing different perfumes for both genders and he also offers different types of aftershave and deodorant products. Their scents are commonly sold in pharmacies and supermarket chains and are described as a mixture of uncommon spices and woods that meet the authentic strength of musk. The products are known for their high quality and strong scent that lasts long.', 88, 386400.0, 386400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3607341046734-jovan-jovan-black-musk-_m_-edc-88-ml-1.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 373', 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 373 is a lively blend of beautiful, pure, and seductive flowers. This perfume creates a happy romantic atmosphere, where the sweet, delicate freesia and osmanthus scents open it up. The cocoa appears at the base to reveal all the charm and elegance you need to feel comfortable and confident during this joyful, romantic encounter.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000373-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-373-1.png'),
(208, 'Lootah Bint Al Shyookh Small Jar Incense ', 'An amazing incense with oriental scent, made of the wonderful lavender extract that fills the place and spreed a feeling of comfort and freshness all around. The scent is strong, highly concentrated and long-lasting.', 100, 1890600.0, 1890600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6297000836508-lootah-lootah-bint-al-shyookh---small-jar-incense-77.png'),
(225, 'Bond No 9 Central Park West EDP', 'Soft pink melodies with notes of ylang ylang and fresh vital lime.
It''s a luxurious composition for both men and women with delicate floral heart with notes of gardenia that spread around.
The intense base evoke feelings of confidence inside and deliver a sensation of joy.
The notes of oakmoss come in the base making the scent softer while remaining for a long time.', 100, 9949800.0, 9949800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888874002401-bond-no.9-bond-no.9-central-park-west-_u_-edp-100-ml.png'),
(33, 'Lacoste Eau De Lacoste L.12.12 Green', 'L.12.12. Green is a natural relaxing fragrance with citrus notes of Italian bergamot, grapefruit and iced melon. There are also the extracts of verbena, blue lavender, thyme, birch leaf and fig. Lacoste L.12.12. design is simple and elegant with the brandÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s sophistication and symbolism. The bottles are sleek and minimalistic with a distinctive logo of the brand - the famous crocodile embroidered cloth. The texture on the surface of the bottle reminds of that of a polo shirt.', 100, 2035500.0, 2035500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/a/lacoste_l12.12_green.jpg'),
(71, 'Hermes L''Ambre des Merveilles Calligraphie', 'It is an oriental vanilla charismatic fragrance for women. It captures aromatic notes of amber, labdanum, vanilla, and patchouli.', 100, 4402200.0, 4402200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346131794997-l_ambre-l_ambre-des-merveilles-calligraphie-_l_-edp-100-ml.jpg'),
(24, 'Candy Addict Berry B EDP ', 'Ready to be instantly transported to a tropical island full of tasty fruit and summer vibes? Berry B ensures you leave a deliciously addictive scent behind you everywhere you go! A perfect blend of raspberry, vanilla and freesia notes. Berry special indeed.', 50, 959100.0, 959100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/ca-berry-b-edp-1.jpg'),
(369, 'Gucci The Voice Of The Snake EDP', 'Let your hair breeze and feel refreshed every morning with this hair mist that has a distinctive fragrance.
