The base remains intense and concentrated for long hours, wrapping your hair with the scent of amber and sandalwood.', 50, 9936000.0, 9936000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(44, 'Bvlgari Aqva Pour Homme Marine', 'A fresh fragrance with seaweed that mixes with green grasses, tangerine fruits and refreshing grapefruit. This fragrance adds vitality and attractive sense for an irresistible look in all your parties.', 50, 2070000.0, 2070000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/v/bvlgari_aqva_pour_homme_marine.jpg'),
(362, 'Dali Haute Parfumerie Ma Force EDP', 'Mysterious power from the surreal sea comes with a charming scent.
It''s inspired by the mysterious power in the busy party with notes of bergamot and spicy black pepper.
