The intense oriental base has notes of oud and sandalwood, delivering self confidence and comfort for a long time.', 100, 6699900.0, 6699900.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(118, 'Ibraheem AlQurashi Musk Collection Cardamom EDP', 'Elegant charming musky notes inspired by oriental style.
A powerful spicy composition infused with cardamom, delivering a glowing elegant fragrance.
An intense scent that remains for long hours, drawing your oriental identity and boosting your elegance.
It''s a special rich fragrance that captivates the hearts of everyone around.', 70, 793500.0, 793500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/1/0/1010372331_ibrahim_alqurashi_musk_collection_-_cardamom.png'),
(27, 'Gucci Guilty Stud', 'Gucci Guilty Stud Pour Femme is a sheer, floral-oriental fragrance, opens with a bright burst of citrus and a dangerous hint of black pepper. This arresting introduction gives way to full-throttle femininity as its heart pulses with fruity and floral notes. The fragrance dries down to a rich, ambery base with notes of patchouli.', 50, 3850200.0, 3850200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/gucci_gucci_guilty_stud_eau_de_toilette_1.jpg'),
(121, 'IL Profvmo Caramella D''Amore EDP', 'Feel the happiness and joy on all your days with this fragrance sweetened with delicious nuts
The delicious top provide the chance to taste the sweetness of pistachio, before it declares the presence of hazelnut wrapped with cotton candy
The delicate floral base has notes of violet, which adds to the softness of the scent, delivering a feeling of fantasy and romance.
It''s a passionate fragrance that remains for long hours, becoming the perfect option on romantic days and occasions in winter.', 100, 4761000.0, 4761000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(32, 'Guerlain L''instant De Guerlain', 'Guerlain L''instant De Guerlain is a woody, aromatic fragrance for men. It is a scent that emits power and elegance; a scent that brings together exuberant virility and delicate femininity. The Indian vetiver highlights this scent. This scent embraces paradoxes in its dazzling collection of perfectly balanced scents. The opening notes are bergamot, star anise, lemon, pepper and citrus. At the heart there are jasmine, tea, hibiscus and smoke. The base notes are the rich sandalwood and the unique patchouli. Guerlain L''instant De Guerlain is a very unique and elegant scent to wear.', 100, 2035500.0, 2035500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_guerlain_perfumes_l_instant_de_guerlain_for_men_eau_de_toilette_1.jpg'),
(159, 'Tiffany & Co. Limited Edition', 'This artisanal, modern, charming scent is infused with noble iris at its heart, which is as invigorating and inspiring as love itself. Its fragrance will capture your senses from the first moment. You can personalize the bottle with any custom engraving to make it the ideal gift.', 50, 4243500.0, 4243500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614226500090-tiffany-_-co.-tiffany-_-co.-limited-edition-_w_-edp-50-ml.jpg'),
(1, 'Dolce & Gabbana The One Men EDP', 'Dolce and Gabbana The One For Men A new iriental woody fragrance that is more intense and enhances the magnetic charm of man. Suitable for night and worth trying.', 50, 2256300.0, 2256300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_dolce_gabbana_perfumes_the_one_for_men_eau_de_parfum_100ml_1_.jpg'),
(97, 'WAW Leather EDP ', 'Explore the scent of Aristocracy luxury, featuring the original scent of leather. Enjoy this wonderful & powerful addition to your aromatic collection. Our advice: Try "Leather" perfume with other fragrances from the "WAW" collection to create your own perfume.', 50, 655500.0, 655500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/w/a/waw-leather1.png'),
(55, 'Hugo Boss Collection Velvet Amber', 'A new and attractive perfume for men and women, this perfume is one of the unique Hugo Boss collection inspired by the luxurious Hugo Boss fashion and luxury fabrics, and they contain various elegant components. Velvet Amber Velvet comes to you with a mixture of royalty ingredients that reflect sophistication and luxury!', 50, 5292300.0, 5292300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_hugo_boss_perfumes_collection_velvet_amber_for_unisex_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(28, 'Burberry Brit Rhythm Floral', 'Burberry introduced the fragrant pair inspired by the British rock scene; Brit Rhythm for Him was launched first in September 2013., followed by the feminine edition Brit Rhythm for Her in 2014. In February 2015, new flankers of the fragrances are coming out - Brit Rhythm for Him Intense and Brit Rhythm for Her Floral. Brit Rhythm Floral for Her is a sensual floral composition enriched with citrus fruit. It opens with fresh accords of lemon from Sicily and orange. The heart notes are floral tones of Egyptian jasmine, lotus, and lilac. Woods, amber, and musk end the composition.', 90, 1028100.0, 1028100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/burberry_brit_rhythm_floral_for_woman.jpg'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Si Passione Red Maestro', 'Unleash your passion and liberate your power with this exquisite, feminine fragrance that allows you to enjoy an amazing blend of black currant, pink pepper, and musk.', 100, 3036000.0, 3036000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614272635838_giorgio_armani_si_passione_red_maestro_edp_100_ml_1.jpg'),
(317, 'Estelle Vendome Infinite Pleasure Only Girl EDP', 'This fragrance is a flirty contrast of dewy rosebuds and vibrant fruits and woods. It offers two contrasting accords: a dewy rose accord capturing your feminine side with a juicy fruitiness, fresh floral bursts, and a sparkling vibrancy. The tempting woods accord reflects your undeniably sensuous side with accents of Jasmine Absolute, Magnolia, and other polished woods, Sheer Vanilla and Ambrette Seeds.', 100, 579600.0, 579600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/placeholder/default/image_4.jpg'),
(28, 'Burberry Summer', 'Description
It is a floral, citrus, and woody fragrance that begins with mandarin orange, mint, and juniper berries. The heart includes spicy thyme laid on the woody-musky base. All in all, the scent is very fresh and dynamic.', 100, 1324800.0, 1324800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/5/0/5055497988061-burberry-burberry-summer-_m_-edt-100-ml.jpg'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Acqua Di Gio Absolu Instinct', 'A warm and soft woody base of ebony and amber bears an energetic and refreshing heart of patchouli and seaweed led to it by delicious citrus drops in a perfect aromatic mixture that improves your unique masculine beauty and shows the power of your bold heart to enhance the attraction and excitement for everyone who has eyes on you. The fragrance is ideally suited for mornings, evenings, and nights.', 75, 2829000.0, 2829000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614272436473-giorgio-armani-giorgio-armani-acqua-di-gio-absolu-instinct-_m_-edp75-ml-1.jpg'),
