This home incense has a distinctive Arabian scent that fast spreads in your homes and covers every corner with the elegant Arabian scent of sandalwood and musk.', 100, 627900.0, 627900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/b/sb100296-droob-sedr-alkhaleej.jpg'),
(12, 'Parfums de Marly Oriana EDP', 'Express your charming femininity with a beautiful touch of fragrance.
