The scent of this perfume enhances your self-confidence and ensures you a day full of relaxation and vitality.', 50, 3105000.0, 3105000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(244, 'Creed Royal Princess Oud Millesime', 'Royal Princess Oud Milesime, by Creed, was launched in 2015 for women. The word Milesime appears on many of Creed''s fragrances as a mark of quality and means that the best crops from a particular year''s harvest were used in that bottle. This floral fragrance opens with top notes from rose, the queen of flowers; powdery violet; and the fresh, complex scent of bergamot. The floral heart features sweet jasmine, Tuscan iris with its earthy aroma and the musk of patchouli, smoothed and sweetened by vanilla. Warm, exotic orientals comprise the base: Siam benzoin; deep, woody oud; resinous and sweet styrax; and milky sandalwood, with its lingering sweetness.', 75, 12178500.0, 12178500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_creed_perfumes_royal_princess_oud_millesime_for_men_eau_de_perfum_3508441104648_1st.jpg'),
(379, 'Lucien Ferrero Maitre Parfumeur Pour Lui EDP', 'Unknown', 100, 6348000.0, 6348000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(43, 'Lava Moments Oud Wood Diffuser Refill With Reed Sticks ', 'It''s a sophisticated, daring scent that keeps the atmosphere refreshed in the summer, adding to the charm of the place. The notes of cardamom and oriental oud spread in the place delivering a classic touch with notes of leather. The diffuser refill comes to you with red sticks so you have additional stock of the fragrance.', 250, 2111400.0, 2111400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2021060000043-lava-moment-lava-moments-oud-wood-diffuser-refill---250-ml.png'),
