(4, 'Mancera Aoud Orchid', 'This sensual fragrance blends orchid with fresh citrus fruits and intense woody notes, giving a wonderful scent for men and women. It features mandarin, peach and coconut at the top, while the heart has notes of orchid and Patchouli. The base contains notes of amber, vanilla and white musk.', 120, 2035500.0, 2035500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_mancera_perfumes_aoud_orchid_for_unisex_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(133, 'Kenzo Aqua Pour Femme', 'Boost your confidence with this aromatic fragrance for women, which will provide you with freshness. Its water-inspired notes will make you feel the freshness with the blend of notes that include sesame, apple, mixed with amber and musk.', 50, 2090700.0, 2090700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/2/3274872357136_kenzo_kenzo_aqua_pour_femme_edt_50_ml_1.jpg'),
(36, 'Narciso Rodriguez For Her Amber Musk', 'Amber Musc is an Oriental frangrance that was made for women by Narciso Rodriguez. Amber Musc was launched in 2013. The nose behind this fragrance is Aurelien Guichard. Top notes are orange blossom and musk; middle notes are agarwood (oud), patchouli and leather; base notes are vanilla, incense and amber.', 100, 5485500.0, 5485500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/n/a/narciso_rodriguez_for_her_amber_musc_eau_de_parfum_1.jpg'),
(369, 'Gucci The Eyes Of The Tiger EDP', 'An air freshener is infused with an exciting fruity breeze that spreads quickly in the air to freshen your breath and gives you a high sense of joy and pleasure. The bottle is elegantly designed to be a luxurious decorative piece in the place.', 500, 9936000.0, 9936000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(37, 'Chanel Egoiste Aftershave Lotion ', 'Feel the comfort and tranquility with the aromatic freshness of lavender and rosemary. The fresh after-shave lotion will delicately scent your skin, moisturizing and enveloping it in a modern captivating scent.
Benefits:
It reduces irritation and redness as well as dryness of the skin.
How to use:
Put an adequate amount on the skin after shaving then massage in a circular motion until absorbed.', 100, 2753100.0, 2753100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/1/3145891140705-chanel-chanel-egoiste-pour-homme-_m_-aftershave-lotion-100-ml.png'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 185', 'Enjoy this fantastic perfume with its unique scent that provides you with refreshing feeling and boosts your confidence. It also reflects the charm of your personality and gives you a special attractiveness with a ideal essential blend that''s rich in amazing green apple, cedar to make men and women attractive and full of refreshing scents through the day and night.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000185-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours---perfume-day-185-1_1_.png'),
(1, 'Dolce & Gabbana Dolce', 'A pleasant floral fragrance filled with femininity and composed of white flowers in harmony with oil of bitter Aurantium and white amaryllis, which is a flower from South Africa used for the first time in designing a perfume, it is a bold mixture, unique and completely rich.', 50, 2063100.0, 2063100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/o/dolce_gabbana_dolce_eau_de_parfum_1.jpg'),
(136, 'Salvatore Ferragamo Incanto Heaven', 'Salvatore Ferragamo Incanto Heaven is a feminine, floral-fruity composition which was launched in the year 2007. The top notes of the perfume are a mix of grapefruit and sering flowers and apple notes. The heart notes are floral notes of a blend of peony and hibiscus with the fruity touch of apricot. The base notes are violet, musk and iris root.', 100, 1041900.0, 1041900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_salvadore_ferragamo_perfumes_incanto_heaven_for_women_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(33, 'Lacoste Eau de Lacoste L.12.12 Jaune', 'It is a scent that triggers optimism, joy, and positive energy. Fresh and citrusy, aromatic-fruity, it represents sunshine rays in a bottle. Opening with accords of grapefruit, it develops into the heart of golden delicious apples. The base is aromatic-woody, made of cypress accords.', 175, 924600.0, 924600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/3/737052896298-lacoste-lacoste-eau-d-lac.-l.12.12-jaune-opt.men-edt-175ml.jpg'),
(69, 'Fendi Fan Di Fendi Acqua', 'Fan di Fendi pour Homme Acqua is a fragrance by Fendi for men and was created in 2013. The fragrance is aquatic-fresh. It was last marketed by LVMH.', 100, 1476600.0, 1476600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/a/fan-di-fendi-pour-homme-acqua-fragrance-eau-de-toilette1.jpg'),
(32, 'Guerlain Shalimar Cologne', 'Four centuries ago in India, the emperor Shah Jahan ordered the creation of the most luxurious gardens of Shalimar as a setting for his love for his beloved wife, the princess Mumtaz Mahal, . Later, he erected the Taj Mahal, a marvel admired by the entire world. This fabulous story inspired Jacques Guerlain to create this exquisitely seductive scent, the worldÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s very first oriental fragrance: Shalimar. Guerlain Perfumer Thierry Wasser has created a new interpretation of this legendary scent.', 100, 2580600.0, 2580600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470117600-guerlain-guerlain-shalimar-cologne-_w_-edt-90ml-1.jpg'),
