(218, 'Issey Miyake Nuit D''Issey Bleu Astral', 'Nuit d''Issey Bleu Astral is a fragrance by Issey Miyake for men and was created in 2017. The fragrance is modern and spicy. Nuit dÃ¢â‚¬â„¢Issey Bleu Astral a sparkling light in a dark night. The strength of the glamor of stars. When the sultriness of leather meets the activity of vetiver and ambery woods.', 75, 2311500.0, 2311500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_issey_miyake_perfumes_nuit_d_issey_bleu_astral_for_men_eau_de_toilette_3423474889051.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Violin', 'This sweet fragrance reflects happiness and joy all around. It takes you on a beautiful journey of captivating memories with its notes of pear and black currant at the top, in addition to Jasmine, Orange blossom and Iris at the heart. Its base has notes of tonka bean, patchouli, vanilla and almond.', 100, 1373100.0, 1373100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006900167_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_violin_100_ml_tayamun_1.jpg'),
(320, 'Thierry Mugler Woodissime', 'A woody parfume that suits both men and women, which resembles wearing a beautiful and expensive leather jacket. Thierry Mugler improved on some authentic and traditional parfumes to show this brilliant fragrance, which unexpectedly blends wood intensity with the brilliance of flowers, and fades with a soft, sharp woody sandalwood scent for long-lasting stability.', 80, 6527400.0, 6527400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_mugler_perfumes_woodissime_edp_80_ml_for_unesex_3439600010404.jpg'),
