(158, 'Amouage Epic', 'Travel across worlds with the exotic and fragrant Amouage Epic, a spellbinding menÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s cologne. This wholly original and mysterious blend fuses balsamic, smoky and spicy accords for an entirely male signature fragrance. Top notes of saffron, cardamom, pink pepper, and nutmeg open the scent with their rich, bold essences, while the heart notes of myrrh and geranium add a touch of vintage Oriental tradition. Base notes of patchouli, incense, oud, and leather finish the blend for a stunning balance of hazy, earthy-sweet elements that you can wear with confidence, day or night.', 100, 8976900.0, 8976900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_amouage_perfumes_epic_for_men_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(324, 'Fendi L''Aquarossa', 'Fendi L''acquarossa parfume by Fendi, The warmth of patchouli shock with the excessive of Sicilian mandarin in Fendi L''Acquarossa by Fendi. Smooth woody and floral notes intertwine in this honor to the passion feminine woman', 50, 3346500.0, 3346500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/f/e/fendi_l_aquarossa.jpg'),
(71, 'Hermes LÃ¢â‚¬â„¢Ambre Des Merveilles', 'Hermes LÃ¢â‚¬â„¢Ambre Des Merveilles is an amazing product with the amalgamation of mystery and marvels, warm and sensual, swathed in amber and vanilla.', 50, 3719100.0, 3719100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/_/l_ambre_des_merveilles_hermes.jpg'),
(35, 'Jaguar Classic Black', 'Jaguar Classic Black is a limited fougere oriental fragrance that portrays elegance and style. The top notes open with invigorating mandarin, bitter orange and green apples. The scent develops in the heart giving a spicy feel thanks to cardamom, black tea, musk and geranium. The dry-down leaves a nice trail owning to creamy notes of sandalwood, cedar, moss, vetiver and Tonka. Classic Black is a symbol of luxury, sophistication and refinement. This versatile fragrance is suitable for daywear and nights out, for breezy fall and sunny summer. Flaunt your charisma with Classic Black from Jaguar.', 100, 655500.0, 655500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/l/classic_black_edt_copy.jpg'),
(12, 'Parfums de Marly Sedley', 'Parfums de Marly Sedley is a fresh aromatic fragrance that is overflowing with citrus. It is ideal for ordinary wear. It is designed with a high-quality formula of grapefruit, bergamot, and mint, to offer you the perfect olfactory experience.
About the Brand:
De Marly is a leading French perfume brand. It offers luxurious perfumes inspired by the eighteenth century when the best perfumes were created for King Louis XV as a tribute to the prestigious horse races that he was an expert on.', 125, 7935000.0, 7935000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(244, 'Creed Aventus For Her', 'Creed released a masculine version of this perfume in 2010, but in 2016, it decided to launch the female accompaniment. Aventus For Her is floral, fruity and warm all wrapped into one. A couple spritzes is all you need to excite your senses. It has a rather intriguing blend of notes that exudes confidence. It opens with a luscious array of violet, lemon, green apple, patchouli, pink pepper, and bergamot. The heart is composed of styrax, rose, Mysore sandalwood, and musk. It ends powerfully with amber, lilac, sweet peach, ylang-ylang, and black currant.', 75, 12461400.0, 12461400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_creed_perfumes_aventus_for_womon_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(16, 'Al Majed For Oud Maamoul Dossary ', 'It''s an oriental incense extracted from the luxurious oud to fill your house with vitality and freshness. The intense scent spreads quickly and lasts for a long time.', 100, 400200.0, 400200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6285091015032-almajed-for-oud-maamoul-dossary---130-gm-1.png'),
(57, 'Byredo Oud Immortel', 'The Oud Immortel is made around oud, a particular sort of wood that due to its use in traditional incense and perfume, has gained great cultural significance and has gotten its existence recorded in one among the world''s oldest written texts - the Sanskrit Vedas from India. Once light heartwood Aquilaria tree becomes infected with a selected sort of mold, it defends itself by saturating its core with a dark, highly fragrant, resin. This dark wood, oud or agarwood holds a fancy fragrance, resembling few or no other natural ingredients.', 100, 7286400.0, 7286400.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(72, 'Franck Olivier Bamboo America EDT', 'Start your day fresh and enthusiastic with strong and glowing fragrance drops
Enjoy the moments of your day accompanied by the scents of violet leaves and bergamot that unfold, heralding the beginning of the journey of elegance
The heart of the fragrance of apple and lotus increases the beauty of the scent and adds touches of attractive softness
The ends of the fragrance bear charming amber notes with the iris breeze, to keep your scent exciting and lively until the last moments', 75, 586500.0, 586500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/5/3516641233129-franck-olivier-franck-olivier-bamboo-america-pour-homme-_m_-edt-75-ml.png'),
(201, 'Afnan Ornament Purple EDP', 'A delicate velvety drop that highlights the details of your femininity and delicate beauty.
