(59, 'Dunhill Edition', 'Dunhill Edition is a sophisticated fragrance for the man who craves quality in every aspect of his life. This aromatic Fougere delights with a rich mix of lavender and nutmeg then excites with a citrus explosion of bergamot and Amalfi lemon. The full-body experience blossoms from a carnation bouquet featuring lily-of-the-valley, clary sage, and jasmine. Earthy undertones of oakmoss, Tonka beans, fir and Virginia cedar float above a bed of fragrant embers. Dunhill Edition was originally released in 1984. The famed Alain Astori is the nose that crafted this classic cologne. This well-balanced concoction is noted for its moderate longevity and spread, so you can apply comfortably without worry.', 100, 917700.0, 917700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/u/dunhill_edition.jpg'),
(62, 'Memo Paris Escales Extraordinaires French Leather Rose Special Box EDP', 'When you inhale the fragrance of French roses in rose water, your soul will be transported to the world of beauty
