About the Brand:
Jo Malone joined the EstÃƒÂ©e Lauder Companies, which is available in 69 countries and territories, in 1999. Jo Malone London is a British brand known for its unique fragrances and luxurious products for bath, body, and home. It has written the rules of perfumery by blending unexpected components of ingredients and introducing elegant and playful concepts, the Jo Malone world continues to develop beautifully.', 100, 2518500.0, 2518500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/9/690251043202-jo-malone-jo-malone-mimosa-_-cardamom-_u_-cologne-30-ml.png'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 392', 'Enjoy the cool breezes of the unique perfume Day 392 from Tous Les Jours .', 55, 683100.0, 683100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000392_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_perfume_day_392_tayamun_1_1_.jpg'),
(86, 'Cartier La Panthere', 'Cartier La Panthere was launched by the established Cartier brand in 2014. A feline floral fragrance born out of radiant, delicate gardenia coming together with velvety notes of musk. Within the flask, a sculpture depicts the majestic, fascinating panther. The fragrance in this set contains captivating perfume that reflects a liberated, passionate woman starting with the top note of the whimsical and intoxicating gardenia flower blended with sweet rose, earthy musk, deep patchouli, and leathery oakmoss. La Panthere is a long-lasting scent accessory and features a moderate sillage thatÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s sure to complement any ensemble without overwhelming others.', 75, 3332700.0, 3332700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/cartier_la_panthere_eau_de_parfum_1.jpg'),
(121, 'IL Profvmo Patchouli Noir EDP', 'From the soft creamy woods, this delicate composition comes to you with intense notes of pure gum.
The base has an amazing blend of patchouli and fresh roses, filling you with an elegant sensual scent.
The fragrance is soft, delivering romance and tranquility to enjoy your special moments.
It''s your perfect option for all your occasions and busy days as well as special nights.', 100, 4761000.0, 4761000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(63, 'Dior Addict', 'Dior Addict EDP is a sensual oriental fragrance for women. Tropical mandarin leaf is tempered with soft, juicy blackberry in the top notes. White floral middle notes include orange blossom, night-blooming cereus, and jasmine, colored with a hint of rose. Base notes blend bittersweet tonka bean with milky sandalwood and sweet vanilla, creating a rich, creamy effect. There is nothing shy or subtle about this long-lasting fragrance; with its heavy sillage, it is best worn at night. Its bold floral notes bring warmth and light to chilly evenings, so it is good for the fall and even better for winter.', 50, 3795000.0, 3795000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/i/dior_addict_eau_de_parfum.jpg'),
(352, 'The Harmonist Royal Earth Refill EDP', 'A sexy and distinctive fragrance that makes you feel fresh and comfortable.
