(69, 'Fendi Fan Di Fendi Pour Homme Giant Edition', 'This masculine scent aims at ambiguous, advanced, and stylish men who has a charisma and modern elegance. thus, the composition tends to be both hot and modern, classic, and refined. Its character is fresh woody Ã¢â‚¬â€œ fragrant, created by parfumers Francois Demachy, Delphine Lebeau-Krowiak and Benoit Lapouza.', 100, 2980800.0, 2980800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/2/3274872286771_fendi_fendi_pour_homme_150_ml_giant_edition_1.jpg'),
(327, 'Laurent Mazzone Hysteric', 'Inspired by the oriental adventures and tales of love, Laurent Mazzone Hysteric perfume will sweep you away like the wind. A start with an intoxicating hint of cardamom and bergamot makes for a fresh beginning that is entwined with a charismatic flowery rose and whiskey. It is a rendezvous with gourmand nuances of patchouli, coffee, and cacao for a wild ending.', 100, 15476700.0, 15476700.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Hijazi', 'Hijazi 100 ML is an Eau de Parfum For Men and Women from Tous Les Jours which encapsulates the feelings of nostalgia with top notes of Pink Pepper, Black Pepper, Saffron that will grab your attention immediately, then the heart notes of Roses, Lavender, Geranium that will take control representing the essence of the perfume to leave you in the end with the base notes of Tonka, Sandalwood, Oud Wood, Oud Grease that will linger with you far beyond that.', 100, 1511100.0, 1511100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006900594_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_hijazi_100_ml_tayamun_1.jpg'),
