(8, 'Chopard Wish Brilliant', 'It is a balsamic white floral fragrance for women that was launched in the market in 2010. It captures aromatic notes of fruits, pink pepper, violet leaf, star jasmine, musk and amber.', 75, 1352400.0, 1352400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/4/3414200516020-chopard-chopard-wish-brilliant-_w_-edp-75-ml.jpg'),
(63, 'Dior Oud Ispahan EDP', 'It represents the majesty of the oriental prestigious palace, with its charming and dazzling sight that pleases everybody who sees it.
The legendary agarwood drops take you to a new world where you discover the magic of the East wrapped in the scent of roses.
Labdanum arouses your curiosity at the beginning of the journey and pushes you to go on an adventure to discover the palace.
The fragrance, with its unique composition, tells you new details and scenes in your life story.', 125, 9798000.0, 9798000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(168, 'Jimmy Choo Illicit', 'The latest parfume for Jimmy Choo, Illicit is floral, feminine, and sensational. With top notes of ginger and orange, and heart of rose and jasmine, and crowned with base notes of honey, amber, and sandalwood. The bottle has been variegated like opal with many architectonic facets, making it a signature of art. The square silver cap adds a contemporary touch to the bottle.', 60, 2739300.0, 2739300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_jimmy_choo_perfumes_illicit_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(32, 'Guerlain Shalimar Souffle', 'Be attractive and elegant with Guerlain Shalimar Souffle Eau de Parfum For Women. This modern version of classic perform by Guerlain gives you a new breath to this legendary scent through a sensual, sparkling and precious interpretation. Get this delicate floral oriental scent with fresh and light citrus aromas of lemon, bergamot, and mandarin in its top notes. Enjoy its middle notes with Indian Sambac jasmine and orange blossom, in addition to vanilla from Tahiti and India together with white musk in base notes', 90, 2863500.0, 2863500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470116665_guerlain_shalimar_souffle_de_parfum_edp_90_ml_1.jpg'),
(77, 'Valentino Voce Viva Perfumed Hair Mist', 'Celebrating a woman''s delicate voice and soft, charming femininity
