(208, 'Lootah Heil Vanilla Small Jar Incense ', 'A luxurious high quality incense for those who are looking for a distinctive scent to their homes. The scent is extracted from the finest carefully selected natural materials. Its enchanting aroma will capture your heart from the first moment and remains stable for a long time without fading.', 100, 2194200.0, 2194200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6297000943008-lootah-lootah-heil-vanilla---small-jar-incense-77-gms.png'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Armani Code A', 'Enjoy a unique ideal refreshment that you will launch in all the moments of your busy day with the energetic perfume blend that''s enriched with the scents of bergamot and lemon with glowing touches of lavender that reaches your heart with love and wraps it with excitement energy. You need to start your day and then come to your love Tonka beans wood touches at the end to overwhelm you in a sense of absolute luxury and calmness in the last moments of the day.', 50, 3594900.0, 3594900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614272129870-giorgio-armani-giorgio-armani-armani-code-a-list-pour-homme-_m_-edt-75-ml-1.jpg'),
(44, 'Bvlgari Omnia', 'An oriental fragrance that mixes spicy black pepper with cinnamon and nutmeg. This fragrance gives a warm and strong scent with a sweet touch of chocolate and almond that surrounds you with pleasant feelings', 65, 1669800.0, 1669800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/8/783320892516_bvlgar_bvlgari_omnia_edp_65_ml_1.jpg'),
