(20, 'Givenchy Ysatis', 'Givenchy Ysatis a floral woody fragrance for women. Classy, feminine and sophisticated, mature, for the special occasion, for the evening. Must have!', 100, 2711700.0, 2711700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_givenchy_perfumes_ysatis_for_women_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(57, 'Byredo 1996 Inez & Vinoodh EDP', 'Classical notes of leather blended with the warmth of patchouli giving you a warm and soft sensual scent.
