(339, 'Mendittorosa Alfa', 'Mendittorosa, the Italian house, has released a trilogy, the scents of the soul â€œAlfa, Omega and Idâ€ to warm our hearts. These odors speak directly to your heart, encapsulating the sensuality of an appealing scene of clear blue sky. Alfa fragrance composes powerful scents of milk and vineyards with saffron and nutmeg, sandalwood, and jasmine, which have been determined to make the scent linger on.', 100, 5161200.0, 5161200.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(101, 'One Word Moonglade EDP ', 'From the dawn of time, Moonglade was always a scene to admire. This fragrance was inspired by this magical moment, sensual like this unusual composition of the delicious aroma freesia & exotic hidden scent of sandalwood.', 100, 690000.0, 690000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/n/one_word_moonglade_1.jpg'),
