The strength and intensity of the fragrance makes it always an optimal choice for you on your busy and important days.', 50, 1035000.0, 1035000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6290171002413-afnan-afnan-naseej-al-zafaran-_u_-edp-50-ml.png'),
(87, 'Lanvin Modern Princess', 'Modern Princess Eau de Parfum by Lanvin is a sexy, sensual floral fragrance whose creator is Christophe Raynaud. The top notes have accords of Pink Lady Apple and Red Currant. The heart notes have a blend of feminine accords like Jasmine, Carnal, and Freesia Flower. The base notes contain accords of Blonde Woods, White Musk and Vanilla Orchid.', 60, 1476600.0, 1476600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_lanvin_perfumes_modern_princess_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 402', 'Enhance your self-confidence with Perfume Day 402. It opens up with Bitter Orange melt in Ylang-ylang, and Jasmine, ending on a bed of spicy Pink Pepper, Lily, and Benzoin.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000402-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-402-1.png'),
(109, 'Aigner Blue', 'Aigner Blue is a floral woody fragrance for men; this sensual cologne with a very unique, sparkling, classy notes and ingredients offers you an elegant and natural presence. The fragrance opens with a contrast of aromas presented in lemon, apple, and clove. At heart, the floral notes of lily-of-the-valley and rose give it a hint of sweetness, while the note of leather offers depth to the blend. To balance all that, the cologne is set on base notes of vanilla, amber, musk, and cedar. Aigner Blue is perfect for any occasion, day or night!', 125, 1338600.0, 1338600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_aigner_perfumes_blue_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(72, 'Franck Olivier Sun Royal Oud EDP', 'Ambery musky ends express your elegance and charm
