(40, 'Tom Ford Tobacco Oud', 'It is a woody, spicy fragrance for women and men that was launched in 2013. The nose behind this fragrance is Olivier Gillotin. Whiskey is placed on the top while middle notes combine cinnamon, coriander, and spicy notes; agarwood (oud), tobacco, sandalwood, patchouli, benzoin, incense, cedar, and vanilla form the base.', 100, 7617600.0, 7617600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066030502-tom-ford-tom-ford-tobacco-oud-_u_-edp-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(32, 'Guerlain L''Instant De Guerlain', 'LÃ¢â‚¬â„¢Instant de Guerlain is one of these unique moments where everything can change. It''s a moment of intense emotion between a man and a woman. A new femininity envelops the woman. Time can stand still. The woman sees her true self. LÃ¢â‚¬â„¢Instant de Guerlain inaugurates a new olfactory interpretation of the oriental family: "Crystalline Amber". In the tradition of the great Guerlain fragrances, this one revisits the celebrated Guerlinade.', 50, 1800900.0, 1800900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470109803_guerlain_l_instant_de_guerlain_edp_50_ml_1.jpg'),
(185, 'Joop Femme EDT', 'An elegant and distinctive fragrance belonging to the family of luxurious woody notes.
The fragrance is specially designed for distinguished women who seek luxury and sophistication.
The fragrance enhances your charming femininity, as it makes you feel comfortable and confident all the time.
