This perfume is the perfect companion for you in all your private times.
About the Brand:
"Yup!" It is a luxury German fashion house specializing in the design and manufacture of contemporary clothing and cosmetics. The company was founded in 1986 by German fashion designer Wolfgang Joop, as the designer''s own brand in Hamburg, Germany. Offer a "yup!" Contemporary women''s and men''s clothing under various labels as well as footwear, accessories, lingerie, jewelry, watches, perfumes and a homeware collection.', 100, 1373100.0, 1373100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/4/3414206000059-joop-joop-femme-_w_-edt-100-ml.png'),
(54, 'Sedr Alkhaleej Al Oud Oud ', 'This home incense has a distinctive Arabian scent that fast spreads in your homes and covers every corner with the elegant Arabian scent of sandalwood and musk.', 100, 289800.0, 289800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287001952185_sedr_alkhaleej_al_oud_oud_50_g_50g_gs-dmm_consignment_1.jpg'),
