(143, 'Carven Paris La Havane', 'This oriental fragrance is inspired by an amazing journey to Havana. The sensual composition has notes of Cuban tobacco, patchouli and leather, providing you a masculine and elegant scent that draws the attention toward your presence wherever you go.', 125, 5513100.0, 5513100.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
