(83, 'Montale Sweet Peony', 'Sweet Peony by Montale is a feminine scent. It was launched in the year 2017. The fragrance features a blend of rose, jasmine, peach, coconut, coffee, clove, vanilla, and sandalwood. The main accords of the fragrance are rose, vanilla, floral, powdery, fresh, and warm spicy.', 100, 3981300.0, 3981300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/o/montale_sweet_peony_100_ml.jpg'),
