(46, 'Bentley Infinite', 'Bentley Infinite is an oriental fragrance for men. A beautiful sensual and sweet scent that is perfect for the warm weather. Very unique and masculine. An enticing blend of woody and spicy accords that lends a robust and attractive fragrance thatÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s entirely magnetic. Top notes of citron, light cedar and lavender promote a lively, tantalizing aroma thatÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s a refreshing boost for the senses, while heart notes of floral geranium, bourbon pepper and delicate violet incorporate their sophisticated twist. Base notes of Haitian vetiver, marine ambergris and earthy patchouli finish the scent for a seductive and masculine cologne thatÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s impossible to ignore.', 100, 1304100.0, 1304100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/e/bentley_infinite_edt_100_ml.jpg'),
