(20, 'Givenchy Live Rosy Crush', 'Live Rosy Crush is a feminine perfume inspired by womenÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s tenacity, independence, and strife for freedom. The opening is pink pepper, goji berries and fresh citrus. Strong rose and peony are at the heart along with sweet musk settles sweetly as it moves to patchouli and vanilla in the base notes. This dazzling blend of roses and peony will sweep you off your feet and accompany you on your path of joy and success. Presented in pink, since pink represents compassion and love. The perfect perfume for a beautiful you.', 100, 1711200.0, 1711200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/2/3274872384460_givenchy_live_rosy_crush_edp_75_ml_1.jpg'),
