(145, 'DKNY Nectar Love', 'Dkny Nectar Love is an original fragrance for women released in 2017 by American designer Donna Karan. The perfume combines floral, fruity, and fresh accords to create a scent that is reminiscent of fresh honey. It is anchored in warm, sweet base notes of beeswax, vanilla, cedar, neroli, and musk. These are followed by fresh middle notes of Mirabelle, jasmine, and lily of the valley. Finally, its top notes consist of juicy nectarine, mandarin orange, grapefruit, and yellow freesia. All of these blend together to create a unique perfume that is sweet, playful, and youthful, but still appropriate for women of almost any age.', 100, 1731900.0, 1731900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_dkny_perfumes_nectar_love_for_women_eau_de_perfum_22548386903.jpg'),
