(74, 'Davidoff Cool Water', 'This fresh aromatic fragrance takes you to lay down on the beach, looking at the ocean and breath the cool and fresh air, enjoying masculine vitality and seduction.', 125, 710700.0, 710700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_davidoff_perfumes_cool_water_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(34, 'Deem Perfumes Garden ', 'Deem Perfumes Garden is a room spray that spreads enticing fragrance in the air and let you enjoy the fresh and aromatic atmosphere.', 100, 690000.0, 690000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006660382_deem_garden_300_ml_1.jpg'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Ombre Leather EDP', 'Tom Ford amber Leather Eau de parfume has an unparalleled scent that come from the heart of the Western Desert and is a unisex parfume. The product has a deep texture scent that prints with a tangible feel. It makes you feel different and beautiful.', 100, 3926100.0, 3926100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066075145_tom_ford_ombre_leather_edp_100_ml.jpg'),
(32, 'Guerlain Mon Gift Set ', 'This gift set contains the Mon Guerlain ritual (100ml) and (5 ml) Eau de Toilette, a perfumed body lotion (75ml), and a perfumed shower gel (75 ml). Mon Guerlain is a tribute to todayÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s femininity, strong, free and sensual femininity, as inspired by Angelina Jolie. This oriental citrus fragrance is a luminous scent that draws its freshness from the floral notes of sambac jasmine and Carla lavender magnified by citrus notes. The perfumed body lotion and perfumed shower gel leave skin soft, supple, and subtly scented.', 75, 4823100.0, 4823100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470141674-guerlain-mon-_w_-set-edp-100-ml-_-edp-5-ml-_-prfm-body-lotion-75-ml-_-prfm-shower-gel-75-ml-02.png'),
(348, 'Goutal Paris Tenue de SoirÃ©e Set ', 'This set features a 100 ml EDP and a 75 ml cream.
The modern fragrance provides a scented touch for an amazing look for women.
The fragrance provides endless elegance with notes of red fruits, iris and patchouli to deliver freshness.
Make the cream your first step in your routine. It works to hydrate, protect and repair the skin, thanks to shea butter along with musk.', 100, 5789100.0, 5789100.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(108, 'Clinique Happy Heart', 'An amazing floral feminine fragrance that gives you a fresh scent with deep and warm feelings, with a mixture of tangerines, carrots, and white woods, let everyone around you wonder about your unreasonable appeal!', 50, 2249400.0, 2249400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/l/clinique_clenique_happy_heart_edp_100_ml.jpg'),
(34, 'Deem Room Sprays Set ', 'This set contains:
Deem Perfumes Hotel - 300 ml
Deem Perfumes Hotel is a room spray that spreads enticing fragrance in the air and let you enjoy the fresh and aromatic air. It has a sweet and fresh smell which makes the atmosphere cheerful.
Deem Perfumes Garden - 300 ml
Deem Perfumes Garden is a room spray that spreads enticing fragrance in the air and let you enjoy the fresh and aromatic atmosphere.
Deem Perfumes Palace - 300 ml
Deem Perfumes Palace is inspired from oriental spirit. This wonderful home fragrance has an aromatic blend of mandarin, flowers, amber, bergamot, tangerine, vetiver, iris, patchouli and vanilla.', 100, 1863000.0, 1863000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/b/sb100322_deem_room_sprays_set_of_3.png'),
(43, 'Dize Jasmine Home Fragrance ', 'A home freshener spray that engulfs the place with a refreshing aroma and replaces unpleasant scents with special and unique scents. The spray is enriched with a blend of splendid ingredients with African orange blossom at the beginning of the scent followed by white jasmine petals and patchouli leaves in the heart, and ends with the mesmerizing scents of cedar woods, and the touches of honey and roses. With this astonishing fragrance, you will enjoy a clean, healthy, and refreshing environment.', 100, 338100.0, 338100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6281074751706-dize-home-_-_-_-_.png'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Armani Prive Rouge Malachite', 'Giorgio Armani Armani, Prive Rouge Malachite is an oriental floral fragrance suitable for men and women, the color of its red glass reflects the warmth and strength of this fragrance, a unique meeting of luxury and delight of the senses.', 100, 8887200.0, 8887200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_giorgio_armani_perfumes_armani_prive_rouge_malachite_for_unisex_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(24, 'Candy Addict Marshmallow Mash Hair Mist ', 'Description
A deliciously nostalgic scent combination that will transport you to a land of fairgrounds and campfires with every spritz! The opening notes of juicy peach lead to the sweet marshmallow leaving you smelling good enough to eat! Marshmallow Mash is your go-to fragrance that keeps your hair subtly fragranced throughout the day!
Moisturize, soften and strengthen your hair with Vitamin E, a powerful antioxidant, and Provitamin B5. Give your hair that extra shine and volume that it deserves, whilst leaving your hair less prone to breakage.
How to use:
From about 20 cms away, spritz the mist evenly over your hair.
Then go and show the world your sweet side!
Don''t forget to shake the bottle before use to liven up the candy!
Reapply throughout the day whenever you need a dose of fabulousness!', 100, 1235100.0, 1235100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/ca_hair_mist-marshmallow.png'),
(86, 'Cartier Baiser Fou', 'Baiser Vole Fou, a fragrance by Cartier, debuted in early 2017 as a member of the Baiser Vole or Ã¢â‚¬Å“Stolen KissÃ¢â‚¬Â collection. Meant to evoke images of flirtatious lipstick kisses, Baiser Vou was designed with luxurious orchid as a middle note. Orchid, a fragrance reminiscent of lipstick, summons imagery of desire and beauty. This strong aroma is carried by coy base notes of white chocolate and vanilla. Raspberry lingers as a top note, giving this sweet fragrance a taste of candy kisses. This aromatic powdery fragrance is a splendid add for any woman''s day.', 75, 1925100.0, 1925100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_cartier_perfumes_baiser_fou_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(81, 'Mabkharat Alemarat Frankincense Cambodian Oud ', 'Incense made from the finest types of Arabic frankincense mixed with pure aromatic oil of the amazing scent of Cambodian oud for a long-lasting, wonderful scent that inspires feelings of joy and happiness withing everyone.', 100, 545100.0, 545100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006907876_mabkharat_alemarat_-_frankincense_cambodian_oud_1.jpg'),
(59, 'Dunhill Pursuit', 'Pull off a stimulating and attractive woodsman smell with Dunhill Pursuit Cologne, introduced in 2006 with the help of celebrated perfumer Michel Girard. The top notes are bergamot and mandarin orange for a refreshing suggestion of citrus. These ingredients are combined with Spikenard lavender for a delightful sweetness, and cardamom, amber, Peruvian pepper tree and cinnamon for a bit of spicy pleasure. The base is contrived of white cedarwood, patchouli, sandalwood, and vanilla. This is an ideal masculine fragrance for the fall and winter months and is a perfect option to wear either at night or during the day.', 75, 1035000.0, 1035000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/d/u/dunhill_pursuit_edt_75ml.jpg'),
(374, 'PH Mistral & Flower of Vichy EDP', 'Unknown', 50, 6009900.0, 6009900.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(12, 'Parfums de Marly Layton Exclusif EDP', 'Luxurious woody fragrance made of the most rare components around the world. It all starts with notes of almond and bergamot mixed with sweetness of mandarin orange. The watery notes add some touch to the scent, which make it special. The rich heart has notes of rose and gardenia, mixed with geranium and the delicate water lily. The base has accords of guaiac wood, mixed with luxurious oud and Indonesian Patchouli and the amazing sandalwood. The notes of amber and oakmoss, mixed with pink pepper and vanilla adds to the richness of the composition.', 125, 9922200.0, 9922200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/7/3700578518149_marly_layton_exclusif_edition_royal.jpg'),
(40, 'Tom Ford FougÃ¨re dâ€™Argent EDP', 'A luxurious and distinctive aromatic blend for those looking for excellence and sophistication.
This scent will captivate everyone''s hearts from the first moment.
Enjoy a perfect, bold finish, and boost your sense of comfort all the time with this amazing scent.
The fragrance is characterized by the strong stability of its scent for long hours without fading.
It is also ideal for both men and women.
About the Brand:
Thomas Carlyle Ford is a famous American fashion designer and filmmaker. He has been one of the most important people in pop culture from the 1990s till this day. He is the owner of the luxury brand which was founded in 2005, in New York City. Tom Ford has produced amazing menswear, beautiful fragrances, high quality sunglasses and cool watches that are very popular with high fashion enthusiasts. His line can be found all over the world. In Europe alone, you can shop his products in many countries such as UK, Spain, France, Belgium, Germany, Greece, Finland, Sweden, Portugal, Ireland, etc.', 250, 15939000.0, 15939000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(48, 'Lancome Hypnose', 'For the woman who knows how to use her charm to fascinate the man she loves, this bewitching fragrance is dedicated to you. The oriental woody composition features passion flower in the top, vanilla in the core and vetiver in the base, delivering a sensual scent that accentuates your femininity.', 75, 2497800.0, 2497800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/1/3147758235500-lancome-lancome-hypnose-_w_-edp-75-ml.jpg'),
(361, 'Unique Luxury Queen Collection EDP', 'A pure oriental fragrance that suits Arabs more than others.
Where the fragrance combines originality and excitement together, it is one of the most widespread types of perfume.
Women can use this perfume and adorn its attractive scent for an unforgettable olfactory experience.
The fragrance contains an amazing blend of caramel, saffron and nutmeg, in addition to sandalwood and honey.', 50, 3505200.0, 3505200.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(86, 'Cartier Le Baiser Du Dragon', 'Le Baiser du Dragon by Cartier, which refers to a Dragon''s Kiss in French, is an exotic woody-aromatic fragrance that layers rich almond and musky florals over a subtly sensual base of vetiver and patchouli. The fragrance opens with a sumptuous, fiery almond and amaretto accord rounded out by citrus and floral tones of neroli and gardenia. Heady jasmine, iris and powdery-fresh red rose dominate the heart notes, flanked by cedar and white musk. Lightly bitter, woody vetiver and earthy-sweet patchouli combine with nuances of caramel, benzoin and dark chocolate to produce a deeply satisfying finish.', 100, 4602300.0, 4602300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/cartier_le_baiser_du_dragon_edp_100_ml.jpg'),
(90, 'Elizabeth Arden 5Th Avenue', '5th Avenue fragrance is the symbol of wealth. This floral perfume is for the intelligent, successful and elegant woman who has a unique sense of style. 5th Avenue celebrates a womanâ€™s justified dreams and ambitions, infinite possibilities and unlimited power. This signature perfume opens with fresh lemon notes, a splash of mandarin, and a light violet scent; all of which are enveloped in ozonic notes. The heart of the fragrance includes a beautiful bouquet of Lotus enhanced by jasmine. The prominent floral notes soften to a smooth, soapy and sweet base with gentle musk and warm amber polished by Orris and delicate cedarwood.', 125, 1000500.0, 1000500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_elizabeth_arden_perfumes_5th_avenue_for_women_eau_de_parfum_4.jpg'),
(55, 'Hugo Boss Femme By Boss', 'In this fragrance, the first note is extracted from the mandarin fruit and gooseberry that makes it a timeless fragrance that lasts for long periods. As for the final note, it is a blend of creamy musk that interacts with the stunning floral trio. Leaving behind a warm and gentle aura to suit your soul full of glamor, grace and softness', 50, 1000500.0, 1000500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/u/hugo_boss_boss_femme_eau_de_parfum_1.jpg'),
(216, 'Jo Malone Bronze Wood & Leather EDC', 'Enjoy the warm scent of vetiver and fizzy on cold winter and fall nights.
The fragrance adds mystery and attractiveness to your look and immerses you with exciting scents.
The fragrance is formulated carefully to be suitable for both men and women. It is designed to remain powerful for long periods of time.
Your spectacular fragrance captures the attention of everyone around you and makes them fall in love with your beautiful look.', 100, 5865000.0, 5865000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/9/690251071340-jo-malone-jo-malone-bronze-wood-_-leather-_u_-cologne-intense-100-ml.png'),
(28, 'Burberry Mini Set ', 'The four-piece set contains one of MR Burberry Indigo (5 ml), one of MR Burberry Eau de Parfum (5 ml) and two of MR Burberry Eau de Toilette (5 ml). Awaken your senses with MR Burberry Indigo, which provides you the feeling of being powerful on your decisive situations. Its deep composition of mint oil, rosemary and amber will spread the freshness wherever you go. Feel the charismatic effect with MR Burberry Eau de Parfum which will take you on a journey where you are lead the way, thanks to its notes of patchouli, amber and vetiver. MR Burberry Eau de Toilette is the masculine version of the Eau de Parfum, which comes in a classic structure to suit you on all of your occasions, with its aromatic notes of tarragon, vetiver and cedar.', 5, 1669800.0, 1669800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/5/0/5045551797080_burberry_burberry_mr_indigo_m_edt_5ml_mr_burberry_edp_5ml_mr_burberry_edt_2_x_5ml_mini_set_gs-dmm_cross_dock_1.jpg'),
(146, 'Britney Spears Private Show', 'Private Show by Britney Spears is a fragrance that has Floral-Fruity composition. It was launched in the year 2016. The top notes have accords of Clementine, Nectarine, and Coffee with Whipped Cream. The heart notes are Dulce de Leche with White flowers of Orange Blossom and Sambac Jasmine. The base notes contain accords of Musk and Amber.', 100, 4367700.0, 4367700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_britney_spears_perfumes_private_show_eau_parfume_for_women.jpg'),
(369, 'RPL Oud Voyage EDP', '#NAME?', 100, 5361300.0, 5361300.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(13, 'Juicy Couture Viva La Juicy Gold Couture', 'Couture Overdose. She is couture all the way. rotation an addictive net of charm and decay at the core of her golden world. For her, all that shines is gold. Her fragrance, Viva La Juicy Gold Couture.', 100, 1849200.0, 1849200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/u/juicy_couture_viva_la_juicy_gold_couture.jpg'),
(232, 'Acqua Di Parma Colonia Mirra', 'An elegant original fragrance consists of a unique combination of aromas where the citrus notes are intertwined with the deep, warm, and aromatic notes of myrrh, blend with the delicate aromas of the orange flowers.', 100, 7935000.0, 7935000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_acqua_di_parma_perfumes_colonia_mirra_for_men_eau_de_cologne.jpg'),
(95, 'COZY Rich Amber Room Spray ', 'Best for:
- Living room & study room
- Amber lovers
- Energetic and luxurious scent
Reasons to buy:
- Long-lasting
- Anti-bacterial
- Suitable for big spaces
- Rich and powerful scent
Rich in power, strength & amber! This anti-bacterial home fragrance imposes an unforgettable presence and has the ability to elevate any atmosphere within seconds. The secret behind its irresistible intensity comes from combining opposites yet exquisite Eastern accords into one. Madagascar ginger, patchouli & amber, three main components differ in scents but tell an energetic story once put together. Witness the luxury behind this rich, fresh & deep aroma, and indulge in a home fragrance you will never be able to forget!', 500, 683100.0, 683100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/o/copy_of_cozy_rich_amber_room_spray_-_500ml.png'),
(20, 'Givenchy L''interdit Set ', 'Don''t hesitate to get your collection from Givenchy, featuring an 80 ml eau de perfume, 75 ml body lotion and 75 ml shower gel.
It''s a complete body care set. Start with the refreshing shower gel, then moisturize your skin with the body lotion before adding an attractive scent.
You can offer it as a perfect elegant gift for your beloved ones on special occasions.', 200, 2753100.0, 2753100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/2/3274872431577-givenchy-l_interdit-eau-de-parfum-80ml-_-body-lotion-75ml_-shower-gel-75ml.png'),
(133, 'Kenzo Kenzo Flower EDT', 'A wonderful fragrance that belongs to the family of luxurious oriental scents and fresh floral notes.
This fragrance is specially designed for women who love uniqueness and distinction.
It is enriched with an exceptional aromatic blend extracted from natural materials.
Enjoy a radiant attractive look with this charming scent.
Having this perfume would be a great addition to your beauty collection.
About the Brand:
Kenzo is a French luxury fashion house founded in 1970 by Japanese designer Kenzo Takada, known for his Asian influence on traditional European styles. It is one of LVMH''s branches, and its creative director is Felipe Oliveira Baptista. Kenzo began designing men''s, then children''s, and home collections in 1987, followed by designing perfumes in 1988. Her perfumes are known for their unique scents extracted from the finest natural ingredients.', 100, 1759500.0, 1759500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3352818518855-kenzo-kenzo-flower-by-kenzo-_w_-edt-100-ml.png'),
(45, 'Coach Women Set ', 'It was launched in 2016. Coach Fragrance is designed as a scent that represent the youth, modern and authentic and natural beauty. The composition is floral with vibrant top notes of raspberry leaf, pink pepper and pear. The core includes an authentic accord of Turkish rose, laid on the base of suede musk and sandalwood.', 100, 2311500.0, 2311500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3386460099783_coach_cch_women_set_edp_bl_100ml_7_5_ml_ne_gs-dmm_cross_dock_1.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 266', 'This bold floral fragrance takes you on a unique experience everytime you wear it. The upper notes of pineapple are followed by iris in the heart and amber in the base, forming a composition of a magnificent scent that adds an elegant piece to your special collection.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000266-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-266-1.png'),
(155, 'Loewe Quizas Seduccion', 'This floral fruity fragrance shows the pure forms of seduction with a nice blend of blackberry, tuberose and orangle blossom. It gives you a sensual touch of elegance that perfectly suits you on all your occasions.', 100, 3408600.0, 3408600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_loewe_perfumes_quizas_seduccion_for_women_eau_de_perfum_1.jpg'),
(1, 'Dolce & Gabbana Dolce Floral Drops', 'Rabie perfume with feminine notes, wonderful, fresh and lively, and smells of fresh flowers spread with dew, with a wonderful mixture of apples, narcissus, and musk.', 50, 1614600.0, 1614600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/o/dolce_gabbana_dolce_floral_drops_edt_75_ml.jpg'),
(86, 'Cartier Eau De Cartier', 'Eau De Cartier, introduced in 2001, enchants the nose with the crispness and warmth of citrus and spice. A befitting fragrance for daytime, it lingers with the fresh green scents of nature. The top notes are zingy bergamot and yuzu, which are expertly paired with the green essence of herbal coriander. Lavender and violet heart notes soften the sharpness of the earlier aromas, infusing the fragrance with intoxicating, flowery charm. White amber, patchouli, and cedar bring the motif to the ground, adding an earthy depth that is both richly savory and slightly sweet. Eau De Cartier is a unique, botanical cologne sure to stand out in a crowd.', 100, 2380500.0, 2380500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_cartier_perfumes_eau_de_cartier_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(37, 'Chanel Chance Eau Tendre', 'A fragrance characterized by the aroma of fruit mixed in harmony with the pure floral extract to form a captivating blend of delicacy and vitality, with a wonderful combination of grapefruit extract, jasmine extract and a soft touch of white musk for a woman full of optimism and vitality.', 100, 2753100.0, 2753100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/h/chanel_chance_eau_tendre_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(88, 'Giorgio Beverly Hills G', 'G Gorgio Beverly Hills for women has accords of flowers and fruits. It is crafted by the perfumer Alain Astori. The top notes of the perfume consist of Pineapple, Melon, and Bitter Grape. The heart notes contain Orchid, Peony, and a slight touch of Peach and Ginger. The base notes contain Sandalwood and Vetiver.', 90, 752100.0, 752100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_giorgio_beverly_hills_perfumes_g_giorgio_beverly_hills_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(95, 'COZY Mystic River Room Spray ', 'Best for:
- Bedroom & Playroom
- Cypress & Aromatic scent lovers
- Sophisticated & Charming atmosphere
Reasons to buy:
- Long-lasting
- Anti-bacterial
- Suitable for big spaces
- Playful & Classy scent
In the land of fancy home fragrances, nothing can highlight sophistication like â€œMystic Riverâ€! This anti-bacterial home fragrance brings Oriental delicacy to you, extracting energizing notes from lemon & mint, adding it to a rich base of vanilla & sandalwood. This chic perfume will invite a charming mystical flow of aroma to your place, hence the name â€œMystic Riverâ€, to enjoy a smooth, playful yet classy home spray that uplifts your surrounding atmosphere at any given second.', 500, 683100.0, 683100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/o/copy_of_cozy_mystic_river_room_spray_-_500ml.png'),
(141, 'Moschino Moschino', 'For the Haute woman who also appreciates a fun joke, Moschino Fresh Couture is a luxurious fragrance offering presented in an irreverent bottle. Despite the perfumeÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s appearance as a cleaning product, it is comprised of gorgeous accords including woods, spices, citrus, and sweet fruits. Spray some on your wrist and you are greeted with top notes of mandarin orange, bergamot, and ylang-ylang. This opens to a floral heart accord of osmanthus and peony with a hint of raspberry. The fragrance is grounded by a warm base of ambroxan, patchouli and wood notes. Launched in 2015, this eau de toilette comes packaged in a playful, ironic bottle modeled after cleaning spray.', 100, 2035500.0, 2035500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8011003826711-moschino-moschino_edt_100_ml.jpg'),
(31, 'Dkhoun Nafae''s Dkhoun Rose EDP', 'The finest strong, creamy ouds come to you from the enchanting fragrant world of the East.
