(79, 'Atelier Cologne Camelia Intrepide', 'Camelia Intrepide by Atelier Cologne is a fresh, new unisex fragrance that was launched in the year 2016. The creator of this fragrance is perfumer Jerome Epinettee. The top notes of the fragrance are Sicilian lemon, Calabrian bergamot, and nutmeg, heart notes are camellia, orris root and violet leaves, base notes are Turkish rose oil, leather, and amber.', 100, 7548600.0, 7548600.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(131, 'Paris Hilton Bling Collection Parfum Spray', 'A wonderful fragrant blend specially designed for elegant women.
