The scent has spread around you since your first appearance to express your different presence and your wonderful look.
The fragrance is also perfectly designed to suit both men and women.', 100, 8797500.0, 8797500.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Vert Des Bois', 'This is a new fragrance that was launched in 2016. It represents a provocative scent of woods and avant-garde processing of green perfume. It opens with clean buds of poplar and Ouzo accord with the smell of anise, along with plum and olive leaf. The heart of white flowers is defined by jasmine, enriched with green mastic. Roasted tonka bean and patchouli end the composition. This edition is available in a 250ml splash.', 250, 17222400.0, 17222400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066060547-tom-ford-tom-ford-vert-des-bois-_u_-edp-50-ml-1.jpg'),
(196, 'Exuma Parfums World Moving Dunes EDP', 'A spicy and warm oriental fragrance with a spicy scent of cinnamon.
The warmth of the incense gives you a mysterious and attention-grabbing allure that accompanies you throughout the day.
The warm heart of the fragrance is enhanced by the notes of tobacco mixed with the warm and seductive scent of patchouli.
An amazing scent will captivate you and everyone around you and remains intense and strong on all of your important occasions.', 50, 3808800.0, 3808800.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(49, 'Lalique L''origine Or Intemporel Noir Premier 1888', 'Lalique L''origine Or Intemporel Noir Premier 1888 is a spicy oriental fragrance for both men and women. It is a scent that combines tobacco and coffee producing an out-of-the-world scent. The opening of the fragrance is beautiful and spicy thanks to Cardamom mixed with Black Pepper and Bergamot. The heart bursts with an explosion of sexy Tobacco before leaning in to the dark notes of Coffee. Violet lingers in the background as the base notes take over. The Vanilla fragrance is dominant in the base along with earthy Patchouli, which is ready to burst, overflowing you with warmth.', 100, 7548600.0, 7548600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_lalique_perfumes_l_origine_or_intemporel_noir_premier_1888_for_unisex_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(59, 'Dunhill Signature Collection Moroccan Amber', 'It is a spicy woody fragrance with woody and earthy notes of cardamom together with ginger. Amber and leather in the base add warmth and skinny to the perfume. The heart blooms saffron and hazelnut to give a more deep and earthy perception.', 100, 3581100.0, 3581100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/5/85715806628-dunhill-dunhill-signature-collection-moroccan-amber-_-_m_-edp-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(13, 'Juicy Couture Couture Couture', 'Couture parfume by Juicy Couture released in 2009.it''s a delightful celebration of sweet, floral parfume for all time. The top notes make an inlet with a citrus mix of mandarin orange, grapefruit, and African orange flower. The heart notes inspire a lovely synthesis of jasmine, plum and honeysuckle. The base notes host with amber, sandalwood, and vanilla. Both feminine and hilarity, the scent leaves a delightful impact.', 50, 1449000.0, 1449000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/j/u/juicy_couture_couture_couture.jpg'),
(39, 'Rekaz Patchouli ', 'This bundle includes: Eau De Parfum 50 ml + Perfume Oil 30 ml / 2.57 Tola
An irreplaceable component in the Arabian perfume world, created especially for the youthful empowered soul! This exclusive bundle presents an intense patchouli perfume & perfume oil, to indulge in its mysterious chypre note. Designed for the Oriental soul, enjoy its irresistible charm as you apply first the perfume oil onto pulse points, then spray the perfume over it to get the powerful long-lasting result.', 100, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/rekaz_patchouli_box_bottles.jpg'),
(63, 'Dior Sauvage Very Cool Spray Fresh', 'Sauvage Very Cool Spray Fresh was released in 2017 as a collaborative effort with perfumer Francois Demachy and draws inspiration from the wilderness. The fragrance opens with spicy and fresh top notes of Reggio bergamot, pink pepper, and grapefruit. At the heart, notes of Sichuan pepper, Provencal lavender, geranium, and vetiver emerge and lead to a refined base of elemi resin, cedarwood, Ambroxan, and patchouli. With this blend of fresh spicy, woody and citrusy aromas, you will experience a new wave of coolness.', 100, 2760000.0, 2760000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_dior_perfumes_sauvage_very_cool_spray_fresh_for_men_eau_de_toilette_3348901352314.jpg'),
(368, 'Olibere Le Jardin Dâ€™Amelie EDP', 'A unique and perfect combination for both men and women.
The fragrance gives you a bold look and enhances your attractiveness and confidence.
The fragrance is enriched with an amazing combination of unique natural ingredients.
The fragrance starts with a refreshing blend of bergamot, raspberry and pink pepper to emanate feelings of comfort
And in the middle is a scent of white woods, amber and musk.
The fragrance ends with a luxurious blend of amber, oud and patchouli.', 50, 2801400.0, 2801400.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(8, 'Chopard Vanille De Madagascar', 'Feminine Parfum with Madagascan vanilla that blended with Bergamot, matcha tea, and orange flower petals. It contains the noblest, natural ingredients: vetiver, magnolia, vanilla, and neroli. It gives you a full sense of comfort and calm after the end of your busy day.', 100, 8611200.0, 8611200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/6/7640177367433_chopard_collection_chopard_collection_vanille_de_madagascar_eau_de_parfum_100_ml_1.jpg'),
(18, 'Penhaligon''s The Coveted Duchess Rose', 'Penhaligon''s The Coveted Duchess Rose is an oriental floral fragrance for women, launched in 2016. The fragrance packs rose, orange, musk, and woody notes, which evokes sensuality in a woman who wears it.', 75, 8652600.0, 8652600.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(45, 'Coach Floral', 'Coach Floral is a feminine and romantic perfume that was introduced in 2018. It has a perfect blend of florals, fruits, and spices that make it perfect for any occasion, night or day. The fragrance opens with notes that will excite your senses and consist of pink peppercorn, citrus Coeur and pineapple sorbet. The heart notes are what give this perfume its name and are gardenia, rose tea and jasmine sambac. The fragrance then settles into the base notes of patchouli, musk and creamy wood. The rounded glass bottle is adorned with the emblem of the brand and a pale pink flower hangs off the neck.', 90, 1400700.0, 1400700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_coach_perfumes_floral_for_women_eau_de_perfum_3386460095341.jpg'),
(1, 'Dolce & Gabbana The One Mysterious Night', 'A fragrance for men from the oriental spice family, masculine and very attractive, made especially for the distinctive and bold man, with a blend of saffron, oud, and tonka.', 100, 2580600.0, 2580600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/_/d_g_the_one_exclusive_edition_1_.jpg'),
(156, 'Victoria''s Secret Pink Warm & Cozy Body Mist', 'A refreshing mist for a touch of fragrance. Provocative and powerful, bare vanilla features a decadent blend of clean, fresh, and aromatic notes. It''s ideal for daily use.', 250, 545100.0, 545100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/6/667548996495-victoria-secret-victoria_s-secret-pink-warm-_-cozy-body-mist-_u_-250-ml.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 292', 'For both men and women, this elegant scent is designed to suit you on every occasion. The composition features a blend of coffee, tobacco and incense notes, releasing a wonderful fragrance with a sensual touch that fills your spirits with positivity and vitality.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000292-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-292-1.png'),
(251, 'Baldessarini Ambre Oud', 'This elegant oud fragrance cames with a warm scent of whiskey, fresh and delicious scent of apple that gives comfort and relaxation feelings after a long day.', 90, 1511100.0, 1511100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_baldessarini_perfumes_amber_oud_for_men_eau_de_perfum_4011700906208.jpg'),
(156, 'Victoria''s Secret Glam Angel Body Mist', 'The wings. The fantasy. The glamour. Our limited-edition runway-ready collection takes the spotlight. The glam Angel, let it bright with the brandy spark and the Icy Woods. The perfect way to add a press of fashion to your fragrance wardrobe.', 250, 545100.0, 545100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/6/667546353375-victoria-secret-victoria_s-secret-glam-angel-body-mist-_u_-250-ml.jpg'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Beau De Jour All Over Body Spray ', 'The notes of amber, woods and musk are blended together to boost your masculinity.
Start your day with the freshness of cool lavender, which delivers self confidence and vitality.
The heart boosts the luxurious feature of the fragrance with a herbal touch,thanks to the notes of basil and rosemary.
The polite man who cares for the details of elegance cannot resist this blend.', 100, 2497800.0, 2497800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066103916-tom-ford-tom-ford-beau-de-jour-_m_-all-over-body-spray-150-ml-1.png'),
(20, 'Givenchy Dahlia Divin Eau Initiale', 'Givenchy Dahlia Divin Eau Initiale is a perfume made for women using white magnolia, the flower symbolizing purity and dignity. This fragrance is made for classy women using beautiful blend of fresh jasmines and rose petals. The opening notes are bergamot and blood orange. The heart notes are fresh magnolia, jasmine, rose and lotus; while the base notes are clean musk and sandalwood. Its light weight mingles with the skin so naturally, it becomes a part of it. This well-balanced and well-composed scent is pretty, feminine and warm. It speaks elegance and delicacy. For every special woman, there is Givenchy Dahlia Divin Eau Initiale.', 50, 2980800.0, 2980800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_givenchy_perfumes_dahlia_divin_eau_initiale_for_women_eau_de_toilette_3274872365940.jpg'),
(17, 'Calvin Klein One Summer 2020 EDT', 'On the seashores of refreshing summer trips, enjoy the salty sea mist caressing your skin.
Express a sense of pleasure and adventure with the scent of sage that penetrates your heart and highlights its strong presence, adding a sense of excitement.
This fragrance adds to your day special moments that remain engraved in your mind and heart long after the trip is over.
Enjoy these unforgettable days with the blend of sandalwood and amber at the base of your distinctive and elegant perfume.', 100, 1476600.0, 1476600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/6/8614229373189-calvin-klein-calvin-klein-ck-one-summer-2020-_u_-edt-100-ml.png'),
(101, 'One Word Syzygy EDP ', 'From the dawn of time, Syzygy has astounded humankind, countless mythical stories have been written in search of its meaning. Syzygy fragrance is inspired by this captivating mystery, blending the dynamic orange flower bergamot with myrrh creating a warm, rich base.', 100, 690000.0, 690000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/n/one_word_syzygy_1.jpg'),
(32, 'Guerlain LUI', 'The floral woody fragrance is designed for those who love to stir up problems. The universal composition has notes of pear, carnation and vanilla, giving you an amazing scent that is not truly feminine or totally masculine.', 51, 3532800.0, 3532800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470177505-guerlain-guerlain_lui-_m_-edp-50-ml-1.jpg'),
(33, 'Lacoste Challenge', 'The fresh blend of this woody spicy scent for men reflects challenge and energy that will fill your spirits. The nice composition of tangerine, ginger and violet leaves will provide you with sensual pleasant harmony, inspiring you to embrace challenges and surprises of life.', 90, 1166100.0, 1166100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/3/737052248097_lacoste_challenge_edt_90ml_1.jpg'),
(44, 'Bvlgari Le Gemme Imperiali Irina', 'A delicate feminine fragrance that takes you to a journey into the purity, mysticism and serenity of Ancient China. This fragrance with floral musk notes adds sensual and sophisticated touch to enjoy elegance and femininity.', 100, 10833000.0, 10833000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_bvlgari_perfumes_le_gmme_imperiali_irina_edp_100_ml_for_unisex_783320461644.jpg'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Tobacco Vanille', 'Tom Ford Tobacco Vanille EDP is a unisex luxurious scent characterized by tobacco. It is an alluring parfume which is produced using marvelous worm, rich, and spicy notes which include; tobacco and spicy notes as top notes. The middle notes comprises of Tonka bean, tobacco blossom, vanilla, and cacao. Finally the base notes are made using dried fruits and woody notes.', 50, 7617600.0, 7617600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_tom_ford_perfumes_tobacco_vanille_for_unisex_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(223, 'Ojar Eagle Eyed Stranger Absolute Perfume Oil', 'An elegant fragrance with intense notes of amber and precious woods
Enjoy the prestigous oriental scent that embodies the beauty of your soul wherever you go.
The intense scent remains until the end of your day, delivering a special look among everyone.
It''s an intense perfume oil for both men and women with a glowing aromatic scent.', 20, 4554000.0, 4554000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 376', 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 376 is designed for the sophisticated fragrance wearers, who shatter expectations with their charisma. It is a woody fragrance with a twist. The burst of the bamboo plant, yuzu, and compote at the opening of the fragrance has a fresh undertone that blends effortlessly with the voluptuousness of the seductive bouquet of rose, jasmine, and lotus flowers to linger long after the scent has faded. The distinctive aroma of the woods can energize your senses and make you feel desired by its slightly provocative fragnance.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000376-tous-les_-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-376-1.png'),
(279, 'Shakespeare Venus And Adonis EDP', 'As an expression of your beauty and charm, the most powerful and fresh fragrance combination comes to you.
A new experience of rare and precious aromatic ingredients that will fill you with a glowing scent.
Enjoy every detail of your day with the scent of perfume that spreads around you and captivates hearts with your love.
A fragrance is the best choice for difference-loving men and women in all their societies.', 100, 3926100.0, 3926100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/7/3788755764770-shakespeare-perfume-shakespeare-venus-and-adonis-spray-100ml.png'),
(10, 'Boucheron Boucheron', 'This fragrance with delicious apricot, lemon and mandarin fruits combines with a soft and delicate scent of floral and rose. This woody fragrance adds a fresh and lively feeling that accompanies you for long hours.', 100, 1373100.0, 1373100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/o/boucheron_boucheron_edp_100_ml.jpg'),
(157, 'Ferrari Red Power Ice3', 'The distinct combination of zesty fruit and spicy earth elements lend to the strong name of FerrariÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s fragrance, Ferrari Red Power Ice 3. This cologne opens up with the commanding and invigorating top notes of grapefruit and coriander. It then shifts down slightly into a clean, rich, woody blend of cardamom and water notes, which make up the heart of this incredible fragrance. Finishing, it slightly smoothes out into the mysterious, cool earthy notes of iris, amber and white musk. This scent was released for men in 2015. As its name indicates, its notes project an element of power and an air of cool confidence.', 125, 1014300.0, 1014300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_ferrari_perfumes_red_power_ice3_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(155, 'Loewe Agua EDT', 'Spicy notes of fresh spices spread in the glowing heart of the composition, touching your heart with enthusiasm.
Start your day with the freshness of yuzu, which deliver vitality, while roseword boost your elegance.
The intense composition spread around, declaring unique presence while remaining for a long time.
It''s your perfect choice on all the bright days of summer so you can accomplish your tasks freely.', 100, 3105000.0, 3105000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/4/8426017066440-loewe-agua-edt-100-ml.png'),
(232, 'Acqua Di Parma Bergamotto di Calabria La Spugnatura EDP', 'An aromatic fragrance that belongs to the fresh citrus olfactory family.
It''s professionally designed to suit both men and women.
This fragrance is designed for those seeking distinction and elegance, delivering an attractive look.
It''s your perfect choice on all your special occasions.
The charming scent captivates the hearts from the very first moment.', 100, 4767900.0, 4767900.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(76, 'Thierry Mugler Angel Men', 'Mugler Angel Men is an original and classic fragrance launched in 1996, the opening is so intense and sweet in artificial way! But it''s elegant and masculine and worth the try!', 100, 2766900.0, 2766900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_mugler_perfumes_angel_men_for_men_eau_de_toilette_3439600666090.jpg'),
(20, 'Givenchy L''interdit Set ', 'This fragrance set for women features an 80 ml bottle of the fragrance along with a 75 ml bath and shower oil and a 75 ml body lotion.
It''s a feminine vital fragrance from the floral family with a rich composition featuring notes of vetiver and patchouli with orange blossom, wrapped with soft jasmine and tuberose.
The scents are carefully blended so you can enjoy an amazing night and happy moments.
The fragrance comes in a feminine collection with shower oil and a small body lotion with the same scent.
It''s easy to pick on your travels and can be offered as a gift for your beloved ones.', 75, 4754100.0, 4754100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/2/3274872420458-givenchy-givenchy-l_interdit-_w_-set-edp-80-ml-_-hydrating-body-lotion-75-ml-_-bath_shower-oil-75-ml-75-ml-1.png'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Si', 'Armani launches a new version of the SÃƒÂ¬ fragrance from 2013, SÃƒÂ¬ Eau de Toilette that comes out in February 2015. This was preceded by editions SÃƒÂ¬ Intense and SÃƒÂ¬ White from 2014. SÃƒÂ¬ Eau de Toilette is a floral, lighter interpretation of the original. The scent is romantic, fresh, youthful and more energetic. It tells you to say "yes" to simplicity, joy of life, dreams and independence. The composition is a chypre - floral, based on contrasts. The scent combines fresh notes of "Neo Jungle Essence", black currant, green pear, Italian bergamot, mandarin and neroli oil with the floral heart of freesia and May rose. A touch of musk, amber wood, vanilla and patchouli end this composition.', 50, 752100.0, 752100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/i/giorgio_armani_s__eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(62, 'Memo Paris Cuirs Nomades Sicilian Leather EDP', 'This fragrance offers you a new and unique experience.
A warm and lively fragrance that gives you a feeling of freshness and comfort.
A sparkling, vibrant fragrance that helps you look elegant and attractive.
The fragrance is enriched with the finest luxurious natural materials to give you a special touch that catches the attention of everyone around you.', 75, 6748200.0, 6748200.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(244, 'Creed White Flowers', 'Created in 2011 to mark the brandÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s 250th anniversary, Creed White Flowers perfume for women captures the purity and intoxication of bright, fruity botanicals in its top notes of green apple, violet leaves, and fresh lemon. Middle notes of spicy geranium, lush rose, and exotic jasmine reveal the lush, titular white florals. Foundational notes of sandalwood and musk are joined by a lingering floral coda of narcissus. A gorgeous trail of refined femininity follows the wearer of this delightful fragrance. Creed White flowers is a complex and impressive blend of floral scents designed to make you feel heavenly.', 75, 19602900.0, 19602900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/5/3508440752055_creed_creed_white_flowers_edp_75_ml_1.jpg'),
(93, 'Mood By Minis', '"Dress for the MoodÃ¢â‚¬Â If your mood was translated into notes, which ''Mood'' fragrance would you pick? Choose your scent every morning based on your mood with this charming set from Minis:
1- Amber Mood:
Feels like a new day? This fragrance is designed for new beginnings, a fresh start full of positivity and surrounded by notes of apple blossom, amber, ylang-ylang & cedarwood.
2- Leather Mood:
Feels like a successful day? If you are ready to take on the world & conquer the impossible, Ã¢â‚¬Å“Leather MoodÃ¢â‚¬Â is there for you! This intense fragrance has the strength & power of cardamom, green matte & leather.
3- Musk Mood:
Feels like a joyful day? Sit back & relax with this cheerful scent draped in neroli sweetness, amber warmth & an aromatic musk base.', 100, 552000.0, 552000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/o/mood.png'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 362', 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 362 is molded by the energy of modernity and romantic sensuality. Without being overly sweet, without being either overly resinous, an irresistible sparkle of delicacy lives all the time. The perfume opens up with a confident aroma of Mango Nectarine, Central Lotus Flower to start decorating this exclusive pyramid. Wait until you fall in love with the sugar-coated Coconut and the sumptuous fruity notes to finally succumb to its magnetism.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000362-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-362-1.png'),
(32, 'Guerlain La Petite Robe Noire Ma Robe Hippie Chic Legere', 'A fragrance created by Guerlain, an Eau de Parfum is enhanced with rose water and cherry. The legendary inverted heart bottle is tinted with an incredibly chic, luminous purple-pink. Through the bottle, you can see the black silhouette of a delicate crocheted dress, ready to experience colorful new adventures.', 100, 1904400.0, 1904400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470134898-guerlain-guerlain-la-petite-robe-noire-ma-robe-hippie-chic-_w_-edp-legere-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(1, 'Dolce & Gabbana The One For Men Baroque Collector Edition', 'Dolce & Gabbana The One For Men Baroque Collector Edition an amazing woody spicy fragrance for men. The newest Perfume of Dolce & Gabbana family and the limited edition of the iconic The One Eau de Toilette. Rich, dense, challenging scent which makes you feel full of life and attractiveness.', 50, 2035500.0, 2035500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_dolce_gabbana_perfumes_the_one_for_men_baroque_collector_edition_for_men_eau_de_toilette_3423473016151.jpg'),
(119, 'Prada Heat Wave EDP', 'The enchanting aromatic scent will take you on a journey to an island at night.
The journey begins with the scents of ylang-ylang and davana, continues with the floral explosion of tuberose and datura, and ends with sweet vanilla.
Enjoy this amazing blend that makes you feel cheerful and refreshing.
It also gives you a very elegant look and enhances your attractiveness and confidence.', 100, 6499800.0, 6499800.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(82, 'Viktor & Rolf Spice Bomb', 'A strong masculine parfume that combines the strongest spices that never fail in showing the power of its scent to ignite your sense of smell as soon as you wear it, a magnificent sensual parfume, definitely bold.', 50, 2635800.0, 2635800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/v/i/viktor_rolf_spicebomb_eau_de_toilette_1.jpg'),
(47, 'Van Cleef & Arpels Reve de Cashmere', 'Extraordinaire oriental fragrance with velvety texture of musk that contains sandalwood, soft cashmere and leather. It blends black vanilla and Indonesian patchouli that brings a warm and soft feeling. It comes in a precious box made of black lacquered wood with a luxurious bottle that makes you feel special.', 125, 7541700.0, 7541700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3386460100618_van_cleef___arpels_van_cleef___arpels_reve_de_cashmere_eau_de_parfum_125_ml_1.jpg'),
(17, 'Calvin Klein Eternity Intense Women', 'Unknown', 100, 1221300.0, 1221300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_calvin_clein_perfumes_eternity_intense_for_women_eau_de_perfum_3614223162925.jpg'),
(24, 'Be Colourful Bundle ', 'This set contains:
