Falling from afar from a magical world full of flowers and purple roses, dreamy and delicate, touching your soul and returning again with its abundant aroma and musky notes that will last for a long time.', 100, 2063100.0, 2063100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/b/sb100379.png'),
(17, 'Calvin Klein Obsession Night', 'It is a citrus floral fragrance that evokes the delicious moments of hot summer nights. It is a garden scented by night-flowering. It opens with citrus bergamot, orange, mandarine, followed by a pure floral heart while the classic base captures vanilla, amber, and sandalwood.', 100, 1380000.0, 1380000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/88300150410-calvin-klein-ck-obsession-night-_l_-edp-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Joie de Vivre Body Spray', 'This body splash will provide you with the charismatic character you want. Its top notes open with magnolia and musk. followed by cherry sprouts at the heart. The base has notes of Japanese Cherry.', 250, 338100.0, 338100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006900495_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_body_splash_joie_de_vivre_tayamun_1.jpg'),
(155, 'Loewe Quizas Pasion', 'This floral fruity fragrance for women is inspired by the tango dance. Its intense composition has notes of red berries, freesia along with amber which will dance on your skin, providing a captivating smell, which is just what you want for all your occasions.', 100, 3884700.0, 3884700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_loewe_perfumes_quizas_pasion_for_women_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(216, 'Jo Malone Cypress & Grapevine EDC', 'A wonderful woody fragrance that is perfect for both men and women.
