About the Brand:
Jo Malone joined the EstÃ©e Lauder Companies, which is available in 69 countries and territories, in 1999. Jo Malone London is a British brand known for its unique fragrances and luxurious products for bath, body, and home. It has written the rules of perfumery by blending unexpected components of ingredients and introducing elegant and playful concepts, the Jo Malone world continues to develop beautifully.', 100, 4857600.0, 4857600.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(20, 'Givenchy Ange Ou Etrange Le Parfum & Accord Illicite Gift Set', 'A new experience! Awaken your senses with Ange ou DÃƒÂ©mon Le Parfum & Accord Illicite, A novel fragrance that combines fragrant jasmine, sensual patchouli, sweet vanilla and sensual musk. It is sensual but warm, powerful but feminine. This fragrance is mysterious, rich and elegant. Accord Illicite is a great addition to the captivating scent. It is warm and comforting. It has a subtle everlasting sillage. It is a magical enhancement of the fragrance. Wear it to your night out or during winter to add warmth to your appearance. It promises an inspirational and a sensational experience, and it is bound to deliver.', 100, 2139000.0, 2139000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfumes_givenchy_perfumes_ange_ou_etrane_le_parfum_for_women_parfum_40ml_2.jpg'),
(38, 'Elie Saab Le Parfum Rose Couture Gift Set ', 'The gift set from Elie Saab contains a Le Parfum Rose Couture Eau de Toilette (90ml) and Eau de Toilette (10ml). Be immersed in a new facet of Elie Saab femininity with the dazzling Rose Couture Eau de Toilette. This addictive chapter in Elie SaabÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s couture fragrance anthology is penned with floral poetry, capturing the ethereal, compelling beauty of ElieÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s aesthetic in a cascade of petals. Sensuous and refined, Rose Couture is a breathtaking bouquet that invites you to a place of pure escapism.', 100, 2829000.0, 2829000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/4/3423473994954-elie-saab-elie-saab-le-parfum-rose-couture-_w_-edt-90-ml-_-edt-10-ml-gift-set-2-piece.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Guitare', 'Guitare 100 ML is an Eau de Parfum For Men and Women from Tous Les Jours which encapsulates the feelings of happiness and joyfulness with top notes of Blood Orange, Mango that will grab your attention immediately, then the heart notes of Raspberry, Star Apple, Water Lily that will take control representing the essence of the perfume to leave you in the end with the base notes of Musk, Sandalwood, Coconut that will linger with you far beyond that.', 100, 1373100.0, 1373100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006903823_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_guitare_100_ml_tayamun_1.jpg'),
(39, 'Rekaz Alarabiah ', 'This bundle includes: Eau De Parfum 50 ml + Perfume Oil 30 ml / 2.57 Tola
A bundle that represents majesty and authentic Arabian scent, its notes were curated from distinctive aromas like cardamom, jasmine, and sandalwood. Enjoy a unique take on Eastern charm, as it combines elements of spiciness, wood warmth, and jasmine softness. indulge in this irresistible fragrance as you apply first the perfume oil onto pulse points, then spray the perfume over it to get the powerful long-lasting result.', 100, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/e/rekaz_alarabiah_box_bottles.jpg'),
(63, 'Dior Homme Intense', 'The appropriately named Dior Homme Intense was released in 2011 and is the perfect blend of sophisticated woody scents, masculine musk aromas, and fragrant floral sweetness. Created by Francois Demachy, the fragrance for men starts with base notes of cedar and vetiver that perfectly mingle with the middle notes of iris, musk mallow, and pear. Lavender top notes keep the fragrance fresh without making it become overwhelming. Spritz this fine cologne on in the morning to complement your work attire, and then wear this long-lasting fragrance well into the night.', 50, 2967000.0, 2967000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3348900838185-dior-homme-intense-1.png'),
(79, 'Atelier Cologne Rose Anonyme Extrait', 'Rose Anonyme Extrait by Atelier Cologne is a unisex floral fragrance. This amazing floral fragrance features accords of Bulgarian rose, Italian bergamot, Indonesian patchouli, and Mediterranean olfactory notes. This fragrance has a fresh and floral composition which makes you feel like the queen of flowers.', 100, 7665900.0, 7665900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/8/7890.jpg'),
(345, 'Liquides Imaginaires Fortis EDP', 'Ancient and mysterious black water with a supernatural power to ward off evil spirits as ancient traditions tell.
A collection of resonant fragrances that form an aromatic jewel that envelopes you in the precious sparkle of guaiac with notes of vanilla and vetiver.
A feeling of sensuality and excessive temptation overwhelms your soul after the dash aroma of saffron and oud.
The composition of the amazing spiritual fragrance helps you to start over to launch towards a bright future and expel all the demons of the past.', 100, 6037500.0, 6037500.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(369, 'Gucci Fading Autumn Acqua Profumata Perfumed Water', 'A splendid blend of fresh floral notes and cheerful fruits appear in harmony with exquisite marine ingredients, resulting in a harmonious delightful mixture that immerses the atmosphere with a strong and glowing scent. It also eliminates all stinky odors in the place and gives a look of elegance and special appeal.', 500, 7728000.0, 7728000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(189, 'Solinotes Cotton Blossom EDP', 'It is a delicate soft powdery scent of a sensual, sexy and attractive fragrance.
Start your aromatic journey with the freshness of bergamot that fills you with enthusiasm and activity all the time.
The aromas of roses and jasmine surround you, adding a sensual, emotional character to the scent.
The base notes contain delicate velvety drops of musk and warm vanilla to increase the beauty of the scent.', 50, 669300.0, 669300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3379501490595-solinotes-solinotes-fleur-de-coton-edp-50ml.png'),
(18, 'Penhaligon''s Eau Sans Pareil EDT', 'A special aromatic blend that reflects the details of feminine attractiveness and sophistication.
The luxurious fragrance combination is all that your beauty needs to remain prominent, attractive, and sexy at all times.
The heart of the fragrance is pure floral with captivating touches of rose and jasmine.
The fragrance is distinguished by its strong and intense scent that stays with you until the last moment without fading.', 100, 4698900.0, 4698900.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(32, 'Guerlain Eau de Cologne Imperiale', 'This luxurious fragrance design was presented to Empress Eugenie, wife of Napoleon III.
Travel back to the past and enjoy ancient memories with the most beautiful and refreshing perfume drops in the world of women.
The perfume narrates a scene from the life of the Empress in the royal palace and her late night parties.
The lemon verbena is accompanied by citrus fruits throughout the palace to announce the appearance of the Queen in her luxurious clothes and precious jewels.
About the Brand:
Guerlain is a legendary French perfume house, one of the oldest perfume houses in the world, with more than 175 years in the world of perfumes. It offers you a group of the most luxurious perfumes that were officially used by the royal families in Europe.', 100, 2601300.0, 2601300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470217669-guerlain-guerlain-eau-de-cologne-imperiale-_w_-edc-100-ml.png'),
(367, 'Alexandre.J The Majestic Amber EDP', '-A stylish aromatic woody fragrance for men that was recently launched in 2020.
-Fragrant notes crowned with freshness, beginning with an aromatic crest crowned with the freshness of lemon, bergamot, and a touch of spicy ginger.
-The heart notes of the fragrance are accompanied by iris and sage clary.
-The base notes are cedarwood, musk, and enchanting amber, for a long-lasting hold.', 100, 4761000.0, 4761000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(44, 'Bvlgari Le Gemme Reali Rubinia', 'A romanity fragrance that symbolizes to a flamboyant gemstone called "The Ruby". This Oriental fragrance combines with Mandarin, Sandalwood and Tonka Bean that gives a pleasant and passionate sense that surrounds you all day.', 100, 10515600.0, 10515600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_bvlgari_perfumes_le_gemme_reali_rubinia_edp_100_ml_for_women_783320468421.jpg'),
(89, 'Azzaro Mademoiselle', 'Mademoiselle by Azzaro is a fresh floral and fruity fragrance presented in a pretty feminine bottle. The fragrance opens with a unique fruity vibe composed of aromatic peach and invigorating mandarin blossom. The middle notes add freshness and slight sweetness with soft peony, smooth jasmine and exquisite orange blossom. The base is mellow with orris and woody notes. AZZARO Mademoiselle is a fresh girly scent for a bubbly woman with romantic dreams. This fragrance is ideal for spring and summer. Wear Azzaro Mademoiselle for a fresh and invigorating feel and a positive aura.', 50, 1497300.0, 1497300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_azzaro_perfumes_mademoiselle_for_women_eau_de_toilette_3351500001606.jpg'),
(22, 'Nicolai Poudre de Musc Intense EDP', 'A bright and glowing aromatic luster of enchanting musk and soft sandalwood.
The heart of the floral fragrance exudes soft, sensual floral notes to excite your senses.
The fragrance reveals the beautiful scent of aldehydes in the first moments.
Start your day with a special and distinctive freshness with this fragrance blend that renews your energy.', 100, 5761500.0, 5761500.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(314, 'Two Mark Oud EDP', 'A new feeling that makes your soul search for the secret of elegance and sophistication
