The oriental fragrance for men and women will be your personal brand, attracting everyone''s attention', 75, 2070000.0, 2070000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6281150544208-two-mark-oud.png'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 320', 'A special addition to your remarkable collection. The composition of this fragrance features upper notes of watermelon, followed by lavender in the heart and cashmeran, providing you with a long-lasting scent that keeps your refreshed and cool for long time.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000320-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-320-1.png'),
(14, 'Maqam Al Shoyoukh EDP ', 'The word "Sheikh" has a deep and long history in the Oriental world, and for a long time, this word has always been reflected with luxury and pride. We offer you this perfume to take you on a captivating journey to Europe with Moroccan jasmine and rose. After, you will feel the fragrance of authentic amber with notes of musk and aged Virginia cedarwood that will create mountains of solidity and strength inside your soul. You will also experience the scent of red apple along with the sweetness of caramel for a sprinkle of deliciousness. This perfume is specially made to make you feel the oriental luxury that surrounds us with its endless splendor.', 120, 4830000.0, 4830000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/a/maqam-alshoyoukh-d_2_.png'),
(34, 'Deem Perfumes Hotel ', 'Deem Perfumes Hotel is a room spray that spreads enticing fragrance in the air and let you enjoy the fresh and aromatic air. It has a sweet and fresh smell which makes the atmosphere cheerful.', 100, 690000.0, 690000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006660399_deem_hotel_300_ml_1.jpg'),
(369, 'Laboratorio Olfattivo Nerosa EDP', '#NAME?', 100, 2304600.0, 2304600.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(327, 'Laurent Mazzone Sensual Orchid', 'Laurent Mazzone Sensual Orchid is a happy perfume that never misses imbuing a day with a smile from the first spritz. This perfume is a warm and embracing oriental fragrance that evokes the wearer with a sweet bouquet. This perfume starts with a voluptuous touch of almond, mandarin orange, and neroli, fused in a subtle yet charming scent of orchid, heliotrope, and ylang-ylang to awake all the sensuality surrounding. The vanilla, benzoin, musk, and labdanum revolve at the base, leaving behind a sweet final scent.', 100, 8335200.0, 8335200.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(192, 'Salvador Dali Laguna EDT', 'A feminine revolution sparked by the fragrance of flowers and fresh and refreshing fruits.
As the sun rises into a new day, enjoy refreshing and lively beginnings of mandarin and plum that rejuvenate your enthusiasm.
The heart of the floral fragrance resembles your tender heart and reflects your glowing passion to heighten feelings of seduction and excitement.
A new and distinctive olfactory experience that ends with touches of warm tonka bean and splendid musk that stays with you for long hours.', 100, 1649100.0, 1649100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3331430890730-salvador-dali-salvador-dali-laguna-_w_-edt-100-ml.png'),
(121, 'IL Profvmo Romeo EDP', 'If you look for luxury and elegance in your special occasions, then it''s time to achieve your dream.
The composition is intense and concentrated, thanks to the notes of lavender and rosemary, which fill you with morning freshness to keep you revitalized.
The notes of leather and tobacco in the base add a classic touch to provide an elegant look.
Your unique scent remains in the minds of everyone, getting you the attention and love you want.', 100, 5354400.0, 5354400.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(364, 'Robert Piguet Casbah EDP', 'An exciting mysterious journey to Marrakech''s busy markets.
The composition has notes of spicy pepper in the beginning along with nutmeg and vital angelica.
The warm heart has notes of tobacco and incense, delivering a classic touch.
Be ready for a new adventure that remains in your mind for a long time even after the end of your day.', 100, 5140500.0, 5140500.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(6, 'Versace Red Jeans Women', 'A fruity floral fragrance, possessing a youthful and modern spirit and refreshes your heart, with a wonderful mixture of peach, violet, and sandalwood.', 75, 841800.0, 841800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_versace_perfumes_red_jeans_women_for_women_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(32, 'Guerlain La Petite Robe Noire Black Perfecto ', 'The classic gift set contains Black Perfecto By La Petite Robe Noire Eau de Pafrum Floral (50ml) and Eau de Pafrum (15ml) purse spray. This fragrance was created by Guerlain. It''s a floral Eau de Toilette celebrating the rose in all its forms. Grass rose water, rose essential oil, and rose absolute are encircled with almond and leather notes. The iconic inverted heart bottle takes on an intensely dark, black look. The white label embroidered roses lend a finishing touch to this couture and fashion style.', 15, 3215400.0, 3215400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470133822-guerlain-guerlain-black-perfecto-by-la-petite-robe-noire-_w_-set-edp-florale-50-ml-_-edp-15-ml-purse-spray-1.jpg'),
(47, 'Van Cleef & Arpels Collection Extraordinaire Santal Blanc', 'It is a new floral, woody musk fragrance for women and men. It starts with mandarin orange and fig nectar with a floral and woody heart. Tonka bean and musk form the base.', 75, 5009400.0, 5009400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3386460108645-van-cleef-van-cleef-_-arpels-collection-extraordinaire-santal-blanc-_u_-edp-75-ml.jpg'),
(196, 'Exuma Parfums Velvet Cachemir Woman EDP', 'The oriental notes of pepper and amber harmonize with the enchanting fragrance of roses in amazing harmony.
The warm and spicy accord begins with the scent of cinnamon mixed with the cool freshness of bergamot.
The fragrance is built on a pure base of vetiver and musk that highlights the sweetness of the scent.
The strong smell of the perfume makes it your best choice on all special occasions.', 100, 3491400.0, 3491400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/5/9/5902734847515-exuma-exuma-parum-valvet-cachemire-100-ml_1_.png'),
(63, 'Dior Miss Dior Originale', 'Miss Dior Originale contains top notes of gardenia, galbanum, bergamot and clary sage. It unfolds into a floral scent of jasmine, neroli, narcissus, lily of the valley, carnation and orris. It is not as akin to modern feminine scents as it is to the old robust perfumes from the mid-twentieth century. This heavy scent ends with warm, spicy notes of patchouli, oakmoss, cistus, sandalwood, amber, vetiver, labdanum, ambergris, and castoreum. This is the type of scent that people will take notice of and that will linger when youÃ¢â‚¬â„¢re gone. It is sensual, heavy and robust.', 100, 4416000.0, 4416000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/i/dior_miss_dior_originale_edt_100_ml.jpg'),
(330, 'Boadicea The Victorious Chariot', 'An Oriental Floral fragrance with sweety fruit of apple, black currant and red berries that combines with tuberose, neroli, ylang-ylang. This fragrance mixes with a soft and fresh scent of jasmine, rose, and cherry that all come with a loveable scent of vanilla.', 100, 10412100.0, 10412100.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(190, 'Sisley Sisley Eau de 2 EDT', 'It evokes the image of a soft and attractive women''s dress with its sexy pink color.
The refreshing blend of basil and bergamot enhances your sense of femininity and enchants hearts.
The captivating fragrance has a passionate floral heart loaded with seductive, passionate drops of iris and jasmine.
Your unique beauty needs these distinctive aromatic details that raise your standing among the audience and increases your femininity.', 100, 3946800.0, 3946800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/4/3473311932006-sisley-sisley-eau-de-sisley-2-_w_-edt-100-ml.png'),
(318, 'Miu Miu Mini Set ', 'This set has 4 wonderful perfume with the refreshing lemon and peach and the attractive scent of jasmine to give you a great smell make you confident.', 7, 2166600.0, 2166600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614224935894_miu_miu_miu_miu_w_edp_2_x_7_5ml_miu_miu_l_eau_bleue_2_x_7_5ml_mini_set_gs-dmm_cross_dock_1.jpg'),
(32, 'Guerlain Santal Royal Guerlain', 'Guerlain Santal Royal is a woody oriental fragrance for men and women alike; derives its inspiration from the East. This is a balanced oud scent that takes you on a trip to the exotic Orient. It embraces the paradox between the dark notes of leather and oud and the floral notes of rose and jasmine. The tantalizing aroma of jasmine and neroli sweeps you off your feet before it develops at the heart with cinnamon, rose and peach. The sweet scents are wrapped up in a base of sandalwood, leathery notes, musk notes and oud notes.', 125, 5947800.0, 5947800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_guerlain_perfumes_santal_royal_guerlain_for_unisex_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(32, 'Guerlain Oud Essentiel', 'Guerlain Oud Essentiel is a unisex oriental, woody fragrance. It brings the East and West together in a beautiful paradox. Oud is a mysterious and exotic element that is always a winning choice. The fragrance opens with a touch of Saffron notes and Pelargonium. At the heart Rose blooms along oud and Atlas cedar. The final notes evoke nostalgia with refined leather notes smoothly blended with incense and GaÃƒÂ¯ac wood. This divine, classy scent is perfect for cool months and special evenings. Guerlain Oud Essentiel conquers the senses, opens the heart and uplifts the spirit.', 125, 5947800.0, 5947800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_guerlain_perfumes_oud_essentiel_for_women_eau_de_perfum-3346470132245.jpg'),
(11, 'Mont Blanc Legend Set ', 'A luxury collection for men who love luxury.
The collection contains 5 perfumes with distinctive scents: 2 x 4.4 ml Mini EDT in Mont Blanc Legend + 2 x 4.4 Mini EDP Spray in Mont Blanc Explorer + 4.4 ml Mini EDT in Mont Blanc Legend Spirit for Men
Enjoy attractive looks with these wonderful fragrances.
The set comes in an elegant package that you can present as a gift to all your loved ones on happy occasions.
