(47, 'Van Cleef & Arpels Van Cleef', 'Van Cleef & Arpels Van Cleef parfume for Women is a sharp oriental and floral fragrance. The top notes include: orange blossom, raspberry and rose. The middle notes are orange blossom, cedar wood, vanilla, and the base notes are musk, Tonka bean and moss. The parfume is recommended as an evening fragrance.', 100, 4222800.0, 4222800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_van_cleef_arpels_perfumes_van_cleef_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(51, 'Al Dakheel Oud Mabsoos Al', 'Full of oriental heritage, it has scents of roses and creamy woods, with sweet fruity aromas to fill the atmosphere with freshness and attractiveness,. The scent stays with you on all your special days without fading', 100, 1193700.0, 1193700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6281150553651-al-dakheel-for-oud-mabsoos-al-shioukh.png'),
(358, 'Maison Rebatchi Cuir Tassili EDP', 'An aromatic creation inspired by the exciting journey through the Algerian desert and its golden sands.
