(5, 'Giorgio Armani Armani Code Absolu Gold Pour Homme', 'This spicy enthusiastic oriental perfume was designed for modern men who love to discover life and progress greatly to their peers, The fragrances amazing combination is rich with the aroma of iris and the heat of saffron that overwhelm your heart with passion and excitement to go ahead with joy and deliver you benzoin and tonka beans for a beautiful and distinctive appearance.', 110, 3332700.0, 3332700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614272642225-giorgio-armani-giorgio-armani-armani-code-absolu-gold-pour-homme-_m_-parfum-110-ml-1.jpg'),
