About the Brand:
Jo Malone joined the EstÃ©e Lauder Companies, which is available in 69 countries and territories, in 1999. Jo Malone London is a British brand known for its unique fragrances and luxurious products for bath, body, and home. It has written the rules of perfumery by blending unexpected components of ingredients and introducing elegant and playful concepts, the Jo Malone world continues to develop beautifully.', 100, 2518500.0, 2518500.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(32, 'Guerlain La Petite Robe Noire', 'Guerlain La Petite Robe Noire presents to the world an au courant fragrance that matches the splendor and everlastingness of the black dress. Lemon, anise and almond are at the floral opening. The heart is lavish with licorice, roses and raspberry macaroons. Vanilla, musk, patchouli and smoked tea make the base sweetly satisfying. The bottle is a gorgeous match of the elegant perfume. Guerlain La Petite Robe Noire is a fresh and youthful fragrance. It is effervescent and sweet. On fall and winter nights, it adds a feel of warmth. With this terrific fragrance, nothing can stop you.', 50, 2118300.0, 2118300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/u/guerlain_la_petit_robe_noir_edp_women.jpg'),
(358, 'Maison Rebatchi Musc Panache EDP', 'A fragrance with a sensual signature that ignites your desire and sensuality.
