(44, 'Bvlgari Pour Homme Soir', 'This is a special fragrance with bergamot and amber that adds love and romance touch to create every moment in your memory.', 100, 1531800.0, 1531800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/v/bvlgari_pour_homme_soir_eau_de_toilette_2.jpg'),
(32, 'Guerlain Vetiver Extreme', 'The scent of the earth, it is a particularly original interpretation of vetiver that the perfumer Guerlain offers us with Vetiver Extreme, where one is woody and fresh, the other promises to be just as woody but aromatic. If the frame is still there, faithful, the agreement becomes more intense. Each facet of the vetiver root is worked to keep its essence and singularities. All the art of the perfumer is embodied in a true "spirit of perfume."', 100, 1952700.0, 1952700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470303201-guerlain-guerlain-vetiver-extreme-_m_-edt-100-ml-1.jpg'),
