(44, 'Bvlgari Man Wood Essence', 'Description
The house of Bvlgari launches this new fragrance in July 2018, as a part of the Bvlgari Man collection. The philosophy of this new fragrance is based on the balance between the urban life of a modern man and the call of nature. Bvlgari Man Wood Essence combines a coriander leaf, lemon zest, and citruses with sugar, mixed with spicy notes, Italian citrus zest along with cedar gives a fresh, green character with it.', 60, 2035500.0, 2035500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/8/783320461019-bvlgari-bvlgari-man-wood-essence-_m_-edp-60-ml.jpg'),
(71, 'Hermes Twilly D''Hermes', 'Twilly D''Hermes is a lively and uplifting perfume that wows you with its citrus and white floral fragrance. The perfume is enhanced by spice and wood. The fragrance wears on your mind with its opening notes of effervescent ginger laced with bitter orange and bergamot. The heart notes are taken by orange blossom, lush tuberose, and heady jasmine, followed by vanilla and silken sandalwood. This perfume is inspired by colorful silk scarves.', 85, 2304600.0, 2304600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_hermes_perfumes_twilly_d_hermes_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(117, 'Laboratorio Olfattivo Di', 'A wonderful fragrance by Thameen Fragrance is perfectly designed for men and women.
