(320, 'Thierry Mugler Supra Floral', 'A bouquet of green notes that brings spring into your hands. A fragrance that opens with the scent of fresh green hyacinth petals and velvet, and moves from light green to dark green, with the base of amber that is always present in oriental parfumes to preserve its sophistication and luxury.', 80, 6527400.0, 6527400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_mugler_perfumes_supra_floral_edp_80_ml_for_unesex_3439604000111.jpg'),
(63, 'Dior Fahrenheit', 'This ozonic fragrance opens its composition with the most intense note so far, suede, accompanied by Sicilian mandarin and sweet licorice root. The heart of the composition provides a new blend of aromas by mixing violet leaf absolute and rum absolute spiced with coriander and caraway. The base of the perfume introduces Bourbon vanilla absolute that highlights the beauty of the ingredients, ensures stability, warms, and cuddles the skin.', 75, 4167600.0, 4167600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3348901116817-christian-dior-christian-dior-fahrenheit-_m_-parfum-75-ml.jpg'),
