(49, 'Lalique White', 'Lalique White is a citrusy, musky, spicy and elegant fragrance for men. Quite calm, clear and clean, this perfume emits a natural scent, which gives a peaceful vibe. This unique and beautiful scent opens with a blast of Calabrian Bergamot and Lemon Tree Leaves. The Sicilian Tamarind accord is mysteriously tempting and exotic as it blends with Philippine Elemi. The shift to peppery and spicy heart is complex in a pleasant way. A light shade of Nutmeg and Cardamom help the scent evolve. The powdery touch by Vanilla perfect the heart notes that yield gracefully to a velvety base as Musk, clean, fresh and classy blend with White Cedar. The scent evolves sweetly thanks to the Moss and Amber.', 125, 2787600.0, 2787600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_lalique_perfumes_lalique_white_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 62', 'Feel refreshed and cool with this amazing fragrance that has top notes of bergamot, followed by cotton candy in the middle and vanilla in the base. The gorgeous composition will fill your spirits with positive vibes, which keeps you in good mood as long as you wear it.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000062-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours---perfume-day-62-1.png'),
(11, 'Mont Blanc Emblem Absolu Gift Set ', 'This three-piece gift set features EDT (100 ml), EDT (7.5 ml) and shower gel (100 ml). This woody spicy scent will convey the feeling of warmth and luxury. The composition features top notes of pear, followed by honey in the heart and vetiver in the base, bringing to you a marvellous scent that envelops you with unique sensation of relax and comfort.', 100, 2035500.0, 2035500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3386460097994-mont-blanc-mont-blanc-emblem-absolu-_m_-set-edt-100-ml-_-edt-7.5-ml-_-all-over-shower-gel-100-ml.jpg'),
(51, 'Al Dakheel Oud Exlamation Silver EDP', 'A fragrance that suits your taste and attracts everyone around you with its distinctive scent.
