(40, 'Tom Ford Italian Cypress', 'This fragrance appeared on the market in September 2008, as part of the Private Blend collection. It is created in associations with Italian Cypress aromas, as fine alchemy of woody resins. Described by the designer as an aromatic chypre, the perfume includes notes of citrus, basil, mint, and woody notes, yielding to a warm heart of Cypress.', 50, 7224300.0, 7224300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066004756-tom-ford-tom-ford-italian-cypress-_u_-edp-50-ml-1.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Body Spray Day 296', 'Body Mist Day 296 from Tour Les Jours has a rosy and acidic scent that lasts a while and provides your body with fresh. It contains Pink pepper, African orange blossom, Benzoin, tonka bean and vanilla', 250, 338100.0, 338100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006900310_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_body_spray_day_296_tayamun_1.jpg'),
