(63, 'Dior Miss Dior Absolutely Blooming', 'Miss Dior Absolutely Blooming is the fruity floral fragrance for the woman who loves life and embraces it wholeheartedly. Wear this fragrance during the day, and throughout the year, when you want to add a refreshing boost to your step. A heavy sillage ensures this long-lasting fragrance fills the room when you enter and remains behind as a tantalizing reminder of your presence when you make your exit. The top notes of this delicious perfume pyramid include pink pepper, black currant, pomegranate, and raspberry. The floral middle notes are peony and May rose. The aromatic base note is white musk.', 50, 4933500.0, 4933500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/i/dior_miss_dior_absolutely_blooming.jpg'),
(281, 'Parfums RP Prive No.4 EDP', 'A luxurious oriental fragrance enriched with agarwood.
