(5, 'Giorgio Armani Emporio Diamonds', 'This beautiful floral perfume works on reflecting the brilliance of women and the energy of their enthusiasm, as well as, enhancing their sense of confidence in all moments. Fragrance drops fall on your skin loaded with the most wonderful scents of flowers and provide you with a sparkling scent that captures hearts and makes the eyes stray to enjoy the beauty of your look. Always be prepared to enjoy the special romantic moments and happy nights.', 100, 2056200.0, 2056200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3605521000590-giorgio-armani-giorgio-armani-emporio-diamonds-_w_-edt-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(172, 'Diptyque 34 boulevard Saint Germain EDT', 'A strong and bold fragrance with a distinctive aromatic blend for men and women.
