(71, 'Hermes Twilly D''Hermes Gift Set ', 'It''s a two piece gift set, it features EDP (50ml) and body lotion (40 ml). The floral daring fragrance is designed for the independent and feminine spirit. The composition has notes of ginger, tuberose and sandalwood, revealing a scent for those who swim against the tide to impose their own rhythm.', 40, 3594900.0, 3594900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346133201745-hermes-hermes-twilly-d_hermes-_w_-set-edp-50-ml-_-moisturizing-body-lotion-40-ml-1.jpg'),
(60, 'S.T. Dupont Royal Amber', 'S. T. Dupont Royal Amber is an oriental perfume for men and women that takes you on a magical carpet ride to the exotic realms of the east. This posh and luxurious amber-based scent has a leathery-woody opening with a blast of oud. The masculine accords of cedar and sandalwood occupy the heart surrounded by a playful hint of red berries. Patchouli and saffron add a rich and sensual air to the heart before oud strikes back again in the base along with geranium. Amber is divine as it blends smoothly with the other notes giving a gorgeous luxurious vibe and a cozy scent.', 100, 3291300.0, 3291300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_s.t.dupont_perfumes_royal_amber_for_unisex_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(76, 'Thierry Mugler Angel', 'An addictive feminine fragrance with a refreshing scent that makes you remember your delightful happy moments with an infinite dream-like feeling. It combines the calmness and tranquility with curiosity and mystery, helping you to pursue your dreams. The bottle is distinguished by its distinctive design which looks like a clear blue sky with the bright stars at night. A fragrance for the attractive, bright woman, with notes of bergamot, chocolate and mandarin.', 50, 1807800.0, 1807800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/h/thierry_mugler_angel.jpg'),
(18, 'Penhaligon''s The Inimitable William Penhaligon EDP', 'A luxurious woody fragrance for men with refined taste.
