(156, 'Victoria''s Secret Dream Angels Desire', 'This aromatic floral fragrance is inspired by natural flowers with calm delicate notes of magnolia and peony mixed with original woody notes of musk to offer you a special olfactory experience.', 30, 1476600.0, 1476600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/6/667525781045-victoria_s-secret-dream-angels-desire-_w_-edp-30-ml-1.jpg'),
