(20, 'Givenchy Ange Ou Etrange', 'Designed by fragrance Givenchy, Ange Ou Etrange is a captivating perfume that manages to convey mysterious yet intoxicating fragrance the moment the bottle is opened. Refreshing top notes of lilies and oranges reach the senses in a fruity presentation followed by heart notes of heliotrope and Lily of the Valley which bring a more mild, floral feel. At the base of this magical combination lies a base not of Patchouli which provides a final woodsy tone to the exquisite perfume. The unmistakable bottle features an elongated teardrop shape with colors that vary from light to dark.', 100, 2484000.0, 2484000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/i/givenchy_ange_ou_etrange_eau_de_parfum_spray.jpg'),
(16, 'Al Majed for Oud Albiyaa EDP', 'Elegant soft woody ingredients that improve your mood throughout the day
