Upon sniffing this scent for the first time, you will take it as your favorite companion and your trusted healer.', 100, 4761000.0, 4761000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 94', 'Inhale natural floral fragrance with Tous Les Jours Day 94 where the scent of Lavender, freesia, basil, mint, sage, Mimose, iris blended with the scent of violet flower, freesia, Coumarin, amber, patchouli, oakmoss, vetiver, and cedar.', 55, 683100.0, 683100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000094_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_perfume_day_94_tayamun_1.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 386', 'Mesmerizing, with force and charisma, but still sensitive, Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 386 recalls the classic elegance combined with the sophistication. Sometimes rebel but always trendy, this fragrance is designed with soft oriental flavor to impress and inspire its wearers. A melange of bergamot, nutmeg, Turkish rose, peony, vanilla, musk, cashmere wood, vetiver, cedarwood, and incense have distinguished this modern bowl of bliss with an undeniable seductive scent.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000386-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-386-1.png'),
