(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 355', 'Tous Les Jours launched a wide array of romance scent notes into Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 355, expressing love and its prohibitions, darkness and light. Saffron, enfolded in cinnamon, exude their charismatic scent, while Orange Blossom transcends the Honey with its intoxicating scent at the heart as if to better diffuse its spellbinding trail. The base unveils its sensibility and warmth into an overwhelming sweet scent of almond, chocolate, melted in the sophisticated scent of leather. A bit seductive, but surely smiling perfume is there for you every day to add sweetens and enticement to the flavor of life.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000355-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-355-1.png'),
(51, 'Al Dakheel Oud Crown Red Cream ', 'A soft musky floral formula of lavender and pure white flowers that envelops your skin in its attractive and sensual scent. It has a soft and fast-absorbing texture that treats all dryness and roughness in your skin. It also provides your skin with intense hydration that starts from the depths to your skin surface.
Benefits:
