(244, 'Creed Cedre Blanc', 'Cedre Blanc is a distinguished fragrance by Creed. Subtle, yet empowering, the mix of bold spices and woody cedar are softened by floral accents. A strong base of cedar, sandalwood, and vetiver hold the aromatic adventure together. Top notes of bergamot, cardamom, galbanum, and bay leaf bring out the woody blend of the base while adding the spice. To ensure the impact of the entire assortment, fragrant geranium and white floral jasmine and lily make up the alluring middle notes for the perfect daytime wear fragrance.', 100, 7383000.0, 7383000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/5/3508441001459_creed_creed_cedre_blanc_edp_100_ml_1.jpg'),
(32, 'Guerlain Black Perfecto By La Petite Robe Noire', 'Black Perfecto by La Petite Robe Noire was launched in 2017 representing the dark and edgy fragrance, with notes of rose, leather, licorice and almond. The inspiration for the perfume is the contrast of style between a biker leather jacket and an elegant black evening dress.', 100, 1787100.0, 1787100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470133549_guerlain_guerlain_black_perfecto_by_la_petite_robe_noire_w_edp_30_ml_1.jpg'),
(147, 'Braccialini Purple', 'BRACCIALINI Purple is floral, fruity and sweet fragrance for women. It is the last finish that you need for a bright and fulfilling day. The fragrance opens with a delightful mixture of mandarin, airy black current and lush pear. The middle notes are a floral blend of Sambac jasmine, ylang-ylang, orange blossom and white flowers. The base contains oriental notes including amber wood, white musk and Tonka bean. Purple is a ravishing color that flatters charming gorgeous women, giving them a seductive aura. Wear this scent for romantic cool nights.', 50, 1490400.0, 1490400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_braccialini_perfumes_purple_for_women_eau_de_perfum_8007033040258.jpg'),
