(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 385', 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 385 possesses an exclusive scent with attractive wooden components that provides an irresistible oriental character. This fragrance opens up with bergamot and pink pepper to subtly smolder you with a mesmeric appeal. Benzoin, amber, vanilla, and tonka bean revolve at heart as a refined concentrate of addiction and sensuality to melt in a warm and exotic touch of woody aroma.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000385-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-385-1.png'),
