(20, 'Givenchy L''Interdit EDP ', 'This three-piece set includes Eau de perfume (80 ml) and a travel-size scent (10 ml) and a body lotion (75 ml). The fragrance''s top features Bergamot at the top, followed by a heart of Orange Blossom, Jasmine, and Tuberose, while the base has notes of Vetiver, Patchouli, Ambroxan and Vanilla.', 10, 4360800.0, 4360800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/2/3274872401723_givenchy_givenchy_l_interdit_woman_edp_80ml_body_lotion_75ml_edp_10ml_set_women_1.jpg'),
