(130, 'Shiseido Zen', 'Shiseido Zen is a vibrant floral scent, with wood and spices designed by Michael Almairac. It opens up with a zesty grapefruit note, sweet bergamot, orange, pineapple, wrapped in blue rose. The heart features a floral bouquet made of freesia, gardenia, violet, lily-of-the-valley, Chinese rose, red apple, and lotus blossom. The base notes are a warm and sensual blend of patchouli, cedarwood, musk and white musk, amber and frankincense. This bottle is designed by Taisuke Kikuchi.', 50, 1814700.0, 1814700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_shiseido_perfumes_zen_for_women_eau_de_perfum_768614102014.jpg'),
