(208, 'Lootah Rawda Small Jar Incense ', 'An amazing incense for those who are looking for exceptional and distinctive scents to fill their homes especially in the morning. The incense has a scent that makes you feel fresh and energetic, and is suitable for starting your day. This wonderful scent is extracted from the finest natural ingredients that are carefully selected.', 100, 1890600.0, 1890600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6297000836515-lootah-lootah-rawda---small-jar-incense-77-gms.png'),
(74, 'Davidoff Champion', 'This woody aromatic fragrance is characterized by its deep masculine scent that represents strength and power. It features top notes of bergamot and lemon flowing into a heart of clary sage and galbanum. The smooth base has a blend of oakmoss and cedar, making it a perfect scent for any occasion.
About the brand
