(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 381', 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 381 Spray is the final touch to a sexy outfit and memorable occasion. This seductive aroma has been said to be a "head-turning love potion." for its richness and warmness. The sophistication of this fragrance is phenomenal since it can boost your confidence and make you feel the most desired, unassigned with gender or time. The wearer will be enveloped with the delicacy and sweetness of the aquatic aroma of tangerine, grapefruit, and black currant, melted in the enticing scent of tuberose, ylang-ylang, jasmine, and orange blossom, pear, pink pepper, lily of the valley. The perfume ends in a fresh scent of sandalwood, musk, cashmere wood, and iris to ensure the blend will go smooth and striking.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000381-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-381-1.png'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Emporio Armani Diamonds Rose', 'Start your day with this refreshment of bergamot and berries that opens the way to the scents of freesia and lily of the valley that settles on your skin for a long time with a charming refreshed look.', 50, 1697400.0, 1697400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3605521819987-giorgio-armani-giorgio-armani-emporio-armani-diamonds-rose-_w_-edt-50-ml-1.jpg'),
(7, 'Xerjoff Shooting Stars Wabar EDP', 'This fragrance is one of the secrets of feminine beauty, making you alluring and exciting to the eyes of all those present
