(5, 'Giorgio Armani Code Absolu', 'An oriental, addictive, spicy fragrance for men. It has the highest percentage of essential oils, as well as notes of tonka beans and vanilla, ensuring this scent will last all day and night. The iconic Armani Code bottle, with its elegant shiny black cap and its textured tuxedo belt, is shrouded in gold.', 110, 3463800.0, 3463800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614272407442_giorgio_armani_code_absolu_edp_110_ml_1.jpg'),
(16, 'Al Majed For Oud Mabsous Fakher ', 'This oriental incense is extracted from the luxurious oud, blended with amazing notes that add modern touches to your house to captivate the hearts of your guests.', 100, 2387400.0, 2387400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6285091014998-almajed-for-oud-mabsous-fakher---56-gm-1.png'),
