(20, 'Givenchy Play In The City Pour Homme', 'This energetic and distinctive refreshment is given by the intense fragrance drops, with their constant heavy scent of citrus and licorice, mixed with a heart rich in the aroma of licorice. It envelops you with a strong aroma that enhances your attraction and boosts your positive energy in the middle of the day. The fragrance ends with concentrated woods and enchanted amber to provide you with a unique and distinctive appearance until the last hours of the day.', 100, 2635800.0, 2635800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/2/3274870001765-givenchy-givenchy-play-in-the-city-pour-homme-_m_-edt-100ml-1.jpg'),
(49, 'Lalique Nilang', 'Lalique Nilang is an oriental fruity fragrance for women, presented in a gorgeous bottle with a flower stopper and crystal glass that celebrates beauty, femininity and nature. The top notes open with a miraculous scent. The Lotus Flower floats ahead of the fruity entrance. Peach and Melon give out a sweet vibe. The middle phase preserves the floral notes with Jasmine, Clove Flower, Freesia and Wild Blueberries. The balanced and sexy base consists of hints of Sandalwood and Amber with delicious Praline and pure Vanilla. This creative blend of different accords is a unique characteristic of Lalique.', 100, 765900.0, 765900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_lalique_perfumes_nilang_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
