(40, 'Tom Ford For Men', 'It''s a Natural Eau de Parfum that with a composition that begins with notes of Ginger, Mandarin Orange, Lemon Leaf Oil, Basil, Bergamot, Violet Leaf, the heart notes of Tunisian Orange Blossom, Pepper, Tobacco Leaf, Grapefruit Blossom that represents the essence of the parfume, and the base notes of Amber, Virginian Patchouli, Oakmoss, Vetiver, Cedar, Leather, Cypriol Oil Or Nagarmotha which stays with you throughout the day.', 100, 4450500.0, 4450500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_tom_ford_perfumes_tom_ford_for_men_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
