(5, 'Giorgio Armani Acqua di Gio EDT', 'A refreshing floral fruity fragrance is designed for women.
The fragrance was launched with a unique fragrance blend in 1995.
The fragrance possesses a wonderful blend of musk, vodka, peony, pineapple, lemon, banana leaf, peach and violet.
This wonderful amalgamation gives you an unparalleled freshness that leaves you spending your day full of vitality and energy.
The heart of the fragrance is enriched with an enchanting blend of jasmine, freesia, and rose.
The fragrance is finally based on a precious base of musk, cedar, sandalwood, and amber to give you a scent that stays steady with you for as long as possible.', 100, 2635800.0, 2635800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3360372054559-giorgio-armani-giorgio-armani-acqu-di-gio-_w_-edt-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(99, 'Vintage Gold Leather', 'A luxurious oriental parfume for men and women with a special blend of oriental Arabic parfumes from leather, oud and musk, amber and saffron captivates you to the charm of the authentic East.', 100, 2256300.0, 2256300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/5/3588981241265_vintage_vintage_gold_leather_edp_100_ml_1.jpg'),
(20, 'Givenchy Live Irresistible Gift Set ', 'GIVENCHY Live Irresistible for Women Gift Set presents a wonderful surprise to the fascinating women of the world. Live IrrÃƒÂ©sistible, an enticing combination of pink novelty and vivid verve. It is a balance of different alluring aromas. It beautifully combines fruits, spices and flowers. It shifts between the fragrances smoothly leaving an appealing scent. The pepper and pineapple notes are captivating. The fragranceÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s sweet and fresh smell is perfect for the summer. The tropical vibe takes you on a time-travelling trip to your most cherished memories. The body lotion given out by Givenchy will keep the aroma lingering on your body, leaving you feeling fresh and luxurious. While the pouch is the feminine touch you need to glow.', 75, 4174500.0, 4174500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_givenchy_perfumes_live_irresistible_for_women_eau_de_perfum_3274872345423.jpg'),
(55, 'Hugo Boss Boss Orange Woman', 'A warm and passionate fragrance that combines exceptionally refreshing notes of crunchy apple freshness and floral notes with a scent of vanilla and sandalwood. All these notes complement each other to create a fragrance that liberates feelings and you can enjoy it with a lot of passion', 50, 1000500.0, 1000500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/u/hugo_boss_boss_orange_woman_eau_de_toilette_1.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 375', 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 375 brings all the joyful and breath-taking aromas of the garden into this bowl of bliss. This perfume opens up with an exotic yet exciting blend of Pomegranate and Lemon to arouse your senses. It entwines a sweet blend of rosebud, green apple, geranium flowers, succumbing to its magnetism. The magnificent bouquet continues at the base of the perfume, where jasmine and wisteria ensure that this perfume is the star of the show. Worth trying!', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000375-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-375-1.png'),
(110, 'Thierry Mugler Passion Edition', 'Thierry Mugler Angel Passion Star Edition is a feminine oriental vanilla fragrance which was launched in the year 2015. The top notes of the perfume are melon, coconut, mandarin orange, jasmine, cassis, cotton candy and bergamot. Heart notes are honey, apricot, blackberry, plum, orchid, peach, jasmine, red berries, lily-of-the-valley and rose. Base notes are amber, patchouli, musk, vanilla, Tonka beans, chocolate, and caramel.', 50, 3339600.0, 3339600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/4/3439600002539_thierry_mugler_thierry_mugler_edition_passion_edp_50_ml_1.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Amour', 'Amour 100 ml is an Eau de Parfum For Men and Women from Tous Les Jours that will suit your delicate and sensitive character with top notes of Pineapples, Hyacinth that will grab your attention immediately, then the heart notes of Jasmine, Pink Pepper, iris Fbasics that will take control representing the essence of the perfume to leave you in the end with the base notes of Musk, Patchouli, Jasmine, Amber, Vanilla, Vetiver that will linger with you far beyond that.', 100, 1373100.0, 1373100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006905537_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_amour_100_ml_tayamun_1.jpg'),
(7, 'Xerjoff Richwood EDP', 'It''s a seductive attractive scent that captivates the hearts and eyes.
A delicate soft oriental scent with notes of black currant and fresh tangerine that keep you enthusiastic.
Your vitality needs what reveals your secrets, while remaining in your company until the end of your day.
Don''t hesitate to try the most daring fragrance that shows your strong character.', 50, 13606800.0, 13606800.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(71, 'Hermes Un Jardin sur la Lagune', 'It''s an oriental floral fragrance that takes you on a journey to reveal the magic of a hidden place in Venice. It''s inspired by a mysterious garden of an English lord built inside a lagoon there. The amazing composition has notes of lily, sea breeze and magnolia, providing a vibrant and distinctive scent that you cannot resist.', 30, 2180400.0, 2180400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346133600036-hermes-hermes-un-jardin-sur-la-lagune-_u_-edt-30-ml-1.jpg'),
(301, 'Wadi Halfa Cylindrical Incense Burner In Dark Wood Style', 'A small wooden incense burner with dark wood color in a cylindrical shape with elegant golden patterns and a charcoal holder. The incense burner adds a distinctive touch to the place and helps the scent spread in a consistent way', 100, 538200.0, 538200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3373-wadi-halfa-_-_-_-_-_.png'),
(131, 'Paris Hilton Heiress Gift Set ', 'Paris Hilton Heiress Gift Set consists of an Eau de Parfum Spray, Shower Gel, and Body Lotion. It is specially created for Women by the brand Paris Hilton.', 100, 2035500.0, 2035500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_paris_hilton_perfumes_heiressset_for_women_eau_de_perfum_608940551912.jpg'),
(40, 'Tom Ford White Suede', 'This fragrance was launched in September 2009 for women. Its collection is based upon the essence of musk, which is one of Tom Ford''s favorite ingredients. It is a very feminine perfume. White suede is blended out of rose, saffron, thyme, mate tea, olibanum, lily-of-the-valley, amber, suede, and sandalwood to form the fragrance. This edition is available in a 100ml bottle.', 100, 7334700.0, 7334700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066022873-tom-ford-tom-ford-white-suede-_w_-edp-250-ml-splash-1.jpg'),
(44, 'Bvlgari Splendida Magnolia Sensuel', 'Description
It was launched in 2018. It deals with the theme of the magnolia flower as one of the shortest-lived flowers that brings an intensive aroma. It is announced as an extremely rich fragrance, mysterious and seductive. It opens with citrus top notes described as sparkling, light, and fresh. The floral heart of magnolia is enriched with white flowers of jasmine and orange blossom. The base is described as sensual and woody with the scent reminiscent of vanilla ice cream.', 30, 2159700.0, 2159700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/8/783320977992-bvlgari-bvlgari-splendida-bvlgari-magnolia-sensuel-_w_-edp-30-ml.jpg'),
(348, 'Goutal Paris Rose Splendide EDT', 'A fragrance of rose and enchanting musk inspired by the beauty of blooming flowers.
The lively and refreshing fragrance exudes a delicious pear aroma that reinvigorates your sense of enthusiasm every day.
The fragrance is enhanced with soft notes of magnolia and vanilla, which makes the scent velvety and attractive, boosting your sensuality and seduction.
Enjoy your beauty and all your romantic dreams and make it an immortal memory that lives in your heart and mind forever.', 100, 4836900.0, 4836900.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(309, 'Oud Lover Dokhon Alfkhamah ', 'A luxurious incense made specially for those seeking luxury and prestige. It captivates the hearts and draws a special image for your house in the eyes of everyone.', 30, 241500.0, 241500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/1/2/1210008878443-oud-lover-dokhon-alfkhamah.png'),
(27, 'Gucci Guilty Pour Femme', 'A rich perfume that combines exotic floral notes with natural fragrances. This fragrance embodies a declaration of self-expression and fearlessness. It is wrapped in gold-colored metal, with a matching shimmering cap to reflect the pale rose tinted fragrance inside.', 90, 2904900.0, 2904900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614227758162_gucci_guilty_pour_femme_edp_90_ml__1.jpg'),
(90, 'Elizabeth Arden Green Tea Bamboo', 'Elizabeth Arden Green Tea Bamboo is a relaxing and refreshing fragrance for women. This perfume is classy and glamorous. This perfume opens with a harmonious blend of sparkling lemon, calming bergamot, grapefruit, relaxing bamboo, sweet tamarind and galbanum. The heart beats with a touch of deep green tea accord, violet leaves, sweet cucumber and syringa Scent TrekÃ¢â€žÂ¢. The dry-down is mellow with soft musk, white birch, lentisque resin, moss, Italian orris and mate. Elizabeth Arden Green Tea Bamboo transmits tranquility, freshness and sparkly sweetness; making it ideal for summertime, holidays and love stories.', 100, 765900.0, 765900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/e/l/elizabeth_arden_green_tea_bamboo_edt_100_ml.jpg'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Sun Di Gioia', 'A delightful summer watery perfume rich in scents of bergamot and jasmine with drops of ylang-plan that delivers you the freshness of the sea breeze offering you the warmth of the sun rays that caress your feeling of joy with a great refreshing and charming lively scent. The fragrance also makes you enjoy the warm summer days.', 100, 3042900.0, 3042900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614271381491-giorgio-armani-ga-armani-sun-di-gioia-_l_-edp-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(77, 'Valentino Valentino Donna', 'Valentino Donna is a chypre-floral fragrance for women, presented in a cute studded pink bottle. It is the ultimate scent for a modern woman whose chic and feminine aura is attractive and head-turning. The opening of the fragrance is fresh and beautiful with bergamot, before developing into a divine blend of Bulgarian rose and powdery iris in the heart. The base is mystical with soft notes of patchouli and warm vanilla with soft leathery undertones. Valentino Donna is for a naturally sultry woman. This soft, smooth and elegant fragrance is ideal for practical daywear.', 50, 3022200.0, 3022200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfum_valentino_donna_for_women_eau_de_parfum.jpg'),
(64, 'Parfums Gres Cabotine Gold', 'Cabotine Gold by Perfumes Gres is a limited edition perfume for women presented in a unique, elegant and colorful bottle. This perfume is developed for a groovy, chic and beguiling woman. The fragrance opens with a delightful fruity mixture of mandarin orange, pink pepper softened by melon. The floral heart encompasses jasmine, Tiare flower and peony. The base is earthy with vetiver, patchouli and amber. Cabotine Gold is an uplifting scent for a more confident and poised presence. This fancy fragrance is perfect for summer. Spice up your collection with beautiful scent and gorgeous bottle.', 100, 793500.0, 793500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_parfums_gres_perfumes_capotine_gold_for_women_eau_de_toilette_7640111492108.jpg'),
(74, 'Davidoff Hot Water', 'This oriental highly masculine fragrance is bold and thrilling. The top notes feature basil blended with wormwood, flowing into the heart that contains paprika and patchouli. The base has notes of benzoin and styrax, making it a perfect scent for your evening events.
About the brand
Davidoff has received acclaim since it introduced its first fragrance in 1988. The brand was founded in Switzerland and has been known for luxurious accessories like watches and leather goods. It offered popular fragrances for men and women.', 110, 621000.0, 621000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_davidoff_perfumes_hot_water_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(27, 'Gucci Flora By Gucci EDT', 'This sensual fragrance is dedicated for the woman who has a youthful, feminine spirit. It''s inspired by the iconic Flora print of Gucci. It opens with citrus fruit along with mandarin and peony, then comes rose, pink pepper and the rare Osmanthus Flower in the heart. A mix of patchouli, sandalwood and vanilla comes at the base. The bottle is decorated with gold details on a black bow ribbon.', 50, 1614600.0, 1614600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_gucci_perfumes_flora_for_women_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(77, 'Valentino Uomo Acqua', 'Valentino Uomo Acqua is a refreshing summer fragrance for men, presented in a suave light gray bottle. The opening is beautiful with the invigorating aromas of mandarin and the classy touch of green tomatoes. A hint of sage and a touch of spicy patchouli burst from the heart. The fantastic mixture of leather and iris produce a smoothly elegant dry-down. This modern and cool fragrance is ideal for spring and summer. Flaunt your sophisticated charms and attractive aura with Valentino Uomo Acqua.', 75, 3436200.0, 3436200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_valentino_perfumes_uomo_acqua_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(20, 'Givenchy Ange Ou Etrange Le Secret', 'Ange Ou Demon Le Secret by Givenchy is a dazzling reinterpretation of the brandÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s original Ange Ou Demon scent. Introduced in 2009, the perfume is a limited-edition fragrance that is soft, slightly spicy and completely mesmerizing. Its tart cranberry top note brings with it white flowers and Italian winter lemon. The heart of this romantic scent is comprised of spirited green tea and sensual crystalline jasmine, supported by the elegant base notes of blond wood and patchouli. Filled with mischievous mystery, this alluring blend is also graceful and seductive. Its beautiful pink crystal bottle gives away no secrets until it is opened.', 100, 2856600.0, 2856600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/i/givenchy_aeo_le_secret_eau_de_parfum_1.jpg'),
(32, 'Guerlain Nahema', 'The Nahema is a part of Guerlain''s Patrimoine Collection. This collection is made of emblematic fragrances, that''s composed for more than a century by five generations of perfumers. These mythical pioneer perfumes compose a unique olfactive library that the Maison Guerlain preserved. Nahema is an enigmatic elixir. Its muse is an oriental rose with spellbinding charm.', 100, 3022200.0, 3022200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470131828-guerlain-guerlain-nahema-_w_-edp-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(348, 'Goutal Paris Eau de Monsieur EDT', 'The fragrance is filled with creamy notes of Sandalwood and Patchouli for a harmonious scent
Bergamot and Mandarin help to rejuvenate your sense of enthusiasm and vitality
The fragrance helps you set out to find your passion and discover a life full of adventures
The middle of the fragrance has geranium that touches your heart with feelings of beauty', 100, 4836900.0, 4836900.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(352, 'The Harmonist Golden Wood Refill EDP', 'A new and distinctive experience for a refined taste that highlights your beauty and attractiveness everywhere.
Enjoy a strong scent that always attracts attention.
An aromatic blend that will captivate the hearts of all attendees to keep your image in mind.
The fragrance is also designed to suit both men and women.', 50, 3470700.0, 3470700.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(7, 'Xerjoff Naxos EDP', 'A pure scent that adheres to your skin to show the purity of your delicate soul.
The notes of lavender spread around to provide you with freshness and comfort.
The heart has notes of cinnamon and honey, which take you high in the sky to enjoy a special stance in everyone''s heart.
The base is warm and dark, thanks to the notes of tobacco and tonka, which deliver a seductive touch to your look.', 100, 7859100.0, 7859100.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(100, 'Perfume Co. Honey Tobacco EDP ', 'Designed for a modern persona, imaginary yet luxurious. The opening note of ylang-ylang richness & the sweet decay of gardenia blends effortlessly with the sophisticated scent of incense.', 100, 1028100.0, 1028100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/e/perfume-co-honey-tobacco.png'),
(5, 'Giorgio Armani Acqua Di Gioia', 'THE ESSENCE OF JOY. There is a charming sensation of freshness from the very first notes which are carried along in a deliciously heady current of crushed Mint, with a zest of Italian Limone Primo Fiore Femminello", harvested from the first spring blossoms in Calabria. At its base, ACQUA DI GIOIA bears the signature of water rooted in the Earth, revealed by luscious LMR Cedarwood Heart sprinkled with sensuous Brown Sugar and Labdanum, which is one of the rare plants to possess animal notes. A beautiful fresh floral fragrance ideal for the warm season.', 100, 4340100.0, 4340100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/i/giorgio_armani_acqua_di_gioia_eau_de_parfum_9.jpg'),
(71, 'Hermes Eau de Narcisse Bleu', 'It''s a floral fragrance that leaves you energetic ahead of a spring or summer day. Its composition has a blend of narcissus, orange blossom and bergamot, delivering an amazing scent that awakens your senses, thanks to the long-lasting freshness its spreads everywhere.', 100, 3456900.0, 3456900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346132001339-hermes-hermes-eau-de-narcisse-bleu-_u_-edc-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(348, 'Goutal Paris Gardenia Passion EDP', 'The scent of Gardenia is inspired by nostalgia and reminds us of Annick''s trip to Japan
The orient appears in the vanilla and tuberose that captivate your heart in a world of beauty
The white crystal perfume evokes feelings of love in his heart, making him wish for your eternal company.
Don''t hesitate to try this new beauty', 100, 5789100.0, 5789100.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(32, 'Guerlain Habit Rouge', 'Habit Rouge incarnates a man who is enamored of refinement and capable of all manners of audacity. It''s for a man who lives his life confidently and distinguishes himself with a trail of extreme elegance. With the modern geometry and mastery of form, Habit Rouge has an eternally elegant French appeal.', 100, 3029100.0, 3029100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/334647023553-guerlain-guerlain-habit-rouge-_m_-edt-100-ml-1_1_.jpg'),
(16, 'Al Majed for Oud Set ', 'This set contains:
Al Majed For Oud Jawak Mauve - 200 ml
This wonderful scent has a charming and strong scent. The ingredients have been carefully selected to give you a refreshing aroma to use on the premises every day. It opens as a bouquet of flowers and jasmine with a citrusy scent, ending with the warmth of musk.
Al Majed For Oud Jawak Green - 200 ml
A luxurious woody scent with a distinctive and attractive scent with notes of bergamot, pear, pink jasmine, cyclamen and sage and the middle notes are peony, Bulgarian rose, freesia and jasmine, ending with the scent of honey, amber and patchouli.
Al Majed For Oud Jawak Off White - 200 ml
A wonderful and distinctive scent for those with refined taste. An amazing experience that will entice you to always enjoy its amazing & long-lasting aroma. An attractive scent for everyone who loves quality, that highlights your glamorous presence anywhere.
About the Brand:
Al Majed Oud Company was established in 1956 AD to establish a promising market in the field of oud trade through the wholesale sector by culminating in more than 60 years of experience in the manufacture of oud and perfumes. Their preparations across the Gulf market, by creating and innovating new aromatic lines have contributed in expanding their customer base and heading to the retail trade to reach more than 160 sales platforms in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia and the Gulf countries.', 100, 3091200.0, 3091200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/b/sb100329-al-majid-for-oud-set-of-3-room-sprays.png'),
(327, 'Laurent Mazzone Army Of Lovers', 'An oriental woody fragrance that keeps you in a good mood for a long time. The compelling composition has notes of rose in the top, patchouli in the middle and honey in the base, providing you with an enticing scent with a soft touch that boosts your beauty to fascinate everyone.', 100, 9922200.0, 9922200.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(133, 'Kenzo L''Eau Aquadisiac Pour Homme', 'It''s a woody spicy fragrance that invites you for a dive into the aquatic world, just like a dream. It''s amazing blend of Yuzu, guaiac wood and pink pepper will provide the long-lastic effect you desire during your special events to captivate and attract everyone there.', 50, 2829000.0, 2829000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_kenzo_perfumes_l_eau_kenzo_aquadisiac_pour_homme_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(156, 'Victoria''s Secret Pink Calm Water Body Mist ', 'Enjoy the bright morning freshness with this soothing fragrant mist.
The contrast of delicious citrus with the heat of pepper reflects your strength and enthusiasm for discovering life.
The fragrance ends with creamy and delicious aromas of vanilla and coconut that excite your senses and feelings.
The perfume envelops you and lasts with you for long hours until the end of your busy day.', 100, 386400.0, 386400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/6/667553844842-victoria_s-secret-victoria_s-secret-pink-calm-water-_w_-body-mist-with-essential-oils-250-ml.png'),
(1, 'Dolce & Gabbana Pour Homme Intenso', 'A Full sensual aromtaic woody fragrance for men, with deep notes of warmth and freshness, with the aroma of basil, tobacco, musk, and amber.', 125, 1455900.0, 1455900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/o/dolce_gabbana_intenso_1.jpg'),
(168, 'Jimmy Choo Floral', 'Jimmy Choo Floral is a feminine radiant delightful fragrance that is perfectly designed for a fashionable woman with a dynamic allure. Its scent reflects women''s confidence and vitality.', 60, 1476600.0, 1476600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3386460103695-jimmy-choo-jimmy-choo-floral-_w_-edt-60-ml-1.jpg'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Oud Minerale', 'It is a woody aquatic fragrance for women and men that was launched in 2017. The nose behind this fragrance is Shyamala Maisondeau. It blooms with sea salt, sea notes, agarwood (oud), pink pepper, styrax, seaweed, balsam fir, pepperwood or hercules club, and ambergris.', 100, 7438200.0, 7438200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066070539-tom-ford-tom-ford-oud-minerale-_u_-edp-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Neroli Portofino Acqua', 'It is an aromatic citrus Eau de Toilette for women and men launched in 2016. The nose behind this fragrance is Rodrigo Flores-Roux. It combines bergamot, lemon, and petitgrain with a heart of orange blossom and neroli.', 50, 7458900.0, 7458900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066047876-tom-ford-tom-ford-neroli-portofino-acqua-_u_-edt-50-ml-1.jpg'),
(89, 'Azzaro Silver Black', 'Azzaro Silver Black is a woody aromatic fragrance for men. The opening of the fragrance is youthful and invigorating with a mixture of green apple, bergamot and lime. The addition of anise in the opening adds a sweet aroma to it, enhanced by the spicy notes in the heart; coriander and cardamom, which are mixed with a hint of juniper. Juniper slowly gives way to an earthy, woody base combining sandalwood, vetiver, and patchouli, completed by a touch of smooth white musk. Azzaro Silver Black is a long-lasting, fresh and cool scent for summertime and casual wear.', 100, 1393800.0, 1393800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/a/z/azzaro_silver_black_edt_100_ml.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 88', 'Experience a burst of refreshment with such an amazing scent. Top notes of freesia, come on a heart of iris and base of vetiver, forms a marvellous composition that keeps you refreshed with unlimited elegance to attract everyone toward your presence.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000088-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours---perfume-day-88-1.png'),
(16, 'Al Majed for Oud Musk Body Spray ', 'The fragrance has the warmth of agarwood and its oriental scent that fills you with a strong scent
The strength of the East emerges with soft fruits and flowers to create an amazing scent.
The scent of vetiver will take your breath away and express your love for elegance
This mist deserves to be included in your beauty collection to use it in all occasions About the Brand:
Al Majed For Oud Company was established in 1956 AD to establish a promising market in the field of oud trade through the wholesale sector by culminating in more than 60 years of experience in the manufacture of oud and perfumes. Their preparations across the Gulf market, by creating and innovating new aromatic lines have contributed in expanding their customer base and heading to the retail trade to reach more than 160 sales platforms in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia and the Gulf countries.', 100, 634800.0, 634800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6285091000243-2035-_-_-_-_-_-_.png'),
