(47, 'Van Cleef & Arpels Gardenia Petale', 'Van Cleef & Arpels Gardenia Petal EDP is a stylish, generous, luxurious fragrance that awakens the senses; Gardenia Petal captures all stages in the life of the gardenia flower. The parfume, high quality, compositions opens with an inimitable accord of fresh, green and citrus notes, followed by floral touches of delicate lily-of-the-valley and exotic jasmine and finishing with the elegant, femininity of gardenia flowers in full bloom at dawn.', 75, 5050800.0, 5050800.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
