(328, 'CnR Create Star Sign Aquarius', 'Impress everyone there and get all the attention you desire with this floral fruity fragrance. The composition features notes of lily in the top, thyme in the heart and iris in the base, revealing an attractive fragrance with a long-lasting effect for the day and night.', 50, 3574200.0, 3574200.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
