(33, 'Lacoste Pour Homme Red', 'Flourish in challenging situations with this fragrance dedicated for the active, competitive men who take actions in risk-taking situations. The top notes of green apple, followed by pine tree in the middle and vetiver in the base forms a composition of a scent that gives you the extra boost of energy and confidence you need.', 75, 1028100.0, 1028100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/3/737052074757-lacoste-lacoste-pour-homme-red-_m_-edt-75-ml.jpg'),
