(109, 'Aigner Starlight Gold', 'Aigner Starlight Gold is a renovated version of the original Starlight perfume. This fragrance includes oriental notes along with the classic floral aromas to add depth to the delicacy of the original perfume. It opens with fruity top notes of plum and bergamot before revealing the middle notes of jasmine, tuberose, ylang-ylang, and violet. These floral notes are brought back down to earth with base notes of moss, amber, vanilla, and sandalwood. Aigner Starlight Gold is a white floral, woody and powdery smell, it will amaze you every time you use it, and for sure it will inspire everyone to try it.', 100, 1352400.0, 1352400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_aigner_perfumes_starlight_gold_for_women_eau_de_perfum_4013670000306.jpg'),
