(37, 'Chanel Allure Homme Sport Aftershave Lotion ', 'This aftershave moisturizing lotion provides softness to the skin with a fresh scent. The quick-absorbing non-greasy lotion helps reduce the roughness caused by the razor providing hydration. It has notes of mandarin and white musk to deliver real freshness along with an amazing scent that remains for long hours.
