The fragrance is designed for people of high taste to give them a high place .', 100, 4505700.0, 4505700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/5/2/5285006700429-ideo-parfumeurs-ideo-parfumeurs-last-canto-_u_-edp-100-ml.png'),
(33, 'Lacoste Eau De Lacoste Sensuelle', 'Eau de Lacoste Sensuelle has an elegant, sensual fragrance, that captures the natural intensity of soft floral notes on a relaxed, warm evening. The fragrance has top notes of Blackcurrant, Fig and Pink Pepper. Heart notes are comprised of Turkish Rose, Gladioslus Inflexus, Sweet Pea. On the base are the scents of Nougatine Accord, Patchoulli and Amber.', 50, 1697400.0, 1697400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/a/lacoste_eau_de_lacoste_eau_de_parfum_1.jpg'),
(119, 'Prada Olfactories Moonlight Shadow EDP', 'A woody fragrance that suits both men and women.
The composition has the notes of fig, leather along with luxurious chocolate.
