(40, 'Tom Ford Rose Prick', 'It is a warm, spicy rose fragrance that blooms with a turmeric and Sichuan pepper top along with a center of Turkish rose, May rose, and Bulgarian rose. Tonka bean and patchouli sit on the base.', 50, 10274100.0, 10274100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066107785-tom-ford-tom-ford-rose-prick-_u_-edp-50-ml-1.jpg'),
