- Versace Eros Pour Homme - 100 ml
For the strong man who is the master of himself, this oriental woody fragrance is dedicated to you. The composition has notes of mint in the top, geranium in the middle, and vanilla in the base, providing you with an irresistible scent that boosts your charismatic character at your special events.', 100, 5175000.0, 5175000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/b/sb100420_mon_amour_1__1.png'),
(196, 'Exuma Parfums Prive Saint Cuir EDP', 'Add a luxurious and aristocratic elegance with these mysterious drops of perfume.
Sharp tones of leather mixed with the magic aromas of amber and cashmere woods are mixed in a special aromatic composition that will captivate you.
The fragrance is specially designed to suit men and women with refined tastes.
A fragrance with a scent that has a seductive charm to it and that is strong and concentrated. It lasts till the last hours of the day.', 100, 4560900.0, 4560900.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(44, 'Bvlgari Splendida Patchouli Tentation', 'It''s a chypre floral fragrance for women that makes you feel seductive and charming. Its amazing notes of patchouli blended with white peach, Morris, and musk will spread your freshness wherever you go, so your feminine touch is noticed everywhere you go.', 50, 3022200.0, 3022200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/8/783320411175-bvlgari-bvl-splendida-patchouli-tentation-50ml-edp-1.jpg'),
(44, 'Bvlgari Le Gemme Astrea EDP', 'A glowing fragrance with luxurious notes of spicy saffron.
The fresh composition has a delicate heart of jasmine, which boosts your femininity.
Be ready for a classic touch and endless elegance with suede and delicious honey.
The scent provides you with self-confidence, getting you the attention on all occasions.', 100, 10833000.0, 10833000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/7/8/783320414930-bvl-le-gemme-astrea-edp-100ml_1.png'),
(266, 'Mustang Ford EDT', 'A distinctive fragrance belonging to the family of luxurious woody notes.
The fragrance is specially designed for men who seek exclusivity and elegance.
The fragrance gives you a bold and attractive masculine look, and enhances your confidence.
The fragrance starts with a refreshing blend of grapefruit and lemon peel to make you feel fresh and energetic.
In the heart are captivating touches of mint and lavender.
The fragrance ends with wonderful notes of musk, sandalwood and patchouli.
About the Brand:
Mustang is a luxury car brand, which has designed 6 distinct fragrances with unique scents, designed by skilled perfumer Elia.', 100, 807300.0, 807300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/4/849017005130-mustang-mustang-ford-for-men-_m_-edt-100-ml.png'),
(22, 'Nicolai Patchouli Intense', 'A multifaceted warm spicy and strong fragrance for men and women opens with lavender, geranium, orange. Heart notes are ceylon cinnamon, rose, patchouli. Base notes are sandalwood, amber, vanilla.', 100, 11488500.0, 11488500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_nicolai_perfumes_patchouli_eau_de_parfum_100ml_1.jpg'),
(348, 'Goutal Paris Le Chevrefeuille EDT', 'The scent of lemon and narcissus evokes nostalgia and makes you travel through time
For every heart that loves beauty and searches for unique brilliance
Taste the sweetness of Lemon and enjoy the notes of Narcissus in this amazing fragrance
The scent of the perfume excites your senses with beauty and confidence
Shine from the first moments with this perfume that captures everyone''s attention when you appear.', 50, 3367200.0, 3367200.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(345, 'Liquides Imaginaires BÃªte Humaine EDP', 'This perfume is the link between real characters and wandering spirits of untamed nature.
It is perfect for the legendary character of wild nature who always dwells in the atmosphere of forests and mysterious far lands.
The woody blend of guaiac and sandalwood with vetiver adds to the excitement and thrill of adventure.
The fragrance gives you the opportunity to enjoy the charming scents of nature as you taste the sweetness of the delicious chestnut and inhale the fragrance of violets.', 100, 8280000.0, 8280000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(20, 'Givenchy Play Intense', 'Bold and sensual, Givenchy Play Intense Perfume was launched in 2008 with its warm, seductive bouquet. Designed for the men who are the risk-takers and trendsetters, this fragrance etches a deliciously unforgettable imprint as you exit a room. Like a dream, the scent is fleeting yet leaves a sense of longing. Perfectly balanced hints of magnolia, Tiare flower, African orange flower, and orchid pair with earthy patchouli, and Tonka beans. The modern and contemporary perfume was presented in an opaque, black bottle shaped like an MP3 player, making the fragranceÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s appearance as inviting as its aroma.', 100, 3332700.0, 3332700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/i/givenchy_play_intense_eau_de_toilette_spray.jpg'),
(348, 'Goutal Paris Grand Amour EDP', 'It reveals to you all the feelings of seduction and love
Mimosa and Musk refresh you and make you the center of attention
The tulips and hyacinths show your unique presence and keep the lights on you until the end
A soft aromatic blend that adds beauty to your senses and increases your softness', 50, 3926100.0, 3926100.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(201, 'Afnan Naseej Al Khuzama EDP', 'The scent of leather dipped in white amber is the secret to the luxury and sophistication that this fragrance holds.
The fragrance starts your day with a soft floral aroma of gardenia and orange blossoms.
The scent becomes more creamy and warm with the emergence of the oriental heart of the warm notes of agarwood.', 50, 1035000.0, 1035000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6290171002420-afnan-afnan-naseej-al-khuzama-_u_-edp-50-ml.png'),
(59, 'Dunhill Desire Red Body Spray ', 'A perfumed body mist with a soft and glowing oriental scent
The composition of the fragrance begins your day with the freshness of apples to renew the feeling of enthusiasm and positivity in your heart
The heart of the perfume has warm notes of teak wood and patchouli to give you a high sense of calm
The scent envelops your skin for long hours and reduces the appearance of odors resulting from exposure to environmental factors', 100, 538200.0, 538200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/5/85715801111-dunhill-dunhill-desire-red-for-men-_m_-body-spray-195-ml.png'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Prive', 'Prive is a floral Eau de parfum that is enriched in rose scents. It has an innovative aromatic combination that ignites the senses to surround you with a sense of joy and happiness. It contains such different components like Gardenia, Black currants, Ylang-ylang, jasmine, Bergamot, Lemon, Tuber, Tangerine, smell of fruit, Spice, Orchids, Lotus, Gardenia, Jasmine, Ylang-ylang, Sandalwood, Amber, White Musk, Vetiver, Incense, Mexican chocolate, Vanilla', 100, 1373100.0, 1373100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006907098_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_prive_100_ml_1.jpg'),
(28, 'Burberry Her Blossom EDT', 'A floral fruity fragrance is designed for the elegant woman.
It was launched with a unique perfume blend in 2019.
The perfume scent is extracted from a rare and very carefully-chosen natural ingredient.
It starts with a fresh scent of Tangerine, Pink Pepper that perfectly blends with the seductive scent of Peony and Plum Blossom at the heart.
The perfume ends with the luxurious scent of Musk and Sandalwood to provide you with a strong scent that stays steady till the last moment.', 50, 1704300.0, 1704300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614228236362-burberry-burberry-her-blossom-_w_-edt-50-ml-1.jpg'),
(320, 'Thierry Mugler Over The Musk', 'A charming woody floral fragrance that offers you an unexpected blend of woody notes mixed with ambrette and black pepper. It gives you the sensual luxury you are looking for in a sophisticated, and vibrant style, to be ready in time for fun or work.', 80, 6527400.0, 6527400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_mugler_perfumes_over_the_musk_edp_80_ml_for_unesex_3439604000210.jpg'),
(208, 'Lootah Bint Al Shyookh Incense ', 'An amazing incense, representing the authenticity of heritage and civilization, made of wonderful lavender that fills the place with a scent that makes you feel comfortable and fresh.', 100, 2946300.0, 2946300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6297000836744-lootah-lootah-bint-al-shyookh-incense-220-gms.png'),
(37, 'Chanel Coco EDT', 'A wonderful women''s perfume that contains amazing ingredients that increase your confidence with every whiff, with a great mix of mimosa, peach and amber.', 100, 4202100.0, 4202100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_chanel_perfumes_coco_for_women_eau_de_toilette_3145891234602.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Paris', 'Paris 100 ml is an Eau de Parfum For Men and Women from Tous Les Jours that will immerse you in feelings of love and passion with top notes of Bergamot, Driedcranberry, Blackcurrant, Nectarine, Apple that will grab your attention immediately, then the heart notes of Magnolia, Gardenia, Lily, Jasmine that will take control representing the essence of the perfume to leave you in the end with the base notes of Amber, Patchouli, Musk, Sandalwood, Vanilla that will linger with you far beyond that.', 100, 1373100.0, 1373100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006906077_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_paris_100_ml_tayamun_1.jpg'),
(48, 'Lancome Idole Le Grand', 'Imagine receiving a perfume souvenir overwhelmed with seductive and exotically erotic rose scents! Want a sneak peek? Without second thoughts, it is Lancome Idole Le Grand Parfum! This masterpiece is a modern musky chypre floral fragrance. Sensual in nature, exotic in flavor, Lancome Idole Le Grand is an irresistible mix of exclusively sourced Isparta rose petal essence in Turkey and centifolia rose grown in France.', 100, 3726000.0, 3726000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614273069175_lancome_lancome_idole_le_grand_parfum_100ml.jpg'),
(223, 'Ojar Cirrus Leather Absolute Perfume Oil', 'Taste the sweetness of pear wrapped with soft freesia in a special composition.
Enjoy the creamy heart that adds to the softness of the scent and evokes your feelings.
The composition is blended in harmony to fulfill the needs of everyone.
It''s an intense perfume oil for both men and women with a glowing aromatic scent.', 20, 4554000.0, 4554000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(7, 'Xerjoff Casamorati Regio', 'Xerjoff Casamorati Regio is an oriental fragrance for both men and women. The scent is fresh, unique and elegance with an amazing bottle, It makes you feel energetic and more younger. perfect for summertime.', 100, 9680700.0, 9680700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_xerjoff_perfumes_casamorati_regio_for_unisex_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(202, 'Karl Lagerfeld Paradise Bay Pour Homme', 'An effect of woody, fresh notes equal against a sunken aromatic base, Paradise Bay Pour Homme opens with a alive explosion of bergamot, green apple, and mint. A heart of violet leaf gives a feature to the parfume before it finishes with a wealthy set of dry vetiver and cashmere wood.', 100, 2035500.0, 2035500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_karl_lagerfeld_perfumes_paradise_bay_pour_homme_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(282, 'Orlov Paris Fancy Red Refillable EDP', 'Fancy Red, an elegant fragrance, perfect for both men and women.
The fragrance smells like a fresh breeze that caresses the skin.
Enjoy cheerful citrus notes, beautiful white flowers, and woody notes that make a lasting elegant impression.
The fragrance is characterized by the strong stability of its scent for long hours without fading to become the perfect companion for you in all your occasions.
This wonderful fragrance is an amazing addition to your perfume collection.', 75, 6699900.0, 6699900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/5/853488006114-orlov-orlov-paris-fancy-red-_u_-edp-75-ml-refillable.png'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Costa Azzura', 'It is a white floral and woody fragrance that is composed of a mixture of ylang-ylang and tuberose with intoxicating Bulgarian rose. Depth and strength are provided by vanilla and cedar. It was launched in 2015.', 100, 7617600.0, 7617600.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(90, 'Elizabeth Arden Provocative Women', 'Elizabeth Arden Provocative Woman is a beautiful floral fragrance. The scent is soft and feminine, seductive and bold. The opening is lush, fruity and floral with quince, fresh water lotus and spicy ginger lily. The heart contains infinite floral scents; intoxicating orchid, papaya blossom and airy pink freesia. Base notes are warm white sand notes, rich and smooth Hinoki wood and delightful red amber. This splendid sophisticated and unique scent is an excellent choice for year-round occasions. Feel irresistibly sexy as you flaunt your sensual charms with Elizabeth Arden Provocative Woman.', 100, 917700.0, 917700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/e/l/elizabeth_arden_provocative_women_edp_100_ml.jpg'),
(47, 'Van Cleef & Arpels Bois D''Iris', 'Van Cleef & Arpels Bois D''Iris EDP for women is really a prestigious fragrance. The parfume starts with an amazing and rare blend of sweet notes. It also combines vetiver and wood, to offer a unique feeling. The base notes consist of vanilla and amber balm.', 75, 5050800.0, 5050800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_van_cleef___arpels_perfumes_bois_d_iris_for_unisex_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(48, 'LancÃƒÂ´me La Nuit Tresor', 'Lancome launches La Nuit Tresor fragrance in February 2015. The scent is a flanker of the original Tresor from 1990. The composition is announced as a gourmand aphrodisiac and a love potion created by perfumers Christophe Raynaud and Amandine Marie. It supposedly depicts the dark side of rose and mixes notes of black rose with Tahitian vanilla orchid absolute. There are also accords of natural incense, papyrus, patchouli and litchi praline added to the mix.', 75, 3070500.0, 3070500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/a/lanc_me_la_nuit_tr_sor.jpg'),
(279, 'Shakespeare Antony And Cleopatra EDP', 'A spicy oriental fragrance that embodies the attraction and passion for discovering life around you.
The fragrance will make you look like a sunrise that will capture the attention of everyone around you.
Enjoy every moment of your day with the fragrance that stays with you all the time.
The composition of the enchanting fragrance stays with you for long hours and expresses the hidden secrets of your soul.', 100, 3926100.0, 3926100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/7/3755646344533-shakespeare-perfume-shakespeare-antony-and-cleopatra-spray-100ml.png'),
(59, 'Dunhill Travel Set ', 'This four-piece set from Dunhill is your perfect choice for your travels. It contains Icon, Icon Absolute, Elite and Racing. Icon is a woody aromatic scent that perfectly expresses natural refinement. Its blend of neroli, cardamom and leather is designed to ideally suit the sophisticated gentleman. Icon Absolute is a woody spicy scent that will awaken your senses, thanks to its accords of bergamot, tobacco leaf and leather. Elite Eau de Parfum is a luxurious woody spicy masculine fragrance designed for the elegant man and his timeless style, with its notes of bergamot, black pepper and sandalwood. Racing is a woody aromatic fragrance designed for the practical man who has a charismatic effect that impresses everyone, thanks to its notes of grapefruit, lavender and vetiver.', 100, 910800.0, 910800.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/5/85715809551_dunhill_dunhill_icon_edp_7ml_icon_absolute_edp_7ml_elite_edp_7ml_racing_edp_7ml_travel_set_gs-dmm_cross_dock_1.jpg'),
(378, 'Maison TahitÃ© Vanillade EDP', '#NAME?', 100, 4174500.0, 4174500.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(16, 'Al Majed For Oud Dkhoon Almajed ', 'Make your house smells great with the amazing intense scent of oud, blended with luxurious oriental notes. The composition fills you with freshness and provides a sensation of comfort and relaxation. It remains as intense for a long time. It''s suitable for everyday use.', 100, 800400.0, 800400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6285091015070-almajed-for-oud-dakhoun-al-majed-56-gm-1.png'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 380', 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 380 is inspired by a smoldering little fire in the darkest of nights, under the blackest skies that hold the brightest of stars. The seduction of this fragrance exudes delicate flowery notes of Bulgarian rose, jasmine, and iris enfolded in exotic species of saffron and powerful woody scent of vetiver and sedge essences, resulting in a nourishing aphrodisiac fragrance. Wear our woody fragrance with confidence, for it is addictive, you can''t stop sniffing its delight.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000380-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-380-1.png'),
(348, 'Goutal Paris Eau d''Hadrien EDT', 'Start your morning with delicious citrus fruits
Lemon blend with bergamot and grapefruit to rejuvenate your energy
The fragrance reflects your enthusiasm to discover life around you
The fragrance has notes of ylang-ylang and cypress to keep the scent attractive until the last moments of the day', 50, 3367200.0, 3367200.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(32, 'Guerlain Idylle Love Blossom ', 'Capture the floral, fresh essence of spring with the Idylle love blossom fragrance. This limited-edition scent was released in 2014, an exclusive buy that could only be found at international airport shops. The weary traveler would have indeed enjoyed this crisp floral chypre, which opens with a top note blend of green leaves, lilac, and honey. This sweet, refreshing mix then gives way to a pleasant combination of intense rose and sharp, heady jasmine in the heart.', 50, 1863000.0, 1863000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470116962-guerlain-guerlain-idylle-love-blossom-_w_-edt-50-ml-_travel-exclusive_-1.jpg'),
(49, 'Lalique Terres Aromatiques Noir Premier 1905', 'Lalique Terres Aromatiques Noir Premier 1905 is an aromatic fragrance for both men and women. It has a subtle black character that is dark, sharp and mysterious. The opening is a blast of tropical scents. The cool and spicy cardamom contrasts with bright lemon tones that are softened with sweet and juicy pineapple. Freesia blends smoothly with thyme and lavender in the heart. The dry-down is warm and lush with a mixture of Tonka, with its deep aroma, woody vetiver and the unique molecule orcanox. Lalique Terres Aromatiques Noir Premier 1905 is a very classy and versatile perfume that glows the best in winter.', 100, 6796500.0, 6796500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_lalique_perfumes_terres_aromatiques_noir_premier_1905_for_unisex_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(17, 'Calvin Klein Perfume Set ', 'This collection includes (One + Eternity + One Gold + Eternity Air + Euphoria) Eau de Toilette 5 pieces x10ml
- One is a revolutionary sensual fragrance for men. It blooms with refreshing notes of bergamot and papaya. The heart emphasizes luxurious flowers while the base is warm with amber and musk notes. - Eternity is a romantic and distinctive scent that blooms with the spirit of green botanicals with a floral heart and warm base of sandalwood. - One Gold is a seasonal, youthful scent that combines the refreshing top notes of fig, bergamot and sage. The luminous heart is purely floral while the sunny vetiver and patchouli gives depth to the perfume. - Eternity Air is a new, fresh Eau de Parfum that captures all the different shades of the atmosphere. Its notes go around contrasts, based on an unusual blend of ozonic notes, sea notes and seaweed. - Euphoria is an exciting and provocative fragrance that blooms with black orchid, mixed with hints of exotic fruits, and seductive flowers of champaca and lotus blossom.', 5, 1331700.0, 1331700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614229407143-calvin_klein-calvin-klein-perfume-set-5-pcs.png'),
(279, 'Shakespeare Twelfth Night EDP', 'A spicy and luxurious fragrance for both women and men.
The fragrance was launched in 2019 with a beautiful aromatic blend.
Enjoy Chinese grapefruit, juniper berries and saffron at the beginning of the fragrance.
The heart of the fragrance has notes of leather and black violet.
The fragrance is based on a base of Cashmeran, Vetiver and Berries.', 100, 3926100.0, 3926100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/0/3015285282185-shakespeare-perfume-shakespeare-twelfth-night-edp-spray-100ml.jpg'),
(4, 'Mancera Roses Vanille', 'The perfumer Pierre Mancera presents Roses Vanille which hits you first with notes of fresh lemon of calabria and then sneaks on you with turkish delight and rose with the base notes of cedarwood, intense vanilla & white musk, which lingers on with you the whole day long with Sweet enough to capture you, rich enough to keep you and complex enough to seduce you fragrance.', 120, 2822100.0, 2822100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/m/a/mancera_roses_vanille_3_1.jpg'),
(28, 'Burberry Weekend Men', 'A weekly holiday with floral notes mixed with delicious fruit scents for you, sir, with this most famous fragrance among the luxurious perfumes that carries more touches of love and warmth produced by you Burberry company to captivate your heart and refresh your soul in addition to drawing attention to everyone around you with stability that lasts all day', 100, 966000.0, 966000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_burberry_perfumes_weekend_for_men_eau_de_toilette_5045252667576.jpg'),
(7, 'Xerjoff Oud Stars Mamluk EDP', 'A delicate, sensual, and exciting floral fragrance, filling you with a high sense of beauty and pleasure.
The scent increases the splendor of your look as soon as the scent of narcissus and iris appears and paints your face with joy and happiness.
Powder particles are scattered around you softly, embodying the dreamy romantic side of your soul and uncovering your glowing feelings.
The fragrance is meticulously and professionally designed to suit men and women who love to add a special luster to their appearance similar to the glow of the shiny sun.', 50, 8970000.0, 8970000.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(51, 'Al Dakheel Oud Sense Group ', 'This amazing collection contains 3 different and distinctive fragrances (30 ml each) that will satisfy all your needs.
It combines multiple aromatic tastes in one box which makes it all you need for a complete perfume collection.
The different scents will offer an unparalleled sense of luxury and elegance.
It''s made with great care to suit different tastes and personalities.
It can be a perfect gift for your loved ones and will introduce them to a wonderful mixture of fragrances.', 100, 1511100.0, 1511100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6281150553927-al-dakheel-for-oud-sense-group.png'),
(32, 'Guerlain Vetiver', 'Guerlain Vetiver is a luxurious woody fragrance for men. A classy, modern and sensational scent, this fragrance gives a complex feeling of stepping back in time. The fragrance opens with the delightful combination of bergamot and neroli. The glittering freshness of lemon and mandarin adds to the magic of the top notes. At the heart, vetiver and cedar sharpen, before giving way to the prominent mix of tobacco, pepper, walnuts and Tonka bean. This wonderful scent brings back memories of old places and people, of forgotten smells and times long gone.', 100, 2187300.0, 2187300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_guerlain_perfumes_vetiver_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(340, 'Biehl Al01', 'It''s a floral fragrance inspired by the sweet life in a glamorous city on the mediterranean. The composition combines top notes of peach, followed by a heart of freesia and a base of amber, adding an irresistable touch with a long-lasting effect to your elegance.', 100, 5554500.0, 5554500.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(7, 'Thameen Fragrance The Cora Hair Fragrance', 'The combination of heritage, beauty, and wealth in the XERJOFF world has been embodied in the form of a hot and glowing perfume for women.
