(77, 'Valentino Donna Noir Absolu', 'Valentino Donna Noir Absolu is an oriental, floral scent for women, presented in a beautiful black ebony studded bottle. The opening is fresh and spicy with black pepper. The peppery note abates as rich and warm notes of rose and plum liquor take over adding a divine vibe. The dry-down is marked by sandalwood and leather. The blend of spicy, woodsy, and leathery notes gives the scent a luxurious aura. Valentino Donna Noir Absolu is a trendy and modern scent with classical air. Designed for a sophisticated cool woman, this fragrance is ideal for wintertime and special occasions.', 100, 4491900.0, 4491900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/d/o/donna_noir_absolu_edp_100ml_1.jpg'),
(27, 'Gucci Bloom Set ', 'A gift-set for women featuring EDP (100ml), roll-on deodorant (7.5ml) and shower gel (100gm). The composition of the fragrance features notes of tuberose, jasmine and rangoon creeper, which provides you a soft touch that no one can resist.', 100, 5444100.0, 5444100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614229653731-gucci-gucci-bloom-_w_-set-edp-100-ml-_-edp-roller-ball-7.4-ml-_-parfum-soap-100-g-1.jpg'),
