(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 23', 'An authentic Arabian scent designed to suit you at all your special times. Amazing notes of bergamot come on top of the composition, followed by incense in the middle and leather in the base, bringing to you a gorgeous scent that fulfills your desire and boosts your attractivness', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000023-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours---perfume-day-23-1.png'),
