Spray your body mist all over the body after showering.
Reapply throughout the day whenever you need a dose of fabulousness!', 250, 476100.0, 476100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/o/body-candy-marshmallow-mash-1.png'),
