(48, 'LancÃƒÂ´me Hypnose Homme', 'This oriental fragrance shows your captivating mysterious masculinity, with a powerful blend of cardamom, mint and patchouli. You''ll get all the attention you want, especially on your night events as you attract all the attendees.', 75, 2753100.0, 2753100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/l/a/lancome-hypnose-homme-eau-de-toilette-75ml_4.jpg'),
