(49, 'Lalique Satine', 'Lalique Satine is an oriental woody fragrance for women. The fragrance opens with a burst of powder floral including jasmine, heliotrope and sweet gardenia. Floral notes give way to warm, soft Tonka beans, to-die-for vanilla notes highlighted by a pepper explosion. The dry-down is soft, powdery with a hint of floral sweetness. The sandalwood, vetiver and patchouli temper the sweetness producing an elegant and womanly trace. Lalique Satine melts into the skin mingling with the senses and becoming a part of the beauty that is you. A sweet, nice, smooth and long-lasting perfume with a unique bottle, Lalique Satine is your scent.', 100, 972900.0, 972900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_lalique_perfumes_satine_for_women_eau_de_perfum_1_.jpg'),
