(63, 'Dior Homme EDT ', 'Introduced in 2005, Dior Homme by Christian Dior is an aromatic, woody floral fragrance for men, and the first of its kind to use iris as part of its scent makeup. Sage, lavender, and bergamot are the top notes of this masculine perfume, with middle notes of iris, cacao, cardamom, and amber. Bookended with base notes of Tahitian vetiver, leather, and patchouli, this perfume formulated by Olivier Polge is elegant, sexy, and unique, especially for winter and evening wear. Dior Homme is worn as a sleek modern suit, leaving behind an immediately recognizable woody and spicy trail of elegance.', 50, 3229200.0, 3229200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/-/c-dior_dior_homme_3348900662636.png'),
