(249, 'Cristiano Ronaldo Legacy', 'This vibrant fragrance for sophisticated men leaves a unique and memorable scent that makes a lasting impression on a first date with its fresh and aromatic of lavender and bergamot.', 100, 1248900.0, 1248900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/r/cristiano_ronaldo_legacy_edt_100_ml.jpg'),
