(30, 'Spring Set', 'This set contains:
Who Am I Just Yes EDP - 100 ml
Who Am I? In this modern world, I Am an essence driven by the Yes behind each & every moment! Just Yes to every blossom drenched with ylang-ylang essence. Yes to all the warmth brought by amber delicacy & to all the sweetness hidden in peppercorn spiciness. Just Yes to all the treasures in life! Exclusive only at Golden Scent.
