Designed for a modern persona, imaginary yet luxurious. The opening note of ylang-ylang richness & the sweet decay of gardenia blends effortlessly with the sophisticated scent of incense.
COZY Light Leather Room Spray - 500 ml
For the love of leather, enjoy this soft warm anti-bacterial home fragrance. Designed to spread coziness and snuggly vibes into your home. This light gentle scent was created by balancing powerful leather accords and Juniper Berries, with the softness of Vetiver. A graceful scent, full of beauty & warmth!
