(32, 'Guerlain La Petite Robe Noire Ma Robe Petales Eau Fraiche', 'A perfume created by Guerlain, An Eau FraÃƒÂ®che in which sparkling mandarin, rose petals, and biting pistachio set hearts aflutter. The legendary glass bottle is instantly recognizable by its rounded shoulders and stopper in the shape of an upside-down heart that reveals a new style of dress. Sketched in black ink, the low-cut petal dress is beautifully set off by translucent glass with a soft green lacquer.', 100, 1904400.0, 1904400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470117310-guerlain-guerlain-la-petite-robe-noire-ma-robe-petales-eau-fraiche-_w_-edt-100-ml-1.jpg'),
