(73, 'Tous Les Jours Lulia', 'Lulia 100 ml is an Eau de Parfum For Men and Women from Tous Les Jours that will evoke great emotions and joyful memories with top notes of Cardamom, Pink Pepper that will grab your attention immediately, then the heart notes of Gardenia, Peony Fbasic, Coconut, Orange Sprouts that will take control representing the essence of the perfume to leave you in the end with the base notes of Sandalwood, Musk, Amber that will linger with you far beyond that.', 100, 1373100.0, 1373100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006905711_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_lulia_100_ml_tayamun_1.jpg'),
(60, 'S.T.Dupont Special Edition Pour Femme', 'Special Edition Pour Femme by S.t Dupont is a limited edition perfume for women, presented in a feminine pink bottle. This fragrance is floral and fruity to suit the style of the cosmopolitan woman. The fragrance has a fruity opening with fresh aromas of lemon, soft pear notes and lavish black current aromas. The captivating opening gives way to a delicate heart of flowers. The floral mid-phase is a combination of smooth jasmine, sensual rose and radiant ylang-ylang. The dry-down is a marvelous mixture of rich musk, powdery patchouli and sweet vanilla.', 100, 3139500.0, 3139500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_s.t.dupont_perfumes_special_edition_pour_femme_for_women_eau_de_perfum_3386460098106.jpg'),
(21, 'Ajwa Home Mix & Match Room Sprays Set', 'Ajwa Home Scent Sprays are home fragrances which replace the bad odour and make the atmosphere gaiety. These home fragrances are long-lasting, refreshing and aromatic. They are suitable for a daily cleaning routine.
This set contains:
