(318, 'Miu Miu Miu Miu Mini Set ', 'It''s a two-piece gift set that features EDP (100 ml) and EDP (20 ml). The floral fragrance makes you feel unique and elegant as desired. The compelling composition combines notes of jasmine, mixed with agikalawood and musk, bringing to you a sophisticated scent that gets you noticed wherever you go.', 20, 3677700.0, 3677700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614223921829-miu-miu-miu-miu-_w_-edp-100-ml-_-edp-20-ml-gift-set-2-piece.jpg'),
(44, 'Bvlgari Rose Goldea', 'A high feminine fragrance that gives you a delicate feeling and enhances your femininity with love and excitement. This fragrance mixes pomegranate with elegant musk and peach fruits. This scent leaves an excitement and romance touch.', 90, 2263200.0, 2263200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/v/bvlgari_rose_goldea_edp_90_ml.jpg'),
