(143, 'Carven Paris Alexandrie', 'This aromatic spicy fragrance is inspired by a forest near Alexandria, where little Egyptian violet leaves can be seen in a desert oasis. The aromatic composition has notes of violet leaf, nutmeg and patchouli, providing a fragrance with a scent that floats on the warmth of the Egyptian breeze.', 125, 5513100.0, 5513100.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Viola', 'Viola 100 ml is an Eau de Parfum For Men and Women from Tous Les Jours that will fill your heart with happiness and pleasure with top notes of Orange, Herbal Scents that will grab your attention immediately, then the heart notes of Jasmine, Tuberose, Gardenia that will take control representing the essence of the perfume to leave you in the end with the base notes of Iris Roots, Sandalwood, Vanilla that will linger with you far beyond that.', 100, 1373100.0, 1373100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006905742_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_viola_100_ml_tayamun_1.jpg'),
