(28, 'Burberry Body Tender', 'A youthful feminine fragrance that gives you a feeling of vitality and elegance thanks to its harmonious blend of flowers and fruits, such as fresh English roses, with white jasmine and sandalwood, added to them lemon, fresh apple, and green absinthe, in addition to ambergris and musk.', 85, 1207500.0, 1207500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/b/u/burberry_body_tender.jpg'),
