(73, 'Tous Les Jours Romeo', 'This perfume touches the heart of every lover, with its scent that reflect the memories of two beloved ones who lived together in perfect harmony. Its top notes feature grapefruit, sea breeze and tangerine. The heart has notes of Laurus nobilis and jasmine, while the base has notes of ambergris oil, patchouli, oakmoss and Guaiac wood.', 100, 1373100.0, 1373100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287006900129_tous_les_jours_tous_les_jours_-_romeo_100_ml_tayamun_1.jpg'),
