(137, 'Michael Kors Glam Ruby', 'Glam Ruby parfume for women is inspired by the beauty and attractiveness of Ruby stone. It is suitable for romantic evenings because of its bold sensuality. The smell of the freshly cut apricot provides the parfume with exotically feminine allure, while cashmere woods delivers a luxuriously warm finish.', 50, 2208000.0, 2208000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_michael_kors_perfumes_glam_ruby_for_women_eau_de_perfum_22548395585_1.jpg'),
