(152, 'Adrienne Vittadini AV', 'AV by Adrienne Vittadini is a floral fragrance for women, presented in a sensational bottle. The opening is aromatic-floral with lovely notes of bergamot, sweet cyclamen and bewitching lily-of-the-valley. The heart is a combination of floral freesia, soft may rose, warm jasmine and lovely ylang-ylang. The base has an excellent mixture of mellow orris, rich sandalwood, woody moss, sensual musk and delightful Tonka bean. The fragrance is sensual but fresh, crisp and pleasant. Feel the ocean air wearing this sexy scent. Ideal for summertime, AV is exquisite, charming and enchanting.', 90, 903900.0, 903900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_adrienne_vittadini_perfumes_av_for_women_eau_de_perfum_899219002376.jpg'),
