About the Brand:
Guerlain is a legendary French perfume house, one of the oldest perfume houses in the world, with more than 175 years in the world of perfumes. It offers you a group of the most luxurious perfumes that were officially used by the royal families in Europe.', 125, 3436200.0, 3436200.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470109537-guerlain-guerlain-aqua-allegoria-herba-fresca-_u_-edt-125-ml.png'),
