(177, 'Agent Provocateur Pure Aphrodisiaque', 'Agent Provocateur Pure Aphrodisiaque Perfume by Agent Provocateur is a fragrance that helps highlight the sensual side of a woman. This feminine scent opens with fruity notes of mandarin orange, pear, and heady rum. Slowly you will realize it blending with floral notes of gardenia, tuberose, orchid, and jasmine. However, the base notes of musk, amber, and a variety of woody notes stir a classy dash of elegance into it.', 80, 3063600.0, 3063600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_agent_provocateur_perfumes_pure_aphrodisiaque_for_women_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
