(40, 'Tom Ford Beau De Jour', 'It is a new masculine fragrance for men that was launched in 2019. It represents a perfectly groomed gentleman. It''s described as a classic, sharp, and maverick scent. It combines classic aromatic fougÃƒÂ¨re accords such as lavender, moss, and amber incorporated in rosemary, geranium, mint, oakmoss, basil, and patchouli', 50, 4560900.0, 4560900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066103909-tom-ford-tom-ford-beau-de-jour-_m_-edp-100-ml-1.png'),
(17, 'Calvin Klein Euphoria Men', 'Make the mystery and excitement your distinctive address with this fragrance full of black pepper and ginger scattered on the basil sticks of black, no doubt you will enjoy more privacy with the smell of fragrant amber and Brazilian red wood with a set of fragrances that make it distinctive and stable for long periods', 100, 1166100.0, 1166100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/calvin_klein_euphoria_eau_de_toilette_1.jpg'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Vanille Fatale', 'It is a balsamic vanilla fragrance. The stirring spice of saffron and coriander opens the scent, infiltrating the senses with the gripping incense of myrrh and olibanum. Reverberating with the tobacco-like pull of roasted barley, the heart of Vanille Fatale is a perfect storm of roasted coffee absolute, narcissus, and frangipani that seduces with grounded floralcy. Madagascan vanilla blends with rich mahogany. its smoky glamour made it all the more exotic with primal suede at the finish.', 100, 7617600.0, 7617600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066080941-tom-ford-tom-ford-vanille-fatale-_u_-edp-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(329, 'Atelier Flou Amarcord', 'This oriental composition is professionally designed for the strong man who takes his descision without being hesitant. The upper notes of incense, come on a heart of vetiver and a base of spicy notes, delivering a refreshing scent that accentuates your masculinity and keeps your presence noticed.', 100, 7859100.0, 7859100.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(258, 'Sainte Valere Enamore EDP', 'Timeless elegance and unique allure lie in its warm woody note.
Spice atoms envelop the fragrance from start to finish, immersing you in a spicy, sensual scent.
Fresh coconut notes appear in the middle of the scent to touch your heart with a sense of comfort and pleasure.
Discover the secret of your beauty with creamy woody notes that make the scent velvety delicate and breathtaking.', 100, 1028100.0, 1028100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287015120525-sainte-valere-sainte-valere-enamore-pour-homme-_m_-edp-100-ml.png'),
(32, 'Guerlain La Petite Robe Noire Intense EDP', 'She is a dreamy and elegant woman who wears a mysterious and sexy black dress and smells of this perfume.
A sensual blend of bergamot and cotton candy enhances your feminine beauty and boosts your sense of pleasure and elegance.
The heart of the fragrance of orange and jasmine flowers expresses the purity of your soul and the clarity of your mind.
The fragrance is calm, soft and pure with enchanting drops of musk and the warmth of patchouli, which stays with you for long hours.
About the Brand:
Guerlain is a legendary French perfume house, one of the oldest perfume houses in the world, with more than 175 years in the world of perfumes. It offers you a group of the most luxurious perfumes that were officially used by the royal families in Europe.', 100, 2380500.0, 2380500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470131996-guerlain-guerlain-la-petite-robe-noire-_w_-edp-intense-50-ml.png'),
(17, 'Calvin Klein Mini Set ', 'This five-piece set contains Eau de toilette of One (two pieces), All, Gold and Be (10 ml), all are suitable for both men and women. One is a citrus aromatic fragrance that spreads its freshness everywhere, thanks to its green notes, blended with papaya, freesia and rose. Be brave with Gold Eau de toilette, which makes you stand out from the crowd, with its notes of bergamot, jasmine and patchouli. Continue your freshness with All Eau de Toilette that makes your signature touched everywhere, with its notes of mandarin, jasmine and amber. Be yoursefl with Be Eau de Toilette that has fresh woody scent. Its notes of juniper, magnolia and vanilla will truly expresses you.', 10, 1524900.0, 1524900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/6/3614225704642_calvin_klein_calvin_klein_one_m_edt_2x10_ml_all_edt_10_ml_one_gold_edt_10_ml_be_edt_10_ml_mini_set_gs-dmm_cross_dock_1.jpg'),
(31, 'Dkhoun Alfaris ', 'This incense is made from the finest Arabian oud, mixed with saffron and amber and wrapped with a modern European touch. It adds a unique feeling to the place, which remains in the memory of your guests for long time.', 100, 1200600.0, 1200600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/9/390007-dkhoun-_-75gr-1.jpg'),
(216, 'Jo Malone 154 EDC', 'A wonderful luxurious woody fragrance.
This perfume is perfectly designed to suit both men and women.
The fragrance is enriched with an amazing aromatic blend of unique natural ingredients.
It opens with a refreshing composition of grapefruit, bergamot, and orange to make you feel vital and energetic for the whole day.
The heart of the fragrance is infused with distinctive touches of nutmeg, lavender, and basil.
The fragrance ends with charming notes of vetiver, patchouli, musk, and vanilla.
About the Brand:
Jo Malone joined the EstÃ©e Lauder Companies, which is available in 69 countries and territories, in 1999. Jo Malone London is a British brand known for its unique fragrances and luxurious products for bath, body, and home. It has written the rules of perfumery by blending unexpected components of ingredients and introducing elegant and playful concepts, the Jo Malone world continues to develop beautifully.', 100, 2518500.0, 2518500.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(32, 'Guerlain Idylle New Version', 'Guerlain Idylle, a perfume that captures profound moments of happiness, extremely happy and joyous situations, peaceful times and moments of bliss. Idylle opens with floral scents. Lily of the valley, peony, white lilac and freesia fill the air. The heart notes are a mix of jasmine and Bulgarian roses. Patchouli and white musk are the sensual final notes. The fragrance is soft and elegant, feminine and classy. It emits a nostalgic lingering trail and warms up the heart. It is the scent of first love, a field of sunflowers, and the sound of the oceans.', 50, 2028600.0, 2028600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470132757_guerlain_idylle_edp_50_ml_1.jpg'),
(108, 'Clinique Happy', 'An aromatic citrus fragrance with medium stability and aroma, which is very wonderful in the summer period and gives you a refreshing and lively dose, suitable for romantic and intimate moments, with a mixture of lemon, lily of the valley and musk.', 100, 2070000.0, 2070000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/l/clinique_happy_men.jpg'),
(3, 'Yves Saint Laurent Mon Paris', 'Yves Saint Laurent Mon Paris the floral fragrance for women and the new eau de toilette version for women. Very soft, feminine scent and a very girly way. Very elegant, classy and exquisite to wear in the day time or nighttime.', 30, 3167100.0, 3167100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_ysl_perfumes_mon_paris_for_women_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(362, 'Dali Haute Parfumerie Fabulous Bukhara EDP', 'An amazing shiny composition that leaves you under the spotlight.
