(309, 'Oud Lover Dokhon Tolah Aswad ', 'The charm of this mysterious dark scent is inspired by the dark scents coming from the extract of oud, blended with luxurious oriental perfume oils. The scent spreads quickly, remaining intense for a long time.', 30, 255300.0, 255300.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6234558686551-oud-lover-dokhon-tolah-black-30g-1.png'),
