(33, 'Lacoste L.12.12 Pour Elle Magnetic', 'This floral fruity fragrance for women is inspired by Lacoste pleated tennis skirt, representing feminine elegance and athletic innovation. Its blend of Violet Leaves Absolute, Jasmine, Vanilla and Patchouli will provide you a delicious scent that you cannot resist', 90, 890100.0, 890100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_lacoste_perfumes_l.12.12_pour_elle_magnetic_for_women_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(6, 'Versace Dylan Blue Pour Homme', 'Aromatic fragrance for men reflects the colors of the Mediterranean Sea and its civilizations and contains distinctive fresh scents that have a sensual nature that combines desire, passion, ambition and sophistication with a mixture of bergamot, patchouli, musk, and saffron.', 50, 1690500.0, 1690500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_versace_perfumes_dylan_blue_pour_homme_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(7, 'Xerjoff Java Blossom Extrait de Parfum', 'Scented notes of sandalwood with oriental oud blend in harmony to deliver an amazing scent.
The soft heart has notes of orange blossom wrapped with incense, adding to the softness of the scent.
The scent is intense and concentrated, filling the place while declaring your presence to stay a step ahead of everyone.
The fragrance is your perfect choice on all the different occasions for both men and women.', 10, 8611200.0, 8611200.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(136, 'Salvatore Ferragamo Uomo Casual Life', 'Salvatore Ferragamo Uomo Casual Life a fragrance specially crafted for men and has a woody aroma. It was introduced to the world in the year 2017. The top notes of the fragrance are violet leaves, cardamom, and lemon, heart notes are coffee, geranium,and ambroxan, base notes are musk, white cedar extract, and cashmere wood. The main accords of the fragrance are musky, warm spicy, amber, citrus, coffee and ozonic.', 50, 2649600.0, 2649600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_salvatore_ferragamo_uomo_casual_life_eau_de_toilette_for_men_100_ml_1.png'),
(60, 'S.T. Dupont Noir S.T. Dupont', 'Noir by S.T. Dupont is a woody oriental fragrance for masculine and seductive men presented in a modish bottle. The fragrance opens with sharp and spicy green notes starting with a splash mint combined seductive lavender and cardamom. The heart continues strong with spicy notes of nutmeg and cloves. The dry-down is a sweet and spicy blend of cashmere wood and vetiver with a hint of hazelnut. The trail is long-lasting. Noir is developed for an easy-going, carefree, optimistic man. Enjoy the nightlife wearing this pleasant, unique and sexy scent.', 100, 779700.0, 779700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_s_t_dupont_perfumes_noir_s_t_dupont_for_men_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(8, 'Chopard 1000 Miglia', 'This fragrance starts in a fresh and vibrant scent with floral aromas of lavender that combines with warm and strong leather notes. This scent provides freshness and masculinity that confirmes your powerful and attractive looking.', 100, 1449000.0, 1449000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_chopard_perfumes_1000_miglia_eau_de_toilette.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 65', 'An oriental spicy fragrance that suit the modern men and women. Featuring notes of grapefruit in the top, jasmine in the middle, and leather in the base, the composition offers you a scent that adds to your elegance and complements your chic look.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000065-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours---perfume-day-65-1.png'),
(32, 'Guerlain La Petite Robe Noire Florale Black Perfecto', 'This fragrance created by Guerlain. The floral Eau de Toilette celebrates the rose in all its forms. Grass rose water, rose essential oil, and rose absolute are encircled with almond and leather notes. The iconic inverted heart bottle takes on an intensely dark, black look. The white label embroidered roses lend the finishing touch to this couture and fashion style. It is terribly chic and bang on-trend.', 100, 1449000.0, 1449000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470135284-guerlain-guerlain-black-perfecto-by-la-petite-robe-noire-_w_-edt-florale-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Oud Wood', 'Tom Ford Oud Wood parfume is a unisex fragrance that contains ingredients such as Oud wood which is considered one of the most rare, precious and costly ingredient in the parfume industry. It also contains rose wood and cardamom that leaves a smoky blend of rare oud wood, sandalwood and vetiver. Furthermore the Tonka beans and amber add warmth and excitement to this wonderful parfume.', 50, 7617600.0, 7617600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_tom_ford_perfumes_oud_wood_for_unisex_eau_de_perfum.jpg'),
(32, 'Guerlain L''instant Magic', 'A woody floral fragrance for women that takes you to the dream world, where the real world turns into a visual dream thanks to its amazing aroma, with the magnificent blend of bergamot, mimosa, and white musk.', 100, 5664900.0, 5664900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470133150_guerlain_l_instant_magic_edp_100_ml_1.jpg'),
(24, 'Candy Addict Purple Rain EDP ', 'Falling from afar from a magical world full of flowers and purple roses, dreamy and delicate, touching your soul and returning again with its abundant aroma and musky notes that will last for a long time.', 50, 959100.0, 959100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/u/purple_rain_bottle.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 391', 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 391 has satisfied the most prestigious perfume tastes. This perfume reveals a charming and joyous impression by a citrus opening of a tangerine scent. The heart reveals a floral blend of orange blossom and rose aroma, tamed by a warm scent of cedarwood, amber, vanilla, frankincense, oud. The intoxicating yet divisive oud aroma has been determined to make the scent linger longer.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000391-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-391-1_1.png'),
(83, 'Montale Pink Extasy', 'Pink Extasy by Montale is a feminine, floral, fruity fragrance created by Pierre Montale. It was launched in the year 2014. The top notes of the perfume are orange, tangerine, and black pepper; heart notes are jasmine, iris, Turkish rose, and orange blossom; base notes are white musk, peach, raspberry, and vanilla.', 100, 2553000.0, 2553000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_montale_perfumes_pink_extasy_for_women_eau_de_perfum_m0060184b.jpg'),
(361, 'Unique Luxury Black Gold EDP', 'This Perfume represent the mysterious black gold, which evoke the feelings.
Saffron and cumin notes are wrapped with roses to show your different presence.
Express the beauty of your soul and charm of your character with the immortal oriental scent, which remain until the end of your day.
The classic base has notes of coffee and tobacco along with raisins add a classic touch to your look.', 50, 4133100.0, 4133100.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(241, 'Gritti Noctem Arabs', 'An oriental woody fragrance professionally designed to suit you on the busy days and special nights. The composition has upper notes of tobacco, followed by oud in the middle and musk in the base, offering you an enticing scent that fills your spirits with vitality and positive vibes.', 100, 5161200.0, 5161200.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(133, 'Kenzo Pour Homme', 'Enjoy this amazing scent that will awaken your senses and leave you more energized, thanks to its blend of bergamot, jasmine and cedarwood. Its aquatic and refreshing notes will boost your confidence leading to more influence on everyone around.', 50, 1731900.0, 1731900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/h/o/homme_edt.jpg'),
(265, 'Saint Hilaire Private Red EDP', 'A luxurious aromatic blend for men with refined taste.
