This enchanting fragrance reflects your inner soul and expresses your strength.
The freshness of the fragrance stays on your skin for long hours to suit all your different looks on occasions.', 100, 917700.0, 917700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/7/3760004322443-saint-hilaire-saint-hilaire-private-red-pour-homme-_m_-edp-100-ml.png'),
(31, 'Dkhoun Bakhoor Set', 'This set contains:
Dkhoun Oud Ariani - 28 gm
This scented incense will fill the air with the aromas of oud wood, known for spreading quickly while lasting for a long time. It will fascinate your guests, as it keeps your house with a good smell. It''s perfect for occasions.
Dkhoun Malisian Oud M - 28 gm
This incense is made from the finest Malaysian woods, which spreads across the place to be smelled everywhere. It spreads warmth along the nice fragrance, making you and your guests feel the calmness and relaxation all the time.
Dkhoun Fakher - 80 gm
This incense reflects the mix of the luxurious oud and notes of patchouli and Portuguese flower, delivering a strong scent that spreads everywhere to boost the elegance of your house.', 100, 4250400.0, 4250400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/s/b/sb100331-dkhoon-bakhoor-set.png'),
(76, 'Thierry Mugler Angel Eau CroisiÃ¨re', 'A sunny blend of fragrances. It was inspired by embodying refined yet carefree evasion that gives a fresh take on cruise spirit. The perfume was designed with a perfect blend that''s rich in mango, grapefruit, black currant sorbet, patchouli, and pralines to give elegant women the proper effect with an attractive, refreshing scent.', 50, 2442600.0, 2442600.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/4/3439600040715-thierry-mugler-thierry-mugler-angel-eau-croisiere-_w_-edt-50-ml.jpg'),
(216, 'Jo Malone Orange Blossom EDC', 'In Los Angeles, the romantic city, with its dreamy aura, enjoy special moments that remain eternal in your memory.
The fragrance opens with the scent of fresh vital mandarin and then uncovers the spectacular water lily.
The fragrance heart exudes a breeze of orange and purple blossoms to touch your soul with a soft scent that evokes emotions and feelings.
The fragrance blend increases your splendor look, making you unique among everyone, and focuses attention on you.', 100, 2518500.0, 2518500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/9/690251006496-jo-malone-jo-malone-orange-blossom-_u_-cologne-100-ml.png'),
(11, 'Mont Blanc Legend Night', 'This perfume is a classic fragrance for men. The blend of natural elements including peppermint, cardamom, and bergamot giving natural radiant aroma. High notes consist of clary sage, peppermint, cardamom, and bergamot; mid notes consist of cedar, lavender, apple, and violet; bottom notes consist of black vanilla, vetiver, musk, and patchouli. The perfume bottle is black with a mix of amber color.', 100, 2766900.0, 2766900.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_mont_blanc_perfumes_legend_night_for_men_eau_de_perfum_3386460087940.jpg'),
(43, 'Dize Karmen Home Fragrance ', 'A home freshener spray that replaces unpleasant scents with a beautiful and refreshing scent that lasts for a long time. It is enriched with an astonishing blend of unique ingredients with very special scents. It is a perfect freshener for a clean and healthy environment and a refreshing smell.', 100, 338100.0, 338100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6281074749598-dize-home-_-_-_-_.png'),
(201, 'Afnan Naseej Al Ward EDP', 'From the sensual velvety world of flowers comes this fragrance with notes of yellow and ripe flowers.
The astonishing blend of the fragrance combines the delicacy of flowers with the oriental aromas of the East, immersing you in a sense of elegance and luxury.
The fragrance base is made with woody touches that add to the scent a delicate velvety character that boosts its beauty.
It is always the best choice for men and women with good and refined taste.', 50, 1035000.0, 1035000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6290171050025-afnan-afnan-naseej-al-ward-_u_-edp-50-ml.png'),
(32, 'Guerlain La Petite Robe Noire Limited Edition', 'At the beginning of this year, La Petite Robe Noire by Guerlain puts on a show with a limited edition 50ml Eau de Parfum illustrated by the artistic duo Kuntzel&Deygas: Ã¢â‚¬Å“This time, weÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ve designed a whole fashion show for La Petite Robe Noire. Fifteen imaginary dresses for the most stylish of Parisians.Ã¢â‚¬Â Inside the pack, find your Eau de Parfum with a fruity floral sillage dressed in one of the 15 designs from the collection.', 100, 2035500.0, 2035500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/3/3346470133181-guerlain-guerlain-la-petite-robe-noire-limited-edition-_w_-edt-50-ml-1.jpg'),
(208, 'Lootah Luminous EDP', 'You are on a date with beauty and freshness that will transport you to your own world with Luminous perfume from the Lootah perfume collection.
This fragrance is designed with refreshing citruses and an attractive scent of jasmine.
It ends with musk and amber, making it your perfect choice every day and every moment.', 100, 2415000.0, 2415000.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6297000836317-lootah-lootah-luminous-eau-de-parfum-100-ml.png'),
(104, 'Mugler Alien Hair Mist ', 'An amazing warm oriental floral Hair Mist. A very feminine scent which lefts your hair with a soft and silky veil and leaves an intense scented silage. Spray it on the tips of your hair.', 100, 1352400.0, 1352400.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/t/h/thierry_mugler_alien_hair_mist.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 370', 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 370 has gone so far and includes the rarest and most expensive woods in the world in its notes. The intoxicating yet divisive oud aroma has been determined to make the scent linger longer. Not only this, but its breath-taking blend with Incense has also recalled the sweet oriental memories. Amber and Musk revolve off the end in a rich, earthy, and warm mixture to leave a final memory of the sweet seduction.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000370-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-370-1.png'),
(7, 'Xerjoff Shooting Stars Dhajala EDP', 'An aromatic mixture that opens the gateway of beauty and attractiveness to place you in a high position among all those present and increase your soul freshness every day.
Tea leaves wrapped in powdery seeds appear to announce your different presence and cherry blossoms accompany you throughout your whole tour.
The scent is strong and fragrant, and spreads quickly in the air and expresses your absolute attractiveness on all occasions so that everyone falls in love with you.
Sandalwood and vanilla with iris root make the scent softer and increase your sense of romance and calm all the time.', 50, 7500300.0, 7500300.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(290, 'LPDO Perfume Fleur Noire EDP', 'The attractive and emotional scent of the perfume is inspired by the delicate femininity.
Enjoy your radiant beauty with delicious citrus notes and a gentle gardenia breeze.
The fragrance ends with soft creamy notes to increase your sense of confidence that lasts for a long time.
The contrast of hot spices with the cool freshness of ylang-ylang enhances your glowing hot passion.', 100, 1373100.0, 1373100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/8053629625415-lpdo-perfume-fleur-noire_1_.png'),
(21, 'Ajwa Home Cotton ', 'Ajwa Home Scent Spray Cotton is a home fragrance which replaces the bad odour and makes the atmosphere gaiety. This home fragrance is long-lasting, refreshing and aromatic. It is suitable for daily cleaning routine.', 100, 241500.0, 241500.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/6/2/6287001780955_ajwa_home_home_scent_from_ajwa_home_cotton_-1.jpg'),
(73, 'Tous Les Jours Perfume Day 348', 'Make your elegant look unique with this floral fragrancce. The composition has notes of mirabelle in the top, followed by Arabian jasmine in the heart and vetiver in the base, which provides you with a refreshing scent that fills you with energy and vitality as long as you wear it, thanks to the long-lasting effect.', 55, 821100.0, 821100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/2/0/2000348-tous-les-jours-tous-les-jours-perfume-day-348-1.png'),
(133, 'Kenzo Flower Tag Eau de Parfum Gift Set ', 'This gift set features EDT (50 ml) and two bottles of nail polish (5 ml). Inspired by the free-spirited art of graffiti, which embodies the creativity of young people around the world, this floral fruity fragrance will leave your own tag recognized by everyone. The intense composition features notes of sweet rhubarb in the top, followed by peony in the middle and tea in the warm base, releasing a distinctive scent for the courageous and energetic young man.', 100, 2546100.0, 2546100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/small_image/750x750/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/3/2/3274871929129-kenzo-kenzo-flower-tag-_w_-set-edt-50-ml-_-nail-polish-2x5-ml_2.jpg'),
(40, 'Tom Ford Lost Cherry', 'It is a new fragrance launched in 2018. It belongs to the fruity fragrance family. It opens the notes with sour cherry, liqueur, and bitter almonds incorporated with Turkish rose, jasmine sambac, and plum.', 100, 10274100.0, 10274100.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/8/888066098878-tom-ford-tom-ford-lost-cherry-_u_-edp-100-ml-1.jpg'),
(355, 'Les Eaux Primordiales Tubereuse Supercritique EDP', 'A wonderful fragrance characterized by its strong and refreshing scent.
The fragrance is designed to suit both men and women.
Enjoy an unparalleled aroma that keeps you feeling fresh all the time.
The fragrance opens with aldehydes, bitter orange and bergamot.
And in the heart are touches of almond milk, jasmine and tuberose.
The fragrance ends with luxurious notes of sandalwood, patchouli, white musk and amber.', 100, 6630900.0, 6630900.0, 0, 0, 'none'),
(174, 'Marc Jacobs Decadence Rouge Noir Edition', 'Marc Jacobs decadence Rouge Noir Edition the newest member of Marc Jacobs family. A woody scent for women with a luxurious powered by rich fruits and floral accords. Housed in a limited edition, handbag-shaped flacon. you must have this perfume!', 100, 3263700.0, 3263700.0, 0, 0, 'https://assets.goldenscent.com/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/g/o/golden_scent_perfume_marc_jacobs_decadence_rouge_noir_edition_eau_de_parfum_spray_for_women_1.png');


